src: with banister right forward towards base of stairs ahead of left leading upwards stairs at top
tgt: With the banister to your right, head forward towards the base of the stairs ahead of you and to the left leading upwards. Climb the stairs and stop at the top.

src: walk past wall mirrors on left up stairs wait at open glass door
tgt: Walk past the wall mirrors on the left. Walk up stairs. Wait at the open glass door.

src: straight turn stairs then
tgt: Go straight and turn left to go up the stairs then stop.

src: bedroom turn turn set of stairs down hallway stand between picture of man band performing
tgt: Leave the bedroom turn left and go down the turn left and go up the set of stairs.  Walk down the hallway and stand between the picture of the man and the band performing.

src: exit bedroom down stairs right at landing down stairs left at landing up stairs wait at photo of person bird
tgt: Exit the bedroom, and walk down the stairs. Make a right at the landing, and walk down the stairs. Make a left at the landing, and walk up the stairs. Wait at the photo of the person holding a bird.

src: bedroom turn down stairs turn right up stairs down hallway wait by door on left
tgt: Leave the bedroom, turn left, walk down the stairs, turn right, walk up the stairs, walk down the hallway, and wait by the door on the left.

src: stairs top level then bedroom on left walk in closet
tgt: Go up the stairs to the top level. Then go to the bedroom on the left, and enter the walk in closet.

src: way up steps hard right turn then steps then through door on left heading towards skateboards stopping
tgt: Make your way up the steps, take a hard right turn and then continue up the steps then through the door on the left heading towards the skateboards and stopping.

src: stairs next floor turn into first doorway bedroom toward bed right closet wait there
tgt: Go up the stairs to the next floor. Turn left into the first doorway. Enter the bedroom and go toward the bed. Turn right and enter the closet. Wait there.

src: exit room turn beside potted plants near balcony doors
tgt: Exit the room and turn left. Wait beside the potted plants near the balcony doors.

src: walk out of room in hallway hard left down corridor with many cabinets next room wait by vase with white flower inside
tgt: Walk out of the room.  In the hallway, turn a hard left, and down the corridor with many cabinets to the next room.  Wait by the vase with white flower inside.

src: exit room straight then stairs stop
tgt: Exit the room and continue straight. Then turn left and go down the stairs and stop.

src: turn hallway then straight until other hallway right into bedroom wait by bed
tgt: Turn left and go out the hallway then go straight until you get to the other hallway and turn right into the bedroom. Wait by the bed.

src: turn around out of room left after stairs right wait in bedroom on right
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the room. Take a left after the stairs and turn right. Wait in the bedroom that is on the right.

src: office head out into hallway in hall straight heading in direction of bathroom in hall right in front of nightstand
tgt: Leave the office and head out into the hallway. In the hall go straight heading in the direction of the bathroom. In the hall take a right. stop in front of the nightstand.

src: enter house left hallway bedroom through door at end in room left into kitchenette in front of mini-fridge
tgt: Enter the house and take a left. Go down the hallway and enter the bedroom through the door at the end. In the room take a left into the kitchenette. Stop in front of the mini-fridge.

src: turn house left down hallway guest bedroom wait by door
tgt: Turn around and enter the house.  Turn to your left and walk down the hallway. Enter the guest bedroom and wait by the door.

src: inside house quick left into hallway way down hallway until through open door directly at end of hallway upon room wait near kitchen area left
tgt: Go inside the house and make a quick left into the hallway. Walk all the way down the hallway until you pass through the open door directly at the end of the hallway. Upon entering the room, wait near the kitchen area to your left.

src: exit room through double doors corridor then into bedroom at far left near bed
tgt: Exit the room through the double doors, cross the corridor, then continue into the bedroom at the far left. Stop and wait near the bed.

src: walk through living room walk past glass towards chairs along wall right side walk through doorway after brown chairs walk through next archway at buffet right into bedroom directly opposite of buffet wait by door
tgt: Walk through the living room. Walk past the glass tables towards the chairs along the wall to the right side. Walk through the doorway after the brown chairs. Walk straight through the next archway. AT the buffet, turn right and walk into the bedroom directly opposite of the buffet. Wait by the door.

src: straight until room double doors ahead straight hallway ahead turn chair into second room on right wait near bed
tgt: Go straight until you exit the room using the double doors ahead. Go straight and enter the hallway ahead. Turn left when you get to the chair and go into the second room on the right. Wait near the bed.

src: walk through room right before white couch up flights of stairs stop at top of stairs
tgt: Walk through room and turn right before white couch, walk up the two flights of stairs, stop at the top of the stairs.

src: walk past credenza right stairs full flight of stairs next bench in kitchen
tgt: Walk past the credenza and take a right up the stairs. Go up the full flight of stairs and stop next to the bench in the kitchen.

src: walk past bar turn right stairs landing right stairs wait top
tgt: Walk past the bar.  Turn to the right and go up the stairs to the landing.  Turn right and continue up the stairs.  Wait when you get the top.

src: down stairs right at bottom of stairs exit through door on right wait by statue of man by window
tgt: Walk down the stairs.  Turn right at the bottom of stairs and exit through the door on the right.  Wait by the statue of a man by the window.

src: stairs left then right so in front of stairs downstairs now down second step wait
tgt: You need to go down the stairs and make a left then make a right so you are in front of the stairs going downstairs. Now go down to the second step and wait.

src: down stairs at bottom of stairs right then though first doorway on right library statue bust on left just past doorway next bust
tgt: Walk down the stairs.  At the bottom of the stairs, make a right.  Then, walk though the first doorway on your right to leave the library.  There will be a statue bust on your left just past the doorway.  Stop next to that bust.

src: exit closet bedroom bedroom double doors on left forward second door on right laundry room wait there
tgt: Exit the closet to the bedroom. Exit the bedroom to the double doors on the left. Go forward and enter the second door on the right leading to the laundry room. Wait there.

src: exit closet then left room right in second door wait there
tgt: Exit the closet then turn left. Turn left and exit the room. Turn right in the second door. Wait there.

src: bedroom right into laundry room wait
tgt: Leave bedroom to hallway, turn right into laundry room and wait.

src: go through glass door stairs left at bottom of stairs by plant
tgt: Go left through the glass door, and go down the stairs to the left. Stop at the bottom of the stairs by the plant.

src: turn stairs wait in front of plant
tgt: Turn left and go down the stairs. Wait in front of that plant.

src: exit laundry room stairs on left beside potted plant
tgt: Exit the laundry room. Go down the stairs on the left. Wait beside the potted plant.

src: stairs slightly right stopping at window statue outside
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn slightly to the right stopping at the window that has a statue outside.

src: walk downstairs wait right of area by door
tgt: Walk downstairs and wait to the right of the sitting area by the door.

src: walk way down stairs slight right toward window there
tgt: Walk all the way down the stairs. Take a slight right toward the window. Stop there.

src: straight into room straight into middle door wait near entrance
tgt: Go straight into the room. Go straight into the middle door and wait near the entrance.

src: forward into massage room slightly into marble room ahead wait just inside doorway
tgt: Walk forward into the massage room. Turn slightly left and walk into the marble room ahead. Wait just inside the doorway.

src: straight into massage room walk through massage room into bathing room once room
tgt: Go straight into the massage room. Walk through the massage room, and into the bathing room. Stop once you enter the room.

src: into glass door on right into bedroom bathroom doorway in back left
tgt: Go into the glass door on the right and into the bedroom. Go to the bathroom doorway in the back left.

src: turn right doorway between white chairs pass in front of bed right then room on left next nightstand with lamp on there
tgt: Turn right and enter the doorway between the two white chairs. Pass in front of the bed and turn right, then enter the room on the left next to the nightstand with a lamp on it. Wait there.

src: walk through glass door between white chairs bedroom turn past foot of bed right after bed past first doorway towards second doorway on left towards bathroom stop
tgt: walk through sliding glass door between two white chairs to enter bedroom, turn left to walk past foot of bed, turn right after bed, past first doorway, walk towards second doorway on left towards bathroom and stop.

src: pass white couches right at beginning of steps
tgt: Pass the white couches and wait right at the beginning of the three steps.

src: walk toward stairs right before
tgt: Walk toward the stairs and stop right before them.

src: turn right at table walk between couches turn at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn right at table and walk between couches, and turn left, wait at bottom of stairs.

src: stairs straight left into kitchen at end of living room in kitchen doorway
tgt: Go up the stairs and go straight. Take a left into the kitchen at the end of the living room. Stop in the kitchen doorway.

src: stairs right up last steps onto hardwood floor straight in doorway on left
tgt: proceed up the stairs, curve right walk up last steps onto hardwood floor, continue straight and stop in the doorway on left.

src: stairs walk past back of sectional sofa on right wait at threshold of dining room
tgt: Walk up stairs. Walk past the back of the sectional sofa on the right. Wait at the threshold of the dining room.

src: turn doors directly ahead walk dining table wait there
tgt: Turn left and enter the doors directly ahead. Walk to the dining table. Wait there.

src: walk past pool on left grass on right house wait at table
tgt: Walk past the pool on the left and the grass on the right. Enter the house, and wait at the dining table.

src: head straight pool then into house large glass door wait by large black glass table with grey chairs
tgt: Head straight and pass the pool then go into the house using the large glass sliding door. Wait by the large black glass table with the grey chairs.

src: straight down stairs once through door at bottom
tgt: Go straight and down the stairs, stopping once passing through the door at the bottom.

src: down spiral staircase through doorway at bottom stop at top of stairs
tgt: Walk down the spiral staircase, and walk through the doorway at the bottom and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: down spiral stairs wait at landing by doorway
tgt: Walk down the spiral stairs and wait at the landing by the doorway.

src: turn towards bathroom door exit through doorway
tgt: Turn towards bathroom door. Exit. Go through doorway.

src: walk forward left towards wood out of door into hallway in hallway walk into main reception hall in main room stop between first table doorway behind
tgt: Walk forward and go to your left towards the wood door.Go out of the door and into the hallway. In the hallway walk straight into the main reception hall. In the main room stop between the first table and the doorway behind you.

src: walk sink through entrance of women bathroom down hall dining room area near open double doors on left
tgt: Walk passed the sink through the entrance of the women's bathroom. Walk down the hall and towards the dining room area. Stop near the open double doors on the left.

src: exit bathroom into hall turn into room next with vase
tgt: Exit bathroom into hall, turn left, walk into dinging room and stop next to table with vase.

src: through bathroom left after bathroom past dining room table by round table with vase on top of round rug
tgt: Go through the bathroom. Take a left after exiting the bathroom and go past the dining room table. Stop by the round table with a vase on top of the round rug.

src: walk through door on left right into hallway turn right at island walk past dining room table chairs by table with plants on
tgt: Walk through the door on the left and turn right. Walk into the hallway and turn left. Turn right at the island and walk past the dining room table and chairs. Stop by the table with the plants on it.

src: exit bathroom turn room door on left right toward table chairs wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn left and exit the room using the door on the left. Turn right and walk toward the table and chairs. Wait there.

src: turn right bathroom turn bedroom via door left right towards chairs table wait just before chairs
tgt: Turn right and exit the bathroom. Turn left and exit the bedroom via the door closest to your left. Turn right and walk towards the chairs and table. Wait just before the chairs.

src: bathroom bedroom right into dining area once in front of liquor cabinet
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and the bedroom. Take a right into the dining and kitchen area. Stop once you are in front of the liquor cabinet.

src: walk sink faucet granite counter straight door towards office glass table there
tgt: Walk straight passing the sink faucet granite counter. Keep walking straight to enter the door leading towards the office glass table and stop there.

src: walk through kitchen past pantry cabinets walk into dining room outside of bathroom
tgt: Walk through the kitchen, and past the pantry cabinets. Walk into the dining room and stop outside of the bathroom.

src: turn left down kitchen past center countertop down hallway in front of open door
tgt: Turn to the left and walk down the kitchen past the center countertop. Walk down the hallway and stop in front of the open door.

src: fitness area right stairs walk patio door at end in patio doorway
tgt: Leave the fitness area and take a right. Go up the stairs and walk to the patio door at the end. Stop in the patio doorway.

src: walk out of gym room right steps into office stand in doorway balcony
tgt: Walk out of the gym room and turn right. Go up the two steps into the office. Stand in the doorway to the balcony.

src: exit exercise room right past bookshelf step out on patio wait near patio set
tgt: Exit the exercise room and turn right.  Walk past the bookshelf and step out on the patio.  Wait near the patio set.

src: turn bathroom into area once in area turn dining room once in dining room turn alongside table at end straight into doorway kitchen stop
tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom into the sitting area. Once in the sitting area, turn left and enter the dining room. Once in the dining room turn left and walk alongside the table. At the end, walk straight into the doorway to the kitchen and stop.

src: walk out of bathroom towards red chairs in between red chairs turn through doorway turn before room table walk straight through doorway before kitchen island
tgt: walk out of bathroom towards red chairs, walk in between two red chairs and turn left to walk through doorway, turn left before you reach dining room table and walk straight through doorway, stop before you reach kitchen island.

src: exit room walk towards armchairs.turn room through archway towards dining room exit that room into kitchen in front of granite counter top
tgt: Exit the room and walk towards the armchairs.Turn left, and leave the room through the archway towards the dining room. Exit that room and go into the kitchen. Stop in front of the granite counter top.

src: pass table chairs steps stairs on right into room on right wait there
tgt: Pass the table and chairs. Go up the steps. Pass the stairs on the right. Go into the room on the right and wait there.

src: through dining room up steps wait in alcove next front door
tgt: Go through the dining room and up the steps. Wait in the alcove, next to the front door.

src: through room towards steps staircase on right into doorway on right
tgt: Go through the room towards the steps and passed the staircase on the right, step into the doorway on the right and stop.

src: kitchen through door on right of stove dining room across next table on right
tgt: Leave the kitchen through the door on the right of the stove. Enter the dining room across and stop next to the table on the right.

src: turn kitchen living area dining room wait next table with lamp on
tgt: Turn around and exit the kitchen and living area. Enter the dining room and wait next to the table with the lamp on it.

src: between couch counter into big archway then into archway step in then
tgt: Go between the couch and the counter, into the big archway, and then straight into the smaller archway, take a step in and then stop.

src: stairway right at couch
tgt: Go down the stairway and take a right, stopping at the couch.

src: downstairs right set of stairs into living room wait just at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go downstairs and to your right. Go down another set of stairs into the living room and wait just at the bottom of those stairs.

src: down stairs then right second set of stairs into living area just before white couch
tgt: Down the stairs then move right down the second set of stairs into the living area, stopping just before the white couch.

src: indoors right on second door turn straight until white chair then
tgt: Go indoors. Turn right on the second door. Turn left and walk straight until you get to a white chair then stop.

src: walk through doorway second right into kitchen turn through kitchen into next room television on left
tgt: Walk straight through the doorway and take the second right into the kitchen. Turn left and proceed through the kitchen into the next room. Stop when the television is on your left.

src: enter home enter second doorway on right kitchen turn through kitchen by tv wait here
tgt: Enter home.  Enter second doorway on the right to enter the kitchen.  Turn left and walk through kitchen.  Stop by TV.  Wait here.

src: exit bathroom past tub tv stop in doorway on left
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Go past the tub and tv and stop in the doorway on the left.

src: walk through doorway left at door after dresser at door
tgt: Walk through doorway, take a left at the door after the dresser, stop at door.

src: bathroom walk past bed in wooden doorway into main room
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk past the bed.  Stop in the wooden doorway looking into the main room.

src: bathroom bedroom in front of door bedroom
tgt: Leave the bathroom and enter the bedroom. Stop in front of the door to exit the bedroom.

src: walk past vanity over polar bear rug right turn into bedroom wait next thermostat
tgt: Walk past the vanity over the polar bear rug. Make a right turn into the bedroom. Wait next to the thermostat.

src: turn right just inside bedroom
tgt: Turn right and stop just inside the bedroom.

src: doorway of bathroom at end of hall wait there
tgt: Go to the doorway of the bathroom at the end of the hall and wait there.

src: stand in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Go stand in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: straight until end if hallway into room on left wait there
tgt: Go straight until you get to the end if the hallway and go into the room on the left. Wait there.

src: walk past refrigerator on rug by beanbag chair
tgt: Walk past the refrigerator and stop on the rug by the beanbag chair.

src: walk forward past kitchen then right wait near window
tgt: Walk forward past the kitchen, then turn right and wait near the window.

src: walk through kitchen right after refrigerator on rug under mirror
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and take a right after the refrigerator. Stop on the rug under the mirror.

src: bathroom right in bedroom into office in office stop in front of desk closest trash bin
tgt: Leave the bathroom and take a right in the bedroom into the office. In the office stop in front of the desk closest to the trash bin.

src: turn left past double sink veer left into room office by first corner of desk wait
tgt: Turn to the left and go past the double sink.  Veer to the left.  Go into that room, it's an office.  Stop by the first corner of the desk you come to.  Wait.

src: exit restroom by towards opened door once door opened door left left into left door then right into room full of bookcases table with chairs
tgt: Exit the restroom by walking towards the opened door. Once walking closer to the opened door, there will be another opened door to the left. Make a left into the left door, then make a right into a room full of bookcases and a table with two leather chairs.

src: walk towards living room then through hallway into room straight ahead wait at entrance room
tgt: Walk towards the living room. Then walk through the hallway and into the room that is straight ahead. Wait at the entrance to the room.

src: walk out of kitchen into living room left walk into hallway past living room in hallway into bedroom ahead in teh bedroom stop once inside doorway
tgt: Walk out of the kitchen heading into the living room. Hang a left and walk into the hallway past the living room. In the hallway go into the bedroom straight ahead. In teh bedroom stop once you are inside the doorway.

src: straight across room slight through opening walk bedroom door stop
tgt: Go straight across the room, and turn slight left through the opening. Walk straight to the bedroom door and stop.

src: walk dining table turn on very first corner library room stop at very first white chair on left
tgt: Walk straight passing the dining table. Turn left on the very first corner entering a library room. Stop at the very first white chair on the left.

src: away from red wall straight over rug through doorway right of small table sculpture stand in front of white chair on left
tgt: Walk away from the red wall, straight over the rug and through the doorway to the right of the small table holding a sculpture. Stand in front of the white chair on your left.

src: past table then into second door from left in white chair right by light blue couch
tgt: Go past the table and then into the second door from the left. Sit down and wait in the white chair that is right by the light blue couch.

src: walk past lounge chairs in front of patio chairs
tgt: Walk past the lounge chairs and stop in front of the patio chairs.

src: walk just left across front of sunning beds wait by doorway next living room/kitchen area
tgt: Walk just to the left and go across the front of the sunning beds and wait by the doorway next to the living room/kitchen area.

src: turn right walk by base of chairs on towards house about feet away from house wait
tgt: Turn to the right and walk by the base of the chairs.  Continue on towards the house.  When you are about 5 feet away from the house, please stop.  Wait.

src: exit bathroom turn through doorway then right past series of framed pictures on wall left right again at entrance room
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left, to walk through the doorway. Then turn right to walk past a series of four framed pictures on the wall to your left. Turn right again and stop at the entrance to the room.

src: walk out of closet right by bed
tgt: Walk out of the closet and turn right. Stop by the bed.

src: out of closet right then right again into bedroom wait near bed
tgt: Go straight out of the closet. Turn right and then turn right again to go into the bedroom. Wait near the bed.

src: walk past stairs down hallway with framed art on left after through door at end into bedroom just after room
tgt: Walk past the stairs and down the hallway with the framed art on the left.  After going through the door at the end into the bedroom and stop just after entering this room.

src: straight hallway stairs on right straight until into room wait near bed
tgt: Go straight down the hallway. Pass the stairs on the right. Continue straight until you go into a room. Wait near the bed.

src: travel hallway past stairs door at end of hallway stand near bed
tgt: Travel straight down the hallway past some stairs, enter the door at the end of the hallway and stand near the bed.

src: turn next white robes
tgt: Turn around and wait next to the white robes.

src: closet bathroom in front of shower
tgt: Leave the closet, and enter the bathroom. Stop in front of the shower.

src: exit closet walk into bathroom past sinks on left in front of shower
tgt: Exit the closet and walk into the bathroom. Go past the sinks on your left and stop in front of the shower.

src: walk towards refrigerator then right past dining table bedroom at end walk through bedroom past bed tub in doorway bathroom
tgt: Walk towards the refrigerator and then turn right.  Walk past the dining table and enter the bedroom at the end.  Walk through the bedroom past the bed and tub and stop in the doorway to the bathroom.

src: walk left of long table toward living area into bedroom on left in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Walk to the left of the long table, toward the living area. Turn into the bedroom on the left. Stop in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: pass dining room table then through door on left bed tub door ahead wait near toilet
tgt: Pass the dining room table then go through the door on the left. Pass the bed and the tub and go to the door straight ahead. Wait near the toilet.

src: exit room turn past pool into hallway wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left. Go past the pool and straight into the hallway. Wait there.

src: turn right plants diamond window in entryway
tgt: Turn around and go to your right. Pass the plants and the diamond window and stop in the entryway.

src: exit spa room turn past treadmill walk past pool wait in hallway by large potted plant
tgt: Exit the spa room and turn left to walk past the treadmill. Walk past the pool and wait in the hallway by the large potted plant.

src: walk outside along sidewalk right onto stone pathway next pool on first stone
tgt: Walk outside along the sidewalk. Turn right onto the stone pathway next to the pool. Stop on the first stone.

src: exit building walk past pool wait on steppingstones near hot tub
tgt: Exit the building, walk past the pool and wait on the steppingstones near the hot tub.

src: step outside along sidewalk pool on right onto stones on right
tgt: Step outside and go along the sidewalk, go passed the pool on the right and stop onto the stones on the right and stop.

src: bedroom walk straight hall once brown leather chairs on left left bedroom in doorway before bedroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and walk straight down the hall. Once you pass the brown leather chairs on your left, take the left to the bedroom. Stop in the doorway before you enter the bedroom.

src: exit door on left hall until chairs chairs at door on left
tgt: Exit the door on the left and go down the hall until you reach the chairs. Pass the chairs and stop at the door on the left.

src: walk through door of bedroom straight towards brown leather chair stop
tgt: Walk through the door of the bedroom, walk straight towards the farthest brown leather chair and stop.

src: stairs level right down stairs at bottom level stop
tgt: Go down the stairs to the level, make a right and go down more stairs, at the bottom level stop.

src: walk towards stairs first flight of steps right second flight of steps at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk towards the stairs and go down the first flight of steps. Turn right and go down the second flight of steps. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs between pillars right second stair at bottom of staircases
tgt: Go down the stairs between the two pillars, and go right down the second stair set. Stop at the bottom of the staircases.

src: turn right walk through door straight in front of lockers
tgt: Turn to your right and walk through the door. Keep walking straight and stop in front of the lockers.

src: walk into door on left into bathroom stop at set of lockers on right
tgt: walk straight into door on the left, continue into bathroom straight stop at set of 4 lockers on your right.

src: away from circular desk down hallway on left past water machine lockers long mirror on right right past mirror
tgt: walk away from the circular desk, down the hallway on the left. Proceed past the water machine and lockers. There will be a long mirror hanging on the right and stop right past the mirror.

src: walk with guardrail on right in doorway next elevator in doorway
tgt: Walk with the guardrail on your right. Turn left in the doorway next to the elevator. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn right down end of hallway through door left of elevator stop
tgt: Turn right and go down to the end of the hallway. Go through the door to the left of the elevator and stop.

src: walk along balcony with on right towards elevator turn beside fire extinguisher in doorway of bedroom
tgt: Walk along balcony with railing on the right, walk towards the elevator.  Turn left beside the fire extinguisher, and stop in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: down hallway wall art hallway past laundry room stop at wooden cabinets on right of hallway
tgt: Walk down the hallway passed the hanging wall art. Continue down the hallway past the laundry room and stop at the wooden cabinets on the right of the hallway.

src: down hall until brown closet doors on right then
tgt: Walk down the hall.  Keep  going until you get to the brown closet doors on the right.  Then you will stop and wait.

src: walk down hall until digital thermostat on left
tgt: Walk straight down the hall until you reach the digital thermostat on your left.

src: enter home through slider walk across living room main front entry beside bathroom
tgt: Enter home through slider and walk across living room to main front entry. Stop beside bathroom.

src: walk inside right white sofas walk towards white round table with white vase white flower straight towards white table on left side of wall outside room next
tgt: Walk inside, and turn right passing the white sofas. Walk towards the white round table with the white vase, and white flower. Walk straight towards the white table on the left side of the wall, and stop outside the room next to it.

src: inside right at round table turn towards front door turn at front door into bathroom in doorway bathroom
tgt: Go inside and turn right.  At the round table, turn left and walk towards the front door.  Turn left at the front door and go into the bathroom.  Stop in the doorway to this bathroom.

src: walk across patio into bedroom wait next area in bedroom
tgt: Walk across the patio into the bedroom. Wait next to the seating area in the bedroom.

src: walk towards house into bedroom off balcony just on inside of door way
tgt: Walk towards the house and into the bedroom off the balcony and stop just on the inside of the door way.

src: move between chairs towards house ahead through open patio doors inside as soon as house black white rug stop just inside doorway before rug
tgt: Move between the two covered chairs and towards the house. Proceed ahead through the open patio doors that lead inside. As soon as you enter the house and are facing the black and white rug stop. You should be just inside the doorway (before you get to the rug).

src: up stairs left wait at top
tgt: Walk up the stairs to the left and wait at the top.

src: up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs, wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk towards up stairs on second stair from top
tgt: Walk towards and up the stairs. Stop on the second stair from the top.

src: down hallway onto large rug walk past large round coffee tables turn at second coffee table wait at first set of doorways
tgt: Walk down the hallway and onto the large rug. Walk past the large round coffee tables. Turn left at the second coffee table and wait at the first set of doorways.

src: railing right straight through room left of room turn into archway chairs in between doorways
tgt: Go passed the railing to the right and go straight through the room to the left of the room, turn left into the archway passed the chairs and stop when in between the two doorways.

src: with stairs right wall with sets of doors outside head towards doors turn last vaulted hallway on wall left at midpoint of vaulted hallway between doors
tgt: With the stairs to your right and you facing the wall with three sets of doors going outside, head towards the doors. Turn left and enter the last vaulted hallway on the wall to your left. Stop at the midpoint of the vaulted hallway between two doors.

src: forward towards foot of stairs then ninety degrees left narrow hallway steps at bottom of steps room on left with treadmill
tgt: Go forward towards the foot of the stairs, then turn ninety degrees to the left and continue down the narrow hallway, going down three steps. At the bottom of the steps, enter the room on the left with the treadmill.

src: into hallway down first set of steps wait inside double doors on left
tgt: Go into the hallway and down the first set of steps. Wait inside the double doors on the left.

src: exit room turn left hallway down steps then into room wait near treadmill
tgt: Exit the room and turn left. Go down the hallway and down the three steps then turn left and go into the room. Wait near the treadmill.

src: stairs then right toward round black table with white chairs after table chairs right left wait near black rectangle table with white chairs
tgt: Go down the stairs then turn right. Walk toward the round black table with the white chairs.  After you pass the table and chairs turn right. Turn left and wait near the black rectangle table with the white chairs.

src: turn bottom of staircase walk ahead few steps right dining room right immediately past dining table turn dining room kitchen few steps left wait there

tgt: Walk down steps to landing then walk straight up steps. turn slight right and cross hallway to bedroom. stop before the rug.

src: down stairs landing then up stairs ahead straight slightly right through double doors of bedroom wait just inside
tgt: Walk down the stairs to the landing, and then up the stairs ahead. Continue straight and slightly right. Go through the double doors of the bedroom and wait just inside.

src: stairs walk past floral arrangement up stairs past smoke detector wait at tv
tgt: Walk down stairs. Walk past floral arrangement. Walk up stairs. Walk past smoke detector. Wait at tv.

src: walk into bathroom area past sink shower walk through open door into bedroom walk past base of bed out through door on other side
tgt: Walk into the bathroom area and continue past the sink and shower. Walk through the open door into the bedroom. walk past the base of the bed and out through the door on the other side.

src: room with toilet step into bathroom turn past foot of beds outside bedroom just after out of bedroom
tgt: Leave the room with the toilet and step into the bigger bathroom.  Turn left and walk past the foot of the two beds and outside the bedroom.  Stop just after stepping out of the bedroom.

src: exit toilet room left walk shower towards bedroom slight right straight bedroom
tgt: Exit toilet room and take left. Walk passed the shower towards bedroom. Slight right and walk straight to exit bedroom.

src: down stairs turn straight until white table with chairs
tgt: Walk down the stairs. Turn left and go straight until you get to a white table with chairs.

src: down stairs straight ahead at bottom turn doorway straight ahead once
tgt: Walk down the stairs straight ahead. At the bottom, turn left and enter the doorway straight ahead. Stop once you enter.

src: continue downstairs left into dining room with wood floors
tgt: Continue downstairs and take a left.  Walk into the dining room with the wood floors.

src: turn house in wood door left once inside forward once right in front of fireplace
tgt: Turn around and enter the house in the wood door to your left. Once inside walk forward and stop once you are right in front of the fireplace.

src: enter through front door through second door straight until fireplace wait here
tgt: Enter through front door.  Enter through second door.  Continue straight until you reach fireplace.  Wait here.

src: enter house through front door walk straight through second door straight into room chairs by fireplace wait between chairs by fireplace
tgt: Enter the house through the front door and walk straight through the second door. Go straight into the room to the two chairs by the fireplace and wait between the two chairs by the fireplace.

src: move slightly right around table forward forward slightly around table forward
tgt: Move slightly to the right around the table. Walk forward. Walk forward. Walk slightly to the left around the table and walk forward.

src: walk past round tables left of last one
tgt: Walk past all the round tables and stop to the left of the last one.

src: walk end of patio towards gazebo wait by last table
tgt: Walk to the end of the patio, towards the gazebo and wait by the last table.

src: with desks right towards railing left until stairs on right stairs on landing in middle
tgt: With the desks to your right, walk towards the railing and go left.  Keep going until you get to the stairs on the right.  Go down the stairs and stop on the landing in the middle.

src: turn right past blue chairs left after second blue chair walkway by rails stairs on right down first flight of stairs at top of second flight
tgt: Turn towards the right and walk past the blue chairs. Take a left after passing the second blue chair and follow the walkway by the rails. Take the stairs on the right. Walk down the first flight of stairs and stop at the top of the second flight.

src: turn around over stairs then on first landing
tgt: Turn around and walk over to the stairs then go down them and wait on the first landing.

src: walk around banister rail stairwell hallway with paneled wall walk towards open door at end of hall at entrance
tgt: Walk around the banister rail and stairwell. Continue down the hallway with paneled wall. Walk towards the open door at the end of the hall and stop at its entrance.

src: right of stairs stairs on left down hallway at first doorway step in
tgt: Go to the right of the stairs and passed the stairs on the left and keep going down the hallway, at the first doorway step in and stop.

src: walk past stairs down hall wait in doorway at end of hall
tgt: Walk past the stairs and down the hall. Wait in the doorway at the end of the hall.

src: head downstairs through first double doors on left down hallway wait in sitting room in front of fireplace
tgt: Head downstairs and through the first double doors on the left. Walk down the hallway and wait in the sitting room in front of the fireplace.

src: stairs way turn left hallway until large room with floral couches wait there by gold table small chairs
tgt: Go down the stairs when you get all the way down turn left and head down that hallway until you get to a large room with floral couches and wait there by the gold table and the two small chairs.

src: down stairs down right down steps past columns turn into room over rope in front of table
tgt: Walk down the stairs that curves down to the right. Walk down the steps past the columns and turn left. Walk into the room and over the rope. Stop in front of the table.

src: walk ahead sink faucet on left way end in front of round table chairs
tgt: Walk straight ahead passing the sink faucet on the left all the way to its end. Stop in front of the round table and six chairs.

src: head around counter past stove end of counter
tgt: Head around the counter and past the stove. Stop when you read the end of the counter.

src: walk around island past sink grill behind chair at table
tgt: Walk around the island past the sink and grill and stop behind the closest chair at the table.

src: turn around through tables chairs center of room in center of wide open space long table with white table cloth other tables chairs on other side of room
tgt: Turn around and walk through the tables and chairs to the center of the room. Stop in the center of the wide open space facing the long table with the white table cloth and the other tables and chairs on the other side of the room.

src: turn way through of table chairs until opening stand in middle of pillars underneath chandelier
tgt: Turn around and make your way through all of the table and chairs until you reach an opening, stand in the middle of four pillars underneath a chandelier.

src: from fireplace walk across large room center of room in front of large main table
tgt: From fireplace walk across large dinning room to center of room. Stop in front of large main table.

src: exit bathroom walk through bedroom right turn first door at left inside room with starfish seashell decorations
tgt: Exit the bathroom.  Walk through the bedroom and take a right turn.  Enter the first door at your left and stop inside the room with the starfish and seashell decorations.

src: bathroom enter bedroom straight exit bedroom in hall first door right enter room next tv
tgt: Leave bathroom and enter bedroom, go straight and exit bedroom, in the hall take first door to the right and enter sitting room. Stand next to the tv.

src: bathroom through bedroom into hallway in hallway first right into television room next door in television room
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go through the bedroom into the hallway. In the hallway take your first right into the television room. Stop next to the door in the television room.

tgt: Exit the shower room, then exit the locker room. Go into the neighboring room to the right, through the doorway next to the mirror on the wall. Stop next to the tissue box on the shelf.

src: walk out of shower room room into room directly previous room
tgt: Walk out of the shower room and leave the room. Go into the room directly connected to the previous room.

src: exit room locker room right right again into archway step into other locker room stop
tgt: Exit the room, exit the locker room, turn right and right again into the archway, and step into the other locker room and stop.

src: head out door right around banisters once ahead of
tgt: Head out the door.  Take a right. Go around the banisters and stop once ahead of them.

src: walk around bed in room out through door on other side of room down hallway around banister stop at first open door bedroom
tgt: Walk around the bed in the room out through the door on the other side of the room. Walk down the hallway around the banister and stop at the first open door to a bedroom.

src: off of bed walk through door into hallway walk into hallway left at first open door
tgt: Get off of the bed and walk through the door into the hallway. Walk into the curved hallway and make a left at the first open door.

src: walk past fireplace through doorway left of lounger chair past table on left in doorway on right next door
tgt: walk past the fireplace, to through the doorway to the left of the lounger chair, walk past the table on the left and stop in the doorway on the right next to the door to outside.

src: walk across bedroom through double doors wait in bathroom on other side of area
tgt: Walk across the bedroom and through the double doors. Wait in the bathroom on the other side of the dining area.

src: fireplace through door on right loveseat room dinner table continue through doorway stop
tgt: Go passed the fireplace and go through the door on the right passed the loveseat. Enter the room and go passed the dinner table. Continue and go through the doorway and stop.

src: walk towards white bookshelf turn at white bookshelf in between tables
tgt: Walk towards the white bookshelf. Turn left at the white bookshelf. Stop in between the two tables.

src: in doorway of room next long wooden table empty aside from plant
tgt: Go and stand in the doorway of the room next to the long wooden table that is empty aside from one plant.

tgt: Turn right and walk past the ping pong table. Turn a slight left and move forward to the white bookcase Turn left at the bookcase, walk a few steps and stop.

tgt: Go to the main entrance by the staircase and take a left. Go into the living room with the mirror.

tgt: Walk across the room toward the winding stairs going up. Turn right before the stairs. Go through the double doors and into the living area with a blue sofa. Stop next to the white chair with a blue pot next to it.

tgt: Walk behind the couch and past the chair. Walk through the room with the stairs and right through the double doors. Stop in front of the coffee table.

tgt: Exit the bedroom, walk through the kitchen, turn left, walk to the red chair, turn left, enter the bathroom, wait at the sink.

tgt: Walk past fireplace.Make a left before kitchen. Walk through bedroom. Wait at threshold of bathroom door.

tgt: exit room slight right into main room. Turn slight right up 2 steps. Stop between 2 bathtubs.

tgt: Walk to the room with the double doors.  Walk up the steps and stop facing the bathtub.

tgt: Leave the empty room through the exit sign, walk towards the bathtub, and wait.

tgt: Walk around the corner towards the couch and fireplace. Walk down the tile walkway past the couches and the bar counter of the kitchen. Turn the corner past the bar counter and walk into the hallway. Continue through the open door at the end of the hall that is nearest to the kitchen. Walk into the room, which is a small movie room.

tgt: Walk past the dining area and through the sliding glass door. Wait outside, on the patio.

tgt: Walk to the far end of the room and stop at the top of the steps.

tgt: Walk past the refrigerator and to the right. Stop in the bedroom across the hall.

tgt: Walk into the hallway and to the right. Walk left down the hall and turn right. Stop just inside the bedroom.

tgt: Go  right and turn right at the hallway, take another right and you are in another hallway, keep going and take a right, go to the end bedroom and stop when you through the doorway.

tgt: Leave dining room to hall way, turn right at pictures of kids on the wall to bedroom. Stop next to guitar.

tgt: Turn around and exit the room though the doorway to the left. Walk across the hallway, up some steps and enter the bathroom.

tgt: Exit the half bath, then turn left down the hallway. Continue forward until you can turn right through the double doors to your right.

tgt: Exit the room and head down the hall, turning right, then left, then right.

src: walk out of area right just inside front entrance
tgt: Walk out of the sitting area and turn right. Wait just inside the front entrance.

tgt: Go through the archway on the right, go to the right side of the black table, cross the room and step near the wooden door with the slats and then stop.

src: exit laundry room turn bed bathroom wait near counter

src: after bedroom bedroom at end of hall into room wait at foot of bed
tgt: After you leave the bedroom you should go the bedroom at the end of the hall. When you go into the room wait at the foot of the bed.

src: walk into hallway right straight into bedroom wait by desk
tgt: Walk into the hallway and make a right. Walk straight into bedroom and wait by the desk.

src: exit bedroom on right right straight through next room wait in middle of room
tgt: Exit the bedroom on the right, make a right, go straight through to the next room, wait in the middle of the room.

tgt: Walk past the pool and go indoors. Take a right, and walk past the couch and stop in the doorway in front of the mirror.

tgt: Go straight towards the open double doors, right past the pool.  Enter the room.  Turn right and go straight, till you're even with the couch.  Then you should stop and wait.

tgt: Walk forward with the pool on your right. Walk into the house through the door ahead of you on the left. In the house take a left and turn down the first right and stop next to the plants.

src: orient parallel grain on wooden floor such that doorway directly ahead of bathroom ahead right double doorway ahead left though double doorway ahead of left once room behind couch straight with glass doors left once kitchen area
tgt: Orient yourself to be parallel to the grain on the wooden floor and such that you see a doorway directly ahead of you, a bathroom ahead and to the right, and a double doorway ahead and to the left. Go though the double doorway ahead of you and to the left. Once you enter the room, go left behind the couch and continue straight with the sliding glass doors to your left. Stop once you reach the kitchen area.

tgt: Go towards the single chandelier in view and then through the white double doors, make a left before the white couch, go straight through the room with the glass sliding doors on the left, go towards the kitchen area, and stop at the counter with the three counter chairs.

tgt: Turn left, and enter inside the door towards the living room. Turn left passing the sofa, and keep walking forward passing the glass table as well, and stop in front of the first kitchen counter.

src: down walkway second door on right inside bedroom by chair
tgt: Walk down the walkway and enter the second door on the right. Wait inside the bedroom by the chair.

tgt: Walk along the banister rail down the hallway passing the small side table with a lamp on top. Walk into the next open door on the right with a written plaque avove the door. Walk into the room with a patchwork blanket on the bed.

src: hallway room with teddy bear on bed
tgt: go down the hallway to the room with the teddy bear on the bed.

src: up stairs wait at middle of last set of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs and wait at the middle of the last set of stairs.

src: right stairs next floor
tgt: Make a right and go up the stairs. Face the next floor.

src: walk staircase right up stairs wall right up stairs wall right halfway up stairs
tgt: Walk to the staircase, turn right, walk up the stairs to the wall, turn right, walk up the stairs to the wall, turn right, wait halfway up the stairs.

src: stairs once level stand at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs. Stop once you reach the level and stand at the bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs then
tgt: Go down the stairs then stop.

src: way down stairs then
tgt: Go all the way down the stairs then wait.

tgt: Go up the stairs. Take a right, and pass the fireplace on the left. Stop beside the flag one the pole.

tgt: Walk all the way to top of the stairs. Walk forwards through the room towards the flag. Stop just in front of the flag.

tgt: Go up the stairs. Turn right and go into the hallway that is to the left of the fireplace. Wait there.

src: hall next pulp fiction poster
tgt: Go down the hall. Stop next to the Pulp Fiction poster.

src: walk straight until poster on left side of wall of pulp fiction wait there
tgt: Walk straight until you get to a poster on the left side of the wall of Pulp Fiction. Wait there.

src: hallway stairs then near set of posters
tgt: Continue down the hallway, pass the stairs and then stop near the set of posters.

tgt: Go up the stairs and take a left. Walk into the bedroom at the end of the hall. Stop in the doorway to the bathroom on the right of the bed.

tgt: Go up the stairs and follow the hallway to the left.  Enter the first bedroom with a white bed and walk towards the bathroom on your left.  Stop in front of the doorway that leads to the toilet.

tgt: Turn left and enter the house. Then turn right and enter the kitchen area.

tgt: Turn around and enter the house. Turn right and then turn immediately right again. Stop near the lightswitches.

tgt: Walk past the pool on the right. Turn left and go up the steps. Go through the gate and wait near the two pots with plants.

tgt: Walk to end of pool and go up step to the left. Walk through security door and stop at front door to house.

tgt: Walk along the edge of the pool.  Then follow along the edge of the house and stand next to the iron gate.
