tgt: Exit the bedroom and enter the laundry room on the right. Wait there.

src: walk past bed on left bedroom left past stairs on left right into open door just after wall paintings on right wait at laundry room threshold
tgt: Walk past the bed on the left. Exit the bedroom, and make a left. Walk past the stairs on the left. Make a right into the open door just after the two wall paintings on the right. Wait at the laundry room threshold.

src: exit room door on right then into room on right wait by sink
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the right then turn left and go into the room on the right. Wait by the sink.

src: down hall stairwell walk into bedroom ahead bed with white comforter blue floor rug underneath
tgt: Walk down the hall passing the stairwell. Walk into the bedroom ahead that has a bed with white comforter and blue floor rug underneath.

src: through near doorway through hallway wait near fireplace
tgt: Go through the near doorway, go through the hallway, wait near the fireplace.

src: enter bedroom wait by fireplace
tgt: Enter the bedroom and wait by the fireplace.

src: down hall into bedroom right past chest of drawers right in bathroom doorway
tgt: Walk down the hall and into the bedroom. Turn right and walk past the chest of drawers. Turn right and stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: stand with stairs on right straight hallway into bedroom at end walk past foot of bed through door on right into bathroom on opposite side of hallway in front of sink
tgt: Stand with the stairs on your right and walk straight down the hallway into the bedroom at the end.  Walk past the foot of the bed and leave through the door on the right.  Walk into the bathroom on the opposite side of the hallway and stop in front of the sink.

src: turn right down hallway into door on end once in bedroom right walk other side of room right straight ahead bathroom
tgt: Turn right and walk down the hallway and into the door on the end. Once in the bedroom, turn right and walk to the other side of the room and turn right. Walk straight ahead and stop when you enter the bathroom.

src: walk past piano through middle entryway right in front of double doors stop
tgt: Walk past the piano and through the middle entryway. Turn right and stop in front of the double doors and stop.

src: walk towards piano middle doorway walk towards stairs between stair cases
tgt: Walk towards the piano, and throught the middle doorway. Walk towards the stairs, and stop between the two stair cases that go down.

src: walk past piano through middle archway straight until double doors on right outside in between staircases
tgt: Walk past the piano and through the middle archway.  Keep walking straight until you get to double doors on the right leading outside and stop in between the two staircases.

src: through door into hall red carpet doorway with striped chair mirror on side stop
tgt: Go through the door into a hall down a red carpet.  When you get to another doorway with a striped chair and mirror on either side, stop.

src: on floor runner turn left through entrance way wait by striped chair
tgt: Go on floor runner and turn left. Go through the entrance way and wait by the striped chair.

src: turn out of doorway red carpet runner through hallway next room walk until just past stairs stop
tgt: Turn left out of the doorway and follow the red carpet runner through the hallway. Enter the next room and walk until just past the stairs and stop.

src: turn hallway right through first door turn in first doorway
tgt: Turn around, go down the hallway, and turn right to go through the first door. Turn left and stop in the first doorway.

src: exit restroom right wall through door wait in doorway on left
tgt: Exit the restroom. Turn right when you get to the wall. Go through the door and wait in the doorway on the left.

src: walk out of bathroom right at end of hall walk through doorway into room entrance left in entrance room left
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom. Turn right at the end of the hall. Walk through the doorway and into the room entrance to the left. Stop in the entrance to the room to the left.

src: at bottom of stairs forward toward black door right toward pool wait by pillars
tgt: At the bottom of the stairs, go forward toward the black door. Turn right and go toward the pool. Wait by the pillars.

src: turn right at arches
tgt: Turn around and turn right. Stop at the arches.

src: walk door then right then forward next columns wait on stone path near grass
tgt: Walk to the door then turn right.  Then walk forward and stand next to the columns. Wait on the stone path near the grass.

src: turn left past rope room right of fireplace once in next room turn walk end of rope right walk at top of stairs
tgt: Turn to your left and go past the rope to exit the room to the right of the fireplace. Once in the next room turn left. Walk to the end of the rope and turn right. Walk and stop at the top of the stairs facing down them.

src: turn right fireplace out of room then at top of stairs on first step
tgt: Turn right and pass the fireplace go out of the room then go left and wait at the top of the stairs on the first step.

src: walk past chairs right through double doors turn walk top of stairs on second stair from top
tgt: Walk past the chairs and turn right. Walk through the double doors and turn left. Walk to the top of the stairs. Stop on the second stair from the top.

src: into kitchen through doorway on left inside dining room
tgt: Go into the kitchen and through the doorway on the left. Wait inside the dining room.

src: enter kitchen then left wall until door through door dining room entrance
tgt: Enter the kitchen, then follow the left wall until you find a door. Go through the door, and stop when you reach the dining room entrance.

src: turn so kitchen forward towards kitchen island move through kitchen left of kitchen island so that island on right counters on left close large sink not one in island arched passageway left through passageway dining room in second arched doorway dining room
tgt: Turn around so you are facing the kitchen. Move forward towards the kitchen island. Move through the kitchen, staying to the left of the kitchen island so that the island is on your right and the counters are on your left. When you get close to the large sink (not the one in the island) there will be an arched passageway to the left. Go through this passageway and towards the dining room. Stop in the second arched doorway leading to the dining room.

src: walk past ottoman on right bedroom right past portraits on wall left bedroom ahead wait near chair
tgt: Walk past the ottoman on the right. Exit the bedroom, and make a right. Walk past the five portraits on the wall to the left. Enter the bedroom straight ahead, and wait near the chair.

src: exit room door on left then right way down hallway until into next room wait by bed
tgt: Exit the room using the door on your left then turn right and go all the way down the hallway until you go into the next room and wait by the bed.

src: left then right down hall wait in bedroom
tgt: Take a left, then a right. Walk down the hall and wait in the bedroom.

src: turn around straight path towards pool turn at next walkway door inside
tgt: Turn around and walk straight down the path towards the pool. Turn left at the next walkway and stop facing the door to go inside.

src: down walkway outside towards pool pool few steps away before building
tgt: Walk down the walkway outside going towards the pool.  Go left when you reach the pool and stop a few steps away before entering the building.

src: follow concrete path pillars turn in front of glass door
tgt: follow concrete path to  2 pillars, turn left and stop in front of sliding glass door.

src: doorway on far right hall right through open door on immediate right closet through doorway stop
tgt: To the doorway on the far right and head down the hall,  take a right and go through the open door, on your immediate right is a closet, go through the doorway and stop.

src: walk out of room into hallway straight path into bathroom wait in closet left
tgt: Walk out of the room and into the hallway.  Continue a straight path into the bathroom.  Wait in the closet to your left.

src: playroom in hallway walk into bathroom across hall in bathroom left into closet in doorway closet
tgt: Leave the playroom, In the hallway walk straight into the bathroom across the hall. In the bathroom take a left into the closet. Stop in the doorway to the closet.

src: storage closet u-turn left through doorway wait on landing
tgt: Leave the storage closet and make a u-turn to the left.  Go through the doorway and wait on the landing.

src: door right.then through first door stand at bottom of second flight of stairs
tgt: Go out the door and turn right.Then go through the first door and stand at the bottom of the second flight of stairs.

src: sharp right turn out of storage closet right outside door stop
tgt: Make a sharp right turn walking out of the storage closet. Turn right and walk outside the door and stop.

src: walk past table desktop computer exit room through white double doors right past framed newspaper articles turn through doorway on left wait
tgt: Walk past the table and desktop computer. Exit room through the white double doors and turn right. Walk past the framed newspaper articles. Turn through the doorway on the left and wait.

src: turn right pass table desk head towards open doors through doors head right hall way through hall way first left stop
tgt: Turn right pass the table and desk and head towards the open doors. GO through the doors and head right towards the hall way. One you make it through the hall way make the first left and stop.

src: turn right exit through double white doors once out right head towards long hallway right hallway door left right left room in small large table
tgt: Turn to your right and exit through the double white doors. Once out, Turn to your right and head towards the long hallway. Right when you start to enter the hallway and there is a door to the left and right, turn to the left and enter the room. Stop when you walk in and are facing both the small and large table.

src: walk into living room walk past couches right in doorway
tgt: Walk into the living room. Walk past the couches and turn right. Stop in the doorway.

src: forward into through living room right at end of room dining room in doorway dining room
tgt: Walk forward into, and through the living room. Take a right at the end of the room and enter the dining room. Stop in the doorway to the dining room.

src: turn walk into living room area with burgundy couches walk couches towards fireplace through doorway on right on opposite side of room into dining area
tgt: Turn and walk into the living room area with burgundy couches. Walk passed the couches towards the fireplace. Go through the doorway on the right on the opposite side of the room and into the dining area.

src: walk through door continue straight through next door in room
tgt: Walk straight through the door and continue straight through the next door, stopping in the room.

src: exit room through doorway straight ahead in front of bed
tgt: Exit room and go through doorway straight ahead. Stop in front of bed.

src: exit room with water heater walk straight across open area into bedroom at bed
tgt: Exit the room with the water heater. Walk straight across the open area and into the bedroom. Stop at the bed.

src: turn until stairs on sides table in front of forward slightly left of table on left side wall open door against wall with art on though door into room many cabinets with dishes
tgt: TURN LEFT UNTIL THERE ARE STAIRS ON BOTH SIDES AND A TABLE IN FRONT OF YOU, WALK FORWARD AND SLIGHTLY TO THE LEFT OF THE TABLE, ON THE LEFT SIDE WALL IS AN OPEN DOOR AGAINST A WALL WITH ART ON IT, WALK THOUGH THE DOOR AND INTO A ROOM THAT HAS MANY CABINETS FILLED WITH DISHES.

src: walk through room towards wooden side table walk past table into storage room with glass cabinets
tgt: Walk through the room towards the wooden side table. Walk past the table and turn into the storage room with the glass cabinets.

src: walk towards dining room wait inside double doors on left
tgt: Walk towards the dining room, wait inside the double doors on the left.

src: away from bed through doorway turn right towards banister turn top of stairs down stairs away from bottom
tgt: walk away from the bed through the doorway turn right and walk towards the banister, turn left and walk to the top of the stairs, walk down the stairs but stop when you are four away from the bottom.

src: walk out of bedroom right enter landing right again steps as toward foot of stairs stop wait
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom. Turning right enter the landing and turn right again to go down the steps. As you get toward the foot of the stairs, stop and wait.

src: exit bedroom right at base of stairs
tgt: Exit bedroom and go right to stairs and go down them. Stop at base of stairs.

src: turn right room turn then right toward stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn right and exit the room. Turn left and then turn right and walk toward the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: exit bedroom left then sharp right at stair landing in front of glass door
tgt: Exit bedroom, make a left then a sharp right, stop at the stair landing, in front of the glass door.

src: bedroom through door on right in o'clock position until door outside walk towards at top of sets of stairs few feet in front of door outside
tgt: Leave the bedroom through the door on the right.  Walk in your one o'clock position until you see a door going outside and walk towards it.  Stop when you are standing at the top of two sets of stairs, a few feet in front of the door going outside.

src: exit stairwell right hard right hallway bedroom wait
tgt: Exit the stairwell to your right.  Take a hard right down the hallway enter the bedroom and wait.

src: turn right at top of stairs past bathroom into room with blue circular thing in middle of room just inside door next white shelf with silver mirror above
tgt: Turn right at the top of the stairs. Go past the bathroom and into the room with the blue circular thing in the middle of the room. Stop just inside the door, next to the white shelf with a silver mirror above it.

src: walk forward then right at room forward again then living room with white sofa
tgt: walk forward then turn right at the room, walk forward again then enter the living room with a white sofa.

src: leave massage room right enter washroom at massage table
tgt: Leave massage room to lobby, turn right and enter washroom, stop at massage table.

src: exit room through door on left head through next doorway on right toward massage table left.. stop there
tgt: Exit the room through the door on the left. Head through the next doorway on the right. Go toward the massage table to the left.. Stop there.

src: walk past massage tables on left exit through open door right at black white tile inset in floor walk through open door wait at massage table
tgt: Walk past the massage tables on the left. Exit through the open door. Make a right at the black and white tile inset in the floor. Walk through the open door. Wait at the massage table.

src: turn in front of dining room table turn up stairs turn up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Turn left in front of the dining room table. Turn left and walk up the stairs. Turn left and walk up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: past red rug then stairs on left way top
tgt: Go past the red rug and then go up the stairs on the left. Stop when you get all the way to the top.

src: enter room in front of left head way up steps at top of stairs table with chair on side
tgt: Enter the room in front of you. Turn left and head all the way up the steps. Stop at the top of the stairs facing the table with a chair on each side.

src: walk past pool wait in corner next door
tgt: Walk past the pool and wait in the corner next to the door.

src: walk left of pool walk past glass door stop by plant
tgt: Walk to the left of the pool. Walk past the glass door and stop by the plant.

src: left of pool walk towards double glass doors ahead next wall with triangle circle openings
tgt: Go to the left of the pool and walk towards the double glass doors straight ahead.  Stop next to the wall with the triangle and circle openings.

src: exit bathroom slight left through lobby stop at display case next bathroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom and make a slight left.  Walk through the lobby and stop at the display case next to the bathroom.

src: room past fireplace wait in hall by curio cabinet
tgt: Leave the room, walk past the fireplace and wait in the hall by the curio cabinet.

src: bedroom walk straight fireplace on right walking in front of cabinet at end of hallway
tgt: Leave the bedroom and walk straight. Pass the fireplace on your right and keep walking. Stop in front of the cabinet at the end of the hallway.

src: past table/chairs couches room though double doors then stairs until window on right with vase red flowers
tgt: Go past the table/chairs and the couches and exit the room though the double doors then turn left and go down stairs until you get to the window on the right with the vase and red flowers.

src: walk out double doors left of room down hall wait in front of double doors on left
tgt: Walk out the double doors to the left of the room. Walk down the hall and wait in front of the double doors on the left.

src: around table through double doors turn steps in front of window
tgt: Go around the table and through the double doors.  Turn left, go down the steps and stop in front of the window.

src: exit bathroom right down end of hall then dining room right through dining room exit out patio doors wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom.  Turn right and walk down to the end of the hall.  Then turn left and enter the dining room. Turn right, walk through the dining room and exit out the patio doors. Wait there.

src: walk out of bathroom right end of hall turn into large room right out of double doors stop
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and to the right. Walk to the end of the hall and turn left. Walk into the large room and turn right. Walk straight out of the double doors and stop.

src: exit bathroom right on second door right double glass doors patio wait near black bench
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right. Turn left on the second door. turn right and go out the double glass doors to the patio. Wait near the black bench.

src: enter bedroom from outside across bedroom door on right wall first doorway on right bathroom wait just inside doorway bathroom
tgt: Enter the bedroom from outside and go across the bedroom to the door on the right wall. Enter the first doorway on the right and enter the bathroom. Wait just inside the doorway to the bathroom.

src: with balcony rear forward past bed on until room into bathroom via first door on right after bathroom
tgt: With the balcony to your rear, move forward past the bed on your left until you can exit the room into the bathroom via the first door on your right. Stop after entering the bathroom.

src: turn inside room walk past television right at first door enter bathroom inside doorway
tgt: Turn to face inside room. Walk past television. Turn right at first door. Enter bathroom. Stop inside doorway.

src: walk through entryway into hallway straight ahead bedroom through door on left in doorway
tgt: Walk through the entryway, and go into the hallway straight ahead. Enter the bedroom through the door on the left. Stop in the doorway.

src: walk past fireplace past stairs into second room left of fire extinguisher stop after in room
tgt: Walk past the fireplace and past the stairs.  Go into the second room to the left of the fire extinguisher and stop after stepping in the room.

src: turn past stairs once stairs door on left in front of door above
tgt: Turn left and walk past the stairs. Once you pass the stairs enter the door on the left in front of you and stop. The door should say frontier above it.

src: door right hallway past first door on right right into hallway behind first big brown leather chair
tgt: Facing the door take a right and go down the hallway going past the first door on your right and take a right into the hallway stopping behind the first big brown leather chair.

src: walk straight ahead through hallway right chair just back of leather chair then
tgt: Walk straight ahead, through the hallway.  Turn right and you will see a leather chair.  Walk just to the back of that leather chair and then stop and wait.

src: straight wall right ends then hard right right behind couch
tgt: Go straight  and till the wall to your right ends then take a hard right and stop right behind the couch.

src: turn hall then right stairs at painting
tgt: Turn left and walk to the hall. Then turn right and head down the stairs. Stop at the painting.

src: stairs left next set of stairs at bottom of set of stairs
tgt: Continue down the stairs, and take a left. Go down the next set of stairs, and stop at the bottom of this set of stairs.

src: at base of stairs turn through leftmost opening after steps right steps just past abstract left
tgt: At the base of the stairs, turn left and go through the leftmost opening after descending three steps. Turn to your right and descend three more steps and stop just past the abstract painting to your left.

src: walk out door towards bed left turn out door slight right turn down first flight of stairs
tgt: Walk out the door towards the bed. Make a left turn and walk out the door. Make a slight right turn and walk down the first flight of stairs.

src: exit bathroom turn bedroom wait in middle of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn left to exit the bedroom. Wait in the middle of the stairs.

src: walk through door into bedroom left through doorway directly of desk once through door steps down stairs stop
tgt: Walk through the door into the bedroom. Take a left, and walk through the doorway that is directly left of the desk. Once through the door, walk 4 steps down the stairs and stop.

src: straight until exit sign then right into room turn balcony wait there
tgt: Go straight until you get to an exit sign then turn right and go into the room. Turn left and go out the balcony. Wait there.

src: hallway away from wooden posts right into wooden doorway archway step into bedroom then into glass doorway outside stop
tgt: Go down the hallway away from the wooden posts, turn right into the wooden doorway archway, step into the bedroom, then turn left and step into the glass doorway to the outside and stop.

src: down hall door with exit sign over right into bedroom at foot of bed turn deck in doorway of deck bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hall towards the door with the "exit" sign over it.  Turn right into the bedroom.  At the foot of the bed turn left and go to the deck.  Stop in the doorway of the deck and the bedroom.

src: walk left of bed into bathroom in doorway
tgt: Walk to the left of the bed into the bathroom. Stop in the doorway.

src: walk into bathroom left of bed just inside
tgt: Walk into the bathroom to the left of the bed. Stop just inside.

src: head indoors stop in bathroom wait near vanity
tgt: Head indoors, stop in the bathroom and wait near the vanity.

src: down stairs wait at bottom of stairway next light switch
tgt: Walk down the stairs and wait at the bottom of the stairway next to the light switch.

src: down next floor stop at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down to the next floor. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: turn slightly right down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn slightly right and walk down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: turn at bottom of stairs head through archway right first set of stairs wait at bottom near cream chair
tgt: Turn left at the bottom of the stairs. Head through the archway and turn right. Go down the first set of stairs. Wait at the bottom near the cream chair.

src: hallway right of stairs bottom of next staircase
tgt: Go down the hallway to the right of the stairs, and go to the bottom of the next staircase.

src: turn down of stairs through doorway on left towards glass door right at glass door down stairs stop
tgt: turn left and walk down all of the stairs, walk through doorway on your left towards glass door, turn right at glass door, walk down the stairs and stop.

src: walk through kitchen turn at large gray sofa
tgt: Walk through the kitchen. turn left, and stop at the large gray sofa.

src: walk dining table then right through kitchen turn white table on other side walk towards couch at corner of couch closest deck
tgt: Walk to the dining table and then turn right and walk through the kitchen.  Turn left when you reach the white table on the other side and walk towards the couch.  Stop at the corner of the couch closest to the deck.

src: walk from room right into kitchen turn behind gray couch
tgt: Walk from living room to the right into the kitchen, turn left and stop behind gray couch.

src: into room with crowd control ropes walk top of staircase
tgt: Go left to go into the room with crowd control ropes. Walk to the top of the staircase.

src: exit room into room on left right then top of stairs stop
tgt: Exit the room into the room on the left, turn right and then left and go to the top of the stairs and stop.

src: exit room through doors left of fireplace wait at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the room through the doors to the left of the fireplace. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk out of room right into great open area stairs landing at top of landing
tgt: Walk out of the room and take a right into the great, open area. Go down the stairs to the landing. Stop at the top of the landing.

src: into corridor right top of stairs stairs mid stairs
tgt: Go into the corridor and make a right to the top of the stairs, go down the stairs and stop mid stairs.

src: walk through down first set of stairs at first landing
tgt: Walk through down the first set of stairs and stop at the first landing.

src: walk across kitchen right past refrigerator forward door on right walk into restroom
tgt: Walk across the kitchen and turn right past the refrigerator. Go forward, enter  the door on your right, and walk into the restroom.

src: walk past refrigerator right around corner right bathroom walk entrance bathroom stop
tgt: Walk past the refrigerator and turn right.  Walk around the corner and turn right, facing the bathroom.  Walk to the entrance to the bathroom and stop.

src: walk mirror on side of wall near door bathroom
tgt: Walk to the mirror on the side of the wall, near the door. Enter the bathroom.

src: stairs after first set of stairs second at step fourth from top
tgt: Go up the stairs after going up the first set of stairs go up the second and stop at the step fourth from the top.

src: up stairs mirror on third step from top
tgt: Walk up the stairs, passing the mirror, and stop on the third step from the top.

src: up steps turn up stairs on tenth step
tgt: Walk up the steps and turn left. Walk up the stairs and stop on the tenth step.

src: walk past stairs into kitchen forward past sink stove wait just inside formal dining room
tgt: Walk past the stairs and into the kitchen. Continue forward past the sink and stove. Wait just inside the formal dining room.

src: walk past stairs into kitchen walk through kitchen room on left dining room just before on carpet
tgt: Walk past the stairs and into the kitchen.  Walk through the kitchen and enter the room on the left that is a dining room.  Stop just before walking on the carpet.

src: pass stairs straight kitchen through kitchen out doorway straight ahead not one on right then there
tgt: Pass the stairs and go straight to the kitchen. Go through the kitchen and out the doorway straight ahead(not the one on the right) then wait there.

src: bathroom walk into main room house through door on left on rug at door on outside
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk into the main room. Leave the house through the door on the left. Stop on the rug at the door on the outside.

src: walk out into room stop in doorway on left
tgt: Walk out into the room and stop in the doorway on the left.

src: exit bathroom then laundry room finally on threshold of door outside
tgt: Exit the bathroom, and then exit the laundry room, and finally turn left to stand on the threshold of the door leading outside.

src: exit room walk towards plant on ground once plant right walk top of stairs turn into first room wait here
tgt: Exit the room and walk towards potted plant on the ground.  Once you reach the plant, turn right, and walk to the top of stairs.  Turn left into the first room, wait here.

src: walk past mirror on wall dining table through doorway onto marble floor straight right carpet stairs right up rest of stairs stop in doorway left
tgt: walk past the mirror on the wall and dining table through the doorway onto marble floor,continue straight, turn right to walk up the carpet stairs, curve right and walk up the rest of the stairs stop in the doorway to the left.

src: walk past dining table into next room up stairs on right right wait near top of stairs
tgt: Walk past the dining table and into the next room. Walk up the stairs on the right. Turn right and wait near the top of the stairs.

src: exit living dinning table right door stop at bar area door
tgt: Exit living, pass the dinning table and make a right door, stop at bar area door.

src: with wall fireplace behind forward with long table left through double doors on right after long table.stop after from wooden floor stone tiles
tgt: With the wall containing the fireplace behind you, walk forward with the long table to your left, exiting through the double doors on your right after passing the long table.Stop after moving from the wooden floor to the stone tiles.

src: area walk large wooden table walk on right side of table right at white double doors inside doorway
tgt: Leave the sitting area and walk to towards the large wooden table.  Walk on right side of the table. Turn right at the white double doors. Stop inside the doorway.

src: turn hallway just doorway at end of hall
tgt: Turn around and turn left down the hallway. Go just passed the doorway at the end of the hall.

src: turn way down hallway into room wait at entrance
tgt: Turn left and go all the way down the hallway and into the room. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk forward turn hallway straight hallway stop at doorway
tgt: Walk forward and turn left to enter the hallway. Go straight down the hallway and stop at the doorway.

src: exit room left through black archway left near sink
tgt: Exit the room, make a left and go through the black archway, take a left and stop near the sink.

src: office left in bedroom left into kitchenette in front of minifridge
tgt: Leave the office and take a left. in the bedroom take a left into the kitchenette. Stop in front of the minifridge.

src: exit room immediate left wait in front of sink on left
tgt: Exit the room and take an immediate left.  Wait in front of the sink on the left.

src: turn right up stairs way top at top hallway at end right bedroom
tgt: Turn right and walk up the stairs all the way to the top. At the top, turn left and enter the hallway. At the end, turn right and stop when you enter the bedroom.

src: rest of stairs turn at glass floor down hallway into room on right in doorway of room on right
tgt: Go up the rest of the stairs and turn left at the glass floor.  Walk down the hallway and go into the room on the right.  Stop in the doorway of this room on the right.

src: stairs turn at glass floor hallway room on right in doorway room
tgt: Go up the stairs and turn left at the glass floor.  Go down the hallway and enter the room on the right.  Stop in the doorway to this room.

src: turn through door next door ahead of before door glass table on left statue of horse on right straight door once door
tgt: Turn left, walk through the door, keep going walking to the next door ahead of you and before you get to the door you will  pass a glass table on your left and a statue of a horse on your right, keep going straight to the door and stop once you pass the door.

src: turn through door past dining table through door wait
tgt: Turn left, walk through the door, walk past the dining table, walk through the door, and wait.

src: walk through doorways
tgt: Walk straight through two doorways.

src: turn left hallway towards bedroom through archway in front of bedroom door
tgt: Turn to the left and go down the hallway towards the bedroom. Go through the archway.  Stop in front of the bedroom door.

src: turn dining room left of forward until stairs walking just past stairs doorway bedroom stop
tgt: Turn towards the dining room, and go to the left of it.  Walk forward until you see the stairs.  Keep walking just past the stairs to the doorway to a bedroom, and stop.

src: kitchen left in hallway straight in doorway bedroom at end of hallway
tgt: Leave the kitchen and take a left in the hallway. Go straight and stop in the doorway to the bedroom at the end of the hallway.

src: up stairs turn big statue wooden chair up next set of stairs there
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn left passing the big statue and the wooden chair. Walk up the next set of stairs and stop there.

src: climb last couple steps landing turn straight next set of stairs up steps stop wait
tgt: Climb the last couple steps to the landing. Turn left and walk straight to the next set of stairs. Walk up four steps, stop, and wait.

src: way up stairs wait on third step top
tgt: Finish going all the way up the stairs and wait on the third step to the top.

src: walk past fireplace out of room walk under chandelier stop
tgt: Walk past the fireplace and out of the room. Walk under the chandelier and stop.

src: pass fireplace then straight door ahead wait by chairs flowers
tgt: Pass the fireplace and then go straight out the door ahead. Wait by the chairs that have flowers.

src: straight through doorway next chairs in middle of room
tgt: Go straight through the doorway, stop next to the chairs in the middle of the room.

src: exit bathroom into bedroom bedroom door on right stairs wait at bottom of stiars

src: walk forward purple chairs behind last purple chair
tgt: Walk forward passing all the three purple chairs. Stop behind the last purple chair.

src: stand so stairs on left walk straight past kitchen area by bar stools kitchen island after kitchen area just right of artworks vertically on wood wall on right
tgt: Stand so the stairs are on your left and walk straight past the kitchen area, passing by four bar stools facing the kitchen island.  After passing the kitchen area, stop just to the right of the three framed artworks placed vertically on the wood wall on the right.

src: walk past kitchen island wait by light switches in living room
tgt: Walk past the kitchen island and wait by the light switches in the living room.

src: walk forward stop near table
tgt: walk forward and stop near the table.

src: with wire vine artwork on left straight into big room with square mosaic on floor through door on left on wall on far side of mosaic walk into room stop at foot of bed
tgt: With the wire vine artwork on your left, walk straight into the big room with the square mosaic on the floor.  Go through the door on the left on the wall on the far side of the mosaic.  Walk into the room and stop at the foot of the bed.

src: hall common room straight across bathroom turn next massage table
tgt: Move down the hall and enter the common room. Go straight across and enter the bathroom. Turn left and wait next to the massage table.

src: down hallway into open space with decorated floor walk into room with sink across room next outlet on floor
tgt: Walk down the hallway into the open space with a decorated floor. Walk into the room with the sink across the room. Stand next to the outlet on the floor.

src: walk across bedroom exit door straight open door into living room behind couch
tgt: Walk across bedroom to glass exit door. walk straight passed open door to outside and into living room, stop behind couch.

src: turn walk past bed right out of door walk towards couches red loveseat stop wait there
tgt: Turn around.  Walk past the bed, turn right out of the door.  Walk towards the couches.  When you are to the red loveseat, stop and wait there.

src: turn around door straight ahead through door forward just before vase against wall right between vase orange chair
tgt: Turn around and walk to the door that is straight ahead. Go through the door and continue forward, stopping just before you get the vase against the wall to your right. You will be standing between the vase and orange chair.

src: stairs down dark brown hallway of way near end
tgt: Go down the stairs and down the dark brown hallway all of the way, and stop when you get near the end.

src: walk end of hall picture on wall
tgt: Walk to the end of the hall and face the picture on the wall.

src: bedroom walk straight down hallway at end of hall facing picture
tgt: Leave bedroom and walk straight down hallway, stop at the end of the hall facing picture.

src: walk through door out of garage down hallway turn right again in between kitchen island table right after island down hallway of fridge before first doorway
tgt: walk through door out of garage, walk down hallway and turn left, turn right again to walk in between kitchen island and dining table, slight right after island and walk down hallway to left of fridge. stop before first doorway.

src: turn hallway way until kitchen walk through kitchen hallway left of refrigerator beside thermostat on wall right
tgt: Turn around and enter the hallway and go all the way until you reach the kitchen. Walk through the kitchen and enter the hallway to the left of the refrigerator. Stop beside the thermostat on the wall to your right.

src: enter building down hall past kitchen wait in hallway
tgt: Enter the building, walk down the hall and past the kitchen. Wait in the hallway.

src: down balcony house through green door down hall bedroom through second door on right next door in bedroom
tgt: Walk down the balcony and enter the house through the green door. walk down the hall and enter the bedroom through the second door on the right. Stop next to the door in the bedroom.

src: walk end of patio door on right second room on right into bedroom
tgt: Walk to the end of the patio and enter the door on your right. Walk to the second room on the right. Walk into the bedroom.

src: through green door left of bedroom past door on right picture on wall bedroom with quilted blanket
tgt: Go through the green door to the left of the bedroom. Go past the door on the right and the picture on the wall. Enter the bedroom with the quilted blanket.

src: turn right through first entry way on left left of table through left entry way move between stairs wall toward door next plant into room with chairs at table stop
tgt: Turn right and go through the first entry way on your left. Go to the left of the table, through the left entry way, and move between the stairs and the wall to go toward the door next to the plant. Walk into the room with the two chairs at a table, and stop.

src: head toward room with table chairs then chandelier head opening on left in front of stars on doorway on into room in front of table chairs
tgt: Head toward the room with the table and chairs and then go left to the chandelier.  Head to the opening on the left and go in front of the stars and continue on to the doorway.  Continue on into the sitting room and stop in front of the table and two chairs.

src: walk out of kitchen turn past table chairs turn down steps hallway in front of table chairs
tgt: Walk out of the kitchen and turn left. Walk past the table and chairs and turn left. Walk down the steps and left down the hallway. Stop in front of the table and chairs.

src: stairs hard left at top of landing up stairs wait on third step from top landing
tgt: Walk up stairs. Make a hard left at the top of the landing. Walk up stairs. Wait on the third step from the top landing.

src: down hall black set of stairs ahead up top of stairs banister next set of stairs upper level of house
tgt: Walk down the hall towards the black set of stairs ahead. Walk up to the top of the stairs. Turn around the banister and continue up the next set of stairs to the upper level of the house.

src: stairs ahead then until fourth step top then stop
tgt: Go up the stairs straight ahead then turn left and continue going up until you get to the fourth step to the top then stop.

src: walk through doorway second left then middle walkway turn in front wooden stand
tgt: Walk through the doorway second the left. Then walk straight the middle walkway, Turn left, and stop in front the the wooden stand.

src: exit room through archway on right past dining room through next archway promptly right wait by window
tgt: Exit the room through the archway on the right, walk past the dining room. Proceed through the next archway and promptly turn right. Wait by the  window.

src: through doorway beside piano through until doorway right wait beside window
tgt: Go through the doorway beside the piano. Continue through until you pass another doorway. Turn right and wait beside the window.

src: turn around down hallway first turn walk through doorway across room turn white table stop by wicker chair
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hallway, taking the first left turn. Walk straight through the doorway and across the room. Turn left passed the white table and stop by the wicker chair.

src: away from bedroom straight left into doorway on left straight through room then just counter with horse statue on left then
tgt: Facing away from the bedroom, go straight, make a left into the doorway on the left, and go straight through the room, then just passed the counter with the horse statue on it make a left and then stop.

src: down hall turn forward into room turn after horse sculpture in front of chair with rounded arms
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn left. Walk forward into the room. Turn left after the horse sculpture. Stop in front of the chair with the rounded arms.

src: walk along glass dividing first office desk desk walk towards purple egg on ground up printer on wall next stone support walls
tgt: Walk along the glass dividing  passed the first office desk. Turn around the desk and walk towards the purple egg on the ground. Walk up to the printer on the wall next to the stone support walls.

src: turn conference room right head forward past desk on left start left toward white bookcase white bookcase behind so in between table photocopier at destination
tgt: Turn around to where there is a conference room to your right and head forward. When you get past the desk on your left start to head left toward a white bookcase. When you get to the white bookcase go behind it so you are in between a table and a photocopier. You are at your destination.

src: into large room towards copy macine wiat there
tgt: Go into the large room towards the copy macine, and wiat there.

src: walk forward hallway upon hallway right through doorway then right again bathroom wait just inside door
tgt: Walk forward to exit the hallway. Upon exiting the hallway, turn right to step through the doorway, and then turn right again to enter the bathroom. Wait just inside the door.

src: room at end of hallway right right into room next glass unit
tgt: Go to the room at the end of the hallway and make a right.  Turn right into the room and stop next to the glass shelving unit.

src: walk down tile hall right right again into door right of plants in room next shelf
tgt: Walk straight down tile hall. Turn right and Turn right again into door right of plants. Stop in room next to glass shelf.

src: walk out of bathroom then out of second room turn room right in front of
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom then walk out of the second room. Turn left and enter the room right in front of you.

src: exit room then next room with white lounge chairs then into room of corner door just inside next screened area
tgt: Exit the room then exit the next room with two white lounge chairs. Then turn left and go into the room of the corner door. Stop just inside, next to the screened area.

src: exit room straight next room too turn then left again into second room on left wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room. Continue going straight and exit the next room too. Turn left and then turn left again into the second room on the left. Wait at the entrance.

src: turn hallway then up stairs then along hall right bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Turn left and enter the hallway.  Then turn left and walk up the stairs then along the hall.  Turn right and enter the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: stairs turn stairs on left down hallway then right into bathroom on right wait near sink
tgt: Go down the stairs turn left and go up the stairs on the left. Walk down the hallway then turn right and go into the bathroom on the right. Wait near the sink.

src: stairs left left stairs down hallway first right into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Go down three stairs, and take a left. Take a left, and go up three stairs, and down a hallway. take the first right into the bathroom. Stop in front of the sink.

src: right staircase once top
tgt: Go up the right staircase and stop once you reach the top.

src: stairs once top
tgt: Go up the stairs and stop once reaching the top.

src: walk staircase left up stairs at third step from top
tgt: Walk to the staircase that curves to the left. Walk up the stairs and stop at the third step from the top.

src: exit bedroom through door on left right travel past stairs forward through door past small red chair wait near thermostat on wall
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door on the left, turn right and travel past the stairs, continue forward through the door and past the small red chair, wait near the thermostat on the wall.

src: bedroom right straight towards large windows at end of bedroom before platform bed on
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Walk straight towards the large windows at the end of the bedroom. Stop before you reach the platform the bed is on.

src: straight room then right after jacuzzi stop near bed
tgt: Go straight and exit the room and then turn right and after you pass the jacuzzi stop near the bed.

src: bathroom right then left reception area walk in direction of elevators before next plant at by stairs
tgt: Leave the bathroom and take a right, then a left and enter the reception area. Walk in the direction of the elevators and stop before you reach them. You should be next to the plant at by the stairs.

src: turn walk through door with red plaque immediate right walk through open door walk towards staircase stop near counter top
tgt: Turn and walk through the door with the red plaque. Take an immediate right and walk through the open door. Walk towards the staircase and stop near the counter top.

src: exit room right room across hall walk past staircase stop before counter
tgt: Exit the room to the right and enter the room across the hall. Walk past the staircase and stop before reaching the counter.

src: exit room right hallway before large mirror on right turn wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Turn right. Go down the hallway. Before you get to the large mirror on the right. Turn left. Wait there.

src: bedroom right hall kitchen through first door on left
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Go down the hall and enter the kitchen through the first door on your left.

src: turn then right down hallway at mirror turn kitchen at entryway by cabinet
tgt: Turn around, then turn right and walk down the hallway. At the mirror turn left to enter the kitchen. Stop at the entryway by the cabinet.

src: enter room right then right again into bathroom wait near tub
tgt: Enter the room. Turn right and then right again. Go into the bathroom and wait near the tub.

src: enter building wait in en suite bathroom
tgt: Enter the building and wait in the en suite bathroom.

src: enter bedroom right first door on right bathroom in front of bathtub
tgt: Enter the bedroom.  Turn right, and take the first door on the right to enter the bathroom.  Stop in front of the bathtub.

src: down carpeted staircase down marble steps turn red carpet down hallway through double doors wait near area right
tgt: Walk down the carpeted staircase and down the three marble steps. Turn left and follow the red carpet down the hallway through the double doors. Wait near the sitting area to the right.

src: stairs left hall sitting room with lamp next fireplace on left
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. Go down the hall and enter the sitting room. Stop with the lamp next to the fireplace on your left.

src: down stairs at bottom turn until clock door left of clock straight end of rug turn room on other side of rope in front of small table with chairs
tgt: Walk down the stairs. At the bottom turn left and walk until you reach the clock. Enter the door to the left of the clock. Walk straight to the end of the rug and turn left to enter the room on the other side of the rope. Stop in front of the small table with 2 chairs.

src: turn right up stairs second level walk forward through door stop
tgt: Turn right and walk up the stairs to the second level. Walk forward through the door and stop.

src: stairs into bedroom at top of stairs in doorway bedroom
tgt: Go up the stairs. Go into the bedroom at the top of the stairs. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: up stairs first room at top in doorway of room
tgt: Walk up the stairs and enter the first room at the top.  Stop in the doorway of this room.

src: step forward same closet door step through doorway laundry room then right forward small hallway then left step for into kitchen
tgt: Step forward towards the same closet door.  Step through the doorway and enter the laundry room then turn to your right. Proceed forward and enter the small hallway and then turn to your left.  Step for into the kitchen.

src: walk towards laundry room right through doorway turn dining room
tgt: Walk straight towards the laundry room, turn right, walk through the doorway, turn left, and enter the dining room.

src: exit closet by between hanging shirts on left cabinet right bearing right enter hallway then several steps forward until even with dark wood wall on left stop wait
tgt: Exit the closet by walking between the hanging shirts on your left and the cabinet to the right. Bearing to the right enter the hallway and then turn left. Take several steps forward until you're even with the dark wood wall on your left and stop and wait.

src: exit bathroom right stairs wait at end
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and go down the stairs. Wait at the end.

src: walk out of room right into hallway right at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk out of the room and turn right. Walk into the hallway and turn right. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: look at open doorway outside out of bathroom head through on left double door on right pathway towards rectangular window right towards rectangular window once at window right steps once bottom of steps kitchen on right destination
tgt: Look at the open doorway outside leading out of the bathroom and head through it. On the left there is a double door and on the right is a pathway towards a rectangular window; take the right towards the rectangular window. Once at the window, turn right and head down the steps. Once you've reached the bottom of the steps and see a kitchen on your right, you've reached your destination.

src: down steps past glass door right past sliding glass door turn by dining room table chairs
tgt: Walk down the steps past the glass door and turn right. Walk past the sliding glass door and turn left. Stop by the dining room table and chairs.

src: continue stairs straight ahead towards glass door in front of right at end of breakfast bar walk with bar stools on right glass door on left up kitchen table on left next there
tgt: Continue walking down the stairs, and walk straight ahead towards the sliding glass door in front of you.  Turn right at the end of the breakfast bar, and walk with the bar stools on your right and the sliding glass door on your left.  Walk up to the kitchen table on your left, and when you are standing next to it, stop there.

src: turn bottom of steps walk into kitchen right along bar then left side of table
tgt: Turn around and go to the bottom of the steps. Walk into the kitchen and turn right. Walk along the bar and then turn left and stop to the left side of the table.

src: stairs bottom of stairs right end of hall right again then in bedroom wait
tgt: Continue down the stairs.  When you get to the bottom of the stairs, turn right and go to the end of the hall.  Turn right again and then you will be in a bedroom.  Stop there and wait.

src: down small stairs right towards portrait right again inside bedroom
tgt: Walk down the small stairs, turn right and walk towards the portrait. Turn right again and wait inside the bedroom.

src: stairs right hall right into bedroom wait by drawer
tgt: Go down the stairs, turn right, go down the hall and turn right into the bedroom, wait by the drawer.

src: turn long hallway near last door
tgt: Turn left and go down the long hallway. Stop near the last door.

src: walk past stairs on right past room on left past wall mural of vineyard on left wait under pendant light from ceiling
tgt: Walk past stairs on the right. Walk past dining room on the left. Walk past wall mural of vineyard on the left. Wait under the pendant light hanging from the ceiling.

src: move past staircase on right wait in narrow hallway between paintings on wall
tgt: Move past the staircase on the right wait in the narrow hallway between the two paintings on the wall.

src: up first flight of stairs top then second flight of stairs on left sharp right around stair case through doorway on left back doorway straight ahead in front of stairs
tgt: Walk up the first flight of stairs to the top, then walk up the second flight of stairs on your left. Take a sharp right around the stair case, and walk through the doorway on your left. Walk back out the doorway, and stop straight ahead in front of the stairs.

src: head stairs up set of stairs left wait at hallway immediate right of stairs
tgt: Head up the stairs and up the set of stairs to the left.    wait at the hallway to the immediate right of the stairs.

src: turn stairs turn at landing continue turn at top of stairs through entryway
tgt: Turn around and go up the stairs. Turn left at the landing and continue going up. Turn left at the top of the stairs and go through entryway.

src: down stairs hard right then in doorway on right
tgt: Walk down the stairs and turn hard right. Then stop in the doorway on the right.

src: stairs quick right that quick right straight ahead until arcade machine on right after arcade machine wait by door
tgt: Go down the stairs and make a quick right. Following that, make another quick right and continue straight ahead  until you see the arcade machine on your right. After you pass the arcade machine, wait by the door.

src: stairs right parallel stairs past pool table in doorway of bedroom left of arcade machine
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn right.  Walk parallel to the stairs and past the pool table and stop in the doorway of the bedroom to the left of the arcade machine.

src: walk behind black leather chairs right doors through door on left as through door on left left walk area into kitchen turn at fridgerator walk into laundry area there next sink on right
tgt: Walk straight behind the two black leather chairs. To your right there will be two doors. Walk through the door on your left. As you walk through the door on the left make a left and walk passed the sitting area and into the kitchen. Turn left at the fridgerator and walk into the laundry area. Wait there next to the sink on your right.

src: stand with door outside right room through door next wooden table after through doorway straight down stairs turn walk area turn at fridge stand in front of sink stop
tgt: Stand with the door going outside to your right and leave the room through the door next to the wooden table.  After going through the doorway, go straight down some stairs and turn left.  Walk to the kitchen area and turn left at the fridge.  Stand in front of the sink and stop.

src: walk across room into doorway right of white desk turn walk straight through area at refrigerator turn striaght into laundry room wait by sink
tgt: Walk across the room into the doorway to the right of the white desk. Turn left and walk straight through the kitchen area. At the refrigerator, turn left. Walk striaght into the laundry room. Wait by the sink.

src: straight down hallway on slight left walk until large room with square design on floor turn into first room on left wait at entrance
tgt: Go straight and down the hallway on the slight left. Walk until you get to a large room with a square design on the floor. Turn left and go into the first room on the left. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk straight across room out left side down hallway until room with doors turn door far left once inside
tgt: Walk straight across the room and out the left side. Walk down the hallway until you reach the room with the doors and turn left. Enter the door to the far left and stop once inside.

src: walk across room past divider hall turn at foyer massage room on left
tgt: Walk across the room past the divider.  Continue to walk done the hall and turn left at the foyer.  Enter the massage room on the left.

src: exit closet into bedroom then towards door on opposite side into hallway straight down then right other bedroom from door ahead other bedroom
tgt: Exit the closet into the bedroom, then continue towards the door on the opposite side and go out into the hallway. Go straight down and then right and enter the other bedroom from the door ahead to the other bedroom.

src: turn closet into door on left of bed right exit into hallway stairs into bedroom at end of hallway turn in bedroom
tgt: Turn around, exit the closet and go into the door on the left of the bed. Go right and exit into the hallway, go passed the stairs and go into the bedroom at the end of the hallway. Turn left and stop in the bedroom.

src: left through closet door on bedroom left rail first bedroom untill end bedroom on left right doorway
tgt: Take a left through the closet door, continue on, exit the bedroom, take a left around the rail, pass the first bedroom and keep going untill you come to the end bedroom on your left, stop right when you enter the doorway.

src: turn right steps walk right behind desks long wooden table beside ping pong table
tgt: Turn right and go up the steps. Walk to the right behind the 2 desks. Stop when reach the long wooden table beside the ping pong table.

src: stairs on right side of small blackboard then straight table in center of room after at table walk office chair in front of computer then straight back past hallway on right long table behind of ping pong table stop wait
tgt: Go up the stairs on the right side of the small blackboard then walk straight to the table in the center of the room. After you are at the table walk to the office chair in front of the computer; then walk straight back past the hallway on the right. When you get to the long table behind of the ping pong table stop and wait.

src: head stairs straight past first tables at third table
tgt: Head up the stairs, go straight past the first two tables and stop at the third table.

src: up steps into bathroom enter bedroom on right next too bookcase
tgt: Walk down hall up steps and turn left into bathroom. Enter bedroom on the right and stop next too bookcase.

src: down hallway towards stairs first room on top of stairs while in front of sink right after into bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hallway towards the stairs and go up them.  Enter the first room on the top of the stairs.  While standing in front of the sink, turn right and stop after walking into the bedroom.

src: down hallway up stairs turn into bathroom right in bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hallway and up the stairs. Turn left and walk into the bathroom. Turn right and stop in the bedroom.

src: stairs out of bathroom left into bedroom stairs on second stair
tgt: Go up the stairs out of the bathroom and take a left into the bedroom going down the stairs stopping on the second stair going down.

src: walk through room bathroom walk around corner towards staircase before stairs downward
tgt: Walk through the room passed the bathroom. Walk around the corner towards the staircase. Stop before the stairs leading downward.

src: left away from bathroom head staircase staircase until
tgt: Go to the left, away from the bathroom.  and head to the staircase.  You'll go down the staircase until you down it.  That's where you will wait.

src: walks fridge on left straight into hallway wait near large vase
tgt: Walks straight and pass the fridge on the left. Go straight into the hallway and wait near the large vase.

src: wall toward kitchen past then left wait at vanity
tgt: Wall toward kitchen and past it, then make a left, and wait at vanity.

src: dining room kitchen kitchen through door on left of oven once hallway
tgt: Leave the dining room, and enter the kitchen. Leave the kitchen through the door on the left of the oven. Stop once you enter the hallway.

src: walk out of bedroom sharp turn right just inside laundry room
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and make a sharp turn right. Stop just inside the laundry room.

src: walk through living room area past couch through open wooden door with painting on wall nearby into walkway on other side right hall painting on wall walk into open door small room with washer dryer
tgt: Walk through the living room area past the couch and through the open wooden door with a painting on the wall nearby. walk into the walkway on the other side and turn right to walk down the hall passing a painting on the wall. Walk into the open door that leads to a small room with a washer and dryer.

src: stand with shelves on right out of room right few steps then right again into laundry room in front of washer dryer
tgt: Stand with the shelves on your right and walk out of the room.  Turn right and take a few steps and then turn right again into the laundry room.  Stop in front of the washer and dryer.

src: bathroom through bedroom hallway in hallway right right in office first room on right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go through the bedroom to the hallway. In the hallway take a right and take another right in the office which is the first room on the right.

src: turn right bathroom bedroom via left door right along hallway wait by first door right
tgt: Turn right and exit the bathroom. Exit the bedroom via the left door. Turn right and walk along the hallway. Wait by the first door to your right.

src: walk out door out bedroom door hallway right down hallway wait by next door on right
tgt: Walk out the door.  Walk out the bedroom door to the hallway. Turn right and walk down the hallway. Wait by the next door on your right.

src: exit bathroom bed turn at brown double doors stop
tgt: Exit bathroom, go passed bed, turn left at brown double doors and stop.

src: exit bathroom stand in bedroom doorway
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Go stand in the bedroom doorway.

src: bathroom walk through bedroom room next door turn towards door into hallway in doorway with flowers in front of mirror right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk through the bedroom to the sitting room next door.  Turn left and go towards the door into the hallway.  Stop in this doorway with some flowers in front of a mirror to your right.

src: exit laundry room walk left through archway toward kitchen walk past telephone turn into first room on left through second set of doors next second wine shelf
tgt: Exit the laundry room and walk to your left.  Go through the archway toward the kitchen.  Walk past the telephone and turn left into the first room on your left.  Walk through the second set of doors and stop next to the second wine shelf.

src: exit laundry room turn left into kitchen area turn through door into long room with lot of wine of shelves about feet into room
tgt: Exit the laundry room and turn left. Go into the kitchen area. Turn left and go through the door into the long room with a lot of wine of the shelves. Stop about five feet into the room.

src: room into kitchen into first room on left until into room with wine bottles in middle of floor across from small picture on wall
tgt: Leave the room. Continue left into the kitchen. Go into the first room on the left and keep going until you go into the room with the wine bottles. Stop in the middle of the floor across from the small picture on the wall.

src: walk forward down hallway next hall past area first right into bedroom once past door
tgt: Walk forward down the hallway. Go down the next hall past the sitting area. Take the first right into the bedroom and stop once you are past the door.

src: walk through hall across room walk into hallway right in front of chair
tgt: Walk through the hall and across the room. Walk into the hallway and turn right. Stop in front of the chair.

src: turn around straight across right into bedroom wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk straight across. Take a right into the bedroom and wait there.

src: walk forward then right hallway way end turn into last door on left stop
tgt: Walk forward and then turn right to head down the hallway. Walk all the way to the end and turn into the last door on the left and stop.

src: walk past framed wall art on left right just before open bedroom door walk past area rug on floor wait at threshold of open door on left
tgt: Walk past the framed wall art on the left. Make a right just before the open bedroom door. Walk past the area rug on the floor. Wait at the threshold of the open door on the left.

src: few steps forward then right down hallway past hutch frames on wall first door on left
tgt: Take a few steps forward then turn right. Walk down the hallway, past the hutch and the three frames on the wall, and go to the first door on your left.

src: walk straight until couches on left turn room double doors wait at entrance
tgt: Walk straight until you pass the couches on your left. Turn left and exit the room using the double doors. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk forward turn at chairs wait at doorway
tgt: Walk forward turn left at the chairs, wait at the doorway.

src: turn around towards double door with glass on left inside door frame
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the double door with the glass on the left. Stop inside the door frame.

src: walk around table chairs toward steps up fourth step stop
tgt: Walk around the table and chairs and toward the steps. Walk up to the fourth step and stop.

src: walk past table staircase up few steps wait here
tgt: Walk past dining table to the staircase.  Walk up a few steps.  Wait here.

src: plant of floor staircase stairs
tgt: Go to the plant of the floor. Go to the staircase. Go up three stairs.

src: walk through doorway next black white art piece into hallway first left in hallway toward bathroom outside closet doorway on left
tgt: Walk through the doorway next to the black and white art piece and into the hallway.  Take the first left in the hallway toward the bathroom, but stop outside the closet doorway on the left.

src: head hallway near end stop in alcove on left outside closet bathroom
tgt: Head down the hallway. Near the end, stop in the alcove on the left outside the closet and bathroom.

src: walk past laundry room into bedroom turn in hallway
tgt: Walk past the laundry room into the bedroom. Turn left and stop in the hallway.

src: turn left kitchen walk through sitting room stop at end in front of door residence
tgt: Turn to your left and exit the kitchen. Walk through the sitting room and stop at the end in front of the door that says residence one.

src: walk forward until white door
tgt: walk forward until you reach the white door.

src: door outside beside large grey couch
tgt: Go to the door that leads outside beside the large grey couch.

src: down stair right towards statue stairs toward stained glass windows staircase walk hanging light
tgt: walk down the stair. turn right. walk towards the statue and go down the stairs. walk toward the stained glass windows. keep walking down the staircase.  walk to the hanging light.

src: first down stairs stop after turn right degrees forward until bookshelf then degrees right straight then after bust turn right degrees once before stairs
tgt: First walk down 2 stairs. Stop and after turn to your right 90 degrees. Walk forward until you get to the bookshelf then turn 90 degrees to your right. Walk straight and then after the bust turn to the right 90 degrees once more before descending down the stairs.

src: turn right stairs then right stairs on stairs near window
tgt: Turn right and go down the stairs.  Then turn right and go down the stairs stopping on the stairs near the window.

src: walk past square mosaic right hallway through opening in o'clock position into room with beds so beds left mirror in front of into room right of mirror in doorway
tgt: Walk past the square mosaic and go right down the hallway.  Go through the opening in the 11 o'clock position and into the room with the three beds.  Stand so they the beds are to your left and the mirror is in front of you.  Walk into the room to the right of the mirror and stop in the doorway.

src: walk forward end of mosaic tiles on floor right walk end of passage turn room right forward until doorway right of mirror
tgt: Walk forward to the end of the mosaic tiles on the floor and turn right. Walk to the end of this passage and turn left, entering the room. Turn right and  walk forward until you reach the doorway to the right of the mirror.

src: walk corner diagonal right down hallway forward across foyer area doorway in front of on right in doorway
tgt: Walk to the corner diagonal to where you are. Turn right and walk down the hallway and continue forward across the foyer area and go to the doorway in front of you on the right. Stop in the doorway.

src: head stairs right in front of doorway by plant
tgt: Head up the stairs, turn right and stop in front of the doorway by the plant.

src: up stairs wait at potted plant on landing
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Wait at the potted plant on the landing.

src: continue stairs then right wait by plant
tgt: Continue going up the stairs and then turn right and wait by the plant.

src: turn down hallway then next hallway then again forward stop near door
tgt: Turn left and walk down the hallway, then proceed down the next hallway. Then turn left again and walk forward and stop near the door.

src: head hallway until hallway on left turn then hallway into first office on right wait there
tgt: Head down the hallway until you get to a hallway on the left and turn left then head down the hallway and turn into the first office on the right and wait there.

src: down hallway lights same way as hall past doorways turn at exit sign in first doorway on right
tgt: walk down the hallway where the lights are faced the same way as the hall, walk past two doorways and turn left at the exit sign, stop in the first doorway on your right.

src: kitchen right into hallway in hall right into den then left into dining room in dining room next door near vent in floor
tgt: Leave the kitchen and take a right into the hallway. In the hall take the right into the den, then a left into the dining room. In the dining room stop next to the door near the vent in the floor.

src: door right into door hallway first right into room with lots of chairs turn into room with door handles on wall
tgt: Go out the door and turn right. Go into the door that leads to a hallway. Take the first right into the room with lots of chairs. Turn left and go into the room with door handles on the wall.

src: turn around out of room right into hallway first right next long table
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the room. Take a right into a hallway and take your first right. Wait next to the long table.

src: exit bedroom turn down stairs stairs at bottom of stairs straight by counter on right
tgt: Exit bedroom, turn left, walk down stairs, continue down stairs, at the bottom of the stairs go straight and stop by the counter on the right.

src: room stairs at right stairs at bottom of stairs left into kitchen in kitchen just before counter with blue top
tgt: Leave the room and go down the stairs. At the landing take a right and continue down the stairs. At the bottom of the stairs take a left into the kitchen. In the kitchen stop just before you reach the counter with the blue top.

src: stairs first landing right next set of stairs down right until at bottom of stairs near mirror turn feet
tgt: Go down the stairs to the first landing. Continue right down the next set of stairs. Go down and right until at the bottom of stairs near the mirror. Turn left and walk 3 feet.

src: walk bottom of stairs turn left then stairs landing around half way up second set of stairs
tgt: Walk to the bottom of the stairs and turn left. Then walk up the stairs to the landing and turn around and walk half way up the second set of stairs.

src: dining room walking in direction away from living room staircase with wooden stairs glass walls first flight of stairs on landing second flight of stairs just before top of second flight of stairs
tgt: Leave the dining room walking in the direction away from the living room.  Go up the staircase with the wooden stairs and glass walls.  Go up the first flight of stairs and turn around on the landing to start to go up the second flight of stairs.  Stop just before you reach the top of the second flight of stairs.

src: walk past table right left up stairs turn stairs at fifth step
tgt: Walk past the table and turn right. Turn left and walk up the stairs. Turn left and continue walking up the stairs. Stop at the fifth step.

src: walk through open double entry doors home turn through first arched door with statue bust near doorway walk into hallway
tgt: Walk through the open double entry doors to the home. Turn left and walk through the first arched door with an statue bust near the doorway. Walk into the hallway.

src: enter building first left in first doorway
tgt: Enter the building, take the first left and stop in the first doorway.

src: turn right building turn doorway wait there
tgt: Turn right and enter the building. Turn left and enter the closest and leftmost doorway. Wait there.

src: up stairs walk hallway up stairs on fourth step
tgt: Walk up the stairs and walk left down the hallway. Walk up the stairs and stop on the fourth step.

src: turn around up stairs out of bathroom turn up stairs wait on second step from top
tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs and out of the bathroom. Turn left. Walk up the stairs and wait on the second step from the top.

src: stairs bathroom stairs in bedroom on fourth stair from bottom
tgt: Go up the stairs and leave the bathroom. Go up the stairs in the bedroom. Stop on the fourth stair from the bottom.

src: turn wait at top of stairs on left
tgt: Turn left. Wait at the top of the stairs on the left.

src: turn walk bar stop at top of steps on left
tgt: Turn left walk to the bar and stop at the top of the steps on the left.

src: turn past kitchen turn at microwave area at top of stairs wait right there
tgt: Turn left and go past the kitchen.  Turn Left at the microwave area.  You will be at the top of the stairs.  Wait right there.

tgt: Walk past the two chairs on the left and down the hall to the left of the fireplace. Turn left at the first doorway where a handicap sign will be on your left. enter the bedroom and stop before you make it to the bed.

src: turn fireplace head out of room hallway on left first room on left with handicap sign once room
tgt: Turn and face the fireplace. Head out of the room to the hallway on your left. Enter the first room on your left with the handicap sign. Stop once you have entered the room.

src: pass bear fireplace turn right in hallway after in first door
tgt: Pass the bear and when you get to the fireplace turn left. Turn right in the hallway and stop after you turn left in first door.

src: stairs double doorway right of front doorway through doorway left into roped area next table stop
tgt: Go down stairs, go to the double doorway to the right of the front doorway, go through that doorway, make a left into the roped area and next to the table and stop.

src: down steps left into double doors on right walk in front of table
tgt: Walk down the steps and to the left. Walk into the double doors on the right. Walk left and stop in front of the table.

src: down stairs into doorway on left between chairs table on left stop
tgt: Walk down the stairs, and go into the doorway on the left. Go between the chairs and the table on the left and stop.

src: walk through door up stairs
tgt: Walk through the door.  Walk up the stairs.

src: exit bedroom toward right hall stone tile stairs left brown dresser with glass vase on top end in doorway area closed doors on left entry way room
tgt: Exit the bedroom and move toward the right down the hall. Go up the stone tile stairs and make a left when you see the brown dresser with the glass vase on top end in the doorway area where there are two closed doors on your left and the entry way to the sitting room.

src: exit bedroom turn hallway right straight towards steps steps turn at top of stairs immediate left into first room once inside room
tgt: Exit bedroom, turn left, enter hallway, turn right, move straight towards steps, go up the steps, turn left at the top of the stairs, take immediate left into first room, stop once inside the room.

tgt: Walk upstairs, onto the balcony.  Once you reach the top walk in between the pillars and into the doorway leading to inside.  Wait by the polka dot chair.

src: stairs right house before rug
tgt: Continue up the stairs and take a right, Enter the house and stop before you reach the rug.

src: turn around up stairs walk into house wait next foot rest with cow skin
tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs. Walk into the house and wait next to the foot rest with the cow skin.

tgt: Exit the closet. Turn right. Turn slightly left and go into the hallway. Pass the chair on the right and continue straight into the room. Wait there.

tgt: Leave the laundry room, and go right. Go down the hallway on the left. Go into the bedroom at the end of the hall on the right. Stop in the doorway.

src: closet right room veer hallway bedroom on right on wall straight ahead once in bedroom
tgt: Leave the closet, and take a right. Leave the room, and veer left down the hallway. Enter the bedroom on the right on the wall straight ahead. Stop once you are in the bedroom.

src: hard right then stairs stop
tgt: Turn hard right, then walk up two stairs and stop.

src: stairs steps up
tgt: Start up the stairs and stop two steps up.

src: walk parallel stairs hallway guitar turn stairs on second stair from bottom
tgt: Walk parallel to the stairs and straight down the hallway.  When you get to the guitar, turn and go up the stairs, stopping on the second stair from the bottom.
