tgt: With the painting of the seascape to your right and the farm scene to your left, go forward, then through the arched opening to your left. Upon entering the kitchen, go to the right and past the kitchen. Looking ahead, you'll see a fireplace. On the same wall as the fireplace, there will be an arched opening to the left of the fireplace. Head to that opening and go through it. After passing through the arched opening, go through the door opening to your left.

tgt: Take a left through the archway on your left going away from the door. Walk past the kitchen and living room. Enter the archway on your left. Take a left into the bedroom and stop in the doorway.

tgt: Walk through the kitchen past the bar stools.  When you get to the dining table, walk toward the long white couch.  Stop in front of the dark pillows on the end closest to you.

tgt: Orient yourself so when you go forward, you'll pass by with the kitchen island on your right, then move forward towards the fireplace in the distance. Once you move onto the carpet, stop and move slightly left to get even with the corner of the table.

src: left walk straight bar into living room walk corner of long white couch on left stop
tgt: Go left and walk straight passed the bar and into the living room. Walk to the corner of the long white couch on your left and stop.

tgt: Walk towards the stairs and continue up the steps. At the top of the first flight of steps, turn right towards the bedroom. Stop just after entering the bedroom.

tgt: Go up the stairs and then at the top of the stairs, turn right and stop near the bed.

tgt: Walk up the stairs and make a sharp turn right. Stop in front of the end table.

tgt: Exit the balcony and go through the living room. Walk up the four steps and stop.

tgt: Pass through the kitchen, make the first right into the gym and wait near the television.

tgt: Turn let and go through the kitchen. Turn left and go past the table and chairs. Turn right and go into the mini gym. Wait near the treadmill.

src: turn stairs at top of stairs right proceed left of pool table between pool table multicade game

tgt: Walk through the kitchen, past the sink, then stop in the doorway of the room on the left.

tgt: Go to the refrigerator. Go to the sink. Go to the dishwasher. Go to the dining room door.

tgt: Turn left and enter the door straight ahead. Stop once you enter the door.

src: hallway past stairs doors before door bathroom
tgt: Go down the hallway, past the stairs and two doors. Stop before entering the door to the bathroom.

tgt: Walk past the stairs and stop in front of the pulp fiction poster.

tgt: After you pass the stairs turn right and wait in the hallway.

src: stairs right right hall once in hallway

src: bedroom left stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a left. Go down the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit room turn stairs then
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go down the stairs then stop.

src: exit bedroom turn down stairs wait at bottom

src: forward toward stairs end of hall in doorway right
tgt: Walk forward toward the stairs. Go to the end of the hall. Stop in the doorway to the right.

src: walk through doorway turn in front of marble counter
tgt: Walk through the doorway, turn left and stop in front of the marble counter.

src: exit bedroom right wait at immediate door on right in from of bedroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom and take a right.  Wait at the immediate door on the right - in from of another bedroom.

src: walk out of bedroom right past chairs right in doorway of bedroom

tgt: Turn around and walk out of the room. Take a right at the chairs and wait in the doorway of the the room on the right.

src: down hall right in front of chair
tgt: Walk down the hall and to the right and stop in front of the chair.

tgt: Move forward to the wall adjacent to the doorway.  Turn to face the doorway.  Move through the door way toward the stairs.  Keep moving until you are on the second step of the stairs and then stop.

tgt: TURN RIGHT TO FACE A HALLWAY WITH A PICTURE ON THE RIGHT AND AN OPENING ON THE LEFT, WALK DOWN THE HALLWAY PAST THE OPENING ON THE LEFT, CONTINUE FORWARD DOWN THE HALL PAST THE BLACK COUCH ON THE RIGHT AND STOP AT THE END OF THE COUCH NEAR A PILLAR ON THE RIGHT.

src: down hallway right portrait of christian first supper walk couches stop near granite counter top near couch area
tgt: Walk down the hallway to the right passed the portrait of the christian first supper. Walk passed the couches an stop near the closest granite counter top near the couch area.

tgt: Turn right and go down the hallway.  Go past the couch.  Stop and wait right by the pillar.

tgt: Turn around and walk forward to the end and then turn left and enter the bedroom. Once in the room, walk to the right side of the room past the fireplace and then enter the door on your right. Stop in the doorway.

tgt: Go to the front of the suitcases. Go into the bedroom. Go to the footstool. Go to the left side of the fireplace.

tgt: Walk straight out of the bathroom past the dresser on the left. Turn left and walk into the room. Turn right and go out the room using the door on the right. Wait in the hallway.

tgt: Walk past the bookshelves and turn left. Turn left and stop in front of the chair.

tgt: Walk towards the bookshelft to your right, and walk all the way around it...Taking two lefts. Stop in front of the chair thats next to the window.

tgt: Go straight around this path of bookshelves, making two hard lefts and stopping at the large shelf in between two windows.

src: walk across room past fireplace in front of white table directly behind dog statue so that tail at
tgt: Walk across the room past the fireplace and stop in front of the white table directly behind the dog statue so that the tail is pointing at you.

src: head straight fireplace dog statue wait by work desk
tgt: Head straight and pass the fireplace, pass the dog statue and wait by the work desk.

src: walk toward fireplace past armchairs workbench next piece of equipment in front of workbench
tgt: Walk toward the fireplace and past the armchairs to the workbench.  Stop next to the piece of equipment in front of the workbench.

tgt: With the fireplace towards your right side, enter the room ahead and exit the next room via the rightmost opening on the opposite wall. Continue forward until the carpet ends, then go past the rope barrier to your right and wait on the carpet to the right of the fireplace.

tgt: Walk down the right side of the hallway. Enter through the doorway on the right. Continue walking straight. Turn right and stop at the entrance of the room next to the rope partition.

tgt: Turn left and then wait next to the fire place on the right.

tgt: Walk along the pool toward the sliding glass doors on the right. Proceed past the pillar and the planters into the building. Wait on the rug by the sliding glass doors.

src: along pool into glass doors step in then
tgt: Go along the pool into the sliding glass doors, take a step in and then stop.

src: straight pool on right into glass doors there near round table
tgt: Go straight and pass the pool on the right. Go into the glass sliding doors and wait there near the round table.

tgt: Turn around and walk to the right past the piano. Walk to the right side of the large column and stop when you reach the first set of benches along the wall.

tgt: Moving away from the alter area, bear left and go between the alter and the pulpit. Jump over the rail and go around the column down the right wall. SIt in the first pew you come to on the left hand side of it.

tgt: Walk out of bedroom, cross hall and enter bedroom, stop on couch.

tgt: exit the bedroom and walk forward to the next bedroom, stop near the bed.

tgt: Exit the sitting area through the second set of doors on the right. Walk down the hall and wait in the room to the left, next to the wardrobe.

tgt: Exit the room. Turn right. Go straight toward the couches. Turn left when you get to the couch and go out the glass sliding door. Wait near the black table and chairs in the patio.

src: enter area then living room area outside on patio on left wait there
tgt: Enter the dining area and then enter the living room area. Walk outside on the patio that is on the left and wait there.

src: enter room with white table next turn right towards leather couches turn outside by glass door
tgt: Enter the room with the white table. Next turn right and walk towards the leather couches.  Turn left, and wait outside by sliding glass door.

src: exit door left right through dining area just past partition screen on right n door area
tgt: Exit the door to your left. Turn right and walk through the dining area. Just past the partition screen on the right, turn left to stand n door to kitchen area.

src: head through door opposite light switch turn head past glass table chairs head past screen step into kitchen area
tgt: Head through the door opposite the light switch.  Turn left and head past the glass table and chairs. Head past the screen. Step into the kitchen area.

tgt: Go through the doorway and turn left heading past the dinning room table.  Turn left by the glass table and stop in front of the kitchen island.

tgt: From kitchen turn right into hall, at end of hall turn right and stop at the laundry room sink.

tgt: Walk towards the table. Turn right walk through the hall. Turn right and wait by the door just before the washing machines.

src: exit kitchen right right laundry room wait near sink
tgt: Exit the kitchen to the right and make another right to enter the laundry room. Wait near the sink.

src: exit closet right into hallway right through hallway first set of steps right in doorway of workout room
tgt: Exit the closet and turn right to go into the hallway. Go right and continue through the hallway. Go up the first set of steps and turn right. Stop in the doorway of the workout room.

tgt: Turn to the right, and go out the door to the right.  Then you will go to the stairs and go up a few, but not all the way.  Then turn to the right.  You will be in a work out room.  Stop just inside of this room.

tgt: Exit the door and turn right towards another door. Walk up the stairs. Turn right and stop in front of the yoga mats.

src: head through doorway into area with large table first arched pathway on left into study/library stop
tgt: Head straight through the doorway into the area with the large table. Enter the first arched pathway on the left into the study/library and stop.

src: away from bed through door across hall walk between round rectangle tables move through first arch left of doorway before on rug
tgt: Walk away from the bed through the door across the hall. Walk between the round and rectangle tables. Move through the first arch to the left of the doorway. Stop before you step on the rug.

src: walk through door then slight left until in room with books
tgt: Walk straight through the door and then make a slight left and continue until you're in the room filled with books.

src: exit room right hallway in middle of hall
tgt: Exit the room to your right and continue down the hallway. Stop in the middle of the hall.

src: walk right through open doors hallway near stairs on left
tgt: Walk right through the open doors an enter the hallway. Stop near the stairs on your left.

src: head through open double doors straight at top of stairs
tgt: Head through the open double doors. Go straight and stop at top of the stairs.

src: bedroom right step in doorway of empty room there
tgt: Leave the bedroom and turn right.  Step in the doorway of the empty room and stop there.

src: exit bedroom right next empty bedroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right.  Stand next to the empty bedroom.

src: walk past bed bedroom right in doorway on right
tgt: Walk past the bed, and exit the bedroom, turn right and stop in the doorway on your right.

tgt: Walk through the big double doors.  Turn to the right.  And go down the hall, past the zebra pictures.  You'll enter the room with big windows and then stop and wait.

src: walk out of living room through wood glass doors right in hallway hallway on right into den through open door right past light switches
tgt: Walk out of the living room through the wood and glass doors and take a right in the hallway down the hallway on the right and go into the den through the open door and stop right past the light switches.

src: through doors right hall through next doors just inside room
tgt: Go through the two doors and move right down the hall. Go through the next two doors and stop just inside the room.

src: walk past small trunk into hallway on left through hallway into bathroom on left just inside bathroom door
tgt: Walk past the small trunk and into the hallway on the left. Walk through the hallway and into the bathroom on the left. Stop just inside the bathroom door.

tgt: Look to the left. Walk through the door on the left. Walk down the narrow hallway. Go through the last door on the left.

src: turn into hallway hallway turn in second door wait near sink
tgt: Turn left into the hallway. Go down the hallway. Turn left in the second door. Wait near the sink.

tgt: Turn around and walk past the long table and chairs.  Turn left at the end of the table and wait there before entering other doors/rooms.

src: turn right along right wall towards front doors walk towards left corner there
tgt: Turn right and walk along the right wall towards the two front facing doors. Walk towards the left corner and stay there.

tgt: Leave the bedroom, walk through the door on the right, walk towards the kitchen, and wait.

src: walk towards doorway
tgt: Walk towards the doorway.

src: hallway right once doorway at end
tgt: Go down the hallway to the right and stop once you reach the doorway at the end.

tgt: Exit the bedroom, and turn right before you reach the staircase. Walk down the black corridor to the room straight ahead. Wait in the doorway.

src: walk right past stairs in entryway at end of hall
tgt: Walk right past the stairs. Stop in the entryway at the end of the hall.

src: exit room right steps wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Turn right and go up the steps. Wait there.

src: walk out of bathroom right up first set of stairs stop
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right. Walk up the first set of stairs and stop.

src: exit door right immediately up small steps at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the door and turn right immediately. Walk up the small three steps, and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: up stairs at second step from top
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Stop at the second step from the top.

src: turn right up top of stairs
tgt: Turn right and walk up to the top of the stairs.

src: walk towards stair case stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Walk towards stair case, go up stairs, and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs into kitchen between window kitchen island chair closest fridge
tgt: Go up the stairs, into the kitchen, and stop between the window and the kitchen island chair closest to the fridge.

src: up stairs hard right turn through kitchen stop near window wall
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn hard right. Turn left through the kitchen and stop near the window wall.

src: up stairs right then around table then past stove
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn to your right.  Then walk around the table then walk past the stove.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right. Walk across the foyer to the table in the center. Turn right. Walk towards the staircase towards the right side of the entry door. Wait at the bottom of the stairway.

tgt: Go into the entry. Walk towards the table with the flower vase in the center of the entry. Stop on the second stair of the staircase that's on the right of the front door.

tgt: Walk straight past the bathtub, turn right, and exit the room out of the wooden door.  Stay right and continue past the billiard table.  Enter the doorway just beyond the wooden chair on the right.  Wait here.

src: walk towards bed out door directly across from towards stairs directly in front of chair across from stairs
tgt: Walk towards the bed, and out the door directly across from it. Walk towards the stairs, and stop directly in front of the chair across from the stairs.

tgt: Walk to the bed and turn right to exit the room. Walk to the front of the stairs and turn around. Go beside the chair to the left and stop in front of the bathroom.

src: turn past stairs hallway then bathroom on right wait by sink
tgt: Turn left and walk past the stairs heading down the hallway.  Then enter the bathroom on your right. Wait by the sink.

src: past stairs on right down hallway down hallway fireplace on right right wait near sink
tgt: Go past the stairs on the right and down the hallway. Continue going down the hallway. Pass the fireplace on the right. Turn right and wait near the sink.

src: walk towards staircase staircase on right straight hallway beside room with double doors down hallway area fireplace on right right into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Walk towards the staircase.  Continue passed the staircase on the right. Walk straight down the hallway beside the room with the double doors. Continue straight down the hallway pass the sitting area and fireplace on the right.  Turn right into the bathroom. Stop in front of the sink.

tgt: Walk straight out of the kitchen and once you reach the desk, turn around and walk outside using the door to the left of the kitchen. Once outside, turn left and walk until you step down and stop.

src: walk out of kitchen into living room right front door on porch turn steps at bottom of steps
tgt: Walk out of kitchen into living room, turn right and go out the front door. On the porch, turn left and walk down steps. Stop at bottom of steps.

tgt: Walk through the kitchen and make a u turn and walk to the porch. Once on the porch walk down the steps between the two houses.

src: turn right left into bathroom in hall near stairs
tgt: Turn right and turn left and go into the bathroom. Stop in the hall near the stairs.

src: enter room with twin beds large wall tv walk past beds into bathroom through bathroom in hallway in front of stairs
tgt: Enter the room with two twin beds and a large wall tv. Walk past the beds, into the bathroom. Go through the bathroom and stop in the hallway in front of the stairs.

tgt: Enter the door on the right, then go over the beds and through the bathroom.  Wait on the hardwood floor past the bathroom adjacent to the stairs.

src: hallway right of white couch open door first set of stairs
tgt: Follow the hallway to the right of the white couch. Enter the open door and go down the first set of stairs.

src: walk towards mirror enter room with staircase stairs turn stairs wait
tgt: Walk straight towards mirror and enter room with staircase. Go down stairs, turn left, go down stairs and wait.

tgt: Exit the office and into the hallway on the left. Turn left and wait in the bedroom at the end of the hallway.

src: office head in direction of living room on left before living room left into hallway bedroom on left of photos on wall once in room
tgt: Leave the office and head in the direction of the living room on your left. Before the living room take a left into a hallway. Enter the bedroom on the left of the photos on the wall. stop once you are in the room.

tgt: Walk out of the double doors. Make a right towards the built-in wall arch. Turn left at the hall entrance. Make a left into the room next to the wall photos.

src: turn around towards wooden cabinet at cabinet right past table stop at doorway left
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the wooden cabinet. At the cabinet, turn right and walk past the table and stop at the 2nd doorway to your left.

src: walk past table then right straight until table wait there
tgt: Walk past the table and then turn right. Go straight until you pass the table and wait there.

src: left side of dining table small vase on floor
tgt: Go to the left side of the dining table. Go to the small vase on the floor.

src: from here then right side near upstairs
tgt: Go out from here. Then take right side near upstairs.

src: theater straight counter in direction of stairs second past counter stop in sink
tgt: Leave the theater and go straight passing the counter, and moving in the direction of the stairs. Take the second left past the counter and stop in he doorway to the sink.

tgt: Leave the room through the door on the left and go straight across to the bottom of the spiral staircase, then go to the door on the right underneath the staircase.

tgt: Go forward through the door and move past the stairs. Turn right, enter the closet and wait on the other side of the door.

src: straight chairs on left right after stairs into room on right right wait in closet

tgt: Walk through the door and past the glass railing. Turn right and walk through the door. Turn right again and stop in front of the closet island.

tgt: Walk forward to the kitchen. Walk past the counter and go to the sitting area on the right. Stop at the end of the counter.

src: walk past stairs kitchen at far end of kitchen
tgt: Walk past the stairs and towards the kitchen. Stop at the far end of the kitchen.

src: stairs on left straight between living room counter along counter few steps from counter stop

tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk through the office and into the hallway. Walk through the hall and into the living room, and stop once you reach the right edge of the rug.

tgt: leave bathroom to office, walk across office to hallway, follow hallway and turn slight left, stop in living room with stairs at the right.

tgt: Walk around the glass table and out of the room. Turn left and walk towards the staircase. Stop in front of the door on your right and wait.

tgt: Walk past the kitchen into the dining area. Wait by the window at the other end of the table.

tgt: Turn to the right. Walk through the hall between the kitchen and the living area. Walk to end of hall. There should be a large wooden table at the end. Stop at the last chair on the right.

src: walk past kitchen walk past room table wait at plant
tgt: Walk past kitchen. Walk past dining room table. Wait at plant.

src: between counter white doors straight in direction until stairs first flight of stairs at first platform
tgt: Go left, between the counter and the white doors. Keep going straight in that direction until you reach the stairs. Go up the first flight of stairs and stop at the first platform.

tgt: Exit the kitchen and walk straight towards the dining table. Keep walking and turn right when you see a white chair on the left. Walk up the four stairs and stop there.

tgt: Exit the kitchen and walk past the dining area. Walk up the stairs and wait on the first landing.

src: walk through doors past bed right before black stairs
tgt: Walk through the doors and past the bed. Stop right before the black stairs.

src: turn inside past bed couch at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and go inside. Walk past the bed and couch. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: through open door on right straight then at steps
tgt: Go through the open door on the right. Keep walking straight then stop at the steps.

src: walk forward past hot tub on path towards doors in front of door on right before house
tgt: Walk forward past the hot tub and stay on the path towards the doors. Stop in front of the door on the right before you enter the house.

tgt: Turn left and walk on the path towards the pillars. Wait by the glass door entrance to the right.

src: stepping stones breezeway at black glass door
tgt: Follow the stepping stones to the breezeway. Stop at the black glass door.

src: walk through doorway right hallway right after exit sign
tgt: Walk through doorway, take a right down the hallway, stop right after the exit sign.

src: step into hallway right down hallway wait in front of door with on
tgt: Step into the hallway and turn right. Walk down the hallway and wait in front of the door with 376 on it.

src: right go.then stop at opp side room
tgt: To take right and go.Then stop at opp side room.

src: right doormat through doorway on left right at blue chair right of christmas tree at stairway at end of stained glass
tgt: Take a right to the doormat, go through the doorway on your left, take a right at the blue chair, go to the right of the christmas tree, and stop at the stairway at the end of the stained glass.

tgt: Walk through the kitchen and wait near the stairs, in the bathroom.

tgt: Walk through the only doorway in the room, then walk through the doorway on your right. Stop once you are between the doorway and the toilet in the room.

tgt: Exit the room and turn right into the bathroom. Wait by the toilet.

src: walk at door then after that door on right then that room window
tgt: Walk straight at the door, then after that you can see another door on your right then enter that room you can see the window.

tgt: Leave dining room to main lobby, walk towards main entry. Stop at entry doors.

tgt: Go out the single open door to the right of the fireplace. Go to the white table. Go in front of the door that goes outside.

tgt: Walk past the stairs and then turn left. Wait at the entrance.

tgt: Head down the hall and stop in the doorway across the hall from the stairs.

tgt: Walk up stairs, at stairs intersection turn left and go up stairs. Stop next to Monroe art.

tgt: Enter the building through the sliding glass doors, walk past the bed and turn right into the bathroom. Wait by the doorway.

src: stairs right wait in front of painting on wall
tgt: Go up the stairs and turn right. Wait in front of the painting on the wall.

src: up stairs right up rest of stairs right at top of stairs stop at base of next staircase
tgt: walk up the stairs, turn right and walk up the rest of the stairs, turn right at the top of the stairs, stop at the base of the next staircase.

tgt: Go up the stairs then turn right. Wait in front of the picture on the wall that has a white frame, white background and blue lines.

tgt: Go down stairs, walk to the back of the couch, go straight through the door way, walk to the end of the bed, walk passed the tub, straight through the door way, stop beside the door.

tgt: Walk towards the chairs. Turn left past the table. Walk through the doorway into the bedroom. Turn left. Walk past the bed towards the bathroom. Stop at the doorway to the bathroom.

tgt: Turn left, walk through the door into the bedroom, turn left again and walk across the bedroom. Wait by the bathtub.

tgt: Go upstairs and take a few steps forward on the floor and stop.

src: up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs in front of at top forward large frame
tgt: Go up the stairs in front of you. At the top, walk forward and stop facing the large frame.

src: exit bathroom then at left side door inside room wait beside bed
tgt: exit the bathroom and then at your left side there is a door, go inside that room and wait beside the bed.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and make a hard left turn to enter the bedroom to your immediate left.

src: walk out door into doorway on left right before bed
tgt: Walk out the door, and into the doorway on your left. Stop right before the bed.

src: walk towards sofa way upstairs
tgt: walk towards the sofa. go all the way upstairs.

src: walk towards staircase up stairs wait near top
tgt: Walk towards staircase.  Walk up stairs. Wait near top.

src: up stairs left near top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs to the left and stop near the top of the stairs.

tgt: Turn right. Turn left at the stairs. Wait in the entry way of the bedroom just ahead.

tgt: Facing the stairs leading upwards, enter the room and then do an extremely sharp left hand turn to go down a narrow hallway. Stop at the entrance to the bedroom after passing a window on your left and a door on your right.

tgt: Go inside then make a left U turn to go into the room at the end of the hallway. Wait at the entrance.

tgt: Walk all the way across the room and wait by the lounge chair.

src: walk between couch dining room table chairs behind outdoor chair
tgt: Walk between the couch and the dining room table and chairs. Stop behind the outdoor chair.

src: away from stairs towards large window between couches dining table wait rug
tgt: Go away from the stairs towards the large window, walking between the couches and the dining table.  Wait when you reach the rug.

tgt: Head toward the stairs and turn left before you get to the stairs. When you see the plant go through the double doors and turn left. Go up four steps on the stairs to your right and wait there.

tgt: Go through the french doors located near the large fern and head over to the staircase next to the living room.

tgt: walk through the doorway, to the left of the table. Walk over the rug and through the doorway under the stairs. Turn towards the left and walk towards the stair on your right. Proceed up four steps and stop.

tgt: go across deck through pass way and up stairs. Stop next to the first rocking chair.

tgt: Exit porch and go up stairs. Wait at rocking chairs.

tgt: Turn around and head outside through the door on the left. Walk towards the rocking chairs. Stop when you reach them.

tgt: Walk out of the room and turn right. Go through the middle door on the right. Walk straight and stop at the room with stairs.

src: into entrance of building after inside building straight on left side of dark brown couch couch through small doorway stop
tgt: Go into the entrance of the building. After inside the building, go straight on the left side of the dark brown couch. Pass the couch and go through the small doorway and stop.

src: walk across patio double doors right enter across living room into hallway stop in archway with counter on right
tgt: Walk across patio to double doors, turn right and enter, walk across living room into hallway stop in archway with counter on your right.

src: away from pool towards grill before table turn right through white glass door walk past chair couch over rug brass pillar on left couch on right straight through arched doorway with candle on wall right outside of doorway movie room
tgt: Walk away from the pool towards the grill, before you pass the table turn right through the white and glass door. Walk straight past the chair and couch, over the rug, There will be a brass pillar on your left and the couch on your right, walk straight through the arched doorway with a candle on the wall to your right. Stop outside of the doorway to the movie room.

tgt: Walk inside, turn right, turn slight right and walk past the dinning table toward the kitchen. Wait near the kitchen sink.

Once in this room walk a few steps forward, then turn left towards the glass table and chairs.  Walk to the opening to the left of the table and stop next to the brown wooden lattice wall.

Walk down the hallway keeping the open kitchen door to your right. Walk past the plug-in on the right wall and out of the hallway. Enter the room on your left with the open archway. Walk forward until you reach mid-point of the table on your left. Turning slightly to your right walk onto the round carpet and wait.
