tgt: Turn to the left and continue walking into the house.  You'll walk past the dining room table and then take a left, into a room with a desk.  Walk to the desk and stop.

src: enter house walk through living room walking left into office across from table with gray chairs on rug in front of black desk
tgt: Enter the house and walk through the living room. Keep walking and take a left into the office across from the dining table with the gray chairs. Stand on the rug in front of the black desk.

src: blue dots into other room
tgt: Follow the blue dots into the other room.

src: exit room walk down hallway slightly hallway stairs on left wait near kitchen bar with chair/stools
tgt: Exit the room. Walk straight down the hallway. Go slightly left to continue down the hallway. Pass the stairs on the left. Wait near the kitchen bar with the chair/stools.

src: turn around down hall walk past stairs wait by counter top
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hall. Walk past the stairs and wait by the counter top.

src: turn exit into hallway straight hallway until potted flowers at intersection left path with lamp forward past stairwell wait near countertop on right
tgt: Turn around and exit into the hallway, continue straight down the hallway until you reach some potted flowers at an intersection, take the left path with a lamp, continue forward past a stairwell and wait near the countertop on your right.

src: cross by couch stop
tgt: Cross by the couch and stop.

src: kitchen about degrees right while couch walk couch just right of right hand arm rest of couch
tgt: Facing the kitchen, look about 30 degrees to your right and you'll see a while couch. Walk to the couch and stop just to the right of the right hand arm rest of the couch.

src: straight into kitchen right table chairs wait near white couch
tgt: Go straight into the kitchen. Turn right and pass the table and chairs. Wait near the white couch.

src: head inside through archway on right wait in entryway by door
tgt: Head inside and through the archway on the right. Wait in the entryway by the door.

src: enter house then past white chair exit room by right left wait near on wall with lady chin
tgt: Enter the house then go past the white chair and exit the room by turning right. Turn left and wait near the drawing on the wall with the lady clasping her chin.

src: with kidney pool behind left though double doors in front of on through room via opening on right hand wall just before display case in front of table right underneath hanging mirror
tgt: With the kidney shaped pool behind you and towards your left, go though the double doors in front of you. Continue on through the room, exiting via the opening on the right hand wall just before the display case. Stop in front of the table to your right that's underneath the hanging mirror.

src: head indoors kitchen stairs then exit through doorway wait on door mat
tgt: Head indoors, pass the kitchen and the stairs. Then exit through the doorway and wait on the door mat.

src: walk over welcome mat through sliding glass door walk past white couches past staircase wait at doorway with welcome mat
tgt: Walk over the welcome mat, through the sliding glass door. Walk past the white couches and continue to walk past the staircase. Wait at the doorway with the welcome mat.

src: walk into door straight ahead through middle of rooms up step onto platform past stairs exit out door far left of stairs once outside
tgt: Walk into the door and straight ahead through the middle of 2 rooms. Walk up the step onto the platform and past the stairs. Exit out the door to the far left of the stairs and stop once you are outside.

src: through door ahead right sink turn into hallway then right carpeted hallway in next room on left near bed
tgt: Go through the door straight ahead. Turn right and go passed the sink. Turn left into the hallway and then turn right and continue down the carpeted hallway. Stop in the next room on the left near the bed.

src: through door right into bathroom left into hall stairs right into first bedroom once rug
tgt: Go through the door to the right into the bathroom. Take a left out into the hall, and go down the stairs to the right. Turn left into the first bedroom and stop once you reach the rug.

src: walk out of bedroom into bathroom out of bathroom right down stairs turn at double doors just inside bedroom
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and into the bathroom. Turn left out of the bathroom and turn right. Walk down the stairs and turn left at the double doors. Stop just inside the bedroom.

src: hallway at first hallway on left right after through doorway
tgt: Walking straight down the hallway, and turn left at your first hallway on the left. stop right after you pass through the doorway.

src: walk across bedroom with bed on right as bedroom by doorway in front of blonde wood closet doors through open doorway on left side next dining table on right
tgt: Walk across the bedroom with the bed on your right as you pass it.  Leave the bedroom by the doorway in front of you.  Pass the blonde wood closet doors, and go through the open doorway on your left side.  Stop next to the dining table, which will be on your right.

src: walk through bedroom down hall turn in doorway
tgt: Walk through the bedroom and down the hall. Turn left and stop in the doorway.

src: turn stairs turn tables near counter
tgt: Turn around and go down the stairs. Turn left and continue passed the tables. Stop near the counter.

src: stairs turn wait in kitchen area
tgt: Move down the stairs, turn left, wait in the kitchen area.

src: steps then straight past round table chairs wait near bar stools on right
tgt: Go down the steps then turn left. Go straight past the round table and chairs. Wait near the bar and stools on the right.

src: walk through door through exercise area out door wait in hallway
tgt: Walk through a door and through the exercise area, and out the door. Wait in the hallway.

src: exit room then right head into door left of picture frame on wall wait there in entrance
tgt: Exit the room then turn right and head into the door that is to the left of the picture frame on the wall. Wait there in the entrance.

src: exit massage room right third door sauna room wait
tgt: Exit the massage room, turn right, go to third door. Enter the sauna room and wait.

src: across room with banquet table wait in doorway large room
tgt: Go across the room with the banquet table and wait in the doorway, that is facing another large room.

src: wait at last doorway on right
tgt: Wait at the last doorway on the right.

src: straight pass chairs then right wait by door farthest left
tgt: Go straight and pass all the chairs then turn right and wait by the door that is farthest to the left.

src: walk through open door with car image next into room with blue flower bedding stuffed animal on bed
tgt: Walk through the open door with the car image next to it. Walk into the room with the blue flower bedding and the stuffed animal on the bed.

src: walk straight of of bedroom right with teddy bear on bed
tgt: Walk straight of of this bedroom and make a right and you will find another with a teddy bear on the bed.

src: walk around foot of bed television walk through open door hallway on other side of room walk into adjacent bedroom animals on bed decorations on wall above
tgt: Walk around the foot of the bed passed the television. Walk through the open door to the hallway on the other side of the room. Walk into the adjacent bedroom that has stuffed animals on the bed and hanging decorations on the wall above.

src: shower head towards stairs upward stairs on last step before top
tgt: Leave the shower and head towards the stairs leading upward. Climb up the stairs and stop on the last step before the top.

src: exit bathroom stairs once top
tgt: Exit the bathroom and go up the stairs. Stop once you reach the top.

src: exit bathroom area walk toward wood stairs on left stairs wait at top
tgt: Exit the bathroom area and walk toward the wood stairs on your left. Climb up the stairs and wait at the top.

src: turn around across long black rug at other side exit door left outside left of blue chairs outdoors
tgt: Turn around and walk across the long black rug. At the other side, exit out the door to your left. Walk outside and stop to the left of the blue chairs facing the outdoors.

src: walk into tv room exit onto balcony next first gray armchair
tgt: Walk into the TV room. Exit onto the balcony. Stop next to the first gray armchair.

src: walk past movie posters through theater room wait outside on balcony
tgt: Walk past the movie posters, through the theater room and wait outside on the balcony.

src: walk toward leather chair right into kitchen turn past refrigerator right
tgt: Walk toward the leather chair and turn right. Walk into the kitchen and turn left. Walk past the refrigerator and turn right and stop.

src: in hall in front of front door slight right into living room once in living room slight right kitchen now refrigerator out of kitchen right wait
tgt: When you are in the hall in front of the front door make a slight right, and go into the living room. Once you are in the living room make another slight right and go to the kitchen. Now to the refrigerator and walk out of the kitchen, make a right and wait.

src: ahead into living room kitchen area through kitchen first right past fridge in hallway
tgt: Go ahead into the living room and kitchen area. Go through the kitchen and take the first right past the fridge, stopping in the hallway.

src: turn around towards staircase near arm chairs walk staircase through room kitchen area walk towards fireplace near backside of counter top
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the staircase near the arm chairs. Walk passed the staircase and continue through the room to the kitchen area. Walk towards the fireplace and near the backside of the counter top.

src: turn until painting of horse with hallway staircase on right towards staircase slightly right so stairs on right with table in front of painting left down though dining room end of dinning table into next room so kitchen on left chairs couch right
tgt: TURN LEFT UNTIL YOU ARE FACING A PAINTING OF A HORSE WITH A HALLWAY AND STAIRCASE ON THE RIGHT, WALK TOWARDS THE STAIRCASE, TURN SLIGHTLY TO THE RIGHT SO THE STAIRS IS ON YOUR RIGHT WITH A DINNING TABLE IN FRONT OF YOU AND A PAINTING TO THE LEFT, WALK DOWN THOUGH THE DINING ROOM TO THE END OF THE DINNING TABLE, WALK INTO THE NEXT ROOM SO THERE IS A KITCHEN ON THE LEFT AND CHAIRS AND COUCH TO THE RIGHT.

src: back walk straight near char
tgt: turn back and walk straight and near char.

src: walk out bathroom door turn right past kitchen until dining room table walk through doorway left of dining room table stop
tgt: Walk out the bathroom door and turn to the right. Walk past the kitchen until you see the dining room table. Walk through the doorway that is to the left of the dining room table and stop.

src: out of bathroom right past kitchen left wait by first column
tgt: Go out of the bathroom and turn right. Go past the kitchen and go left and wait by the first column.

src: exit bathroom right kitchen turn right there
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Pass the kitchen and turn left. Wait right there.

src: walk base of stairs turn up stairs turn up second flight of stairs stop at top
tgt: walk to the base of the stairs, turn left and walk up the stairs, turn left and walk up the second flight of stairs, stop at the top.

src: white carpeted stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Go up the white carpeted stairs and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs on left wait at top
tgt: Go up the stairs on your left and wait at the top.

src: enter house stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Enter the house and walk up three stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: inside house in middle way white couch black table white stairs stop
tgt: Go inside the house in the middle way, passed the white couch and black table, go up the white stairs and stop.

src: walk towards white couch inside of house walk in between table couch top of stairs then wait
tgt: Walk towards the white couch inside of the house.  Walk in between the table and the couch to the top of the three stairs, then wait.

src: enter bedroom through doorway walk across room balcony wait behind couch
tgt: Enter the bedroom through the doorway. Walk across the room to the balcony and wait behind the couch.

src: bathroom left bedroom onto balcony on balcony stop once doorway
tgt: Leave the bathroom and take a left. Exit the bedroom and go onto the balcony. On the balcony stop once you pass the doorway.

src: walk ahead into bedroom across bedroom behind couch facing outside
tgt: Walk straight ahead and into the bedroom. Go across the bedroom and stop behind the couch facing outside.

src: stairs until in room with pool table
tgt: Go down the stairs until you're in the room with a pool table.

src: turn left down stairs at very bottom
tgt: Turn to the left and walk down the stairs.   Stop at the very bottom.

src: down stairs turn down next flight of stairs right down last stairs stop
tgt: walk down the stairs, turn left and walk down the next flight of stairs, turn right and walk down the last stairs and stop.

src: bedroom through door on right side of bed into room with door on opposite side of hallway right once in second bedroom in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom through the door on the right side of the bed.  Go into the room with the door on the opposite side of the hallway.  Turn right once you are in the second bedroom and stop in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: exit bedroom hall into next bedroom in bathroom doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom and cross the hall into the next bedroom. Stop in its bathroom doorway.

src: exit bathroom toward room then room door on right straight until room then right at doorway of bathroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom toward the room then exit the room using the door on the right go straight until you enter another room then go right and stand at the doorway of the bathroom.

src: walk out of closet walk across hall left of animal pictures walk into hallway past sculpture on table into bedroom next chair stop
tgt: Walk out of the closet and walk across the hall to the left of the animal pictures. Walk into the hallway past the sculpture on the table and into the bedroom next to the chair and stop.

src: exit closet right room slightly left into hallway straight ahead straight pass chair on right into room wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the closet. Turn right. Exit the room. Turn slightly left and go into the hallway straight ahead. Continue straight pass the chair on the right and into the room. Wait at the entrance.

src: turn left closet hall left next room down hall bedroom at end
tgt: Turn to the left and exit the closet.  Cross the hall to the left and enter the next room. Walk down that hall and enter the bedroom at the end.

src: toward sink area on left doorway on left slight left bedroom toward bed there
tgt: Go toward the sink area on the left. Enter doorway on the left. Take a slight left and enter the bedroom. Go toward the bed. Stop there.

src: walk past wet bar with green buddha statue bedroom wait in front of bed
tgt: Walk past the wet bar with the green smiling Buddha statue. Enter the bedroom and wait in front of the bed.

src: walk past built-in bar on left through open bedroom door left of bar wait at bench at foot of bed
tgt: Walk past the built-in bar on the left. Walk through the open bedroom door to the left of the bar. Wait at the bench at the foot of the bed.

src: turn right in front of fireplace walk around chairs in front of stairway
tgt: Turn right in front of the fireplace. Walk around the roped off chairs. Stop in front of the stairway.

src: turn around towards fireplace once fireplace right room once turn left walk top of stairs stop
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the fireplace. Once you reach the fireplace, turn right and exit the room. Once out turn left and walk to the top of the stairs and stop.

src: walk through doorway next black wardrobe path then right path then at top of stairs on left
tgt: Walk through the doorway next to the black wardrobe. Follow the path when it turns left. Then turn right where the path does. Then stop at the top of the stairs on the left.

src: head towards staircase begin stairs wait on step
tgt: Head towards staircase and begin going up stairs. Wait on the 6th step.

src: walk towards wall painting turn up curving staircase walk halfway up flight of stairs
tgt: Walk towards the wall painting. Turn and walk up the curving staircase and walk halfway up the flight of stairs.

src: turn around up first steps of stairs wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk up the first five to six steps of the stairs. Wait there.

src: stairs then right straight wait near table sofa chairs
tgt: Go up the stairs then U turn right and go straight. Wait near the table and sofa chairs.

src: steps at top along railing at end of railing table with grey chairs
tgt: Continue up the steps. At the top, turn around and walk along the railing. At the end of the railing, stop to the table with grey chairs.

src: finish last few steps right past stair railing counter into large living room wait by chair at end of table
tgt: Finish walking up the last few steps and turn right. Walk past the stair railing and counter, into the large living room. Wait by the chair at the closest end of the table.

src: down stairs wait near bottom
tgt: Walk down the stairs and wait near the bottom.

src: down stairway right on third stair from bottom
tgt: Walk down the stairway that curves to the right and stop on the third stair from the bottom.

src: down stairs then beside light switch
tgt: walk down the stairs then stop beside the light switch.

src: bathroom right right again past table with glass counter top once on marble floor
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go right.  Turn right again and walk past the table with the glass counter top.  Stop once you step on the marble floor.

src: bathroom right right again forward then just after tile floor
tgt: Leave the bathroom and turn right. Turn right again and move forward. Then stop just after reaching the tile floor.

src: walk out door right past cabinet just past cabinet
tgt: Walk out the door. Turn right and go past cabinet. Stop just past the cabinet.

src: walk toward staircase right through room right past chairs in hallway
tgt: Walk toward the staircase and turn right. Walk through the room and right past the chairs. Stop in the hallway.

src: exit intersection towards staircase right straight chairs on right right into intersection in middle of intersection
tgt: Exit the intersection towards the staircase, make a right and go straight passed the two chairs on the right, make another right into the intersection and stop in the middle of the intersection.

src: right then door right again wall way doorway on far right then right in hallway
tgt: Go to your right and then enter the door. Turn right again and follow the wall all the way to the doorway on the far right. Then turn right and stop in the hallway.

src: exit room hallway in hallway turn towards left at watermelon painting then in front of black yellow painting
tgt: Exit the room and enter the hallway. In the hallway, turn left and continue towards the left at the watermelon painting. Then stop in front of the black and yellow painting.

src: exit room turn straight hall turn stairs on right into room wait near bed
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go straight down the hall. Turn left and pass the stairs on the right. Go into the room and wait near the bed.

src: walk forward down hallway ahead at end turn forward turn past stairs into doorway straight ahead
tgt: Walk forward down the hallway ahead. At the end, turn left and walk forward. Turn left and walk past the stairs into the doorway straight ahead and stop.

src: down stairs into dining room across from stairs right into kitchen stop in front of cabinet with glasses on right
tgt: Walk down the stairs and straight into the dining room across from the stairs. Take a right into the kitchen Stop in front of the cabinet with glasses on the right.

src: stairs into doorway on right wait
tgt: Go down the stairs, go into the doorway on your right and wait.

src: stairs into dining room just as dining room right kitchen
tgt: Go down the stairs and straight into the dining room. Just as you enter the dining room, turn right and enter the kitchen.

src: turn right room once out right way end of hallway at end right bedroom
tgt: Turn right and exit the room. Once out, turn right and walk all the way to the end of the hallway. At the end,turn right and stop when you enter the bedroom.

src: exit bedroom right down corridor end bedroom on right wait here
tgt: Exit bedroom and turn right.  Head down the corridor.  When you reach the end, enter the bedroom on the right.  Wait here.

src: bedroom right bedroom through last door on right next lamp on table
tgt: Leave the bedroom, and go right. Enter the bedroom through the last door on the right. Stop next to the lamp on the table.

src: stairs then hallway then last room right by nightstand
tgt: Move up the stairs and then turn left. Continue down the hallway and then enter the last room to the right, stopping by the nightstand.

src: stairs left hall right at third door on right walk in room in front of door on right of closet
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a left. Go down the hall and take a right at the third door on the right. walk in the room and stop in front of the door on the right of the closet.

src: up stairs corner left down hallway art walk through door at end of hallway into bedroom with paintings of women
tgt: Walk up the remaining stairs. Turn the corner to the left and walk down the hallway passed the hanging art. Walk through the door at the end of the hallway and into the bedroom with the paintings of women.

src: into kitchen walk right right at round table walk towards closed front door through door left of front door in doorway bathroom
tgt: Go into the kitchen and walk right.  Turn right at the round table and walk towards the closed front door.  Go through the door to the left of the front door and stop in the doorway to the bathroom.

src: kitchen turn right kitchen walk toward round table right round table turn on second door wait near sink
tgt: When you get to the kitchen turn right. Exit the kitchen and walk toward the round table. Turn right when you get to the round table. Turn left on the second door and wait near the sink.

src: walk out of dining room right across foyer right toward front door of house in doorway of powder room left of front door
tgt: Walk out of the dining room and turn right. Walk across the foyer, right, toward the front door of the house. Stop in the doorway of the powder room that is to the left of the front door.

src: start in game room toward foosball table turn into bedroom walk through bedroom at bathroom door
tgt: Start in the game room. Walk toward the foosball table. Turn left into the bedroom. Walk through the bedroom. Stop at the bathroom door.

src: turn bedroom door turn again bedroom in bathroom door
tgt: Turn left and walk to the bedroom door. Turn left again, cross the bedroom, and stop in the bathroom door.

src: turn head towards table game left at door head inside bedroom walk towards bathroom at entrance of bathroom
tgt: Turn left and head towards the table game. Make a left at the door. Head inside the bedroom and walk towards the bathroom. Stop at the entrance of the bathroom.

src: turn steps turn into room wait near mirror on left
tgt: Turn left. Go up the three steps. Turn left and go into the room. Wait near the mirror on the left.

src: walk past chairs up steps wait in first room on left
tgt: Walk past the chairs and up the steps. Wait in the first room on the left.

src: slightly left turn hallway steps then walk through door before once work equipment
tgt: Make a slightly left turn and continue down the hallway, go up the three steps and then walk left through the nearest door before stopping once you see the work out equipment.

src: exit massage room turn walk down hallway slight in lounge room door on left between benches
tgt: exit massage room and turn left walk straight down hallway turn slight left in lounge room and enter the door on the left. stop between two benches.

src: away from bed through doorway down hallway left metal vine art on wall on right slightly right past identical chairs through doorway on left in front of mirrors
tgt: walk away from the bed and through the doorway, down the hallway to the left. There will be metal vine art hanging on the wall on the right. walk slightly to the right past three identical chairs and through the doorway on the left. Stop in front of the two mirrors.

src: exit massage room walk hallway on left walk end of hallway other side of room wait in men locker area by mirrors
tgt: Exit the massage room and walk to the hallway on the left. Walk to the end of the hallway and to the other side of the room. Wait in the men's locker area by the mirrors.

src: walk circular desk towards decoration pots through hallway with pots through glass door walk past water cooler through open doorway
tgt: Walk passed the circular desk towards the decoration pots. Walk through the hallway with the pots and continue through the glass door. Walk Past the water cooler and through the open doorway.

src: forward with glass door on right right at first door past wood rice paper partition in doorway
tgt: Walk forward with the glass door on your right. Take a right at the first door past the wood and rice paper partition and stop in the doorway.

src: move forward down hall past receptionist area with water cooler in first doorway right
tgt: Move forward down the hall past the receptionist area with the water cooler. Stop in the first doorway to the right.

src: walk through doorway on left that towards open doorway across way pool in from door next green push
tgt: Walk through doorway on the left that, walk towards the open doorway across the way that passes the pool, stop in from the door next to the green push.

src: through door walkway past pool at black door
tgt: Go through the door to the walkway. Continue past the pool. Stop at the black door.

src: turn right out of door path past pool until door inside wait there by plants
tgt: Turn to the right and go out of the door.  Follow the path, go past the pool.  Go until you reach the door to go inside.  Wait there by the plants.

src: down out door down staircase at landing walk other set of stairs at stop of stairs through doorway after through door
tgt: Walk down out the door and down the nearest staircase. At the landing, walk straight up the other set of stairs. At the stop of the stairs, move through the nearest doorway. Stop after passing through the door.

src: turn through doors down stairs other side of stairs first door on left before
tgt: Turn left to go through the doors and down the stairs. Go up the other side of the stairs, and go to the first door on your left before stopping.

src: walk top of stairs down stairs past plant up stairs across hall walk through first door right of corner between pictures in front of circular stairs
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs. Walk down the stairs past the plant. Walk up the stairs and across the hall. Walk through the first door to the right of the corner, between the two pictures. Stop in front of the circular stairs.

src: way down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go all the way down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: down stairs wait at bottom
tgt: Walk down the stairs and wait at the bottom.

src: turn right until stairs down stairs until bottom of staircase now towards painting in front of directly in front of painting
tgt: Turn to the right until you are looking down the stairs.  Walk down the stairs until you reach the bottom of the staircase.  Now, walk towards the painting that is in front of you.  Stop when you are standing directly in front of the painting.

src: away from orange leather couch right by metal chairs walk past frosted glass wall with on right as house past orange sculpture outside door
tgt: Walk away from the orange leather couch and make a right by the two metal chairs.  Walk past the frosted glass wall, with will be on your right as you pass.  Exit the house.  Stop when you get past the orange sculpture outside the door.

src: turn around hallway out front door next large rocks
tgt: Turn around and proceed down the hallway and walk out the front door. Stand next to the large rocks.

src: around metal wall on left exit onto patio patio into dirt next large boulders
tgt: Go around the metal wall on the left and exit onto the patio. Step off the patio into the dirt. Stop next to the two large boulders.

src: turn long hallway on runner few steps top of stairs
tgt: Turn around and go down a long hallway.  Stay on the runner.  Go up a few steps.  when you get to the top of the stairs, that's where you will wait.

src: down hall red gold runner small flight of stairs at top of stairs just outside bathroom
tgt: Walk down the hall following the red and gold runner, and go up the small flight of stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs just outside the bathroom.

src: rug hallway stairs at bathroom door
tgt: Follow the rug down the hallway. Go up the stairs and stop at the bathroom door.

src: walk down hallway turn into office wait there
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway. Turn left into the office and wait there.

src: walk then at door
tgt: walk straight then turn left at the door.

src: walk ahead hallway in first doorway left
tgt: Walk straight ahead down the hallway and stop in the first doorway to the left.

src: walk potted plant right into room with sink tub
tgt: Walk to the potted plant. Make a right into the room with the sink and tub.

src: away from couch under landing of staircase above head doors in front of through doorway just right of center door into bathroom walk into bathroom in front of mirror
tgt: Walk away from the couch and under the landing of the staircase above your head.  There are five doors in front of you.  Walk through the doorway that is just to the right of the center door.  This will take you into a bathroom.  Walk into the bathroom and stop in front of the mirror.

src: walk past kitchen bathroom through second door on right in front of bathroom sink
tgt: Walk past the kitchen and enter the bathroom through the second door on the right. Stop in front of the bathroom sink.

src: walk through door forward green counter with coffee maker turn into bathroom wait in front of door toilet room
tgt: Walk through the door and continue forward to the green counter with the coffee maker. Turn Left and walk into the bathroom and wait in front of the door to the toilet room.

src: room walk straight hallway past front door at sink right in front of door toilet room
tgt: Leave the room and walk straight down the hallway past the front door.  At the sink, turn right and stop in front of the door to the toilet room.

src: room narrow hallway right by sink wait in bathroom
tgt: Leave the room and travel down the narrow hallway.  Turn right by the sink and wait in the bathroom.

src: right of white bookcase through archway until green vase
tgt: Go to the right of the white bookcase. Keep going through the archway until you reach the green vase.

src: hall directly in front of right in front of tall green vase
tgt: Go down the hall directly in front of you and stop right in front of the tall green vase.

src: forward toward white shelves down path right of shelves in front of large green vase
tgt: Walk forward toward the white shelves. Walk down the path to the right of the shelves. Stop in front of the large, green vase.

src: exit room door on right left into room on left right into room on right left wait in hallway
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the right. Turn left and go into the room on the left. Turn right and go into the room on the right. Turn left and wait in the hallway.

src: walk past pink blue arm chair through doorway right hard left walk into office continue right past bookshelves turn right through doorway then hard left through second doorway outside door restroom
tgt: Walk past the pink and blue patterned arm chair and through the doorway to the right. Turn a hard left and walk into the office and continue to the right past the bookshelves. Turn right through the doorway and then turn a hard left through the second doorway. Wait outside the door to the restroom.

src: door behind red chair into brown office room into bedroom in front of bathroom door
tgt: Go out the door behind the red chair. Go into the brown office room. Go into the bedroom. Go in front of the bathroom door.

src: walk outside right walk past patio furniture stop by hedge next steps
tgt: Walk outside and turn right. Walk left past the patio furniture and stop by the hedge next to the steps.

src: outside right couches walk straight until steps on left around there
tgt: Go outside and turn right. Pass the couches and walk straight until you get to the steps on the left. Wait around there.

src: walk outside right past patio stand near chair swing
tgt: Walk outside, turn right and walk past the patio set. Stand near the chair swing.

src: walk through laundry room past washing machines through door into hallway down hall between banister rails corner near blue armchairs walk desk on opposite wall with bulletin boards above
tgt: Walk through the laundry room past the washing machines through the door into the hallway. Walk down the hall between the banister rails. Turn the corner near the blue armchairs and walk to the desk on the opposite wall with the bulletin boards above.

src: walk out of laundry room right straight hallway then right wait near blue chairs
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room and take a right. Walk straight down the hallway, then turn right and wait near the blue chairs.

src: walk dryer through doorway right straight towards blue chairs wait in front of blue chairs
tgt: Walk passed washer and dryer and through doorway. Turn right, go straight towards blue chairs and wait in front of blue chairs.

src: walk large open doorway right diagonally across room tile on floor doorway step inside
tgt: walk straight to large open doorway.  turn right and walk diagonally across room to star tile on floor.  go to bedroom doorway.  step inside.

src: walk across hallway into area through area wait past wet bar through doorway
tgt: Walk across the hallway into the sitting area. Go through the sitting area and wait past the wet bar through the doorway.

src: walk ahead room turn right past sink next room bedroom into wait n't further
tgt: Walk straight ahead and enter a room, turn to the right and go past the sink.  Enter the next room, which is a bedroom and when you walk into it, stop, wait.  Don't go any further.

src: hallway turn at first doorway through across animal skin then left into laundry room just at doorway wait
tgt: Go down the hallway and turn left at the first doorway.  Go through, across an animal skin, and then turn left.  Go into the laundry room.  Stand just at the doorway and wait.

src: move forward down hallway past open double doors right around stairs room on left past bear rug
tgt: Move forward down the hallway, past the open double doors. Make a right and go around the stairs.  Enter the room on the left past the bear rug.

src: walk through hallway stairway turn past stairs laundry room wait at washer
tgt: Walk through the hallway to the stairway, turn left, walk past the stairs, enter the laundry room, wait at the washer.

src: with wall right forward until building though door right after building hallway right after through door at end of hallway
tgt: With the wall to your right, move forward until you can enter the building though a door to your right. After entering the building, take the hallway to your right. Stop after passing through the door at the end of the hallway.

src: walk past garden hose into house through doorway right after through doorway
tgt: Walk past the garden hose and into the house. Walk through the doorway to the right and stop after passing through the doorway.

src: turn through breezeway right house turn inside house through archway then through open door just inside doorway
tgt: Turn left and move through the breezeway. Turn right and enter the house. Turn left inside the house and move through the archway, then through the open door and stop just inside the doorway.

src: walk through door on left left into room wait at bathroom doorway
tgt: Walk through door on the left and make a left. Walk into room and wait at bathroom doorway.

src: exit room door on left then into room next door then right into bathroom wait near toilet
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the left then turn left and go into the room next door then turn right and go into the bathroom. Wait near the toilet.

src: if in front of television right out of door in hallway turn through door of bedroom once in bedroom walk window right wait in doorway of bathroom
tgt: If you are standing in front of the television make a right and walk out of the door. When you are in the hallway turn left and go through the door of the bedroom. Once you are in the bedroom walk to the window and make a right, wait in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: stairs wait at door left of blue couch at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs, wait at the door to the left of the blue couch at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk forward away from stairs behind stairs into living room in living room left in entry hallway in front of door
tgt: Walk forward away from the stairs behind you, and go down the stairs into the living room. In the living room take a left and stop in the entry hallway in front of the door.

src: down stairs head hallway toward bedroom by thermostat outside bedroom wait
tgt: Walk down the stairs and head left down the hallway toward the bedroom. Stop by the thermostat outside the bedroom and wait.

src: through archway opposite chalk board right brown table through archway step into room stop
tgt: Go through the archway opposite the chalk board, turn right and go passed the brown table and through the archway and take a step into the room and stop.

src: laundry room kitchen right before table bedroom at end of hall once door
tgt: Leave the laundry room, and enter the kitchen. Take a right before the table. Enter the bedroom at the end of the hall. Stop once you pass the door.

src: walk for moment before hard right through doorway into living room stop near television
tgt: Walk straight for a moment before taking a hard right and continue through the doorway into the living room and stop near the television.

src: turn around into saloon door
tgt: Turn around and walk into the saloon door.

src: painting on green wall turn right until staircase in front of door on right towards door on right side of staircase doors bookcase left walk though swinging doors doors into door on left side so that in bedroom
tgt: FACING A PAINTING ON A GREEN WALL TURN TO THE RIGHT UNTIL A STAIRCASE IS IN FRONT OF YOU AND A DOOR ON THE RIGHT, WALK TOWARDS THE DOOR ON THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE STAIRCASE, FACING SWINGING DOORS AND A BOOKCASE TO THE LEFT WALK THOUGH THE SWINGING DOORS, FACING THREE DOORS WALK INTO THE DOOR ON THE LEFT SIDE SO THAT YOU ARE IN A BEDROOM.

src: walk towards stairs then right through double swinging doors left stand in front of bedroom
tgt: Walk towards the stairs and then walk to your right and go through the double swinging doors.  Make a left and stand in front of the bedroom.

src: right down long hall in entryway on left first white table
tgt: Go right and down the long hall. Stop in the entryway on the left passed the first white table.

src: walk inside straight circular marble table in middle of room turn in front of drinking fountain
tgt: Walk inside and go straight.  When you get to the circular marble table in the middle of the room, turn left.  Stop in front of the drinking fountain.

src: walk inside through doorways table with white tablecloth left through immediate doorway then in front of drinking fountain
tgt: Walk inside through both doorways, pass the table with the white tablecloth and make a left through the immediate doorway, then stop in front of the drinking fountain.

src: head past pool jacuzzi door towards bedroom before bedroom
tgt: Head past the pool and jacuzzi enter the door, towards the bedroom. Stop before entering the bedroom.

src: right pool forward right through doors then in leftmost entryway
tgt: Go to your right passed the pool. Continue forward and turn right. Go through the doors and then stop in the leftmost entryway.

src: walk past patio chairs right into building turn by metal chair
tgt: Walk past the patio chairs and to the right. Walk into the building and turn left. Stop by the metal chair.

src: walk out of gym turn in front of mirror into bedroom turn past bench in front of cabinet
tgt: Walk out of the gym and turn left in front of the mirror into the bedroom. Turn left past the bench and stop in front of the cabinet.

src: forward with gym equipment left wall mirror right through doorway nearest wall mirror degrees right forward third door left turn pass through doorway right bench right forward with bench left cabinet right through entryway stop at tall wooden cabinet left
tgt: Move forward with the gym equipment to your left and the wall mirror to your right. Pass through the doorway nearest the wall mirror. Turn 45 degrees right and move forward. Stop when you reach the third door to your left and turn left. Pass through the doorway and turn to your right when you pass the bench to your right. Move forward with the bench to your left and the cabinet to your right. Pass through the entryway and stop at the tall wooden cabinet to your left.

src: face wall in giant mirror through doorway left hallway until mirror on right turn through double doors bedroom turn right once room into bathroom until above head doorways in front of
tgt: Face the wall that is covered in a giant mirror, and proceed through the doorway to your left. Follow the hallway until there is a mirror on your right and turn left through the double doors to enter a bedroom. Turn right once you enter the room and proceed into the bathroom until there is a chandelier above your head and two doorways in front of you.

src: walk into kitchen onto patio stand in patio doorway next breakfast bar
tgt: Walk into the kitchen and go out onto the patio. Stand in the patio doorway next to the breakfast bar.

src: right kitchen through kitchen at left angle wait near patio door
tgt: Go to the right to enter the kitchen. Continue through the kitchen at a left angle and wait near the patio door.

src: turn around past kitchen island off left head towards open area outdoor seating area wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk past the kitchen island.  Veer off to the left, and head towards the open area that is an outdoor seating area.  Wait there.

src: straight bar with stools then straight wait by stairs
tgt: Go straight and pass the bar with the stools and then continue going straight and wait by the stairs.

src: toward counter then along counter right of single step stop
tgt: Go toward the counter and then along the counter to the right of it, go to the single step and stop.

src: walk forward around right side of kitchen island forward past white chair on right wait near base of staircase
tgt: Walk forward and around the right side of the kitchen island. Continue forward past the white chair on the right.  Wait near the base of the staircase.

src: face inside of house while in doorway into second door on right further one from outside doorway stairs then right stairs then in front of couch with red chair ottoman next
tgt: Face the inside of the house while standing in the doorway. Go into the second door on your right (the further one from the outside doorway). Go down some stairs, and then turn right. Go down more stairs, and then turn left, standing in front of a couch with a red chair and ottoman next to it.

src: turn in second door on right stairs second set of stairs right last couple steps stop
tgt: Turn around and go in the second door on the right. Go down the stairs, and go down the second set of stairs to the right. Go left down the last couple steps and stop.

src: enter house second doorway on right open door steps right steps turn steps just as room wait there
tgt: Enter the house and proceed to the second doorway on your right. Enter the open door and go down five steps. Turn right and go down four steps. Turn left and go down two steps. Stop just as you enter the room and wait there.

src: walk past kitchen until dining room table turn table chairs straight until table chairs on left then there
tgt: Walk straight past the kitchen until you get to the dining room table. Turn left and pass the table and chairs. Continue straight until you pass another table and chairs on the left. Then wait there.

src: leave pantry towards stairs behind chairs at way
tgt: Leave pantry to kitchen, turn left and walk towards the stairs. stop behind the chairs at entry way.

src: walk past wall oven on right walk between kitchen island dining table walk past built-in kitchen desk on left past formal dining room on left wait at column on left
tgt: Walk past the wall oven on the right. Walk between the kitchen island and the dining table. Walk past the built-in kitchen desk on the left. Walk past the formal dining room on the left. Wait at the column on the left.

src: dining room walk in direction of couch ahead walk behind couch in front of wall next oven
tgt: Leave the dining room and walk in the direction of the couch ahead. Walk behind the couch and stop in front of the wall next to the oven.

src: towards archway past dining table into room with kitchen family room just inside room
tgt: Go towards the archway past the dining table and into the room with the kitchen and family room.  Stop just inside the room.

src: turn left past table chairs through hall way in kitchen/living room past little bit of counter bar stool then
tgt: Turn to the left.  GO past the table and chairs.  Continue through the hall way and you'll be in the kitchen/living room.  Go past a little bit of the counter, and a bar stool.  Then stop and wait.

src: from stairs right into room straight ahead in sitting room walk rear right into small room on right once small room
tgt: From the stairs take a right and go into the sitting room straight ahead. In the sitting room walk to the rear and take a right into the small room on the right. Stop once you have entered the small room.

src: turn walk around banister into room with arched door way through open room other end with throw rug armchairs walk into door past small table into room with drawn back
tgt: Turn and walk around the banister into the room with the arched door way. Walk through the open room to the other end with a throw rug and armchairs. Walk into the door  past the small table and into the room with drawn back curtains.

src: turn steps room slightly right across room room into next empty room inside before rug
tgt: turn left passed the steps and enter the room. Go slightly right and continue across the room. Exit the room into the next empty room. Stop inside before the rug.

src: walk through living room right down hall bedroom at end of hall left into kitchenette in front of mini-fridge
tgt: Walk through the living room and take a right. Walk down the hall and enter the bedroom at the end of the hall. Take a left into the kitchenette. Stop in front of the mini-fridge.

src: with back corner of room head towards base of staircase in front of on wooden flooring past staircase through door ahead of in front of dishwasher in kitchenette left
tgt: With your back to the nearest corner of the room, head towards the base of the staircase in front of you. Continue on the wooden flooring past the staircase and go through the door opening ahead of you. Stop in front of the dishwasher in the kitchenette to your left.

src: walk toward stairs stairs bedroom at end of hallway in front of mini-fridge on left
tgt: Walk toward the stairs. Pass the stairs and enter the bedroom at the end of the hallway. Stop in front of the mini-fridge on the left.

src: exit room turn into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: exit bedroom hallway first door on left bathroom wait just inside
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go down the hallway to the first door on the left. Enter the bathroom and wait just inside.

src: turn around out of bedroom into hallway once in hallway turn in first door left in front of first sink
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bedroom and into the hallway. Once in the hallway, turn in the first door to your left. Stop in front of the first sink .

src: turn at green vase into main work room right towards entry at desk with white trash
tgt: Turn left at green vase into main work room. Turn right and walk towards the entry. Stop at desk with white trash can.

src: turn down hallway walk past desk right past long conference table wait next white trashcan
tgt: Turn left and walk down the hallway. Walk past the desk, turn right and walk past the long conference table. Wait next to the white trashcan.

src: walk towards large green vase turn at vase walk through stone hallway right on table right between green table brown table under stone arch
tgt: walk towards large green vase, turn left at vase, walk straight through stone hallway, walk to the right on table, turn right and walk between green table and brown table, stop under stone arch.

src: walk into very large living room until stairs dining room wait at second step
tgt: walk into the very large living room and keep going, until you reach the stairs to the dining room, and wait at the second step.

src: walk out of recreation area stairs stairs stop
tgt: Walk out of the recreation area heading to the stairs. Go up three stairs and stop.

src: pass pool table then bar with stools then couches on right straight until steps steps then
tgt: Pass the pool table then pass the bar with the stools. Then pass the couches on the right and contunue straight until you get to some steps go up three steps then stop.

src: walk down hallway by with man hands
tgt: Walk straight down hallway and wait by painting with man clutching his hands.

src: turn right hall wait by photographs on wall
tgt: Turn right and go down the hall. Wait by the framed photographs on the wall.

src: walk down hallway stairs on left hallway around near portraits on left wall
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway. Passed the stairs on the left. Follow the hallway around and stop near the four portraits hanging on the left wall.

src: bedroom right down hall exit room left in doorway living room
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Walk down the hall and exit the room. Take a left and stop in the doorway to the living room.

src: turn bathroom doorway hall with towel left though door in hall right walk end of hallway turn at end of hall until open door left recessed statue in front of door on left living room
tgt: TURN TO FACE THE BATHROOM DOORWAY THAT OPENS TO THE HALL WITH A TOWEL TO THE LEFT, WALK THOUGH THE DOOR, IN THE HALL TURN RIGHT AND WALK TO THE END OF THE HALLWAY, TURN LEFT AT THE END OF THE HALL UNTIL YOU FACE AN OPEN DOOR TO THE LEFT AND A RECESSED STATUE IN FRONT OF YOU, WALK TO THE DOOR ON THE LEFT THAT LEADS TO A LIVING ROOM.

src: walk end of hall hard left wait in doorway
tgt: Walk to the end of the hall. Turn hard left. Wait in the doorway.

src: turn around desks walk towards kitchen down stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn left. Walk around desks. Walk towards kitchen. Walk down stairs. Stop at bottom of stairs.

src: walk into open office area walk around first desk along glass wall past next desk with arrow from ceiling above with word host walk past desk black cabinet ahead then small set of stairs ahead
tgt: Walk into the open office area and walk around the first desk and along the glass wall past the next desk with arrow hanging from the ceiling above with the word host. Walk past the desk and the black cabinet ahead then continue down the small set of stairs ahead,.

src: turn after wooden crate walk past glass walls on left left staircase on bottom step
tgt: Turn left after the wooden crate. Walk past the glass walls on the left. Go down the left staircase and stop on the bottom step.

src: forward into kitchen through door at end of kitchen left in doorway garage
tgt: Walk forward into the kitchen and through the door at the end of the kitchen. Take a left and stop in the doorway to the garage.

src: through room with tables through door at end of room
tgt: Go through the room with the two tables and through the door at the end of the room.

src: head through kitchen wait in doorway kitchen
tgt: Head straight through the kitchen. Wait in the doorway exiting the kitchen.

src: walk across kitchen towards table walk left of table out of room then right at bottom of steps
tgt: Walk across the kitchen towards the table. Walk to the left of the table out of the room. Then turn right and stop at the bottom of the steps.

src: through kitchen exit french doors then right bottom of stairs
tgt: Go through the kitchen and exit to left towards the french doors.  Then go right and wait and the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk through kitchen past oven sink turn at table chairs through doorway stairs on second step
tgt: Walk through the kitchen past the oven and sink.  Turn left at the table and chairs and through the doorway.  Go up the stairs and stop on the second step.

src: walk slightly toward candy cane chair into hallway straight ahead straight until small gold table with gold chairs
tgt: Walk slightly left toward the candy cane colored chair. Go into the hallway that is straight ahead. Walk straight until you get to a small gold table with two gold chairs.

src: walk towards grandfather clock door left
tgt: walk towards the grandfather clock. take the door to the left.

src: walk forward door on left side next striped chair forward door k turn fireplace there
tgt: Walk forward and enter the door on the left side next to the striped chair. Walk forward to enter another door,k and turn left towards the fireplace, and stop there.

src: exit room through door left of beds once outside room turn straight into room at end of wall on left inside in front of screen
tgt: Exit the room through the door to the left of the beds.  Once outside the room turn left and walk straight into the room at the end of the wall on the left.  Step inside and stop in front of the screen.

src: exit room turn into room next door on left wait near sink.s
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go into the room next door on the left. Wait near the sink.s.

src: exit room through left door curve on tiled floor wait in entrance next bathroom by wood screen
tgt: Exit the room through the left door.  Curve left, staying on tiled floor, and wait in the entrance to the next bathroom by the wood screen.

src: room past counter white chairs on pgi doormat
tgt: Leave the room going past the counter and the white chairs. Stop on the PGI doormat.

src: double doors out patio wait there
tgt: Go straight out the double doors and out to the patio. Wait there.

src: walk out of kitchen onto patio on pgi rug outside of door
tgt: Walk out of the kitchen and onto the patio. Stop on the PGI rug outside of the door.

src: stairs wait at top once wooden floor
tgt: Continue up stairs and wait at the top, once you reach wooden floor.

src: up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairway on top of stairs on landing in hallway
tgt: Go straight up the stairway and keep going and stop on the top of the stairs on the landing in the hallway.

src: exit bathroom down hallway first into bedroom wait in front of bed
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk down the hallway.  Take the first left into the bedroom.  Wait in front of the bed.

src: exit bathroom turn straight down hallway turn at first open door in front of bed
tgt: Exit bathroom, turn left, go straight down hallway, turn left at the first open door, stop in front of the bed.

src: bathroom hall first into bedroom just inside door
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go down the hall. Take the first left into a bedroom. Stop just inside the door.

src: walk around stairs right of table chairs left of bar at end of bar by bowl of fruit
tgt: Walk around the stairs, and go to the right of the table and chairs. Pass the left of the bar, and stop at the end of the bar by the bowl of fruit.

src: down stars sharp turn right past dining room table chairs walk end of island stop
tgt: Walk down the stars and make a sharp turn left. Turn right and walk past the dining room table and chairs. Walk to the end of the island and stop.

src: stairs left then hall bar on right side of living room
tgt: Go down the stairs and to the left. Then go down the hall passed the bar and stop on the right side of the living room.

src: exit room double doors on right right steps right into room wait near coffee table
tgt: Exit the room using the double doors on the right. Turn right and go up the steps. Turn right into the room. Wait near the coffee table.

src: bedroom through door at foot of bed right in hallway right in front of windows up stairs at top of stairs through doorway on right towards glass table on carpet
tgt: Leave the bedroom through the door at the foot of the bed to the right.  In the hallway, turn right in front of the windows and walk up the stairs.  At the top of the stairs, walk through the doorway on the right.  Walk towards the glass table and stop when you step on the carpet.

src: exit bedroom right up stairs right into living room wait there
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right. Walk up the stairs. Turn right into the living room and wait there.

src: down stairs left past couch right in front of couch hall then in bedroom on far right wait
tgt: Walk down the stairs and make a left past the couch. Make a right when you're in front of the couch go down the hall then go in the bedroom on the far right and wait.

src: down stairs walks toward tall plant right into room with bed
tgt: Walk down the stairs. Walks toward the tall potted plant. Make a right into the room with a bed.

src: stairs right past kitchen first bedroom right in doorway
tgt: Go down the stairs, taking a right and continuing past the kitchen. Enter the first bedroom to your right, stopping in the doorway.

src: past double glass doors outside pass through archway sharply right at open door right in doorway wait in doorway
tgt: Go past the double glass doors leading outside and pass through the archway.  Turn sharply right at the open door to your right and stand in the doorway. Wait in the doorway.

src: straight steps right into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Go straight and go down the steps. Turn right and go into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: towards room down steps stop after first set of steps right into room with sink in doorway
tgt: Go towards the room located down the steps, stop after the first set of steps. Turn right into room with sink and stay in the doorway.

src: head corridor away from cinema room living area walk toward large couch area left there
tgt: Head down the corridor away from the cinema room. Enter the living area and walk toward the large couch. Enter the dining area to the left. Stop there.

src: media room veer left behind couch dining room on left in dining room left of first chair at head of table
tgt: Leave the media room and veer left. Go behind the couch to the dining room on the left. Stop in the dining room to the left of the first chair at the head of the table.

src: straight then past couches turn by large table with chairs
tgt: Go straight then go past the couches and turn left. Stand by the large table with the chairs.

src: exit bathroom through bedroom bedroom down hallway first door across from cabinets wait in doorway
tgt: Exit the bathroom, walk through the bedroom, exit the bedroom, walk down the hallway to the first door across from the cabinets, wait in the doorway.

src: head out of bathroom right bedroom wait in doorway of first room on right
tgt: Head out of the bathroom and turn right and exit the bedroom. Wait in the doorway of the first room on the right.

src: through doorway right through hall in doorway on right
tgt: go through doorway, turn right, walk through hall and stop in doorway on right.

src: cross table hallway turn piano couches straight until second last couch
tgt: Cross the table and continue down the hallway. Turn left passed the piano. Go to the couches and go straight until you reach the second to last couch.

src: walk diagonally far corner of room by couch nearest corner
tgt: Walk diagonally towards the far corner of the room. Stop by the couch, nearest the corner.

src: walk across room towards right towards columns left areas walk last sitting area on end with brown chairs at end of couch in area area glass
tgt: Walk across the room towards the right. Go towards the columns to the left and enter the sitting areas. Walk to the last sitting area on the end with the brown chairs. Stop at the end of the couch in this sitting area facing the sitting area and the glass windows.

src: walk out of closet through bathroom turn down hallway past fireplace right past plants by chair
tgt: Walk out of the closet and through the bathroom. Turn left and walk down the hallway past the fireplace. Turn right past the plants and stop by the chair.

src: turn right through open door into bathroom once in bathroom forward into hallway past black bathroom sink in hallway turn way down end of hallway flower vase on table right open double doors bedroom turn right bedroom once in bedroom walk white doors on left of room there
tgt: Turn to the right, and walk through the open door into the bathroom.  Once in the bathroom proceed forward into the hallway, you'll walk past the black bathroom sink.  In the hallway turn left and walk all the way down to the end of the hallway where there is a flower vase on a table.  To your right will be open double doors leading to a bedroom.  Turn to the right and enter the bedroom.  Once in the bedroom walk to the white doors on the left of the room and stop there.

src: exit bathroom turn head hallway then bedroom on right
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Head straight down the hallway, then enter the bedroom on the right.

src: exit room straight into room on right wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room. Go straight into the room on the right. Wait at the entrance.

src: exit room head strait across corridor room room on far right wait near doorway
tgt: Exit the room and head strait across the corridor to the room to the room on the far right. Wait near the doorway.

src: walk out of massage room walk across hall through door between paintings on right just inside doorway
tgt: Walk out of the massage room and walk across the hall through the door between the paintings on the right. Stop just inside the doorway.

src: step in front of shower exit doorway into bedroom far of bed right exit doorway into hall turn immediately step left step into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: take a step to stand in front of shower.  exit doorway into bedroom.  go to far end of the bed.  turn right and exit doorway into hall. turn left immediately and take a step.  take another left and step into bathroom in front of the sink.

src: door bed desk single painting closet sink
tgt: Go to the door. Go to the bed. Go to the desk. Go to the single painting. Go to the closet. Go to the sink.

src: in bathroom out of bathroom past bed hallway turn left then bathroom stand in front of mirror combination area
tgt: You're in a bathroom, walk out of the bathroom and past the bed.  Go down a hallway and turn to the left.  Then enter the bathroom and stand in front of the mirror and sink combination area.

src: turn around out of bathroom right out of bedroom right next counter
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom. Take a right and walk out of the bedroom. Take a right and wait next to the counter.

src: turn around out of restroom then door on right stairs right once after counter
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the restroom, then take the door on your right and go up the stairs. Turn right once you get up them, and stop after the counter.

src: exit bathroom bedroom right stairs stop near counter
tgt: Exit the bathroom, exit the bedroom, turn right, go down the stairs, stop near counter.

src: turn left toward kitchen at bottom of stairs right stairs at landing turn forward in hall doorway bathroom on left
tgt: Turn to the left. Walk toward the kitchen. Stop at the bottom of the stairs. Turn right. Go up the stairs. At the landing, turn left. Walk forward. Stop in the hall when the doorway to the bathroom is on the left.

src: turn stairs at top of stairs left hallway in hallway before next room
tgt: Turn left and go up the stairs. At the top of the stairs turn left and go down the hallway. Stop in the hallway before entering the next room.

src: walk toward kitchen counter in direction of wall-mounted tv up stairs right into living area left hallway walk into hallway painting on wall on right in front of painting
tgt: Walk toward the kitchen counter in the direction of the wall-mounted TV. Walk up the stairs to your right and into the living area. To your left there will be a hallway. Walk into the hallway. There is a painting on the wall on your right. Stop in front of the painting.

src: through doorway opposite white double doors left into doorway on right bed on right through doorway on left into bathroom stop
tgt: Go through the doorway opposite the white double doors, make a left, go into the doorway on the right, go passed the bed on the right, go through the doorway on the left, step into the bathroom and stop.

src: exit kitchen bedroom bathroom wait in front of bathtub
tgt: Exit the kitchen and enter the bedroom. Enter the bathroom and wait in front of the bathtub.

src: kitchen into dinning area once in dinning area right through doorway now left turn walk bedroom on right into bedroom left doorway at end of room though doorway wait in bathroom
tgt: You need to leave the kitchen and go into the dinning area. Once you are in the dinning area go right and through the doorway. Now make a left turn and walk to the bedroom on the right, go into the bedroom and make a left to go to the doorway at the end of the room. Go though the doorway and wait in the bathroom.

src: with glass wall immediate left ahead of forward right hallway pass by doors on right then pass by door on left veer slightly right in front of set of double doors left even with jam of single door in front of
tgt: With a glass wall to your immediate left and another one ahead of you, walk forward and turn right down the hallway. Pass by three doors on your right, then pass by a door on your left. Veer slightly right and stop in front of a set of double doors to your left and even with the jam of a single door in front of you.

src: down hall right down hall under exit sign
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn right. Walk down the hall and stop under the exit sign.

src: straight then right down entire hallway until at double doors under exit sign
tgt: Go straight and then head right, down the entire hallway until stopping at the double doors under the exit sign.

src: walk across bedroom in hall
tgt: Walk across bedroom and stop in the hall.

src: exit room walk straight until room wait in hallway
tgt: Exit the room. Walk straight until you exit the room. Wait in the hallway.

src: exit bedroom walk through adjacent room with also bedroom in second bedroom bed on left as window on right in doorway out of second bedroom into hallway
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk through the adjacent room, with is also a bedroom.  In this second bedroom, a bed will be on your left as you pass, and a window will be on your right.  Stop in the doorway leading out of the second bedroom into the hallway.

src: exit room room hallway at double doors tall planter
tgt: Exit dining room to sitting room and continue to arched hallway. Stop at the double doors and tall planter.

src: so room with piano walk past piano entryway on right end of room now through entryway wait in front of tall flower pot beside door outside porch
tgt: You should turn so you are facing the room with the piano and walk past the piano and to the entryway on the right end of the room. Now walk through the entryway and wait in front of the tall flower pot beside the door to the outside porch.

src: turn left walk across living room turn right enter through doorway in front of potted plant

tgt: Enter the bedroom and turn left continuing to the door. Exit the room and go down the steps, waiting on the stairs.

src: exit bathroom into bedroom turn exit on left through stairs stairs until la painting
tgt: Exit the bathroom into the bedroom and turn left. continue to the exit on the left and go through to the stairs. Go down most the stairs until the LA painting.

src: enter bedroom turn halfway stairs
tgt: Enter the bedroom, turn left, wait halfway down the stairs.

src: walk forward fireplace on left side forward hall turn wait at doorway
tgt: Walk forward and pass the fireplace on your left side and continue forward to the hall. Turn left and wait at the doorway.

src: walk across living room chairs in hallway turn in doorway
tgt: walk straight across living room passed all chairs to hallway. In hallway turn left and walk to doorway. Stop in doorway.

src: past chairs into hallway turn there on rug
tgt: Go past the chairs and into the hallway turn left and wait there on the rug.

src: turn tree stairs on first landing
tgt: Turn around and pass the tree. Go to the stairs and stop on the first landing.

src: exit room head towards stairs on right few steps onto level stop
tgt: Exit the room and head towards the stairs on the right, go up a few steps onto the level and stop.

src: walk through doorway stairs up third stair there
tgt: Walk through the doorway. When you get to the stairs go up to the third stair and stop there.

src: walk around sunken area through ninety degree arc right sunken area right side about even with fireplace on right almost end of steps on left turn steps then
tgt: Walk around the sunken area through a ninety degree arc to the right, keeping the sunken area to your right side. When you're about even with the fireplace on your right and almost to the end of the three steps on your left, turn left and climb the three steps. Then stop.

src: walk ahead past large columns then right once right walk forward turn up few steps beside plant under stairwell
tgt: Walk straight ahead past the 2 large columns and then turn right. Once you turn right walk forward, turn left and walk up the few steps and stop beside the plant that is under the stairwell.

src: walk past white couches wait near tall plant at side of stairs
tgt: walk past the white couches, wait near the tall plant at the side of the stairs.

src: turn right into large door on right outside wait there
tgt: Turn right and go into the large door on the right that leads to the outside. Wait there.

src: walk into main room sharp turn right outside just past mat
tgt: Walk into the main room and make a sharp turn right. Walk outside and stop just past the mat.

src: enter open space then through door on right just past black doormat
tgt: Enter the open space, then go through the door on the right.  Wait just past the black doormat.

src: walk straight into room right past bed into bathroom wait in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Walk straight and into the room. Take a right and walk past the bed and into the bathroom. Wait in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: enter building through door into bedroom on right forward at door of bathroom
tgt: Enter the building through the door. Move into the bedroom on the right. Move forward and stop at the door of the bathroom.

src: walk along patio into entrance door home down hall into bedroom walk bed through door bathroom
tgt: Walk along the patio into the nearest entrance door to the home. Walk down the hall into the bedroom. Walk passed the bed and through the door to the bathroom.

src: into front door walk along left side of room until doorway on right side of wall into hallway walk straight ahead at bathroom door
tgt: Go into the front door, and walk along the left side of the room until you reach a doorway on the right side of the wall. Go into the hallway and walk straight ahead. Stop at the bathroom door.

tgt: Enter the house, walk past the front counter, turn left, and enter the bathroom.

src: walk into house through french doors.walk past bar television turn into first doorway women bathroom wait by door
tgt: Walk into the house through the french doors.Walk past the bar and television. Turn left into the first doorway. This is the women's bathroom. Wait by the door.

src: enter house by step through sliding glass door towards kitchen right towards staircase by pillar in center of room area front entrance living room area
tgt: Enter the house by going up the step and through the sliding glass door. Proceed towards the kitchen and turn right towards the staircase. Stop by the pillar in the center of the room separating the dining area, front entrance and living room area.

src: enter building past sitting room right wait near dining table
tgt: Enter the building, past the sitting room and turn right. Wait near the dining table.

src: walk indoors forward area right forward near wooden pillar on left
tgt: Walk indoors, walk forward to the kitchen area, turn right, walk forward and wait near the wooden pillar on the left.

src: exit bedroom staircase bottom of staircase couch
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Go to the staircase. Go to the bottom of the staircase. Go to the couch.

src: head out of bedroom down stairs right into living room wait near sofa
tgt: Head out of the bedroom and down the stairs, turn right into the living room and wait near the sofa.

src: exit room door on right stairs on left right wait near couches
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the right. Go down the stairs on the left. Turn right and wait near the couches.

src: room wait in hall outside door
tgt: Leave the room and wait in the hall, outside the door.

src: out of room wait just outside doorway
tgt: Go out of the room and wait just outside the doorway.

src: exit room through doorway right into doorway stop
tgt: Exit the room through the doorway to the right, step into the doorway and stop.

src: turn up small staircase on step from top
tgt: Turn left and walk up the small staircase. Stop on the 3rd step from the top.

src: stairs wait at top landing
tgt: Walk up stairs. Wait at the top landing.

src: exit room turn stairs stairs before steps away from top of stairs wait there
tgt: Exit the room and turn left to take the stairs. Go up stairs. Stop before two steps away from the top of the stairs. Wait there.

tgt: Turn left and walk through the kitchen, then down the hall.  Then enter the living room on your left.

src: with fireplace on right out of main room past stairs turn in area in front of gold footstool
tgt: With the fireplace on your right, walk straight out of the main room and past the stairs.  Turn left in the sitting area in front of the gold footstool.

src: kitchen through door on right of refrigerator living room through last door on left once room
tgt: Leave the kitchen through the door on the right of the refrigerator. Enter the living room through the last door on the left. Stop once you enter the room.

src: walk into kitchen into hall between refrigerator outdoor cooking area in hall straight into bedroom across hall left into bathroom through last door on left
tgt: Walk into the kitchen, and go into the hall between the refrigerator and the outdoor cooking area. In the hall go straight into the bedroom across the hall. Take a left into the bathroom through the last door on the left.

src: walk around island counter into open door directly ahead tv in open room step into bathroom
tgt: Walk around the island counter and into the open door. Walk directly ahead to the tv in the open room. Step into the bathroom.

src: walk past basket kitchen island walk straight across hall into bedroom walk past bed turn into bathroom stop
tgt: Walk past the basket and kitchen island. Walk straight across the hall into the bedroom. Walk past the bed and turn left. Walk into the bathroom and stop.

src: stairs step in doorway of room closest stairs
tgt: Go up the stairs and step in the doorway of the room closest to the stairs.

src: up stairs at entrance of leftmost room
tgt: Walk up the stairs and stand at the entrance of the leftmost room.

src: turn stairs bedroom at top of stairs
tgt: Turn left and go up the stairs. Go to the bedroom at the top of the stairs.

src: exit bathroom through bedroom exit hallway between kitchen living room back door table
tgt: Exit the bathroom, go through the bedroom and exit it, go down the hallway, walk between the kitchen and living room and stand facing the back door and dining table.

tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and exit the bedroom. Walk across the hallway and turn left and wait by table next to the kitchen area.
