tgt: TUrn around.  Leave the bathroom through the doorway.  Go into the bedroom, past the foot of the bed, turn to the right.  and down the hallway.  Then you'll be in the kitchen/living room.  Go behind the couch and in front of the island area.  Go towards the table, and then wait.

src: turn around down stairs at bottom of stairs walk into first doorway on left once through doorway at entry of laundry room
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs.  At the bottom of the stairs walk into the first doorway on your left.  Stop once you walk through the doorway, at the entry of the laundry room.

src: set of stairs through door on left after through doorway
tgt: Go down the set of stairs and walk through the door on the left.  Stop after passing through the doorway.

src: exit living space by stairs downward way bottom first left doorway there
tgt: Exit the living space by taking the stairs that lead downward. Walk all the way to the bottom. Take the first left. Enter the doorway. Stop there.

src: left straight.then stop at near bathroom opp side
tgt: To take left and go straight.Then stop at near bathroom. To take opp side.

src: turn on hallway after stairs straight towards brown chairs right in room before brown charis
tgt: Turn left on the hallway after the stairs, walk straight towards the two brown chairs, turn right in the room before the two brown charis.

src: walk past steps into hallway turn down hall down steps right just before chairs in front of doorway
tgt: Walk past the steps into the hallway. Turn left and walk down the hall. Walk down the steps and turn right just before the chairs. Stop in front of the doorway.

src: walk forward through open door forward open door on right hand side into room with medical table
tgt: WALK FORWARD THROUGH THE OPEN DOOR, CONTINUE FORWARD AND ENTER THE OPEN DOOR ON THE RIGHT HAND SIDE, WALK INTO THE ROOM WITH A MEDICAL TABLE.

src: past telephone out door straight right door then room before water table
tgt: Go past the telephone and out the door.  Go straight but take the right door.  Then enter the room and stop before you get to the water table.

tgt: Walk passed the massage tables and through the open door near the foot of the tables and into the hall. Walk through the open door to the right into the room with the tanning machine.

tgt: Walk towards the mirror then turn right. Exit the bathroom and take the doorway on the left. Go past the wooden shelves and into the conference room. Go through the door turn right at the first doorway and then enter the room.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and go slightly left through the second door across the hall. Walk through the double doors on the left. Enter the first door on the right and wait inside near the sitting area.

tgt: Turn right and walk towards the mirror. Turn right again and exit the bathroom via the left door. Turn right and walk through the other doorway. Walk across the office and take the hallway to the left. Enter the first room to the right with a painting on the wall.

src: walk staircase staircase in middle of staircase
tgt: walk to the staircase, go down the staircase and stop in the middle of the staircase.

src: turn staircase staircase about way down then wait there
tgt: Turn around and go to the staircase.  Go down the staircase.  Go about half way down and then stop.  Wait there.

src: down hallway overlook stairs right halfway stairs
tgt: Walk down the hallway to the overlook, go down the stairs to the right, wait halfway down the stairs.

src: turn around past dining room bath room on left wait near closet doors
tgt: Turn around and walk past the dining room and enter the bath room on your left.  Wait near the closet doors.

tgt: Turn hard right and walk towards the balcony area. Walk across and under the balcony. Enter the doorway left of the stairs. Wait there.

tgt: Turn around and walk into the middle room behind you with the long black table and the large painting of sailboats. Walk to the other side of the room towards the steps past the long black table. Once you reach the steps, turn left and walk forward into the small red and white hallway ahead. Stop once you enter the hallway.

tgt: Continue down the stairs and turn let. Walk through the entrance ahead, into the bedroom. Walk past the bed and lounge chairs and start down the stairs ahead. Walk halfway down the stairs.

tgt: Walk down the stairs and turn left. Walk into the building and past the orange chairs. Walk through the glass door and stop on the third step from the bottom.

tgt: Go down the stairs. Once you reach the grilling area, turn left and enter the house. Walk straight across the room and enter the glass door to go down the steps. Stop at the bottom of the steps.

src: walk kitchen out of room hall past large ornately mirror right hand side
tgt: Walk to the kitchen, it is out of this room and straight down the hall past the large ornately framed mirror to the right hand side.

src: walk down hallway love seat on right right at first doorway after large mirror on left doorway then wait
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway passing a love seat on your right. Turn right at the first doorway after you pass a large mirror on the left. Enter the doorway then wait.

tgt: Walk through the hallway, and out of the bedroom. Walk straight down the hall and take the first right into the kitchen through the first door on the right. Stop next to the pantry door.

src: turn around down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: way down stairs at bottom stop
tgt: Go all the way down the stairs and at the bottom stop.

src: turn around down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit bathroom outside outside on porch
tgt: Exit bathroom to bedroom, turn left , walk to door going outside. stop outside on porch.

src: bathroom through bedroom out of bedroom through patio door once on patio
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go through the bedroom. Go out of the bedroom through the patio door. Stop once you are on the patio.

tgt: Leave the bathroom and go straight into the bedroom. Make a left to go to the hall then make a slight right and wait in the doorway of the side door going outside.

tgt: Go straight into the bedroom and turn right until you reach the fireplace.

src: walk straight toward bed wait near fireplace on right
tgt: Walk straight toward the bed. Wait near the fireplace on the right.

src: walk foot of bed right towards fireplace stand in corner behind chair fireplace
tgt: Walk to the foot of the bed and turn right towards the fireplace.  Stand in the corner behind the chair and the fireplace.

src: toward lounge chairs left after wall with glass frosted glass hall past wall sculpture wait in doorway between paintings
tgt: Go toward the three lounge chairs and take a left after the wall with glass and frosted glass. Go down the hall past the wall sculpture and wait in the doorway between the two paintings.

tgt: Walk straight until you see three lounge chairs. Turn left and go straight until you pass a room with a large square design on the floor. Go out the door on the far left and wait at the entrance.

tgt: Walk around the hollow square wall and to the left. Walk down the hall wand into the doorway between the paintings. Stop in the doorway.

tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn left. Walk past the wooden churner and turn left. Walk to the right of the table and stop to the left of the painting.

src: exit bedroom straight down patio turn at room wait at entrance living room
tgt: Exit bedroom to hallway, turn left and walk straight down patio, turn left at dining room, wait at entrance to living room.

src: door from forward through doorway then ninety degrees left paved corridor until area through large opening walk past dining table with table left entrance room on right just past dining table just
tgt: Facing the door furthest from you, walk forward through the doorway, then turn ninety degrees to the left. Continue down the paved corridor until you can enter the dining area to your left through the large opening. Walk past the dining table with the table to your left and stop to the entrance to the room on your right, just past the dining table you just passed.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and to the right. Walk past the dresser and out of the bedroom. Walk to the right and stop just inside the doorway by the stairs.

tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and exit the room using the door on the right. Turn right and go down the hallway. Wait near the grand piano.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk through the master bathroom.  Enter the hallway to the right, proceed forward and wait by the stairs.

tgt: TURN RIGHT TO FACE AN OPEN DOOR WITH A CABINET ON THE RIGHT, WALK THOUGH THE DOOR INTO A HALLWAY, TURN LEFT AND WALK DOWN A SHORT HALLWAY, FACING A NEW ROOM WITH A COUCH ON THE RIGHT AND A STAIR CASE ON THE LEFT AND WITH A DOOR WAY IN FRONT OF YOU WALK FORWARD TOWARDS THE DOORWAY, WALK TO THE END OF THE HALL SO THAT YOU ARE FACING TWO BEDROOMS, TURN SLIGHTLY TO THE LEFT AND WALK INTO THE BEDROOM ON THE LEFT HAND SIDE.

src: through door hall turn cross over glass floor small hallway doorway of room on left
tgt: Go through the door to the hall. Turn left and cross over the glass floor to the small hallway. Go to the doorway of the room on the left.

src: turn right exit room turn across hallway room turn bedroom wait there
tgt: Turn right exit the room. Turn left and walk across the hallway and room. Turn left and enter the bedroom. Wait there.

tgt: With the black and white painting to your left, walk straight towards the room with the couch and rug in it.  When you enter this room, walk through it and walk outside.  Stop just after stepping outside.

tgt: Turn to your left and walk down the hallway to the end. Once you are in the room. Walk through the room and out the door leading outside and stop.

tgt: Go forward though the door. Go over the rug and between the couch and chairs. Stop outside.

tgt: Walk into the garage and turn right. Walk into the doorway on the right and stop just inside the fitness room.

tgt: Turn right and go into the garage. Turn right and go into the room. Wait there.

tgt: At the bottom of the stairs, take the first right and enter through the doorway. As soon as you are in the garage, continue to the closest door which should be on the right hand side. Enter through and you'll find a room that has a exercise machine, gym mats, a table, etc and that'll be your destination.

tgt: Exit out the door and walk towards the second corner on the right that leads to the staircase. Walk down the staircase, and stop at the middle of the stairs.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk towards the stairs. Then walk down the stairs stopping in the middle of  the stairs.

tgt: Go towards refrigerator and turn right. Go though doorway. Go towards the stairs and wait on 3rd step.

tgt: Walk in the direction of the refrigerator rand take a right to exit the kitchen. Walk to the stairs and go up four stairs stopping on the fourth stair.

tgt: Walk out of the kitchen and straight across the rug directly in front of you and proceed to the colorfully painted staircase.

tgt: Leave the bathroom and go up the stairs.  Stop at the top of the staircase in front of the railing.

tgt: Turn left and go up to the top of the staircase.

tgt: Walk down the hallway towards the first exit sign on your right, take a left down the hallway right in front of the exit sign, take a left down the first hallway, stop under the exit sign.

tgt: Walk across the hall. Turn left on the first hallway to your left. Keep walking and turn left again on the first hallway to your left. Wait there.

tgt: Go down the hall, make a left, continue down hall until you get to an exit sign on the left, then stop at the exit sign.

tgt: Turn left and walk toward the patio. Walk past the chairs, go through the sliding door and wait just inside the living room.

src: straight toward couches in patio into house wait near circular couches
tgt: Go straight toward the couches in the patio. Go into the house and wait near the circular couches.

src: stand with stairs on left walk straight along pathway right walkway off way walk past pillars area outside into building just after into building near sofa in front of fireplace
tgt: Stand with the stairs on your left and walk straight along the pathway.  Turn right when the walkway branches off that way and walk past the pillars and sitting area outside and into the building.  Stop just after stepping into the building, near a sofa in front of a fireplace.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and through the television room into the hallway. In the hall go to the stairs and go up the stairs, stopping on the fourth from the top stair.

src: exit bathroom room up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom, exit the waiting room, walk up the stairs, wait at the top of the stairs.

tgt: Exit the bathroom into the living room. Continue up the spiral staircase and stop three-quarters of the way up the staircase.

tgt: Walk up the stairs and into the kitchen. Wait near the barstools.

tgt: Walk up the flight of stairs and turn the corner continuing up to the top of the stairs. Walk towards the island counter in the middle of the room with bar stools on one side.

src: up stairs in front of way top once kitchen behind bar stools
tgt: Walk up the stairs in front of you all the way to the top. Stop once you enter the kitchen behind the bar stools.

tgt: Turn left at the coffee table, and walk towards the end off the hallway. There will be entryways on either side of you, ignore them and continue going straight. When you move forward once again you will come to a wall to your left and an option to turn right. Ignore the hallway to turn right and continue going straight. You will enter a doorway and there will be a coffee table to your right. Continue towards the stairs. Your final destination is at the foot of the steps.

src: from entrance go hallway straight until at base of stairwell
tgt: From the entrance go left down the hallway, straight until stopping at the base of the stairwell.

src: down hall past double doors at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the hall past the double doors. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: inside right bed doorway left down hall door on left stop
tgt: Go inside and turn right. Go passed the bed and enter the doorway. Go to your left and walk down the hall. Enter the door on the left and stop.

src: walk into left bedroom door past bed walk into hallway turn left past last picture in bedroom doorway
tgt: Walk into the left bedroom door past the bed. Walk into the hallway and turn left. Turn left past the last picture and stop in the bedroom doorway.

tgt: Walk forward and go left. Go down the hallway, and into the foyer. Stop in front of the main entry door.

tgt: Walk to the counter and turn left. Walk through both entryways and stop between the front door and the dining room table and chairs.

tgt: Walk into the room with a sink and long counter top. Walk through the room along the counter and walk through the arched doorway at the end. Turn the corner and walk past the open draped window. Continue into the open area ahead and stop near the dining area with a spherical chandelier above.

src: exit sitting room towards kitchen in front of door near dining table
tgt: Exit the sitting room, walk towards the kitchen and stop in front of the door, near the dining table.

src: walk toward fireplace then right right again then straight until round table with candles in clear vase on right there
tgt: Walk toward the fireplace then turn right. Turn right again then go straight until you get to a  round table with three candles in a clear vase on the right. Wait there.

src: turn right circle around couch forward at table
tgt: Turn right. Circle around couch. Go forward. Stop at table.

src: walk toward kitchen stairs wait on fourth step
tgt: Walk toward kitchen and ascend stairs and wait on fourth step.

src: walk straight toward kitchen right steps straight steps
tgt: Walk straight toward the kitchen. Turn right and go up the three steps. Continue straight and go up two more steps.

tgt: Head into the kitchen and turn right to walk up the stairs. Stop and wait on the stairs near the first window.

tgt: Walk out the door to your right. Once out, turn left and then left again to enter the bathroom. Stop in front of the sinks.

tgt: Exit the room using the door on the right. Turn left and go into the room next door on the left. Wait near the sink.

tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn through a one hundred eighty degree arc to the left to enter the bathroom, stopping at the entrance to the shower.

tgt: Walk forward into lobby with benches.  Turn left after table with white cloth.  Walk to water fountain.  Wait here.

tgt: Go straight toward the round table. Turn left before you get to the round table and wait near the drinking fountain.

src: small white table in middle of room into room across from drinking fountain
tgt: Go to the small white table in the middle of the room. Go into the room across from you that has a drinking fountain.

src: room with table right cabinet left walk towards glass wall behind lattice room divider glass door wall table in front of slightly left walk into kitchen
tgt: FACING A ROOM WITH A TABLE TO THE RIGHT AND A CABINET TO THE LEFT WALK TOWARDS A GLASS WALL BEHIND A LATTICE ROOM DIVIDER, FACING THE GLASS DOOR WALL AND A TABLE IN FRONT OF YOU TURN SLIGHTLY TO THE LEFT AND WALK INTO THE KITCHEN.

tgt: Move straight past the wooden room divider, then make a sharp right into the doorway of the kitchen. Wait in the doorway.

src: walk past table around screen back door then
tgt: Walk past the table and around the screen to the back door then turn left.

src: walk out of laundry room turn wait by dinning room table
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room, turn left and wait by the dinning room table.

tgt: walk past the washer and dryer and exit the laundry room. Turn left and proceed next to the dining table with a wooden bench and stop.

tgt: Turn around and walk out the door by the sink, Make a left turn, walking to the dining bench.

tgt: Go into the hallway and turn left. Walk past the stairs and wait outside on the doorstep.

tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom. Take a left. When you get to the rug, take a left. Walk outside and wait just outside the door.

tgt: Turn right at the bottom of the stairs and enter the room at the end.  Turn left after walking into the bedroom and walk into the bathroom.  Stop in front of the first sink.

src: straight hallway until room turn into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Go straight down the hallway until you get to a room. Turn left and go into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: turn bedroom then again bathroom next bath tub
tgt: Turn left and enter the bedroom. Then turn left again and enter the bathroom. Stand next to the bath tub.

src: up stairs right at open doorway left walk into room by bed
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Make a right at the open doorway. Make a left and walk into the room, by the bed.

src: stairs right into hall turn bedroom at bed
tgt: Go up the stairs, turn right and go into the hall, turn left and enter the bedroom, stop at bed.

src: forward of way up stairs then right open doorway through doorway left large bedroom wait there
tgt: Walk forward all of the way up the stairs, then turn to the right to an open doorway.  Go through the doorway, veering to the left where you'll see a large bedroom, wait there.

src: living room enter hall turn forward down hall slight right furniture right at laundry room facing trash
tgt: leave living room and enter hall turn left and go forward down hall. Make a slight right to avoid furniture. Turn right at laundry room and stop facing trash can.

src: across hallway room right wait in doorway laundry room
tgt: Go across the hallway and enter the room. Turn right and wait in the doorway to the laundry room.

src: left out of double doors straight ahead chair at end of hall right into utility room
tgt: Make a left and walk out of the double doors. Walk straight ahead to the chair at the end of the hall. Make a right into the utility room.

src: up flight of wooden stairs top animal head on wall walk into bedroom area near closet door
tgt: Walk up the flight of wooden stairs to the top. Pass the mounted animal head on the wall and walk into the bedroom area near the closet door.

src: turn around up stairs then slight right in doorway in front of
tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs, then turn slight right and stand in the doorway in front of you.

src: turn up stairs straight doorway step into bedroom
tgt: Turn left and walk up the stairs.  Go straight, to a doorway.  Walk one step into the bedroom.

src: exit bedroom right kitchen wait by light switch
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right. Turn left to enter the kitchen. Wait by the light switch.

src: walk out of bedroom into hallway ahead right down hallway past wall art into door on left kitchen area near central counter top with sink in
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom into the hallway ahead. Turn right and walk down the hallway past the hanging wall art. Turn into the door on the left that leads to a kitchen area and stop near the central counter top with a sink built in.

src: walk out of bedroom right into entryway on left in kitchen
tgt: walk out of the bedroom and turn right. Walk into the entryway on the left and stop in the kitchen.

src: walk forward towards living room walk around futon into bathroom inside bathroom
tgt: Walk forward towards the living room.  Walk around the futon and into the bathroom. Stop inside the bathroom.

src: walk past stairs on left room with large wraparound couch walk through room enter until just inside bathroom
tgt: Walk past the stairs on your left and enter the room with the large wraparound couch.  Walk through this room and enter until just inside the bathroom.

src: walk inside room across stairs slightly right towards bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Walk inside the room across the stairs. Turn slightly right and walk towards the bathroom and wait by the sink.

src: exit bathroom at stairs
tgt: Exit bathroom to hallway and wait at the stairs.

src: continue in hallway right in hall stop at top of stairs
tgt: Continue straight and in to the hallway. Turn right in the hall and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: doorways from bathroom hallway few step slightly right steps down staircase wait by top of stairs
tgt: Walk out two doorways from the bathroom. Enter the hallway and make a few step slightly left. Turn right and take two steps down the staircase. Wait by the top of the stairs.

src: stairs left at living room kitchen left into fitness room next door
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left at the living room. Enter the kitchen and take a left into the fitness room. Stop next to the door.

src: set of stairs turn left left hallway right into next room into exercise room
tgt: Go down the set of stairs and turn left. Go down the left hallway and turn right into the next room. Go left into the exercise room.

src: stairs u turn straight until dining room with table chairs at table chairs into room on left wait near treadmill
tgt: Go down the stairs. U turn left. Go straight until you get to the dining room with a table and chairs. At the table and chairs go into the room on the left. Wait near the treadmill.

src: continue through hallway great room then near bookshelves
tgt: Continue through the hallway, pass the great room, then stop near the bookshelves.

src: walk past floral arrangement on floor right past potted plant on floor right through open white door wait at wall radiator on right
tgt: Walk past the floral arrangement on the floor to the right. Walk past the potted plant on the floor to the right. Walk through the open white door. Wait at the wall radiator on the right.

src: walk far end of hallway through door wait in front of bookshelf
tgt: Walk to the far end of the hallway and through the door. Wait in front of the bookshelf.

src: stairs right into room right of horse picture on wall into bathroom of room couple of feet into bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairs and turn right. Go into the room to the right of the horse picture on the wall. Go into the bathroom of that room and stop a couple of feet into the bathroom.

src: climb stairs then hard right room right after bedroom towards left bathroom on left
tgt: Climb the stairs and then take a hard right to enter the room to your right. After entering the bedroom, continue towards your left and enter the bathroom that will be on your left.

src: stairs right at horse painting enter bedroom turn bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Go up stairs and turn right at horse painting and enter bedroom. Turn left and enter the bathroom. Wait by sink.

src: past couch down hallway right kitchen wait there
tgt: Go past the couch and down the hallway.  Stop right when you get to the kitchen.  Wait there.

src: porch right then down hall wait in entryway of kitchen
tgt: Leave the porch and make a right then walk down the hall and wait in the entryway of the kitchen.

src: walk forward around black leather chair on left forward past dining table wait at entrance kitchen
tgt: Walk forward, around the black leather chair on the left. Continue forward past the dining table and wait at the entrance to the kitchen.

src: bathroom ad bedroom room on left of stairs before fireplace
tgt: Leave the bathroom ad bedroom. Enter the room on the left of the stairs. Stop before you pass the fireplace.

src: turn exit into bedroom.once in bedroom turn bedroom into hallway hallway left of stairs hallway way until bedroom outdoors
tgt: Turn around and exit into the bedroom.Once in the bedroom, Turn left and exit the bedroom Into the hallway. Follow the hallway to the left of the stairs. Continue down the hallway all the way until you reach the bedroom and stop facing the outdoors.

src: exit bathroom then bedroom via exit left veer left stairs downwards through door opening at abstract painting ninety degrees left step into bedroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom, then exit the bedroom via the exit to the left. Veer to the left, bypassing the stairs leading downwards and go through the door opening. At the abstract painting, turn ninety degrees to the left and step into the bedroom.

src: walk past round table chairs stairs on right on landing straight rather than rest of stairs on right into doorway of room with fireplace chairs in in doorway of room
tgt: Walk past the round table and chairs and go up the stairs on the right.  On the landing, keep going straight rather than going up the rest of the stairs on the right and go into the doorway of the room with a fireplace and chairs in it.  Stop in the doorway of this room.

src: turn around straight chairs until stairs on right up top of stairs stop
tgt: Turn around and walk straight passed the chairs until you reach the stairs on your right. Walk up to the top of the stairs and stop.

src: walk then right small stair then living room
tgt: walk straight then turn right, go up the small stair then enter the living room.

src: turn right in between counter table chairs walk left of bar ahead wait in entry way of garage
tgt: Turn to the right. Walk in between the counter and table and chairs. Walk to the left of the bar ahead. Wait in the entry way of the garage.

src: walk into kitchen hall on left into garage at end of hall on rug in garage
tgt: Walk into the kitchen and go down the hall on the left. Go into the garage at the end of the hall. Stop on the rug in the garage.

src: walk past kitchen into hall left of big mirror on wall way down hall into garage just inside garage on doormat
tgt: Walk past the kitchen and into the hall to the left of the big mirror on the wall. Go all the way down the hall and into the garage. Stop just inside the garage, on the doormat.

src: walk towards foot of bed turn walk through doorway bedroom turn at top of stairs
tgt: walk towards foot of bed, turn left, walk straight through doorway to exit bedroom, turn left and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: exit bedroom stop at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the bedroom and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: exit room through middle door turn directly in front of stairs
tgt: Exit the room through the middle door. Turn left, and walk directly in front of the stairs.

src: stairs stop
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop.

src: turn around down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs stop after last step
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop after stepping off the last step.

src: turn bathroom walk along hallway right wait by white sofa portrait
tgt: Turn left and exit the bathroom. Walk along the hallway. Turn right and wait by the white sofa and portrait.

src: walk out of bathroom across hall right through double doors behind couch
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and across the hall. Turn right and walk through the double doors. Stop behind the couch.

src: bathroom hall at end of hall right living room next shelves on right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go down the hall. At the end of the hall take a right and enter the living room. Stop next to the three shelves on the right.

src: walk forward past table with lamp forward past dining room table in front of stairs
tgt: Walk forward past the table with the lamp. Keep walking forward past the dining room table and stop in front of the stairs.

src: walk behind couch across living room towards stairs slight right head towards stairs stairs
tgt: walk behind the couch across the living room towards the stairs. turn slight right and head towards the stairs. Stop when you reach the stairs.

src: walk out of living room away from patio walk through dining room stairway at foot of stairs
tgt: Walk out of the living room, away from the patio. Walk through the dining room and to the stairway. Stop at the foot of the stairs.

src: walk through front entrance of house straight then once in main living room wait once in living room
tgt: Walk through the front entrance of the house. Keep walking straight and then turn left once in the main living room and wait once in the smaller living room.

src: inside through front door continue through door with oval window turn immediately into living area next chair with flower pattern
tgt: Go inside through the front door. Continue straight through the door with the oval window. Turn left immediately into the living area. Stop next to the chair with the flower pattern.

src: walk straight large wooden doors house once inside house into first room on left stop
tgt: Walk straight and enter the 2 large wooden doors and enter the house. Once inside the house, turn into the first room on your left and stop.

src: turn then slightly hallway on yellow rug hallway until right of gold mirror then right turn wooden table then head straight until on grey mat on floor wait there
tgt: Turn around, then turn slightly left and head down the hallway, stepping on the yellow rug. Continue down the hallway until you're to the right of the gold framed mirror, then turn right. Turn left when you reach the wooden table, then head straight until you're standing on the grey mat on the floor. Wait there.

src: turn right along rug right hand turn at end of hallway walk between table pedestal top of stairs wait at top of stairway
tgt: Turn right and walk along the rug. Make a right hand turn at the end of the hallway. Walk between the table and the pedestal to the top of the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairway.

src: exit doorway turn left way down hallway right under arch wait in front of double doors by stairs
tgt: Exit the doorway and turn to the left. Go all the way down the hallway. Turn right and go under the arch. Wait in front of the double doors by the stairs.

src: turn around past stairs down hallway slightly left way down hallway until bedroom on end once
tgt: Turn around and walk past the stairs and down the hallway slightly to the left. Keep walking all the way down the hallway until you enter the bedroom on the end and stop once you enter.

src: head in direction of stairs upwards pass by with stairs on right past wooden door right mirrored doors on right then right narrow corridor corridor past fireplace on right through door directly ahead of into bedroom
tgt: Head in the direction of the stairs leading upwards and pass by them with the stairs on your right. Move past the wooden door to your right, the mirrored doors on your right, and then turn right down the narrow corridor. Continue down the corridor past the fireplace on your right and through the door opening directly ahead of you into the bedroom.

src: stairs down long hallway until bedroom
tgt: Go left passed the stairs and down the long hallway until you reach the bedroom.

src: walk stairs bottom
tgt: Walk to the stairs and go down.  Stop when you reach the bottom.

src: walk downstairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk downstairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk ahead left stairs turn way down stairs stopping at very bottom
tgt: Walk straight ahead and turn left and go down the stairs. Turn and go all the way down the stairs stopping at the very bottom.

src: bathroom right hallway in office
tgt: Leave the bathroom and turn right. Go down the hallway and stop in the office.

src: exit bathroom then right by door right then door left then room at end of corridor through double frosted glass wooden doors
tgt: Exit the bathroom and then turn right, passing by the door to your right, then the door to your left. Then enter the room at the end of the corridor through the double frosted glass and wooden doors.

src: exit bathroom right down hall through doorway in front of at end of hall in front of table in room
tgt: Exit the bathroom and make a right.  Walk down the hall and through the doorway in front of you at the end of the hall.  Stop in front of the table in that room.

src: walk out of room across hall into doorway between paintings stop
tgt: Walk out of the room and across the hall into the doorway between the paintings and stop.

src: walk doorway out of room walk across square mosaic floor opposite wall through door on right in doorway room
tgt: Walk to the doorway leading out of the room.  Walk across the square mosaic floor to the opposite wall and go through the door on the right.  Stop in the doorway to this room.

src: room doorway on right on wall on opposite side of floor mosaic in doorway of room
tgt: Leave the room and go to the doorway on the right on the wall on the opposite side of the floor mosaic.  Stop in the doorway of this room.

src: straight into next room fireplace bear entryway on left then
tgt: Go straight into the next room. Go Passed the fireplace and the bear and  and enter the entryway on the left. Then stop.

src: from entrance straight ahead from fireplace carpeted path begins
tgt: From the entrance go straight ahead and turn left from the fireplace. Stop there where the carpeted path begins.

src: enter room turn at fireplace wait in hallway by cabinet
tgt: Enter the room and turn left at the fireplace. Wait in the hallway by the cabinet.

src: exit bedroom right right at laundry room wait in front of bathroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom and take a right. Turn right at the laundry room. Wait in front of the bathroom.

src: exit room by straight then straight until n't anymore turn right walk straight until door right way into room wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room by walking straight then continue going straight until you can't go anymore turn right and walk straight until you get to a door. Turn right and head all the way down into the room. Wait at the entrance.

src: exit bedroom bathroom right hall right before laundry room step into bedroom stop before tile
tgt: Exit the bedroom, exit the bathroom, turn right down the hall, turn right before the laundry room, and take a step into the bedroom and stop before the tile runs out.

src: move forward through door then down hallway through into living room at end of hall just inside room
tgt: Move forward through the door and then turn left. Head down the hallway, walk through the into the living room at the end of the hall and stop just inside the room.

src: move forward turn through hallway living room wait near white couch
tgt: Move forward, turn left, walk through the hallway, enter the living room and wait near the white couch.

src: through hallway with glass doors left left brown double doors on left few feet shy of rug
tgt: Go through the hallway with the glass doors to the left, make a left, go passed the brown double doors on the left, stop a few feet shy of the rug.

src: bedroom into hallway stairs on fourth step from bottom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and go into the hallway. Go down the stairs. Stop on the fourth step from the bottom.

src: bathroom right at intersection left slight left stairs few steps short of bottom stop
tgt: Go passed the bathroom to the right and at the intersection take a left and go slight left down the stairs, a few steps short of the bottom stop.

src: exit bathroom turn down stairs near bottom stair
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Walk down the stairs and stop near the bottom stair.

src: turn room then promptly stairs into arched hallway wait near bathroom door
tgt: Turn around to exit the room, then promptly turn left, pass the stairs and into the arched hallway. Wait near the bathroom door.

src: turn hallway walk past stairs near bathroom door
tgt: Turn around and enter the hallway.  Walk past the stairs and stand near the bathroom door.

src: walk out of room with tv left into small hallway left stairs walk around stairs just short of bathroom doors
tgt: Walk out of the room with the TV to your left. Walk into the small hallway and make a left towards the stairs. Walk around the stairs and stop just short of the bathroom doors.

src: up steps right up steps right past table chairs walk right through doorway past couch inside bedroom
tgt: Walk up the steps and turn right. Walk up the steps and walk right past the table and chairs. Walk right through the doorway past the couch and stop inside the bedroom.

src: walk upstairs room wait in bedroom next table
tgt: Walk upstairs to the sitting room. Wait in the bedroom next to the table.

src: up stairs toward table right into bedroom wait in door area
tgt: Walk up stairs, walk toward dinning table, turn right into bedroom, and wait in door area.

src: walk past foot of bed out door just after out of room
tgt: Walk past the foot of the bed and out the door.  Stop just after stepping out of the room.

src: walk past bed through open door slightly right once large windows
tgt: Walk past the bed and through the open door, turning slightly right and stopping once you see the two large windows.

src: continue straight arrive at open door at end of room turn through door once past door stop railing directly in front of
tgt: Continue walking straight and arrive at the open door at the end of the room.  Turn left to walk through the door.  Once past the door, stop.  A railing should be directly in front of you.

src: enter bedroom right past first room on right past stairs on left into living area by piano
tgt: Enter the bedroom and turn right. Walk past the first room on your right and past the stairs on your left. Turn left into the living area and stop by the piano.

src: enter bedroom right down hall way left into living room stop between gray chaise lounger white chair with ottoman
tgt: Enter the bedroom and take a right. Walk down the hall way and take a left into the living room. Stop between the gray chaise lounger, and the white chair with ottoman.

src: turn around through open door right turn arm chair down hall left at large open living room stand between lounge chair piano
tgt: Turn around and walk through the open door. Make a right turn when you see the arm chair. Walk down the hall. Make a left at the large open living room and stand between the lounge chair and the piano.

src: face fireplace walk through door left of fireplace great room stop through doors before first circular dining table
tgt: Face the fireplace and walk through the door to the left of the fireplace to enter the "Great Room."  Stop when you get through the doors before you get to the first circular dining table.

src: walk through living room fire place through open glass double doors into room with great room plaque above door walk into dining room stop near table ahead
tgt: Walk through the living room passed the fire place. Go through the open glass double doors into the room with great room plaque above the door. Walk into the dining room and stop near the closest table ahead.

src: forward in front of book case move arch way of great room then through then forward dining table
tgt: Move forward to stand in front of the book case. Move to stand facing the arch way of the great room and then move through it. Then move forward to face the nearest dining table.

src: head hallway turn into bedroom by railing into bedroom stop by bed
tgt: Head down the hallway and turn left into the bedroom by the railing.  Go into the bedroom and stop by the bed.

src: travel forward down hallway past potted plant railing straight until doorway on left room on left
tgt: Travel forward down the hallway, past the potted plant, you will reach some railing, continue straight until you reach the doorway on your left, enter the room on your left.

src: walk way down hallway turn at very first corner brown railing visible on right bedroom door at rug underneath bed
tgt: Walk all the way straight down the hallway. Turn left at the very first corner where the brown railing is visible on the right. Enter the bedroom door, and stop at the rug placed underneath the bed.

src: turn table at end of long table bathtub cross into room next stairs
tgt: Turn left and go passed the table. At the end of the long table, pass the bathtub and cross into the room. Stop next to the stairs.

src: exit door beneath exit sign turn walk towards silver enter room behind bathtub wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Exit the door beneath the exit sign.  Turn left, and walk towards silver bathtub.  Enter room behind bathtub.  Wait at bottom of stairs.

src: exit room through open door walk past table bathtub through double doors wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Exit the room through the open door. Walk past the table and the bathtub. Go through the double doors and wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: straight in between table china closet.turn towards piano turn right hallway wait
tgt: Go straight in between the table and china closet.Turn left and walk towards the piano. Turn, right, enter the hallway, and wait.

src: walk toward grand piano piano turn right in hallway
tgt: Walk toward the grand piano. When you get to the piano turn right. Wait in that hallway.

src: walk through living room left piano right at piano hall once in hall
tgt: Walk through the living room, and take a left towards the piano. Take a right at the piano and enter the hall. Stop once you are in the hall.

src: through hallway stand in front of bathroom door
tgt: Go through the hallway and stand in front of the bathroom door.

src: degree turn down hallway past openings on side of passageway down steps through open doorway destination
tgt: Make a 180 degree turn and walk down the hallway past the two openings on either side of the passageway. Walk down the steps and through the open doorway and there you'll have reached your destination.

src: stairs head straight down hall ahead bedroom at end of hall once onto carpet
tgt: Go down the three stairs, and head straight, down the hall ahead. Enter the bedroom at the end of the hall. Stop once you step onto the carpet.

src: veer right of pool table then stairs wait on landing by baluster
tgt: Veer right of the Pool Table and then walk down the stairs. Wait on the landing by the baluster.

src: walk right of pool table right top of stairs staircase
tgt: Walk to the right of the pool table. Turn right and go to the top of the stairs. Go down the staircase.

src: right pool table stairs on left stairs stop
tgt: Go to the right passed the pool table and to the stairs on the left. Go down the stairs and stop.

src: stairs left across second set of stairs up stairs on second stair from bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. Walk across to the second set of stairs and walk up two stairs and stop on the second stair from the bottom.

src: down stairs turn at bottom of staircase walk towards next staircase up steps stop
tgt: walk down the stairs. turn left at the bottom of the staircase. walk towards the next staircase, up two steps, and stop.

src: walk downstairs past table wait on second step of stairs left
tgt: Walk downstairs, past the table and wait on the second step of the stairs to the left.

src: walk far end of sitting room wait at bottom of steps
tgt: Walk to the far end of the sitting room and wait at the bottom of the steps.

src: walk behind couch end of couch turn down stairs so kitchen in front of
tgt: Walk behind the couch, when you get to the end of the couch, turn left and  walk down the stairs so you can see the kitchen in front of you.

src: turn hall stairs left stop
tgt: Turn around and go down the hall. Go down the stairs to the left and stop.

src: walk forward turn at first visible corner inside right towards closet in front of handbags
tgt: Walk forward and turn left at the first visible corner. Walk inside, and turn right towards the closet. Stop in front of all the handbags.

src: room walk straight hall turn at end after few steps right closet just after into room
tgt: Leave the room and walk straight down the hall and turn left at the end.  After taking a few steps, turn right and enter the closet.  Stop just after stepping into this room.

src: exit really nice closet down hallway then into extra nice closet on right wait near hand bags
tgt: Exit the really nice closet, walk down the hallway. Then turn left and walk into the extra nice closet on your right. Wait near the hand bags.

src: walk through bedroom hard right up stairs wait on rug next book shelves
tgt: Walk through the bedroom and make a hard right and walk up the stairs. Wait on the rug next to the book shelves.

src: doorway right of bed head stairs at top
tgt: Go out the doorway to the right of the bed and head up the stairs, stopping at the top.

src: exit bedroom right stairs in middle of red rug next plant
tgt: exit bedroom to the right and go up stairs. stop in the middle of red rug next to plant.

src: walk past bed room on right stairs stop at bottom
tgt: Walk past the bed and go to the room on the right. Go down the stairs and stop at the bottom.

src: walk left of bed exit through door hall down hall right turn at stairs down stairs halfway stairs
tgt: Walk to the left of the bed. Exit through the door that leads to the hall. Walk down the hall. Right turn at stairs. Walk down the stairs. Stop halfway down the stairs.

src: walk left of bed through door right of painting of girl walk into hallway stairs wait on stair
tgt: Walk to the left of the bed and through the door to the right of the painting of the girl. Walk into the hallway and head down the stairs. Wait on the 11th stair.

src: stairs toward kitchen area right doorways here through very middle into empty room couple of feet inside of room
tgt: Go down the stairs. Walk toward the kitchen area. Turn right. There are 5 doorways here. Go through the very middle one into the empty room. Stop a couple of feet inside of that room.

src: down stairs right at couch right into middle room on right wait in room
tgt: Walk down the stairs and turn right at the couch. Take a right into the middle room on the right. Wait in this room.

src: down stairs right past couch into hallway walk into third door from right just inside doorway
tgt: Walk down the stairs and turn right. Walk past the couch and into the hallway. Walk into the third door from the right and stop just inside the doorway.

src: walk across far side of corridor then near stairway on left wait
tgt: Walk across to the far side of the corridor, then stop near the stairway on the left and wait.

src: turn around across room with large carpet wait by bench just before stairs entrance on left
tgt: Turn around and walk across the room with the large carpet. Wait by the bench just before the stairs entrance on the left.

src: walk straight until wait near stairs
tgt: Walk straight until you get to stairs. Wait near the stairs.

src: walk fireplace head out turn fireplace sharp left at bathroom there
tgt: Walk left passing the fireplace and head out, Turn left, passing another fireplace and make a sharp left at the bathroom and stop there.

src: turn out of room christmas tree walk through living room towards fire place through door on left in bathroom
tgt: Turn and walk out of the room passed the Christmas tree. Walk through the living room towards the fire place and through the door on the left and stop in the bathroom.

src: turn doorway through once through left near fireplace head through bathroom door
tgt: Turn around and face the doorway. Go through it. Once through it, turn left and go near the fireplace. Head left and through the bathroom door.

src: turn around down hallway right bedroom by bed
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hallway. turn to your right and enter the bedroom. stop by the bed.

src: exit bedroom down hall right at first door in doorway
tgt: exit bedroom down hall, turn right at first door, stop in doorway.

src: away from bedroom down hall stairs right wait at door other bedroom
tgt: Walk away from the bedroom and down the hall towards the stairs. Turn right and wait at the door to the other bedroom.

src: along side of pool down step then few stairs doorway pool area wait here
tgt: Go along the side of the pool, down a step and then up a few stairs to the doorway to exit the pool area.  Wait here.

src: turn right stairs forward past pool stairs
tgt: Turn to the right and go down the stairs. Walk forward past the pool and go up the five stairs.

src: walk pool stairs right of pool wait at landing on stairs
tgt: Walk to the pool, go up the stairs to the right of the pool, wait at the landing on the stairs.

src: through door left straight hallway
tgt: Go through the door to the left, and go straight down the hallway.

src: walk forward exit through far door on left down hall stop with fire extinguisher on left before main entrance
tgt: Walk forward and exit through the far door on your left. Walk down the hall and stop with the fire extinguisher on your left before you reach the main entrance.

src: exit through doorway directly of ballroom down corridor slight left main restaurant visible
tgt: Exit through doorway directly left of the Ballroom. Walk down corridor. Take a slight left. Stop when Main Restaurant becomes visible.

src: walk past glass table up steps on fourth step from top
tgt: Walk past the glass dining table and up the steps.  Stop on the fourth step from the top.

src: walk forward towards stairs stairs on fifth stair from top
tgt: Walk forward towards the stairs. Go up the stairs and stop on the fifth stair from the top.

src: living room walk stairs first flight of stairs then on 5th step of second set of stairs
tgt: Leave the living room and walk to the stairs. Go up the first flight of stairs then wait on the 5th step of the second set of stairs.

src: walk forward up stairs into door on right then few stairs
tgt: Walk forward up the stairs and into the door on the right.  Then turn left and walk up a few stairs.

src: top of stairs into room next power system breaker bottom of staircase steps stop
tgt: Go to the top of the stairs. Go into the room next to the power system breaker. Go to the bottom of the staircase. Go up three steps and stop.

src: up stairs veer right across garage walk through doorway turn up steps on third step
tgt: Walk up the stairs and veer right across the garage. Walk through the doorway and turn left. Walk up the steps and stop on the third step.

src: walk table straight chairs wall of doors stand in front of middle door stop
tgt: walk left around table to and go straight passed the chairs to the wall of doors. Stand in front of the middle door and stop.

src: walk around desk door at far end of room rug before room
tgt: Walk around the desk and towards the the door at the far end of the room. Stop off the rug before you leave the room.

src: turn left through door ahead transom
tgt: Turn around and make a left. Walk through the door straight ahead that has the arched transom.

src: exit wet bar walk straight through living room wait inside bedroom at end of hallway
tgt: Exit the wet bar and walk straight, through the living room. Wait inside the bedroom at the end of the hallway.

src: turn right between white couch glass railing hall past bathroom turn left bedroom just entry stop wait

tgt: Exit the bedroom and wait outside in the living room.

tgt: Go inside and turn right. Continue straight along the wall until it opens to your left. Stop at that point.

tgt: Go inside. Turn right and go past table. Go past cabinet with sink. Stop at hallway.

tgt: Exit the door and turn left to the very first room. Walk inside the room and stop there.

src: pass couches stairs on right steps top

src: walk across room stairs on last step before top
tgt: Walk across the room and go up the stairs.  Stop on the last step before reaching the top.

Go around the end of the table then walk directly out the the end of the large table in the middle of the room.   Once you get to the end of the table, you will be beside two black chairs.  Walk to the middle of the hallway made by the two large tables in the middle of the room and stop.

Continue forward, then enter the kitchen area to your left, passing though to the opposite side of the kitchen. There, you'll see two doors. One leading to the dining room and the other leading to the laundry room. Enter the laundry room.

Walk through the opened archway and into the next room with a fireplace.
