src: walk past fireplace between pink chairs through dinning room stop in kitchen next barstools
tgt: Walk past the fireplace, between the pink chairs. Walk through the dinning room and stop in the kitchen next to the barstools.

src: with christmas tree right towards red chair into dining room down length of dining room into kitchen at other end of table just after into kitchen
tgt: With the Christmas tree to your right, walk towards the red chair and into the dining room.  Walk down the length of the dining room and into the kitchen at the other end of the table.  Stop just after stepping into the kitchen.

src: walk right around couches through door toward stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk right around the couches, through the door, and toward the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: enter into house from backyard room toward white table with vase flowers in behind white couch sideways walk side while couches white table with flowers with right.turn entry way toward end of entry way stairs right first stair wait there for further instruction
tgt: Enter into the house from the backyard. You'll need to enter the room and go toward the white table with the vase and flowers in it. Walk behind the white couch. You may need to turn sideways and walk to the side while you round the couches. Pass the white table with flowers with it to your right.Turn left down the entry way. Toward the end of the entry way there will be stairs to your right. Go up the first stair and wait there for further instruction.

src: walk past couches into hallway toward front door right up steps on landing
tgt: Walk past the couches and into the hallway. walk toward the front door and turn right. Walk up the steps and stop on the landing.

src: walk through lobby towards glass doors turn before doors walk right side of golden urn wait here
tgt: Walk through the lobby towards the revolving glass doors.  Turn left before you reach the doors.  Walk to the right side of the golden urn. Wait here.

src: turn head towards open door left right before door turn straight head area in front of first table with magazines on near windows
tgt: Turn left and head towards the open door, take a left right before the door, turn left, go straight a head to the sitting area and stop in front of the first table with magazines on it near the windows.

src: walk door turn next small table between chairs
tgt: Walk to the revolving door and turn left. Stop next to the small table between two chairs.

src: walk open doorway left of stairs walk before through doorway so long wooden bench
tgt: Walk to the open doorway to the left of the stairs.  Walk before you go through the doorway so you'll be facing a long wooden bench.

src: walk forward around table on left side straight through room wooden door just before in doorway
tgt: Walk forward and go around the dining table on the left side. Go straight through this room, and go to the wooden door leading to outside. Stop just before you are in the doorway.

src: walk left of table straight before outside
tgt: Walk to the left of the table, continue straight. Stop before going outside.

src: walk upstairs room left of red painting wait by white chair
tgt: Walk upstairs.  Enter the room to the left of the red painting.  Wait by white chair.

src: up stairs top of stairs ahead through doorway left of red painting on wall bedroom bedroom
tgt: Walk up the stairs.  When you get to the top of the stairs, walk straight ahead and go through the doorway to the left of the red painting that is hanging on the wall.  This is a bedroom.  Stop when you enter the bedroom.

src: stairs walking straight through doorway left of red painting bedroom
tgt: Go up the stairs and keep walking straight through the doorway to the left of the red painting.  Stop when you enter this bedroom.

src: exit through door right down hallway hallway past couches chairs bed large bathroom wait by first sink on left
tgt: Exit through the door to the right and walk down the hallway. Follow the hallway past both couches, the chairs and bed. Enter the large bathroom and wait by the first sink on the left.

src: straight couch on left then straight bed on left into room on right wait by first sink
tgt: Go straight and pass the couch on your left then continue going straight and pass the bed on your left. Go into the room on the right and wait by the first sink.

src: walk into bedroom with white bed white chairs next door balcony next into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Walk into the bedroom with white bed, two white chairs next to it, and door to the balcony next to pool. Go into the bathroom and stop in front of the nearest sink.

src: walk foot of bed open door on other side of room walk sofa dining room table
tgt: Walk passed the foot of the bed and towards the open door on the other side of the room. Walk passed the sofa and towards the dining room table.

src: turn around past bed door on right then onto checkerboard floor stop
tgt: Turn around and walk past the bed. Go out the door on your right, and then step onto the checkerboard floor and stop.

src: exit bedroom through door on right wait in kitchen on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door on the right wait in the kitchen on the right.

src: pass white table with straw chairs then right then u turn garage steps wait there
tgt: Pass the white table with the straw chairs and then turn right and then u turn left to the garage go down the steps and wait there.

src: turn room behind with table chairs walk other side of room exit out door on right once turn door outside turn once in doorway garage
tgt: Turn around and enter the room behind you with the table and chairs. Walk to the other side of the room and exit out the door on your right. Once out turn left to face the door leading outside. Turn left once more and stop in the doorway leading to the garage.

src: behind couch kitchen room on left into dinning room walk past table now through entryway on right then left in hall now in doorway of garage
tgt: When you are behind the couch and facing the kitchen and dinning room on the left, you need to go into the dinning room and walk past the table. Now go through the entryway on the right then make left in the hall. You should now turn left and wait in the doorway of the garage.

src: exit bathroom hall through archway into room at table turn right enter hall at trash hooks
tgt: exit bathroom to hall, turn left and follow hall through archway into dining room. at table turn right enter hall. Stop at trash can and coat hooks.

src: exit bathroom turn way through opening with arch walk middle of kitchen through doorway on right next portrait
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Walk all the way down through the opening with an arch.  Walk to the middle of the kitchen and go through the doorway on the right next to the portrait. .

src: exit bathroom turn down hallway through doorway ahead of at end of hallway kitchen from kitchen though first doorway on right
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left.  Walk down the hallway and through the doorway straight ahead of you at the end of the hallway to enter the kitchen.  From the kitchen, walk though the first doorway on your right and stop.

src: stairs right right head front door in doorway
tgt: Go down the stairs and go right. Take a right and head to the front door. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn right down stairs right again wait just inside front door on right
tgt: Turn right and walk down the stairs and turn right again. Wait just inside the front door on the right.

src: stairs on right right toward open wooden door on right
tgt: Go down the stairs on the right and turn right. Go toward the open wooden door on the right and stop.

src: walk around couch kitchen right at open doorway stop at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk around the couch and towards the kitchen.  Turn right at the open doorway and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: couch turn then through doorway on left in front of stairs
tgt: Go passed the couch and turn left then go through the doorway on the left and stop in front of the stairs.

src: travel toward cabinets behind couch turn toward ovens right into hallway at foot of stairs
tgt: Travel toward the cabinets behind the couch. Turn left and travel toward the ovens. Turn right into the hallway. Stop at the foot of the stairs.

src: walk in direction of dining room left before table left in doorway wine room
tgt: Walk in the direction of the dining room, and take a left before you pass the table. Take a left, and stand in the doorway to the wine room.

src: walk toward deck turn before outside walk through dining area turn walk room with wine left of large portrait painting in glass doorway wine room
tgt: Walk toward the deck but turn left before going outside.  Walk through the dining area and turn left.  Walk to the room with the wine bottles to the left of the large portrait painting.  Stop in the glass doorway to the wine room.

src: exit kitchen area hard left past dining room table left into wine room wait there
tgt: Exit the kitchen area and make a hard left. Walk past the dining room table. Make a left into the wine room and wait there.

src: walk front door of house in entryway
tgt: Walk straight to open front door of house. Stop in entryway.

src: walk forwards house just inside house past door
tgt: Walk forwards and enter the house. Stop just inside the house, past the door.

src: up steps on straight stone path once past bench wait by door in entry of house
tgt: Walk up the steps and continue on straight, following the stone path. Once past the bench, wait by the door in the entry of the house.

src: exit kitchen left straight then into glass doorway pool stop
tgt: Exit the kitchen to the left, go straight and then left into the glass doorway leading the pool and stop.

src: walk through passage on left walking until outside just after through doorway outside
tgt: Walk through the passage on the left and keep walking until you go outside.  Stop just after having stepped through the doorway going outside.

src: kitchen patio out of patio door in patio doorway
tgt: Leave the kitchen heading to the patio. Take a left out of the patio door and stop in the patio doorway.

src: through wooden double doors walk first door on left stairs wait on landing
tgt: Go through the wooden double doors and walk to first door on your left. Go up three stairs and wait on the landing.

src: past white couches room double doors turn steps of stairs
tgt: Go past the white couches and exit the room using the double doors. Turn left and go up three steps of the stairs.

src: exit room through doors on left on landing at top of steps
tgt: Exit the room and go through the doors on the left. Stop on the landing, at the top of the steps.

src: turn around by island left near dining room table
tgt: Turn around and walk by the island. Continue to the left and stop near the dining room table.

src: straight through kitchen turn wait near round table chairs
tgt: Go straight through the kitchen. Turn left and wait near the round table and chairs.

src: walk through kitchen turn at refrigerator in front of first doorway right into pantry
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and turn left at the refrigerator.  Stop in front of the first doorway to your right and look into the pantry.

src: turn then right after oddly shaped chair wait in doorway
tgt: Turn left and then turn right after the oddly shaped chair. Wait in the doorway.

src: turn house right side of petition walk across room once chair on right into doorway stop
tgt: Turn around and enter the house. Go to the right side of the petition and walk across the room. Once you pass the 2nd chair on your right, turn into the doorway and stop.

src: inside into room with glass table chairs walk right of table into first door on right in doorway
tgt: Go inside and go into the room with a glass table and eight chairs. Walk to the right of the table and turn into the first door on the right. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn right in front of windows way down door on right through door into hallway turn bathroom in front of bathtub
tgt: Turn right. Walk in front of the windows all the way down to the door on the right. Exit through the door into the hallway. Turn left and enter the bathroom. Stop in front of the bathtub.

src: right way towards wall right towards room with tub
tgt: Go right all the way down towards the wall. Take a right and ro towards the room with the tub.

src: head toward flat screen television on wall tv turn right then straight into bathroom wait by tub
tgt: Head toward the flat screen television on the wall, when you get to the tv turn right then turn left and go straight into the bathroom and wait by the tub.

src: turn degrees into bedroom forward with bed right toward doorway with white chair footstool right through doorway degrees left forward with glass right through doorway left large artwork on wall through bedroom with bed on right black chair footstool on left entryway outside patio
tgt: Turn 45 degrees to your and move into the bedroom. Move forward with the bed to your right. Go toward the doorway with the white chair and footstool to your right. Pass through the doorway and turn 45 degrees to the left. Move forward with the glass railing to your right. Pass through the doorway and turn to your left when you reach the large artwork on the wall. Move through the bedroom with the bed on your right and the black chair and footstool on your left. Stop when you reach the entryway to the outside patio.

src: exit bathroom slight left across bedroom slight left into hallway left of stairs hallway slight left forward across bedroom balcony at couch
tgt: exit bathroom and turn slight left walking across bedroom to door, turn slight left and walk into hallway left of stairs. continue down hallway, turn slight left and walk forward, walk across bedroom to outside balcony. stop at couch.

src: right out door into hallway past staircase turn then again past foot of bed just before door outside couch couple of chairs on balcony
tgt: Go to the right and out the door into the hallway, past the staircase.  Turn left and then left again.  Walk past the foot of the bed.  Just before you get to the door that leads outside, you will stop.  There is a couch and a couple of chairs on the balcony.

src: walk out door in front of walking door across patio door then right wood door straight until back outside furniture yard
tgt: Walk out the door in front of you. Keep walking and enter the door across the patio. Enter the door and then turn right and exit the wood door. Keep walking straight until you are back outside facing the furniture and the yard.

src: with table left room through double doors building through doors on opposite wall into exercise room room through door on right forward until building again through set of doors
tgt: With the table to your left, exit the room through the double doors and reenter the building through the doors on the opposite wall into the exercise room. Exit the room through the door on your right, and continue forward until you exit the building again through a set of sliding doors.

src: exit through double doors right slight left through double doors gym area exit gym area door on right slight left through door area wait there
tgt: Exit through double doors to the right. Take a slight left. Walk through double doors and enter the Gym area. Exit Gym area to the door on the right. Take a slight left. Walk through sliding door to Patio area. Wait there.

src: walk into bedroom bed right pass dresser right into doorway right out into hallway over star tile in middle of floor stop in doorway inside living room
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and towards the bed taking a right and walking pass the dresser and take a right into the doorway and right out into the hallway over the star tile in the middle of the floor and stop in the doorway inside the living room.

src: walk into bedroom area table with sculpture of hand then out of room into hallway walk small curio cabinet walk into room around corner plants in vase pass by bar counter sink in room
tgt: Walk into the bedroom area passed the table with the sculpture of the hand and then out of the room into the hallway. Walk passed the small curio cabinet. Walk into the room around the corner passed the plants in a vase. Pass by the bar counter and sink in the room.

src: turn left past bed turn right then quickly left through doorway across hall then living room stop wait
tgt: Turn to the left and go past the bed.  Turn to the right and then quickly to the left.  You'll go through the doorway and across the hall.  Then you will enter the living room and stop and wait.

src: walk behind couch towards fireplace turn past fireplace coffee table slightly directly in front of wall with pictures of children puppy on
tgt: Walk behind couch towards the fireplace. Turn left and proceed past fireplace and coffee table. Continue slightly left and wait directly in front of wall with pictures of children and a puppy on it.

src: pass fireplace into large arch toward hallway by pictures on wall
tgt: Pass the fireplace and go into the large arch leading toward the hallway. Stop by the pictures on the wall.

src: walk behind couch turn exit living room wait at pictures on wall
tgt: Walk behind couch and turn left, exit living room and wait at pictures on the wall.

src: exit closet right out of bedroom at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the closet. Take a right out of the bedroom. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: closet out of bedroom stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Leave the closet and go out of the bedroom to the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: in closet out of closet turn left through doorway right veer right at top of stairs
tgt: You're in a closet.  Walk out of the closet and turn to the left.  and go through the doorway.  Go to the right and veer to the right.  Stop and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk top of stairs down steps walk left of chair just outside stop
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs. Walk down the steps and walk to the left of the chair. Walk just outside and stop.

src: turn right steps glass table with purple chairs red couches clear glass doors wait by patio table chairs near pool
tgt: Turn right and go down the steps. Pass the glass table with the purple chairs. Pass the red couches and go out the clear glass sliding doors. Wait by the patio table and chairs near the pool.

src: turn right at kitchen counter through area onto patio stop
tgt: Turn right at kitchen counter. Walk through dining area onto patio and stop.

src: exit bathroom slight left toward curtained archway pass through archway room door on left immediate right through double doors into next bedroom door on left there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Take a slight left toward the curtained archway. Pass through the archway. Exit the room to the door on the left. Take an immediate right through the double doors. Turn into the next bedroom door on the left. Stop there.

src: walk past bed on right past wall-mounted tv on right through open door on left through open door on right wait at threshold of bedroom door on left
tgt: Walk past the bed on the right. Walk past the wall-mounted TV on the right. Walk through the open door on the left. Walk through the open door on the right. Wait at the threshold of the bedroom door on the left.

src: turn bathroom walk across bedroom exit out curtains once out turn white door once turn right double white doors forward in next door on left facing into bedroom
tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom. Walk across the bedroom and exit out the curtains. Once out, turn left and exit out the white door. Once out turn right and enter the double white doors. Walk forward and turn in the next door on the left and stop facing into the bedroom.

src: walk through lounge room past wooden armchairs walk glass floor lamp up small set of steps corner left down hallway walk into open door room with blue couches small clock on table
tgt: Walk through the lounge room past the wooden armchairs. Walk passed the glass floor lamp and up the small set of steps. Turn the corner to the left and walk down the hallway. Walk into the open door that leads to a room with blue couches and a small clock on a table.

src: up steps right of piano forward down steps in first doorway on left
tgt: Walk up the two steps to the right of the piano. Continue forward and walk down the the 5 steps. Stop in the first doorway on your left.

src: walk right past piano stairs into first room on left stand in doorway
tgt: Walk to the right past the piano. Go down the stairs. Turn into the first room on the left and stand in the doorway.

src: turn building walk right side of see through wall room halfway through between table door cabinet
tgt: Turn around and enter the building. Walk to the right side of the see through wall to enter the room. Stop halfway through when you are between the table and the 2 door cabinet.

src: indoors past wall with holes wait near table chairs
tgt: Go indoors. Go past the wall with holes and wait near the table and chairs.

src: walk through doors right of wall by table chairs
tgt: Walk through the doors and to the right of the grated wall. Stop by the table and chairs.

src: right staircase turn on landing stairs at second stair from top
tgt: Go up the right staircase.  Turn left on the landing and continue up the stairs, stopping at the second stair from the top.

src: turn up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn left and walk up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs landing turn of steps at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up stairs to landing, turn left and continue to top of steps, wait at top of stairs.

src: walk past printer of way down hallway exit signs turn down hallway in front of last wooden door on left
tgt: Walk past the printer and go all of the way down the hallway.  When you reach the "exit" signs, turn left and walk down the hallway.  Stop in front of the last wooden door on the left.

src: hall toward exit signs turn at end walk end of next hall stop between last doors on left 5-e 5-d
tgt: Go down the hall toward the exit signs and turn left at the end. Walk to the end of the next hall and stop between the last two doors on the left, which are marked 5-E and 5-D.

src: walk towards exit sign turn wait at end of corridor
tgt: Walk towards the exit sign and turn left. Wait at the end of the corridor.

src: exit laundry room right inside office through double doors on right
tgt: Exit the laundry room and turn right. Stop inside the office through the double doors on the right.

src: laundry room walk right into room on right in front of couch after into office
tgt: Leave the laundry room and walk right.  Turn into the room on the right that is in front of the couch.  Stop after stepping into this office.

src: exit laundry room then right then right on first door wait by entrance
tgt: Exit the laundry room then turn right. Then turn right on the first door and wait by the entrance.

src: walk ahead at hall table walk over dining room right at front of half bathroom
tgt: Walk ahead and turn left at hall table. Walk over the dining room and turn right. Stop at front of half bathroom.

src: turn left at small table walk straight then second right wait in front of bathroom
tgt: Turn around and take a left at the small table. Walk straight and then take the second right. Wait in front of the bathroom.

src: walk in house right down hall second right into hallway outside of bathroom on left
tgt: Walk in the house and take a right. Walk down the hall and take your second right into the hallway. Stop outside of the bathroom on your left.

src: through double doors turn past stairs into room ahead near table chairs
tgt: Go through double doors. Turn left and go up past the stairs. Go into the room ahead and wait near the table and chairs.

src: enter house walk hallway past stairs room in front of in front of table
tgt: Enter the house. Walk to the hallway past the stairs. Enter the room in front of you. Stop in front of the table.

src: enter home forward steps turn walk towards room with couches black table wait here
tgt: Enter home.  Continue forward, and walk down two steps.  Turn left.  Walk towards room with two couches and black table.  Wait here.

src: turn end of walkway through doorway right next hall on right right steps stop
tgt: Turn around and go to the end of the walkway, go through the doorway and take a right, keep going to the next hall on the right, turn right, go down the steps, and stop.

src: walk along walkway into building walk past shelf right down stairs stop
tgt: Walk along the walkway and into the building Walk past the shelf and to the right. Walk down the stairs and stop.

src: down curved pathway into room past shelves stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the curved pathway and into the room and past the shelves. Go down the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: turn through door hall right then towards blue lips turn left right
tgt: Turn around and go through the door. Follow the hall and turn right. Then go towards the blue lips and turn left. Go to the right and stop.

src: steps into house large glass door right hallway turn then right wait near purple flowers on left
tgt: Go down the steps. Go into the house using the large glass door. Turn right and go down the hallway. Turn left and then turn right and wait near the purple flowers on the left.

src: turn house then right walk lips then then right shortly after bathroom
tgt: Turn around and enter the house.  Then turn right and walk to the lips.  Then turn left and then right shortly after and enter the bathroom.

src: away from door turn after wooden barrier straight right side of table completely straight towards similar wooden barrier stop in front of wicker chair on right
tgt: Walk away from the door and turn left after the wooden barrier, walk straight to the right side of the table passing it completely. Continue straight towards a similar wooden barrier and stop in front of the wicker chair on your right.

src: turn through opening in front of straight across room past tables then in doorway of next room
tgt: Turn left through the opening in front of you. Walk straight across the room past the tables and then stop in the doorway of the next room.

src: walk forward few steps sharp left turn straight past dining table just past doorway on right side wait by wicker chair
tgt: Walk forward a few steps and make a sharp left turn. Walk straight past the dining table. Stop just past the doorway on the right side. Wait by the wicker chair.

src: enter house through glass doors straight chairs against wall exit through door wait by red statue
tgt: Enter the house through the glass doors.  Continue straight and pass the two chairs against the wall.  Exit through the door.  Wait by red statue.

src: straight indoors straight glass door wait near red statue on right
tgt: Go straight and go indoors. Continue straight and go out the glass door. Wait near the red statue on the right.

src: enter house straight house onto patio outside patio door
tgt: Enter the house and go straight. Ext the house onto the patio. Stop outside the patio door.

src: exit room through hall way door turn through bathroom wait in doorway next bed
tgt: Exit the room through the hall way door, turn left and walk through the bathroom. Wait in the doorway next to the bed.

src: walk around foot of bed stairs down hard right walk straight through narrow door into bathroom walk through bathroom wait at door into bedroom
tgt: Walk around the foot of the bed to get to the stairs and walk down them. Take a hard right and walk straight through a narrow door into a bathroom. Walk through the bathroom and wait at the door leading into another bedroom.

src: turn through doorway turn straight before next doorway
tgt: Turn left and go through the doorway, Turn left and  go straight and stop before the next doorway.

src: walk next pool with pool on left hand side bar with sink in right by l-shaped table with single wooden chair
tgt: Walk next to the pool with the pool on your left hand side.  When you get to the bar with the sink in it, turn right and stop by the L-shaped table with the single wooden chair.

src: turn towards left along edge of pool once other side of room turn right head towards desk then behind desk steps
tgt: Turn towards your left and walk along the edge of the pool. Once you reach the other side of the room turn right. Head towards the desk and then stop behind the desk facing the 3 steps.

src: cross patio wait at far end of steps
tgt: Cross the patio and wait at the far end of the steps.

src: left into room in front of staircase in garage right into fitness roo
tgt: Make a left into the room in front of the staircase. In the garage, make a right into the fitness roo.

src: walk toward stairs into garage right into gym just inside doorway
tgt: Walk toward the stairs and turn left into the garage. Turn right and walk into the gym. Stop just inside the doorway.

src: forward first open doorway on left forward into room stop wait at doorway on right
tgt: Go forward to the first open doorway which is on the left.  Go forward into the room and stop and wait at the doorway on the right.

src: walk top of stairs down steps turn down stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs. Walk down the steps and turn left. Walk down the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk out of bathroom turn stairs bottom of stairs stop
tgt: walk straight out of the bathroom, turn left down the stairs,  walk to the bottom of the stairs and stop.

src: left down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Take a left and walk down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk through area wait in bathroom
tgt: Walk through the sitting area and wait in the bathroom.

src: through room left of television right into bathroom stop
tgt: Go through the room and to the left of the television, turn right into the bathroom and stop.

src: walk straight ahead desk tv walk past bar on right right into bathroom in
tgt: Walk straight ahead to past the desk and TV. Walk past the bar on your right and turn right into the bathroom. Stop when you walk in.

src: turn towards long hallway first door on right across rooms in between tables chairs door across with barbers room chair
tgt: Turn around towards the long hallway and go out the first door on the right. Go across the rooms in between the tables and chairs towards the door straight across with the barbers chair. Enter the room and stop facing the chair.

src: hallway with rug first room on right over first set of doubles across room enter that room wait
tgt: Go left down the hallway with the rug. Enter the first room on the right, walk over to the first set of doubles across the room.  Enter that room and wait.

src: rail bathroom door hexagon table dining table dog painting
tgt: Go to the rail. Go to the bathroom door. Go to the hexagon table. Go to the dining table. Go to the dog painting.

src: exit laundry room living room past white couch turn kitchen wait by kitchen island
tgt: Exit the laundry room, enter the living room, walk past the white couch, turn left, walk to the kitchen, wait by the kitchen island.

src: bathroom slight left hall enter living room left behind couches towards window wall right head towards kitchen at counter
tgt: Leave bathroom and make slight left crossing the hall. enter living room, take left and go behind couches towards the window wall. Turn right and head towards the kitchen. Stop at the counter.

src: into large lobby across lobby towards bar stools at counter wait there
tgt: Go into the large lobby.  Go across the lobby towards the bar stools at the counter Wait there.

src: walk past table with flowers into room with chandelier walk past couches in doorway outside
tgt: Walk past the table with the flowers and into the room with the chandelier Walk past the couches and stop in the doorway to the outside. .

src: walk toward round table with black vase white flowers on left into room with arch ahead past couches out door patio wait near patio couches
tgt: Walk toward the round table with the black vase and the white flowers on the left. Go into the room with the arch straight ahead. Go past the couches and out the door to the patio. Wait near the patio couches.

src: move table with bouquet then slightly into room with couches piano through couches out open door at far end of room outside on patio
tgt: Move to the table with the bouquet.  Then turn slightly left and head into the room with the couches and piano.  Move through the couches and out the open door at the far end of the room, to stand outside on the patio.

src: straight bed room door on left into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Go straight and pass the bed. Exit the room using the door on the left into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: turn door right of tv once in room tub windows
tgt: Turn left and exit out the door to the right of the TV. Stop once you are in the room facing the tub and the windows.

src: through bedroom into doorway left step into bathroom stop
tgt: Go through the bedroom and into the doorway to the left, take a step into the bathroom and stop.

src: stairs into bedroom on top stair
tgt: Go up the stairs into the bedroom. Stop on the top stair.

src: turn steps wait there
tgt: Turn left. Go up the steps and wait there.

src: away from pool stairs inside up steps wait at top
tgt: Walk away from the pool and towards the stairs leading inside.  Walk up steps.  Wait at the top.

src: exit bedroom turn past stairs hallway left turn again past side table with lamp walk through doorway right at next hallway wait near wooden banister
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left. Walk past the stairs, following the hallway to the left. Turn left again and walk past the side table with the lamp. Walk through the doorway and turn right at the next hallway. Wait near the wooden banister.

src: exit room walk towards staircase walk staircase hallway around straight lamp on right through open door right after first door stop near railing
tgt: Exit room and walk towards the staircase.  Walk passed the staircase and follow the hallway around. Continue straight passed the lamp on the right and through the open door. Turn right after the first door and stop near the railing.

src: walk into hall past stairs turn hallway past end table right past front door stop by railing
tgt: Walk into the hall and past the stairs. Turn left down the hallway past the end table. Turn right past the front door and stop by the railing.

src: head inside room towards stairs wait near doorway left of stairs
tgt: Head inside and cross the room towards the stairs. Wait near the doorway to the left of the stairs.

src: head straight left of tables left of staircase in front of hall

tgt: Exit the bathroom and head left down the hallway. Keep going until there is an arch ahead, and turn left from the arc, stopping in front of the front door.

tgt: Turn to the left and walk to the right of the brown leather sofa. Walk around the coffee table in front of the fire place. Walk around the lounge chair and go through the rounded entryway. and walk towards the circular rug Stop in front of the artwork with writing on the right.

src: through door turn enter bathroom
