src: down stairs into wine room on left
tgt: Walk down the stairs and go into the wine room on the left.

src: down stairs turn painting walk glass door door room stop
tgt: Walk down the stairs.  Turn left when you reach the painting. Walk to the glass door, open the door, enter the room, and stop.

src: down stairs wait by wine wall
tgt: Walk down stairs and wait by the wine wall.

src: from front door straight back until table with white table cloth end of table left stand in doorway right in doorway bathroom doorway in doorway
tgt: From the front door you need to walk straight back until you get to the table with the white table cloth. When you walk to the end of the table make a left and stand in the doorway. Make a right when you are in the doorway and go to the bathroom doorway. You have to wait in the doorway.

src: turn just past first covered white table in doorway of bathroom on right
tgt: Turn left just past the first covered white table. Stop in the doorway of the bathroom on your right.

src: turn right head towards hall way left at door restrooms than immediate right at first door destination there
tgt: Turn right and head towards the hall way. Make a left at the door labeled restrooms than make your immediate right. Turn left at the first door and the destination is there.

src: exit powder room then right down hall right past wine rack
tgt: Exit the powder room then turn right and walk down the hall. Turn to your right and walk past the wine rack.

src: exit bathroom right slight right through room turn wait near glass doors
tgt: Exit bathroom, take a right, go slight right through the room, turn left and wait near the glass doors.

src: bathroom right right head past wine room once past wine room
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and go right. Take a right and head past the wine room. Stop once you are past the wine room.

src: enter building walk through dining area wait in doorway under mounted deer head
tgt: Enter the building and walk through the dining area. Wait in the doorway under the mounted deer head.

src: walk into house turn past table chairs until fireplace into room right of fireplace
tgt: Walk straight into the house. Turn left and go past the table and chairs until you get to a fireplace. Go into the room that is to the right of the fireplace.

src: walk inside past pillars in room with tables until fireplace through door right of fireplace under mounted deer head
tgt: Walk inside past the two pillars.  In the room with the tables, walk left until you see the fireplace.  Go through the door to the right of the fireplace and stop when you are standing under the mounted deer head.

src: turn head towards hall way continue until square right through glass doors first into shop
tgt: Turn around and head towards the hall way. Continue , until you see the square windows and make a right. Continue through the glass doors and make your first left into the shop.

src: walk through hallway wall with candles walk into next room along wall with square glass panes through open glass double doors walk large empty planters through glass doors into room with paintings vending machine
tgt: Walk through the hallway passed the wall with candles. Walk into the next room along the wall with square glass panes. Walk through the open glass double doors. Walk passed the large empty planters and through the glass doors into the room with paintings and a vending machine.

src: hallway room at end right past desk through door through door on left wait in shop
tgt: Go down the hallway to the room at the end. Turn right and walk past the desk and through the door. Go through the door on the left and wait in the shop.

src: through living room right at dining room table until front door in hallway
tgt: Go through the living room, take a right at the dining room table, and continue until you reach the front door, stopping in the hallway.

src: walk towards blue chairs past blue chairs towards table chairs turn right through large doorway straight towards black pillar wait by black pillar
tgt: Walk towards blue chairs. Go past blue chairs towards wooden table and chairs and turn right through large doorway. Go straight towards black pillar and wait by black pillar.

src: straight in between couch coffee table walk past blue chairs right hall in entry way
tgt: Go straight in between the couch and the coffee table. Walk past the blue chairs. Take a right down the hall, stop in the entry way.

src: enter dining room with hardwood floors turn after dining room walk past dinner table door left of swirly blue orange painting wait here
tgt: Enter the dining room with hardwood floors.  Turn left after you enter the dining room and walk past the dinner table.  Enter the door to the left of the swirly blue and orange painting. Wait here.

src: though door into dining room turn left past dining room table turn right door wait in room with sink in corner
tgt: Go though the door into the dining room and turn to the left. Go past the dining room table and turn to the right. Enter the door and wait in the room with the sink in the corner.

src: into dining room past table into room with black tile floor stand in room next door
tgt: Go into the dining room. Go past the table and into the room with black tile floor. Stand in the room next to the door.

src: room straight stairs on landing stairs
tgt: Leave this room, and go straight. Go down the stairs. Stop on the landing to the stairs.

src: through white hallway staircase bottom of staircase
tgt: Go through the white hallway to the staircase. Go to the bottom of the staircase.

src: down hall toward top of stairs right on landing at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the hall toward the top of the stairs and turn right. Stop on the landing at the bottom of the stairs.

src: porch walk into house through door left into first hallway on left walk forwards turn second door on left just before through door sink
tgt: Leave the porch and walk into the house through the door. Take a left into the first hallway you come to on the left. Walk forwards and turn to face the second door on the left. Stop just before entering through the door, facing the sink.

src: inside through second door on left in doorway laundry room
tgt: Go inside and go through the second door on the left.  Stop in this doorway to the laundry room.

src: walk into house through patio doors walk past bedroom door laundry room wait near sink
tgt: Walk into the house the through the patio doors. Walk past the bedroom door and enter the laundry room.  Wait near the sink.

src: stairs walk straight first right into play room walk forward beside dollhouse
tgt: Go up the stairs and walk straight. Take the first right into the play room and walk forward. Stop beside the dollhouse.

src: up stairs at top through doorway on right then into room on right in front of dollhouse
tgt: Walk up the stairs.  At the top, go through the doorway on the right.  Then go into the room on the right and stop in front of the dollhouse.

src: turn right up stairs walk doorway right room wait by entrance
tgt: Turn right and walk up the stairs. Walk to the doorway to your right. Enter the room and wait by the entrance.

src: rotate body left walk forwards towards treadmill door left
tgt: Rotate body to the left. Walk forwards towards the treadmill, Stop when you reach the door to the left.

src: turn past exercise equipment towards pool at end of lounge chair before pool
tgt: Turn left and walk past the exercise equipment towards the pool. Stop at the end of the lounge chair before you reach the pool.

src: walk straight toward pool wait there near lounge chairs
tgt: Walk straight toward the pool and wait there near the lounge chairs.

src: turn around out of room wait at bottom of steps
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the room. Wait at the bottom of the steps.

src: turn until black chairs in front of fireplace behind black chairs towards first open door on left at first door turn stairs down up on platform
tgt: TURN LEFT UNTIL YOU ARE FACING TWO BLACK CHAIRS IN FRONT OF A FIREPLACE, WALK BEHIND THE BLACK CHAIRS TOWARDS THE FIRST OPEN DOOR ON THE LEFT, AT THE FIRST DOOR TURN LEFT TO FACE STAIRS HEADING BOTH DOWN AND UP, WALK ON TO THE PLATFORM.

src: walk past wall openings walk past wood table wait at stair landing
tgt: Walk past arched wall openings. Walk past folding wood table. Wait at stair landing.

src: turn around through room with woven chairs up steps turn through open doors through hallway stop before window with white shade down
tgt: Turn around and walk through the room with the woven chairs. Walk up the two steps and turn left through the open doors. Walk through the hallway and stop before the window with white shade that is drawn down.

src: walk past couches up steps first left room in front of doorknob
tgt: Walk past the couches and up the steps. Take the first left and enter the room.  Stop in front of the doorknob.

src: cross room steps through door on left
tgt: Cross the room and go up the steps. Wait through the door on the left.

src: turn right stairs up stairs desk chair beside chair
tgt: Turn right, walk to the stairs, walk up the stairs, walk to the desk chair and stop beside the chair.

src: exit room stairs room large glass windows
tgt: Exit the room. Go up the stairs. Cross the room to the large glass windows.

src: cross room stairs right towards desk wait by glass wall
tgt: Cross the room and go up the stairs. Continue to the right towards the desk. Wait by the glass wall.

src: walk toward air conditioners turn toward stairs once bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk toward the air conditioners, turn left to go toward the stairs, and stop once you reach the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk towards chimney stairs wait near crab
tgt: Walk towards the chimney and head down the stairs.  Wait near the crab.

src: step turn right steps wait there
tgt: Go down the step and turn left. Turn right and go down the steps. Wait there.

src: hard right through bedroom door turn hallway turn walk towards stairs down stairs
tgt: turn hard right. go through bedroom door. turn left. go to door that leads to the hallway. turn left. walk towards the stairs. walk down stairs.

src: exit closet into bedroom bedroom wait in hallway on rug
tgt: Exit the closet into the bedroom. Exit the bedroom and wait in the hallway on the rug.

src: exit closet walk towards red carpet turn room walk past bookcase wait by small set of stairs
tgt: Exit the closet. Walk towards the red carpet turn left and exit the room. Walk past the bookcase and wait by the small set of stairs.

src: exit bathroom right walk straight until table chairs there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and walk straight until you get to the table and chairs. Stop there.

src: walk out of bathroom right by dining room table chairs
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right. Stop by the dining room table and chairs.

src: with toilet left straight door with sign right into open area past area dining table chairs behind chair at table kitchen
tgt: With the toilet to your left, walk straight.  When you get to the door with the sign that says "Residence One", turn right and walk into the open area.  Walk past the sitting area and towards the dining table and chairs.  Stop behind the chair at this table that is closest to the kitchen.

src: walk past jacket on chair left office right right opposite exit sign from ceiling on left wait in threshold of open door
tgt: Walk past the jacket hanging on the chair to the left. Exit the office, and make a right. Make a right opposite the exit sign hanging from the ceiling on the left. Wait in the threshold of the open door.

src: office right right at double glass door next first desk
tgt: Leave the office, and take a right. Take a right at the double glass door. Stop next to the first desk.

src: hard around desk office then right first office on right wait near doorway
tgt: Walk hard left around the desk to exit the office, then turn right and enter the first office on the right. Wait near the doorway.

src: past stairs straight dining room table stop wait just after kitchen area
tgt: Go past the stairs and continue straight passing the dining room table. Stop and wait just after you enter the kitchen area.

src: turn across floor stairs table near couches
tgt: Turn around and go across the floor passing the stairs and the table. Stop near the couches.

src: walk past staircase staircase on right as straight ahead past dining table also on right as sink sink on left as
tgt: Walk past the staircase.  The staircase will be on your right as you pass.  Continue to walk straight ahead past the dining table, which will also be on your right as you pass.  Stop when you get to the sink.  The sink will be on your left as you approach it.

src: exit bedroom walk towards stairs by bookcase downstairs stop inside bedroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk towards the stairs by the bookcase. Go downstairs and stop inside the bedroom.

src: exit bedroom turn left past plant of left down stairs into next bedroom wait at foot of bed
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left. Go past the plant of the left and walk down the stairs and into the next bedroom and wait at the foot of the bed.

src: walk forward towards stairs at stairs turn small set of wood stairs bedroom once bed
tgt: Walk forward towards the stairs. At the stairs, turn left and go down the small set of wood stairs. Enter the bedroom and stop once you reach the bed.

src: turn right around counter out of kitchen steps turn forward up thermostat
tgt: Turn right around the counter and walk straight out of the kitchen. Go down the three steps.  Turn left and walk forward up to the thermostat.

src: walk out of kitchen stairs at bottom of stairs left next cabinet on left
tgt: Walk out of the kitchen and go down the stairs. At the bottom of the stairs take a left and stop next to the cabinet on the left.

src: turn right straight end of room take then near sofa
tgt: turn right go straight  to the end of room take left then stand near sofa.

src: right through living room in hallway left corridor next first lamp on console table behind couch
tgt: Take a right and go through the living room. In the hallway take a left and go down a corridor stopping next to the first lamp on the console table behind the couch.

src: walk past blue couch right exit room turn straight towards plants wait by potted plants
tgt: Walk past blue couch, turn right, and exit room. Turn left, go straight towards potted plants. Wait by potted plants.

src: exit living room turn patio entryway wait by potted plant
tgt: Exit the living room, turn left, enter the patio entryway, wait by the potted plant.

src: walk forward then mirror then at stairs
tgt: walk forward then turn left when you see a mirror then stop at the stairs.

src: up small set of steps right corridor with large white vase straight until mirror urn on table left wait on stairs
tgt: Walk up small set of steps.  Turn right and walk down corridor with large white vase.  Continue straight until you reach the mirror and urn sitting on table.  Make a left.  Wait on stairs.

src: up steps right towards hallway staircase on left forward way end round big mirror on wall turn staircase. at fourth stairs
tgt: Walk up the three steps, and turn right towards the hallway passing the staircase on your left. Walk forward all the way to the end where you see a round big mirror on the wall. Turn left to the staircase., and stop at the fourth stairs.

src: turn door on right then right into room next door wait at entrance
tgt: Turn left and go out the door on your right then turn right and go into the room next door. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk towards ski on wall down stairs on left at bottom right right again into bedroom room
tgt: Walk towards where it says "SKI" on the wall.  Walk down the stairs on the left and at the bottom, turn right.  Turn right again and walk into the bedroom.  Stop when you enter the room.

src: turn around towards word ski on wall then door on right once out door turn right bedroom whole room
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the word SKI on the wall and then turn left. Exit out the door on your right. Once out the door turn right and enter the bedroom and stop facing the whole room.

src: walk toward black sheer curtain right behind yellow couches turn curtain walk past bed stop at foot of bathtub
tgt: Walk toward the black sheer curtain.  Turn right to walk behind the yellow couches.  Turn left to go around the curtain.  Walk past the bed and stop at the foot of the bathtub.

src: past yellow lounge sofa right end of lounge sofa turn left past bed wait by tub
tgt: Go past the yellow lounge sofa and turn right. Go to the end of the lounge sofa and turn left. Go past the bed and wait by the tub.

src: walk past yellow sofa around bed bathroom stand near bath tub
tgt: Walk past the yellow sofa and proceed around the bed and enter the bathroom .  Stand near the bath tub.

src: walk onto paving stones turn path toward door wait in entry way
tgt: Walk onto the paving stones and turn left, following the path toward the door. Wait in the entry way.

src: forward along concrete pathway first left forward door there
tgt: Go forward along concrete pathway. Take the first left. Go forward. Enter the door. Stop there.

src: straight then right by entrance inside
tgt: Go straight then turn left and wait right by the entrance to go inside.

src: stairway through hall with cabinets at entrance bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairway and through the hall with cabinets.  Stop at the entrance to the bathroom.

src: turn right stairs hall
tgt: Turn around and go right up the stairs and go down the hall.

src: turn away from first hallway turn again stairs walk down next hallway then at entrance of room
tgt: Turn left away from the first hallway. Turn left again and climb the stairs. Walk straight down the next hallway, then stop at the entrance of the room.

src: walk straight across room door on left at first kitchen island first right wait in bathroom
tgt: Walk straight across the room keeping the sliding door on the left. Turn left at the first kitchen island. Make the first right and wait in the bathroom.

src: walk past dining room left kitchen bar stools right through open door after thermostat on wall right hard left onto carpeted floor wait at floor ceiling mirror
tgt: Walk past the dining room. Make a left opposite the kitchen bar stools. Make a right through the open door after the thermostat on the wall to the right. Make a hard left onto the carpeted floor. Wait at the floor to ceiling mirror.

src: enter house walk towards kitchen left at first kitchen counter first right bathroom left in doorway on right in closet
tgt: Enter the house and walk towards the kitchen. Take the left at the first kitchen counter. Take the first right and enter the bathroom. Take a left and stop in the doorway on the right in the closet.

src: straight through work area bedroom right few steps then right in big hallway stop wait
tgt: You'll go straight, through a work out area.  When you get to the bedroom, youl'll turn right.  Go a few more steps and then turn right. You will be in a big hallway.  Stop and wait.

src: walk out of closet area into gym room walk gym equipment through open door ahead walk bed in bedroom into office area
tgt: Walk out of the closet area and into the gym room. Walk passed the gym equipment and through the open door ahead.  Walk passed the bed in the bedroom and into the office area.

src: exit closet straight hallway past bathroom weight machines straight towards bedroom once in bedroom immediate right enter office left past desk double doors through doorway wait by wall art of deer
tgt: Exit closet and go straight down hallway past bathroom and weight machines. Continue straight towards bedroom and once in bedroom take an immediate right. Enter office and go left past the desk and towards the double doors. Go through the doorway and wait by wall art of deer.

src: down stairs forward next with guitar
tgt: Walk down the stairs. Walk forward and stop next to paining with guitar.

src: stairs right at bottom walk through door ahead right in hallway beside picture of man with guitar
tgt: Go down the stairs to your right. At the bottom walk straight through the door ahead to the right. Stop in the hallway beside the picture of the man with the guitar.

src: down stairs turn at bottom right again past mirrored table through doorway in front of picture of guitar player
tgt: walk down the stairs, turn left at the bottom and right again past the mirrored table, walk through the doorway and stop in front of the picture of a guitar player.

src: in office open door hallway though door down hallway until end turn right forward until first door on right hand side
tgt: STARTING IN AN OFFICE FACING AN OPEN DOOR LOOKING DOWN A HALLWAY, WALK THOUGH THE DOOR AND DOWN THE HALLWAY UNTIL YOU REACH THE END, TURN TO THE RIGHT AND WALK FORWARD UNTIL YOU REACH THE FIRST DOOR ON THE RIGHT HAND SIDE.

src: exit office straight towards exit sign hallway until turn right wait in front of door s-c
tgt: Exit office and go straight towards exit sign. Continue straight down hallway until you reach a turn. Turn right and wait in front of door S-C.

src: walk out of room into hallway walk exit sign into hallway on other side of room walk along glass partition walls around first corner at closed wooden doors
tgt: Walk out of the room into the hallway. Walk passed the exit sign into the hallway on the other side of the room. Walk along the glass partition walls around the first corner and stop at the closed wooden doors.

src: exit bedroom through door turn forward white glass door on left enter inside glass door forward in front of white table
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door and turn left. Walk forward to the patterned white glass door on your left. Enter inside the glass door, and walk forward, and stop in front of the white table.

src: exit right hall hall then at french doors at end of hall before mirror
tgt: Exit to your right and go left down the hall. Follow the hall and then turn left at the french doors. Enter them and stop at the end of the hall before the mirror,.

src: exit bedroom through door on right of television turn down hallway walk through glass double doors on left wait near mirror on wall
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door on the right of the television. Turn left and walk down the hallway. Walk through the glass double doors on the left and wait near the mirror on the wall.

src: walk out of room walk into bathroom on left wait there
tgt: Walk out of the room walk into the bathroom on the left and wait there.

src: last tank door left of plant sink
tgt: Go to the last tank. Go to the door. Go to the left of the plant. Go to the sink.

src: walk out of utility room walk into second door on left by corner of sink
tgt: Walk straight out of the utility room. Walk into the second door on your left. Stop by the corner of the sink.

src: right then keyboard purple room stop near doorway
tgt: Go right and then go left passed the keyboard. Enter the purple room and stop near the doorway.

src: from top of stairs head right down hallway past piano head into door in room outside bathroom
tgt: From the top of the stairs head right and down the hallway. Continue past the piano and head into the door. Stop in that room, outside the bathroom.

src: walk along left wall through door next keyboard once door bathroom
tgt: Walk along the left wall and through the door next to the keyboard. Stop once you reach the door to the bathroom.

src: left at couch stairs through kitchen into hallway outside of door on right after kitchen
tgt: Take a left at the couch and go up the stairs. Walk through the kitchen and into the hallway. Stop outside of the door on the right after you exit the kitchen.

src: steps behind couch forward into kitchen once in kitchen around central island left kitchen through opening right of refrigerator just outside kitchen with glass doors outside left door towards bedroom right
tgt: Climb the two steps behind the couch and continue forward into the kitchen. Once in the kitchen, walk around the central island, keeping it to your left, and exit the kitchen through the opening to the right of the refrigerator. Stop just outside the kitchen with the sliding glass doors leading outside to your left and the door leading towards a bedroom to your right.

src: walk into kitchen turn past kitchen island so under arched doorway outside first doorway on right next small countryside on wall
tgt: Walk into the kitchen and turn left past the kitchen island. So under the arched doorway and stop outside the first doorway on the right, next to a small countryside painting on the wall.

src: left after dresser out of room wait in hallway just outside room
tgt: Take a left after the dresser and walk out of the room. Wait in the hallway just outside the room.

src: walk-in closet stop in front of door room with toilet in
tgt: Leave the walk-in closet and stop in front of the door that leads to the room with the toilet in it.

src: walk shoe rack walking outside restroom door
tgt: Walk straight passing the shoe rack. Keep walking and stop outside the restroom door.

src: turn right across kitchen area walk towards white sofas in living room around white sofa close right wall
tgt: Turn right and walk across the kitchen area. Walk towards the white sofas in the living room. Stay around the white sofa close to the right wall.

src: walk into kitchen forward past dining table into living room in front of first beige couch on right
tgt: Walk into the kitchen and go forward past the dining table. Go into the living room and stop in front of the first beige couch on the right.

src: walk out of closet into kitchen walk along counter past dining room table chairs walk into living room area between couch table
tgt: Walk out of the closet into the kitchen. Walk along the counter and past the dining room table and chairs. Walk into the living room area. Stop between the couch and the table.

src: right hallway couple of stairs on rigth
tgt: Go right down the hallway and go down a couple of stairs on the rigth.

src: walk past floral couch through grey door right halfway stairs in middle of flight
tgt: Walk past he floral couch and go through the grey door. Turn right and head halfway down the stairs, arriving in the middle of the flight.

src: walk through door down hall downstairs near top of stairs
tgt: Walk through the door, down the hall and start downstairs. Stop near the top of the stairs.

src: walk forward out of kitchen into room with pink chairs walk across foyer office in doorway office
tgt: Walk forward and out of the kitchen into the room with the pink dining chairs. Walk across the foyer and enter the office. Stop in the doorway to the office.

src: walk through pantry area slight right through dinning room then through foyer step into office area wait in doorway
tgt: Walk through the pantry area and make a slight right and go through the dinning room.  Then walk through the foyer and step into the office area and wait in the doorway.

src: turn right hallway into dirnng room past table chairs pillar slight right of past chair into door on far left right inside of den door
tgt: Turn right, go down the hallway.  Go into the dirnng room and past the table and chairs.  Go to the pillar and to the slight right of it.  GO past the chair and into the door on the far left.  Wait right inside of that den's door.

src: stairs turn past stairs through doorway into office office through bookshelf passage on left wait by mirror
tgt: Proceed up the stairs, turn left and walk past the stairs, through the doorway into the office. Exit the office through the bookshelf passage on the left and wait by the mirror.

src: head fowards front door into office on opposite side of door turn degrees forward few feet then turn walk into copy room just inside door
tgt: Head fowards the front door.  Go into the office on the opposite side of the door.  Turn left 90 degrees and walk forward a few feet, then take another 90 left turn and walk into the copy room.  Stop just inside the door.

src: office left wait in entryway of second office with copy machine
tgt: Enter the office and take a left. Wait in the entryway of the second office with the copy machine.

src: turn walk past stairs walk into bedroom walk past bed door on left at entrance bathroom
tgt: Turn around. Walk past the stairs. Walk into the bedroom. Walk past the bed to the door on the left. Stop at the entrance to the bathroom.

src: turn around towards stairs through doors through doors left inside bathroom
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the stairs. Keep walking through the doors. Walk through the doors to your left and wait inside the bathroom.

src: exit kitchen way straight down tiny stairs bedroom door door turn bathroom right there
tgt: Exit the kitchen. Walk all the way straight and walk down the tiny three stairs that lead to a bedroom door. Pass the door and turn left to enter the bathroom. Stop right there.

src: forward stairs left at top of stairs bathroom on left in doorway
tgt: Go forward, and go up the stairs. Take a left at the top of the stairs. Enter the bathroom on the left. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn up stairs turn wait in entryway of bedroom
tgt: Turn left and walk up the stairs. Turn left and wait in the entryway of the bedroom.

src: up steps on right living room area turn at top in bathroom doorway left
tgt: Walk up the steps on the right to the living room area and turn left at the top. Stop in the bathroom doorway to the left.

src: exit room from double doors next fireplace then hall until living room in front of front door
tgt: Exit the room from the double doors next to the fireplace, then continue down the hall until reaching the living room in front of the front door.

src: turn into hallway hallway until living room steps just behind cloth chair divider living room from dining room
tgt: Turn around and go into the hallway. Continue down the hallway until you reach the living room and go down the 2 steps. Stop just behind the cloth chair closest to the divider separating the living room from the dining room.

src: walk out double doors near fireplace down hall after doors on left turn into living room near white chair before sofa
tgt: Walk out the double doors near the fireplace. Walk down the hall. After passing two doors on the left, turn left into the living room. Stop near the white chair before the sofa.

src: turn around past sink right past dishwasher wait at end of counters in front of cupboards
tgt: Turn around and walk past the sink and take a right. Walk past the dishwasher and wait at the end of the counters and in front of the cupboards.

src: turn right past counter island past dishwasher stove in front of cabinets wait
tgt: Turn to the right and go past the counter island.  Go past the dishwasher and towards the stove.  When you get in front of the cabinets, stop there and wait.

src: turn right around island right around island in front of counter of stove
tgt: Turn right. Walk around kitchen island. Turn right around kitchen island. Stop in front of counter to left of the stove.

src: hallway towards stairs down stairs straight down stairs right down rest of stairs turn straight right in front of stove
tgt: walk down hallway towards stairs, walk down stairs, continue straight, walk down more stairs, turn right and walk down the rest of the stairs, turn left, walk straight and turn right and stop in front of stove.

src: straight stairs left into kitchen by oven
tgt: Go straight down the stairs and go left into the kitchen. Stop by the oven.

src: stairs directly ahead head way down stairs bottom floor turn kitchen wait by stove
tgt: Go down the stairs directly ahead. Head all the way down the stairs to the bottom floor. Turn left. Enter the kitchen. Wait by the stove.

src: enter room turn past bed turn into bathroom wait near tub
tgt: Enter the room. Turn left and go past the bed. Turn left into the bathroom. Wait near the tub.

src: enter bedroom left then other left enter bedroom wait
tgt: Enter bedroom make a left, then a other left, and enter bedroom and wait.

src: enter bedroom ahead left into bathroom on left next bathtub
tgt: Enter the bedroom ahead, and go left. Go into the bathroom on the left. Stop next to the bathtub.

src: turn right enter into house once in house red purple chairs stairs stop
tgt: Turn right and enter into the house. Once in the house, pass the red and purple chairs and go up the stairs and stop.

src: enter building walk past first set of steps wait on second set of steps
tgt: Enter the building and walk past the first set of steps and wait on the second set of steps.

src: walk forward house kitchen stairs on left on second stair from top
tgt: Walk forward and enter the house. Go to the kitchen, and go up the stairs on the left. Stop on the second stair from the top.

src: walk into corridor just of statue first door on right wait near sink
tgt: Walk into corridor just left of the statue.  Enter the first door on the right.  Wait near sink.

src: down hall left outside right just past circular black art piece of wall just outside doorway into room with sink
tgt: Walk down the hall, windows to your left looking outside. Turn right just past the circular black art piece of the wall. Stop just outside the doorway leading into the room with the sink.

src: move down hallway right just past metal art on wall
tgt: Move straight down the hallway, and turn right and wait just past the metal art on the wall.

src: turn around towards kitchen as soon as seating area before tiled kitchen area right towards doorway into bedroom walk into bedroom turn past bed so that bed on right tv on left past bathtub door into bathroom just inside doorway bathroom
tgt: Turn around to walk towards the kitchen. As soon as you leave the seating area and before you enter the tiled kitchen area, turn right to move towards the doorway that leads into the bedroom. Walk into the bedroom and turn left to walk past the bed, so that the bed is on your right and the TV is on your left. Walk past the bathtub and towards the door into the bathroom. Stop when you are standing just inside the doorway to the bathroom.

src: walk between couches right through doorway left straight past bed bathtub wait in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Walk between the two couches and take a right. Walk through the doorway and take a left. Walk straight past the bed and the bathtub and wait in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: away from fireplace in bedroom on right past bed tub in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Walk away from the fireplace and go in the bedroom on the right.  Walk past the bed and tub and stop in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: head through dining area turn stairs up second stair stop wait there
tgt: Head through the dining area and turn left to the stairs. Go up to the second stair, stop and wait there.

src: walk towards staircase wait at bottom of stairs near colorful face painting
tgt: Walk towards staircase.  Wait at bottom of stairs near colorful face painting.

src: turn right past table chairs turn toward stairs right steps then
tgt: Turn right and go past the table and chairs. Turn left and walk toward the stairs. Turn right and go up three steps then stop.

src: after stairs right turn right into room right of thermostat wait by first bathroom sink
tgt: After you go up the stairs go right turn right and go into the room that is to the right of the thermostat. Wait by the first bathroom sink.

src: from top of stairs walkway then right into bathroom on left
tgt: From the top of the stairs, head down the walkway, then veer right and go into the bathroom on your left.

src: toward hallway by stairs right toward bedroom turn in bathroom by first sink
tgt: Go toward the hallway by the stairs and turn right toward the bedroom.  Turn left and stop in the bathroom by the first sink.

src: at base of stairs path right past black table water fountain onto rocks just before onto blue basketball court
tgt: At the base of the stairs, take the path to the right and walk past the black table and water fountain.  Step onto the rocks and stop just before stepping onto the blue basketball court.

src: at bottom of stairs left stone floor toward basketball hoop in rocks wait
tgt: At the bottom of the stairs take a left and follow the stone floor. Walk toward the basketball hoop and stop in the rocks and wait.

src: walk right walkway past patio table wait in gravel by basketball court
tgt: Walk to the right down the walkway past the patio table. Wait in the gravel by the basketball court.

src: bedroom right down hallway into bathroom through last door on right in bathroom doorway
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Walk down the hallway and go into the bathroom through the last door on the right. Stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: straight rooms end of room ours near white color door
tgt: Go straight and cross one  or two rooms and end of the room is ours. Near white color door.

src: down hall carpet on down hall at last doors on right there not bathroom wait just outside
tgt: Walk down the hall, following the carpet.  Continue on down the hall.  When you are at the last doors on the right, turn there.  Do not enter the bathroom, but wait just outside.

src: exit room turn straight into room walk past bed straight into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go straight into the room. Walk past the bed and continue straight into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: face banister through doorway on right turn hallway walk through bedroom once into bathroom
tgt: face banister to stairs, walk through doorway on your right, turn left down hallway, walk straight through bedroom and stop once you walk into bathroom.

src: walk forward hall then then forward into bedroom into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Walk forward and enter the hall, then turn left. Then walk forward into the bedroom and continue into the bathroom.  Wait near the sink.

src: walk ahead through open doorway down hall up small set of steps wide circular concrete wall out of doorway outside of home
tgt: Walk ahead through the open doorway. Walk down the hall and up the small set of steps. Continue walking passed the wide circular concrete wall. Walk out of the doorway to the outside of the home.

src: straight on through door then steps turn left walk past wooden shelf then gate wait
tgt: Go straight on through the door.  Then go up the steps.  Turn to the left and walk past the wooden shelf.  Then go to the gate and stop there and wait.

src: walk out of room turn right down hallway up stairs turn past shelf outside right by gate
tgt: Walk out of the room and turn left. Turn right and walk down the hallway. Walk up the stairs and turn left. Walk past the shelf. Walk outside and turn right. Stop by the gate.

src: straight then stairs down near exit room
tgt: Go straight then turn left to the stairs go down near the exit room.

src: head hallway with railing turn stairs at foot of stairs
tgt: Head down the hallway with the railing and turn left going down the stairs.  Stop at the foot of the stairs.

src: hall along handrail then at stairs at bottom
tgt: Go down the hall along the handrail, then turn left at the stairs and go down. Stop at the bottom.

src: after inside building right stairs wait on second step
tgt: After you walk inside the building make a right and go to the stairs, and wait on the second step.

src: through doorway away from outside area right toward christmas tree steps up onto staircase then
tgt: Go through the doorway away from the outside area, make a right toward the Christmas tree, take two steps up onto the staircase and then stop.

src: straight ahead right few steps up stairwell
tgt: Go straight ahead and turn right, stopping a few steps up the stairwell.

src: hallway walking straight past stairs doorway at end of hall stop wait
tgt: You have to walk down the hallway and keep walking straight past the stairs, when you get to the doorway at the end of the hall stop and wait.

src: hallway in doorway outdoor area
tgt: Go down the hallway and stop in the doorway that leads to the outdoor sitting area.

src: walk through glass door right outside before loungers
tgt: Walk straight through sliding glass door to patio. Stop right when you get outside before loungers.

src: exit bedroom continue straight through double doors outside past bed at guardrail next first of tall windows with circle holes in
tgt: Exit the bedroom and continue straight through the double doors, going outside, past the bed, and turning left at the guardrail. Stop next to the first of three tall windows with circle holes in them.

src: walk across hall out door wait on other side of bed near railing
tgt: Walk across the hall and out the door. Wait on the other side of the bed, near the railing.

src: exit bedroom across hall walk murphy bed turn on walk under porch
tgt: Exit bedroom, across hall to outside. walk passed Murphy bed, turn left on walk and stop under porch.

src: turn right hallway into bathroom on right
tgt: Turn right down the hallway, and go into the bathroom on the right.

src: exit bedroom wait in bathroom doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom and wait in the bathroom doorway.

src: walk towards bedroom door right into bathroom
tgt: Walk towards the bedroom door , turn right into the bathroom.

src: walk past striped area rug right onto marble floor walk past bathroom on left left zebra painting walk through open door wait at mirror
tgt: Walk past the striped area rug. Make a right onto the marble floor. Walk past the bathroom on the left. Make a left opposite the zebra painting. Walk through the open door, and wait at the mirror.

src: pass red rug then antelope rug turn right into hallway then on second opening wait by closet entrance on left
tgt: Pass the red rug then when you get to the antelope rug turn right and go into the hallway then turn left on the second opening and wait by the closet entrance on the left.

src: in front of giraffe print chair wall between kitchen doorway doorway on left next walk through door down hall picture of left now through doorway wait in front of doorway of first closet on left
tgt: When you are standing in front of the giraffe print chair and are facing the wall between the kitchen and doorway, go to the doorway on the left. Next walk through the door and down the hall, when you get to the picture of the zebra make a left. Now go through the doorway and wait in front of the doorway of the first closet on the left.

src: bathroom right past dining room through doorway wait in front of bathroom
tgt: Leave the bathroom, turn right, walk past the dining room, walk through the doorway and wait in front of the bathroom.

src: head into hallway right through room with white furniture head through doorway stop
tgt: Head into the hallway and turn right.  Go through the room with white furniture.  Head through the doorway and stop.

src: right into doorway walk across room into next hallway at door left
tgt: Turn right into doorway Walk straight across dining room into next  hallway. stop at door to right and hallway to the left.

src: exit room walk straight into room across bed into second room on left wait near white bench on right
tgt: Exit the room and walk straight into the room across. Pass the bed and go into the second room on the left. Wait near the white bench on the right.

src: walk across hall through bedroom just inside bathroom
tgt: Walk across the hall and through the bedroom. Stop just inside the bathroom.

src: walk forward through doorway straight ahead into bedroom across into bathroom in front of first window
tgt: Walk forward through the closest doorway. Go straight ahead into the bedroom across. Go into the bathroom. Stop in front of the first window.

src: enter hallway through door right of bookcase veer living room through last door on right on left edge of carpet
tgt: Enter the hallway through the door to the right of the bookcase. Veer left and enter the living room through the last door on the right. Stop on the left edge of the carpet.

src: turn hallway on right through open door on left on rug
tgt: turn around and go down the the hallway on the right. Go through the least open door on the left and stop on the rug.

src: turn hallway behind way down in wood door on end left once in on rug
tgt: Turn around and enter the hallway behind you. Walk all the way down and turn in the wood door on the end to your left. Once in, stop on the rug,.

src: stairs right straight past long table in front of sink
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn right. Walk straight past the long table. Stop in front of the sink.

src: down stairs right in between counter grey chairs
tgt: Walk down the stairs and take a right. Wait in between the counter and the grey chairs.

src: rest of stairs right straight pass area area on left area on right potted plant directly right wall with fireplace directly in front of door outside directly left
tgt: Go down the rest of the stairs and turn right.  Keep walking straight pass the dining area.  Stop when the kitchen area is on your left and the sitting area is on your right.  There will be a potted plant directly to your right and a wall with a fireplace directly in front of you and a door going outside directly to your left.

src: walk through area past dishwasher door on right laundry room just past door in front of window
tgt: Walk through the kitchen area past the dishwasher.  Enter the door on your right to the laundry room.  Stop just past the door in front of the window.

src: straight stairs bar dishwasher in front of tall white cabinets
tgt: Go straight passed the stairs and passed the bar. Go to passed the dishwasher and stop in front of the tall white cabinets.

src: walk into kitchen past glass door past counter kitchen beside sink
tgt: Walk into the kitchen, go past the glass door and continue past the counter. Exit the kitchen and stop beside the sink.

src: turn right across hall benches wait in between benches by entrance outside
tgt: Turn right and walk across the hall towards the benches. Wait in between the benches by the entrance going outside.

src: walk through large open walkway with wooden roof trusses walk along tiled walkway past armchair area tables with white table clothes walk between first benches near entryway door
tgt: Walk through the large open walkway with wooden beamed roof trusses. Walk along the tiled walkway past the armchair area and tables with white table clothes. Walk between the first two benches near the entryway door.

src: forward into lobby veer right at leather benches stop between leather benches before rug
tgt: Walk forward into the lobby. Veer right at the two leather benches. Stop between the two leather benches before you reach the rug.

src: exit kitchen towards stairs at base of stairs
tgt: Exit kitchen towards stairs. Stop at base of stairs.

src: away from pool on left side of island slightly past cabinets room table towards stairs directly between base of stairs doorway
tgt: walk away from the pool, on the left side of the island, continue slightly left past the cabinets and dining room table towards the stairs, stop when you are directly between the base of the stairs and a doorway.

src: turn into kitchen with set of stairs left across house bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn left to face into the kitchen with a set of stairs to the left. Walk across the house to the bottom of the stairs.

src: head past kitchen sink refrigerator in front of washing machines
tgt: Head past the kitchen sink and refrigerator and stop in front of the washing and drying machines.

src: walk through walkway in between chairs in front of washer dryer electric breaker box on wall
tgt: Walk straight through the walkway in between the chairs and stove. Stop in front of the washer and dryer facing the electric breaker box on the wall.

src: walk past sink in front of washing machine
tgt: Walk past the sink and stop in front of the washing machine.

src: stairs into theater on left at bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs and go into the theater on the left at the bottom.

src: head stairs through first door on left wait in cinema room
tgt: Head down the stairs. Go through the first door on the Left. Wait in the cinema room.

src: stairs turn left into room with white couches wait there
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Go into the room with white couches and wait there.

src: staircase forward hallway bedroom through door wait in doorway
tgt: Move down the staircase and continue forward down the hallway. Enter the bedroom through the door and wait in the doorway.

src: down stairs slight left hallway movie posters on wall wait in doorway of bedroom at end of hall
tgt: Walk down the stairs and make a slight left to go down the hallway that has the movie posters on the wall. Wait in the doorway of the bedroom at the end of the hall.

src: down stairs through first hall on left straight door at end of hallway immediatly after through door
tgt: Walk down stairs, and walk through the first hall on your left. Walk straight to the door at the end of the hallway, stop immediatly after you walk through the door.

src: turn behind sofa living room straight through door towards kitchen stop
tgt: Turn around and go behind the sofa. Enter the living room and go straight through the door towards the kitchen and stop.

src: turn end of bed just over dooway into empty closet sink stop
tgt: Turn around and go to the end of bed, just over the dooway into the empty closet and sink and stop.

src: exit balcony into bedroom head in open doorway left
tgt: Exit the balcony into the bedroom. Head straight and stop in the open doorway to the left.

src: turn towards right into bedroom door at end of hallway right into bathroom inside door bathtub glass
tgt: Turn towards your right. Walk into the bedroom door at the end of the hallway. Turn to your right and walk into the bathroom. Stop inside the door facing the bathtub and the glass windows.

src: walk int bedroom right into bathroom next at left
tgt: Walk int bedroom, turn right into bathroom and stop next to sink at left.

src: walk into room right then right again by sink
tgt: Walk straight into the room and turn right then turn right again and wait by the sink.

src: turn past pool door house on right once inside turn right straight ahead kitchen
tgt: Turn left and walk past the pool. Enter the door to the house on your right. Once inside turn right. Walk straight ahead and stop when you enter the kitchen.

src: turn around by pool potted plants right into house right wait by table
tgt: Turn around and walk by the pool and potted plants. Take a right into the house. Take another right and wait by the table.

src: walk around pool on side closest building open door inside right in doorway kitchen
tgt: Walk around the pool on the side closest to the building.  When you see an open door, go inside and turn right.  Stop in the doorway to the kitchen.

src: tub rug couch go thermostat electrical receptacle bed
tgt: Go to the tub. Go to the rug. Go to the couch. Go to the thermostat. Go to the electrical receptacle. Go to the bed.

src: first past bed around pool table straight recliners room ahead once past door
tgt: Take the first left past the bed and go around the pool table. Go straight and pass the recliners and enter the room straight ahead. Stop once you are past the door.

src: bedroom game room slight left walk between pool table chairs enter hallway straight at edge of bed
tgt: leave bedroom to game room. turn slight left and walk between pool table and chairs, enter hallway, walk straight and stop at edge of bed.

src: walk through room behind couch out through door in corner down hallway into room with sink counter top
tgt: Walk through the room behind the couch and out through the door in the corner. Walk down the hallway and into the room with the sink and counter top.

src: straight past couch till at double doors right through hallwayand turn left into room little bar wait
tgt: Go straight, past the couch till you are at the double doors. That's when you turn right.  Go through the hallwayand turn to the left.  Go into that room, it's a little bar.  Stop there and wait.

src: walk edge of open door walk through open door left at open door frame
tgt: Walk straight to the edge of the open door. Walk through the open door. Make a left at the open door frame.

src: stair into first door on left next white table
tgt: Go down the stair and go into the first door on the left. Stop next to the white table.

src: stairs at bottom of stairs in room
tgt: Go down the stairs and at the bottom of the stairs turn left and stop in the room.

src: head into dining room on left wait by table
tgt: Head downstairs into the dining room on the left. Wait by the table.

src: enter house angle right close chairs on right side past staircase right wait in doorway with double doors
tgt: Enter the house and angle right, walking close to the chairs on the right side. Continue past the staircase and turn right. Wait in the doorway with the double doors.

src: large open staircase into room veer right of staircase through third double door on right
tgt: Facing the large open staircase, go into the room and veer to the right of the staircase, going through the third arched double door opening on the right.

src: inside slight right forward along left wall into second last archway then
tgt: Go inside, turn slight right and start going forward along the left wall, go into the second to last archway then stop.

src: walk toward bar area in back corner small room next bar in front of doorway room
tgt: Walk toward the bar area in the back corner. There is a small room next to the bar. Stop in front of the doorway to that room.

src: in between round tables then right past long rectangular table next entrance of bar
tgt: Go in between the round tables and then go right past the long rectangular table.  Stop next the to the entrance of the bar.

src: walk right side of wooden pole through tables chairs towards double wood doors with wreath above right last tables walk in front of long buffet table once past buffet table walk left of tables in front of bar stop at far pillar on bar
tgt: Walk to the right side of the wooden pole, through the tables and chairs towards the double wood doors with a wreath hanging above them. Turn right when you reach the last two tables and walk in front of the long buffet table, once past the buffet table walk to the left of the tables but in front of the bar and stop at the far pillar on the bar.

src: stairs into room right of marilyn monroe wait by entrance
tgt: Go down the stairs and when you go into the room to the right of the Marilyn Monroe painting wait by the entrance.

src: turn stairs down level door just at right room
tgt: Turn left and go down the stairs. Keep going down. When you reach the lower level, enter the door just at your right. Enter the room.

src: stairs into doorway of bedroom with large bed door outside
tgt: Go down the stairs, and into the doorway of a bedroom with a large bed and a door to the outside.

src: stairs right straight until room with black table fireplace wait near fireplace
tgt: Go down the stairs. Turn right and go straight until you get to a room with a black table and a fireplace. Wait near the fireplace.

src: between columns then right through double doors hallway at end room right under velvet rope stand in front of fireplace wait there
tgt: Go between the two columns and then turn right. Go through the double doors and proceed down the hallway. At the end enter the room to the right, go under the velvet rope and stand in front of the fireplace. Wait there.

src: head away from front door flight of stairs right hallway down through sets of doors just before ropes on right side step over rope just before fireplace
tgt: Head away from front door down a flight of 3 stairs, Turn right. Follow hallway down through 2 sets of doors. Stop just before the ropes. On the right side step over the rope and just before the fireplace.

src: head end of hallway upstairs in middle of first flight of stairs
tgt: Head to the end of the hallway, go upstairs and stop in the middle of the first flight of stairs.

src: with door left painting right hallway then steps up stairs left at end of hallway
tgt: With the door to your left and the painting to your right, start walking down the hallway and then take four steps up the stairs to your left at the end of the hallway.

src: turn hard left down hall then left up stairs in middle of stairs
tgt: Turn to your hard left and walk down the hall. Then turn to your left and walk up the stairs. Stop in the middle of the stairs.

src: spiral stairs walk straight until kitchen then there
tgt: Go down the spiral stairs. Walk straight until you get to the kitchen then wait there.

src: down stairs kitchen wait near counter top
tgt: Walk down the stairs and enter the kitchen.  Wait near the counter top.

src: circular staircase walk into kitchen in front of in front of jars at end of wooden counter top
tgt: Go down the circular staircase and walk into the kitchen in front of you,  Stop in front of the jars at the end of the wooden counter top.

src: bedroom forward machine right into living room hard left door stand in doorway not
tgt: Leave bedroom to hall and go forward to washing machine. Turn right into living room and take a hard left to front door. Stand in the doorway to outside but do not exit.

src: walk out of door washer dryer right at next doorway slight right turn then left turn at door with brown rug on floor
tgt: Walk out of the door facing the washer and dryer. Make a right at the next doorway. Make a slight right turn and then a left turn at the door with the brown rug on the floor.

src: walk out of bedroom into laundry room right out of room into living room area left stand in front doorway
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and into the laundry room, make a right out of the room and into a living room area. Make a left and stand in the front doorway.

src: straight glass table with white chairs then into hallway then at doorway
tgt: Go straight. Pass the glass table with the white chairs then turn left and go into that hallway then turn left and stop at that doorway.

src: turn dining room walk across dining room then exit through doorway on left left then at entrance of empty room
tgt: Turn around and enter the dining room. Walk across the dining room, then exit through the doorway on the left. Turn to the left, then stop at the entrance of the empty room.

src: walk through entryway into room with beige chairs glass table after table turn through doorway first left wait in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Walk through entryway into dining room with the beige chairs and glass table. After you pass the table, turn left and go through doorway. Take the first left and wait in doorway of bathroom.

src: around table out into hallway right then around next corner next round pillar
tgt: Go around the table and out into the hallway. Turn right and then turn left around the next corner. Stop next to the round pillar.

src: door right right at hallway just after at next hallway
tgt: To out the door to your right, right at the hallway, and stop just after you turn left at the next hallway.

src: exit room on right then right in hall turn by fire extinguisher
tgt: Exit the room on the right and then turn right in the hall. Turn left and stop by the fire extinguisher.

src: upstairs right enter hallway stop at first doorway
tgt: go upstairs, turn right, enter hallway stop at first doorway.

src: stairs towards narrow hallway top at beginning of hallway
tgt: Go up the stairs, and continue towards a narrow hallway when you reach the top. Stop at the beginning of the hallway.

src: up stairs right once top walk over see-through floor into hallway stop wait in hallway in front of entrances right left
tgt: Walk up the stairs and make a right once you reach the top. Walk over the see-through floor and into the hallway. Stop and wait in the hallway in front of the two entrances, one to your right and one to your left.

src: exit bathroom turn at entry way door
tgt: Exit bathroom, turn left and stop at entry way door.

src: turn into hall turn steps
tgt: Turn around and go out into the hall. Turn left and go up the two steps.

src: away from sink through doorway turn windows up marble steps stop
tgt: walk away from sink through doorway, turn left when you reach the windows, walk up two marble steps and stop.

src: down bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down to the bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs upon bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs. Stop upon reaching the bottom.

src: stairs wait beside chairs at base of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and wait beside the chairs at the base of the stairs.

src: bedroom in hall stairs stairs stop
tgt: Leave the bedroom. In the hall go to the stairs. Go up two stairs and stop.

src: head out door in front of down hallway once stairs on left at bottom
tgt: Head out the door in front of you and down the hallway. Once you reach the stairs on your left, stop at the bottom facing up.

src: walk out oft bedroom up second step stop
tgt: Walk out oft the bedroom. Walk up to the second step and stop.

src: stairs left head end of glass table wait
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn to your left and head to the end of the glass table and wait.

src: head stairs immediate left forward near dinning table
tgt: Head down the stairs, make an immediate left, move forward and wait near the dinning table.

src: head downstairs turn past glass tables wait in front of table with head bust portrait artwork
tgt: Head downstairs and turn left, walking past the glass tables.  Wait in front of the table with the head bust and portrait artwork.

src: up stairs turn down hallway past bathroom into bedroom wait just inside door
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn left. Walk down the hallway and past the bathroom, into the bedroom. Wait just inside the door.

src: kitchen stairs at top of stairs left bedroom at end of hall once door step on rug
tgt: Leave the kitchen going up the stairs. At the top of the stairs take a left. Enter the bedroom at the end of the hall. Stop once you pass the door, and step on the rug.

src: walk through kitchen towards stairwell television on wall up set of steps corner at top into hallway walk past bathroom into bedroom at end of hall bed large photo art on opposite wall
tgt: Walk through the kitchen towards the stairwell passing the television on the wall. Walk up the set of steps and turn the corner at the top into a hallway. Walk past the bathroom and into the bedroom at the end of the hall, which has a bed and large photo art on the opposite wall.

src: walk into great room walk past table chairs walk past bar through open french doors outside doors
tgt: Walk into great room. Walk past dining table and chairs. Walk past bar. Walk through open french doors. Wait outside doors.

src: enter area then forward backyard wait by door
tgt: Enter the dining area, and then move forward to the backyard, and wait by the door.

src: walk out of sitting room forward into hall in dining hall around table right out of doors once out of doors onto patio stop parallel wooden bench on left
tgt: Walk out of the sitting room and go forward into the dining hall. In the dining hall go around the table to the right and walk straight out of the doors. Once you walk out of the doors onto the patio stop parallel to the wooden bench on your left.

src: up stairs left down stairs down narrow hallway in hallway second door on left right into bedroom in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk up the stairs and take a left. Go down these stairs and walk down the narrow hallway. In the hallway take the second door on your left, and a right into the bedroom. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: wastebasket vase steps steps light switch bedroom door
tgt: Go to the wastebasket. Go to the vase. Go down two steps. Go three steps. Go to the light switch. Go to the bedroom door.

src: walk through lobby stairs left hallway second left then right in bedroom
tgt: Walk through the lobby, go down the stairs to the left. Continue down the hallway; take the second left, and then a right. Stop in the bedroom.

src: into foyer toward white door on left into room with stairs right stairs straight then left hallway then right into dining room then
tgt: Go left into the foyer toward the white door on the left. Go into the room with stairs, turn right passed the stairs and keep going straight, then turn left to go down the hallway, then turn right into the dining room, then stop.

src: walk into foyer left room with stairs on right right hall dining room first on right once on rug
tgt: Walk into to the foyer and take a left. Enter the room with the stairs on the right. Veer right down the hall. Enter the dining room which is first on the right. Stop once you step on the rug.

src: into open room with white flooring turn then through second doorway on right past stairs through doorway just past art piece of dancer on black white rug next long wooden dining table
tgt: Go into the open room with white flooring. Turn left, then go through the second doorway on the right. Walk past the stairs. Go through the doorway just past the art piece of a dancer. Stop on the black and white rug, next to the long wooden dining table.

src: walk through doorway into house forward past sink machine wait in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk through the doorway and into the house. Continue forward past the sink and washing machine. Wait in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: from porch enter house walk through kitchen into bedroom wait at bed
tgt: From porch enter house walk through kitchen into bedroom. Wait at bed.

src: walk into building past stove refrigerator stop in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk into the building and past the stove and refrigerator and stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: right right then straight into bedroom next plants in bedroom
tgt: Go to the right and take a right. Then go straight and into the bedroom. Stop next to the plants in the bedroom.

src: turn right walk through double doors right right again past couch through area on into bedroom there wait
tgt: Turn to the right   Walk through the double doors to the right.  Turn right again and walk past the couch, through the kitchen area.  And on into the bedroom.  Stop there.  Wait.

src: exit entryway right through sitting room through kitchen bedroom wait at table with bird sculpture
tgt: Exit the entryway, turn right, walk through the sitting room, walk through the kitchen, enter the bedroom, wait at the table with the bird sculpture.

src: down stairs turn wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the stairs and turn left.  Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk downstairs wait at base of staircase
tgt: Walk downstairs and wait at the base of the staircase.

src: down staircase turn down stairs stop
tgt: walk down the staircase, turn left and walk down all stairs and stop.

src: door step out right out door hard right into bedroom inside doorway
tgt: Open the shower door and step out. Turn right. Walk out the door. Make a hard right and walk into the bedroom. Stop inside the doorway.

src: exit bathroom right into bedroom stop at dresser
tgt: exit bathroom to hall, turn right and continue down hall into the bedroom, Stop at the dresser.

src: bathroom right until bedroom then
tgt: Leave the bathroom and turn right.  Keep going until you enter the bedroom and then stop.

src: forward into house down hallway in living room right into dining room behind bench next mirror
tgt: Walk forward into the house and down the hallway. In the living room take a right and walk into the dining room. Stop behind the bench next to the mirror.

src: turn until opening at living room with light switch on right into living room right behind couch past round table forward walk table near in bar shelf on right
tgt: TURN LEFT UNTIL YOU FACE AN OPENING LOOKING AT A LIVING ROOM WITH A LIGHT SWITCH ON THE RIGHT, WALK INTO THE LIVING ROOM AND TURN RIGHT, WALK BEHIND THE COUCH PAST A ROUND TABLE, CONTINUING FORWARD WALK TO THE DINNING TABLE NEAR A BUILT IN BAR SHELF ON THE RIGHT.

src: walk into living room right towards dining table between table large mirror on right
tgt: Walk into the living room and turn right.  Walk towards the dining table.  Stop between the table and the large mirror on the right.

src: walk towards door in kitchen right straight towards room turn at edge of counter enter room stop

tgt: Turn right and walk down the small hallway and out the door. Stop once you walk outside.

tgt: walk towards fireplace, turn left and walk through doorway to exit bedroom, pass bedroom on right, stop in next doorway on right and stop.

tgt: Exit the toilet room. Go toward the bathtub. Turn right. Exit the bathroom. Go straight ahead toward the double doors. Go through the double doors toward the couch. Stop there.

tgt: Go up the stairs. Take a right and stop in the door past the exercise bike.

tgt: walk straight the landing then stop at the front of the glass door.

After climbing four steps and reaching the top, turn left and climb five more steps. Enter the room that's ahead of you and just past the foot of a longer flight of stairs.

tgt: Continue up the stairs.  Turn right and walk into the middle of the open area.  Turn right and walk towards the front door.  Turn right and climb up all the stairs.

tgt: If you would go to the bedroom with the striped blanket on it you will find a large empty closet located directly across from it.

tgt: To take right and turn left and enter bedroom. Opp side of bedroom.

tgt: Continue up the stairs. Go straight through the doorway and into the bedroom.  Turn to the left and go past the chair.  Go out the doorway to the rooftop.  Walk through the door and then stop.  Wait.

tgt: walk towards the red rope.

tgt: Walk forward and enter the door that is straight and in front of you at the end. Walk inside the room, and turn left. Walk forward towards the bed and turn right towards the door in the center, not the corner, and stop there.

src: away from rug slight right at giant through doorway right towards foot of bed in first doorway on right
tgt: walk away from rug, turn slight right at giant 1, walk through doorway to left, turn left, turn right and walk towards foot of bed, stop in first doorway on right.

src: turn head between stairs wall down hallway toward center door through room right head toward bed right again closet through door in front of
tgt: Turn left, and head between the stairs and the wall.  Head down the hallway toward the center door and go through.  Enter the room, turn right, head toward the bed, and turn right again.  Enter the closet through the door in front of you.

tgt: Walk towards sofa.  Continue past recliner to enter the bedroom at the far side of room.  Turn left and walk to the far side of the bed.  Wait by lamp.

src: walk across living room into bedroom turn at bathtub
tgt: Walk across living room into bedroom, turn left and stop at bathtub.

src: turn around into room out door straight ahead on other side once bedroom turn other side of bed on other side of bed
tgt: Turn around and walk into the sitting room and out the door straight ahead on the other side. Once you enter the bedroom turn left and walk to the other side of the bed. Stop on the other side of the bed.

src: walk into bedroom area around bed out of door into hallway down flight of stairs until final set of stairs
tgt: Walk into the bedroom area. Walk around the bed and out of the door into the hallway. Walk down the flight of stairs to the until the final set of stairs.

tgt: Walk into the bedroom and go around the bed. At the end of the bed turn left and leave the room. Go down the stairs on the right and wait on the third step on the second set of steps.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Go through the hallway and turn right to stop.

src: walk through door then head through hallway right turn immediately
tgt: Walk through the door, and then head left and walk through the hallway, make a right turn and stop immediately.

src: bathroom bedroom forward in hall right at end of hall at top of stairs
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and bedroom. Go forward in the hall and take a right at the end of the hall. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: pass between couch stairs continue into hall right through door before cheetah wall hanging
tgt: pass between couch and stairs continue into hall.  Turn right and pass through door, stop before cheetah wall hanging.

src: turn left around past blue couch walk hallway right into room with leopard painting on wall just inside doorway wait
tgt: Turn to the left, all around, and go past the blue couch.  Walk to the hallway and turn right.  Go into a room with the leopard painting on the wall.  Stand just inside the doorway and wait.

src: walk through living room right at smoke detector wait on zebra rug
tgt: Walk through the living room. Make a right at the smoke detector. Wait on the zebra rug.

src: steps past table chairs then right steps then there
tgt: Go up the steps. Go past the table and chairs then U turn right. Go down the steps then wait there.

tgt: Walk up the steps and past the pig. Wait in the doorway on the other side of the table.

tgt: Walk up the steps. Walk around the dining table. Stop in the doorway to the left of the big yellow art on the wall.

tgt: Walk past sink on right. Make hard right at window in laundry room. Walk through open door on left. Make hard right into dining room. Walk past dining room table on right. Walk through open door on left.Wait at plantation shuttered window on right.

src: through door beside sink through kitchen dining room walk past buffet table into living room right beside window
tgt: Go through the door beside the sink and through the kitchen to the dining room. Walk past the buffet table into the living room. Stop right beside the window.

tgt: Exit the laundry room through the door on your right into the kitchen. There is a doorway to the right of the kitchen that you'll need to go through into the dinning area. Go left from the doorway past the dinning area into the living room with burgundy couches.

src: staircase at bottom left near doorway
tgt: Descend the staircase. At the bottom take a left and stop near the doorway.

src: stairs turn straight until set of table chairs on right fireplace on left wait there
tgt: Go down the stairs. Turn left and go straight until you get to a set of table and chairs on the right and the fireplace on the left. Wait there.

src: stairs turn at bottom straight toward doorway kitchen near wooden pillar before doorway
tgt: Proceed down the stairs and turn left at the bottom.  Go straight toward the doorway to the kitchen, stopping near the wooden pillar before the doorway.

src: hallway right left at intersection in hallway once left
tgt: Go down the hallway to your right. Take a left at the intersection in the hallway. Stop once you take the left.

tgt: Walk past the exit sign and down the hall. Turn left and stop in the next hallway.

src: right hall turn at first hallway on left wait at beginning of hallway
tgt: Go right down the hall. Turn left at the first hallway on your left. Wait at the beginning of the hallway.

tgt: With the bed to your left, exit the room though the doorway directly ahead of you. Continue forward past all the furniture and exit that room through the next doorway directly ahead of you. Continue into that bedroom until you almost reach the foot of the bed.

tgt: Walk into the living room, and keep going. Enter the bedroom across from the original. Stop once you pass the door.

tgt: Head straight down the hallway, pass a mirror then wait by the last door in the hallway.

tgt: Turn left  and walk down the hallway, stop at the entrance of the exercise room.

src: down hallway stop at end outside of exercise room
tgt: Walk down the hallway and stop at the end, outside of the exercise room.

tgt: Turn and around and take a right turn to go between the benches. Turn left passed the pillar and stop at the end of the first bench on the right.

tgt: Walk a bit forward, and turn right at the very first empty space between the benches. Keep walking forward passing the pole, and stop in front of the bench that have maroon cushions on them.

Walk towards the painting of the man to the right, passing by the table and chairs in the dining area. Walk into the room with the sink and stop just in front of the cutting board that is on the counter.

src: inside turn steps table chairs kitchen turn right into room wait near microwave
tgt: Go inside turn left and go up the steps. Pass the table and chairs. When you get to the kitchen turn right and go into the room. Wait near the microwave.

src: into living room navigate behind couch left forward at end of hall
tgt: Go into the living room, navigate behind the couch to the left, move forward, stop at the end of the hall.

tgt: Walk up the stairs and take a right. Stop in front of the ornate glass double doors.

src: walk through bathroom right walk past couch table chairs behind chairs
tgt: Walk through the bathroom and turn right. Walk left past the couch, table, and chairs. Stop behind the chairs.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom door, and turn right into the living room.  Walk towards the tree statue and wait in front of the door leading outside.

tgt: Walk through the bathroom past the sink and through the door to the hallway Walk into the hall and through the nearby open door with an old rotary phone on the wall. Walk into the room, which is a bedroom. Walk Past the bed and night stand through the open door in the corner.

tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom.  Then enter the bedroom. Wait near the bedroom door and the chair.

tgt: Head inside, turn right, walk forward into the bathroom, wait near the bathtub.

tgt: Go up the stairs past the painting on the right. Take a right and walk up the staircase opposite to the bathroom.

tgt: Go to the other side of the library and stand on the red dot. Follow the blue dots.

tgt: Turn so the windows of the room are on your left.  Walk to the end of the long table, next to the lamp.

tgt: Turn around and walk towards the leftmost and farthest red chair in the room and wait there.

tgt: Go down the stairs and then after take a slight left and go into the kitchen then stop.

Stop in front of the first urinal.

tgt: Head up the stairs and stop in front of the sculpture on the wall.
