tgt: Leave the closet and bedroom and go into the hallway. In the hall go straight and down the stairs. Turn right at the last door on the right which enters a bathroom. Stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: turn slightly towards right slightly forward bedroom forward at top of stairs on left turn down stairs wait on third stair
tgt: Turn slightly towards the right. Turn slightly left. Walk forward. Exit the bedroom. Continue walking forward. Stop at the top of the stairs on the left. Turn left and walk down the stairs. Wait on the third stair down.

src: room from door on left down hallway stairs on fourth step from top
tgt: Leave the room from the door on your left.  Walk down the hallway to the stairs and stop on the fourth step from the top.

src: exit room through doorway on left straight way down hallway until staircase stairs then on fourth stair
tgt: Exit the room through the doorway on the left. Walk straight all the way down the hallway until you reach the staircase. Start walking down the stairs, then stop on the fourth stair.

src: steps next forward until room on left with double doors
tgt: Go down the three steps next to you and continue forward until you can enter the room on your left with the double doors.

src: jaunt over massage room with pillars walls
tgt: Take a jaunt over to the massage room with the pillars and striped walls.

src: steps straight then into double doors wait by table
tgt: Go down the steps and continue straight and then go left into the double doors and wait by the table.

src: steps then u turn straight until into room with washer dryer wait at entrance
tgt: Go down the steps and then U turn left and continue going straight until you go into a room with a washer and dryer. Wait at the entrance.

src: turn around down stairs turn room with washer dryer wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Turn left and enter the room with the washer and dryer. Wait there.

src: stairs turn wait in front of glass door
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Wait in front of the glass door.

src: exit bathroom turn fireplace turn next stairs coat room
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. When you reach the fireplace, turn left. Wait next to the stairs and coat room.

src: exit room left toward fireplace then left next room
tgt: Exit room, make a left, Heading toward fireplace, then make a left, wait next to "Coat Room".

src: exit room turn black bench on left turn past stairs on left wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and pass the black bench on the left. Turn left and walk past the stairs on the left. Wait there.

src: walk out into laundry room into room on other side forward on rug next white round table
tgt: walk out into the laundry room and into the sitting room on the other side. walk forward and stop on the rug next to the white round table.

src: walk out of bathroom walk through laundry room right across from open door living room area next white chair by small circular table on carpet in living room
tgt: Walk straight out of the bathroom.  Walk through the laundry room.  Make a right across from the open door to enter the living room area.  Stop next to the white chair by the small circular table on the carpet in the living room.

src: exit bathroom walk straight area on right wait in front of oval white coffee table
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk straight to the living area on your right. Wait in front of the oval white coffee table.

src: walk past bed wait on balcony
tgt: Walk past the bed. Wait on the balcony.

src: walk outside on balcony
tgt: Walk outside and wait on the balcony.

src: walk towards glass doors outside wait by potted plants
tgt: Walk straight towards the sliding glass doors, and go outside.  Wait by the potted plants.

src: turn down stairs at bottom turn down steps theater room stop
tgt: Turn left and walk down the stairs. At the bottom, turn left and walk down the 2 steps to enter the theater room and stop.

src: steps turn steps into viewing room stop
tgt: Go down the steps, turn left and go down the two steps into the viewing room and stop.

src: downstairs in theater room
tgt: Go downstairs and stop in the theater room.

src: walk past long table towards glass doors wait by door
tgt: Walk past the long table towards the sliding glass doors. Wait by the door.

src: towards dining table then table right of dining table near glass door then
tgt: Go towards the dining table, and then go passed the dining table to the right of the dining table. Go near the glass door then stop.

src: in entryway of room right walk straight back door pool wait in front of door
tgt: When you are in the entryway of the sitting room make a right and walk straight back to the door going to the pool. Wait in front of the door.

src: stairs until middle steps before way
tgt: Go down the stairs until you get to the middle and wait 3 steps before going all the way down.

src: down stairs staircase on meets with staircase
tgt: Walk down the stairs and stop when the staircase you are on meets up with another staircase.

src: stairs not way on section ground triangle-shaped guardrail out of ground
tgt: Go down the stairs, but not all the way. Stop on the section where the ground is triangle-shaped and a guardrail is coming out of the ground.

src: away from computers towards exit room through door on left right until double doors in front of then in front of open door on right empty workroom
tgt: Walk away from the computers towards the exit.  Exit the room through the door on your left.  Turn right.  Walk until you reach two double doors in front of you, then turn left.  Stop in front of the open door on your right that leads to another empty workroom.

src: exit office then right exit sign turn there
tgt: Exit the office then turn right when you get to the exit sign turn left and wait there.

src: walk across office exit wood door on left once turn right forward towards wooden doors turn right before doors in hallway right outside first door right still hallway
tgt: Walk across the office and exit the wood door on the left. Once out turn right and walk forward towards the wooden doors. Turn left right before you reach the doors. Stop in the hallway right outside the first door to your right. You are still facing the hallway.

src: left hallway then bedroom doors
tgt: Go to the left.  Go down a hallway and then stop when you come to two bedroom doors.

src: walk forward down hallway with stairs on left straight in hallway past rooms at end of room right just past doorway in bedroom
tgt: Walk forward down the hallway with the stairs on your left. Keep going straight in the hallway past the two rooms. At the end of the room take a right and stop just past the doorway in the bedroom.

src: turn right until hallway with in bookcase down hallway until end of hallway open bedroom door on right side
tgt: TURN RIGHT UNTIL YOU FACE THE HALLWAY WITH A BUILT IN BOOKCASE, WALK DOWN THE HALLWAY UNTIL YOU REACH THE END OF THE HALLWAY AND THE OPEN BEDROOM DOOR ON THE RIGHT SIDE.

src: down corridor toward exit sign door on left just inside room
tgt: Walk down the corridor toward the exit sign. Enter the door on the left and stop just inside the room.

src: walk far end of hall turn at exit sign wait in room
tgt: Walk to the far end of the hall. Turn left at the exit sign and wait in the room.

src: walk end of hall into room on left stop
tgt: Walk to the end of the hall and into the room on the left and stop.

src: towards stairs way top doors right on
tgt: go up towards the stairs all the way to the top you will see two doors , one leads to the right and one leads straight on.

src: stairway banister on left steps almost carpet again right end of carpet while on left right towards stairway up stairway stop wait at top of stairway on landing
tgt: Keeping the stairway banister on your left, continue walking up the steps almost to the carpet. Turning again to your right, walk to the end of the carpet while keeping it on your left. Turn right towards the stairway. Walk up the stairway and stop and wait at the top of the stairway on the landing.

src: stairs mat stairs stairs
tgt: Go up three stairs. Go to the mat. Go up two stairs . Go up three stairs.

src: walk out door ahead once turn left wood door way through room enter last door on right right side of bathroom past sinks in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk out the door straight ahead. Once out turn left and enter the wood door. Walk all the way through the room and enter the last door on the right. Go to the right side of the bathroom past the sinks and stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: walk straight into bedroom on left into bathroom on right by sink
tgt: Walk straight and turn into the bedroom on the left. Turn into the bathroom on the right and stop by the sink.

src: exit room turn into room next door right into bathroom sinks into other bedroom wait near entrance
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and to into the room next door. Turn right into the bathroom. Pass the sinks and go into the other bedroom. Wait near the entrance.

src: straight hall with paintings straight door on right wait there
tgt: Go straight down the hall with the paintings. Continue straight to the door on the right and wait there.

src: straight then slightly straight then lounge chairs into door on right straight ahead wait at entrance
tgt: Go straight then slightly left to continue straight. Then pass the three lounge chairs and go into the door on the right straight ahead. Wait at the entrance.

src: turn right wait in doorway of women bathroom
tgt: Turn right and wait in the doorway of the women's bathroom.

src: exit office turn right end of hall right bathroom wait at painting
tgt: Exit the office, turn right, walk to the end of the hall, turn right, enter the bathroom, wait at the painting.

src: walk towards balcony right into hallway walk straight right then right into bathroom in front of chevron picture on wall
tgt: Walk towards the balcony and take a right into the hallway. Walk straight and take a right, then another right into the bathroom. Stop in front of the chevron picture on the wall.

src: walk towards right hallway towards painting right at feather hallway first right into bathroom bathroom
tgt: walk towards railing. Turn right and walk down hallway towards feather painting. turn right at feather painting and walk down hallway. make first right into bathroom. stop when you enter the bathroom.

src: turn left straight through door up stairs upstairs straight door outside just doorway then
tgt: Turn to the left.  Go straight, through the door, up the stairs.  When you get upstairs, go straight to the door.  This leads you to the outside.  Go just to the doorway and then stop.

src: through door stairs staircase right outdoor area wait there
tgt: Go through the door that leads to the stairs, go up the staircase, turn right to enter the outdoor area, and wait there.

src: walk toward room with brown wooded furniture room inside room turn up stairs outside house wait by entrance
tgt: Walk toward the room with brown wooded furniture. Enter the room. Inside the room turn left and walk up the stairs exiting outside the house and wait by the entrance.

src: walk kitchen left at first counter heading past stairs in doorway main entrance
tgt: Walk straight to leave the kitchen and take a left at the first counter, and another left heading past the stairs. Stop in the doorway to the main entrance.

src: in kitchen walk past double ovens turn towards back of counter walk past staircase door outside of house on welcome mat wait
tgt: You're in a kitchen.  Walk past the double ovens.  Turn left and walk towards the back of the counter.  Walk past the staircase.  Go to the door to the outside of the house.  Stop on the welcome mat and wait.

src: forward into kitchen until cabinets directly past oven turn through space between island counter turn toward open doorway once on welcome mat outside of doorway
tgt: Move forward into the kitchen until you reach the cabinets directly past the oven.  Turn left and move through the space between the kitchen island an the counter.  Turn left and move to toward the open doorway.  Stop once you are on the welcome mat outside of the doorway.

src: exit living room through doorway on left left through doorway step near doorway on right
tgt: Exit the living room through the doorway on the left, make a left and go through the doorway, step near the doorway on the right and stop.

src: library left straight into bedroom outside of closet
tgt: Leave the library and take a left. Go straight into the bedroom. Stop outside of the closet.

src: turn right out large door on left once out turn into bedroom ahead once in stop in front of wood door on right
tgt: Turn right and walk out the large door on the left. Once out, turn left and walk into the bedroom ahead. Once in stop in front of the wood door on your right.

src: stairs wait near double doors
tgt: Go down the stairs and wait near the double doors.

src: down stairs promptly right wait by doorway
tgt: Walk down the stairs, promptly turn right and wait by the doorway.

src: stairs stop at bottom of stairs in front of door
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs in front of the door.

src: exit room straight until room with couches.turn right room wait in hallway
tgt: Exit the room. Go straight until you get to a room with couches.Turn right to exit that room. Wait in the hallway.

src: turn doors straight ahead out of bathroom once theater room exit out first door on right
tgt: Turn around and exit 2 doors straight ahead to get out of the bathroom. Once you enter the theater room, exit out the first door on your right and stop.

src: walk out of bathroom into theater right in doorway
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and into the theater. Turn right and stop in the doorway.

src: walk between wall on left potted plants on right about meters then just after white iron fence on left slight right through open door slight right again then straight past wood glass bookshelf on right after end of bookshelf door on right just that walls cinderblock as down steps hallway turn through first open door on left through door about 05.-1 meter at narrow long room with blue fabric couch on left desk bookshelf on right
tgt: Walk straight between a wall on your left and two potted plants on your right. Continue about 5 meters and then just after you pass a white iron fence on the left, you will turn slight right through the open door. Turn slight right again and then walk straight, past the wood and glass bookshelf that will be on your right. After the end of the bookshelf you will see a door on your right, and just past that you will notice the walls become all cinderblock as you walk down four steps and enter a hallway. Turn left through the first open door on your left, and walk through the door about 05.-1 meter. Stop. You will be looking at a narrow but long room with a blue fabric couch on the left and a desk and bookshelf on the right.

src: head indoors across room down steps turn by table
tgt: Head indoors, walk across the room, walk down the steps, turn left and stop by the table.

src: pass floor plants exit through door downstairs enter room on left
tgt: pass floor plants and exit through door, go downstairs and enter room on left.

src: pass round table chairs turn bar with chairs/stools walk straight until hallway on right into hallway wait there
tgt: Pass the round table and chairs. Turn left when you get to the bar with chairs/stools. Walk straight until you get to a hallway on the right. Turn into that hallway and wait there.

src: exit area forward in center of door openings
tgt: Exit eating area, walk forward, stop in center of the three door openings.

src: walk through dining room past table into hall on other side walk around support columns past small bar counter through arched door in hallway next bar area
tgt: Walk through the dining room past the table and into the hall on the other side. Walk around the support columns past the small bar counter and through the arched door. Stop in the hallway next to the bar area.

src: exit immediately left corner inside bedroom right towards closet there
tgt: Exit and immediately turn to the left corner. Walk inside the bedroom and turn right towards the closet, and stop there.

src: room turn into bedroom right closet
tgt: Leave the room, turn left, walk into the bedroom, turn right, and enter the closet.

src: turn right room walk left next room walk in closet on left at clothes on shelves
tgt: Turn to your right and exit the room. Walk to your left and enter the next room. Walk in and enter the closet on your left. Stop when you are at the clothes hanging and on shelves.

src: bedroom stairs just outside doorway stairs on mat on tile at bottom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and go down the stairs just outside the doorway.  Go down all the stairs and stop on the mat on the tile at the bottom.

src: exit bedroom hard right down stairs wait on red rug
tgt: Exit the bedroom, and make a hard right. Walk down stairs, and wait on the red rug.

src: exit bedroom downstairs on rug at base of stairs
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go downstairs. Stop on the rug at the base of the stairs.

src: exit room right hall through double doors second room on right wait in doorway
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Continue down the hall and through the double doors. Go to the second room on the right and wait in the doorway.

src: walk out of office right hallway through double door stand in front of second door on right
tgt: Walk out of office and turn right. Walk down hallway through double door. Stand in front of second door on right.

src: office right down hallway through double doors inside doorway office with on door
tgt: Leave the office and take a right. Walk down the hallway through the double doors. Stop inside the doorway to office with the 02 on the door.

src: head stairway left on landing after stairs walkway with wooden railing landing path right before ball catcher end of walkway
tgt: Head up the stairway. Make a left on the landing after you have finished going up stairs. You'll see a walkway lined with a wooden railing. Continue down the landing path. End right before the ball catcher and the end of the walkway.

src: upstairs left walkway after banister
tgt: Go upstairs, and take a left. Go down the walkway. Stop after you pass the banister.

src: stairs turn then near entrance of room
tgt: Go up the stairs. Turn left and then wait near the entrance of that room.

src: upstairs through doorway at bottom of stairs
tgt: go upstairs, go through doorway, stop at bottom of stairs.

src: stairs into study at top of stairs left in study stair stop
tgt: Go up the stairs and into the study at the top of the stairs. Take a left in the study and go up one stair and stop.

src: stairs toward area then then towards stairs at stairs
tgt: Go up the stairs, walk toward dining area, then then turn left towards the stairs. Stop at the stairs.

src: walk into kitchen towards stove out of kitchen through at end of room stairs left into living room in front of ottoman in living room
tgt: Walk into the kitchen towards the stove and go out of the kitchen through he door at the end of the room. Go to the stairs and take a left into the living room. Stop in front of the ottoman in the living room.

src: turn behind across kitchen in front of stairs turn into first room wait there
tgt: Turn around behind and walk across the kitchen and stop in front of the stairs. Turn left into the first room and wait there.

src: past sink right at oven straight turn into doorway walk towards stairway straight turn at large doorway
tgt: Walked past sink, turn right at oven and walk straight. Turn left into doorway. Walk towards stairway, go straight, and turn left and wait at large doorway.

src: enter doorway walk towards brown recliner past recliner walk towards arcade machine turn in front of arcade machine doorway on right
tgt: Enter the doorway and walk towards the brown recliner. Continue past the recliner and walk towards the arcade machine. Turn left in front of the arcade machine and enter the doorway on the right.

src: exit bedroom walk past pool table stand near arcade game
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk past the pool table .  Stand near the arcade game.

src: bedroom veer left into bedroom left of arcade machine once bedroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom, and veer left. Go into the bedroom to the left of the arcade machine. Stop once you enter the bedroom.

src: walk into front door of house once inside turn living room
tgt: Walk into the front door of the house. Once inside turn left and enter the living room.

src: turn around house into main doors once in turn living room wait right there on wood floor
tgt: Turn around and walk to the house.  Go into the main doors.  Once in, turn left.  Enter the living room but wait right there on the wood floor.

src: turn around up paved entryway walk into front door of home walk through open door near stairwell into living room with couches against walls
tgt: Turn around and walk up the paved entryway. Walk into the front door of the home and walk through the open door near the stairwell into the living room with couches against the walls.

src: exit bedroom straight across hall across next room turn left through double doors wait there
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go straight across the hall. Keep walking across the next room and turn left. Go through the double doors and wait there.

src: walk through door past sculpture ithrough room with red rug through double doors picture with zebras
tgt: walk through the door past the sculpture and ithrough the room with a red rug, through the double doors and face a picture with the zebras.

src: walk past flowers bedroom forward through living room exit through double doors on left right wait near entrance hallway
tgt: Walk past the flowers and exit the bedroom. Continue forward through the living room and exit through the double doors on the left. Turn right and wait near the entrance to the hallway.

src: upstairs stairs table on left at fridge into doorway stop
tgt: Go upstairs, go passed the stairs and table on your left, go left at the fridge, go into the doorway and stop.

src: up stairs then straight into kitchen turn by refrigerator wait in next room by sink
tgt: Walk up the stairs, then continue straight into the kitchen. Turn left by the refrigerator and wait in the next room by the sink.

src: steps then straight until kitchen fridge turn into room wait near sink
tgt: Go up the steps then continue straight until you get to the kitchen. When you get to the fridge turn left and go into the room. Wait near the sink.

src: down hallway right head toward chair right in laundry room doorway
tgt: Walk down the hallway and turn right.  Head toward the chair.  Turn right and stop in the laundry room doorway.

src: turn around down hall room on right hall laundry room on right inside doorway
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hall to the room on the right, go down the hall to the laundry room on the right and stop inside the doorway.

src: hallway right then right again there in laundry room
tgt: Go down the hallway and turn right then turn right again and wait there in the laundry room.

src: after stove turn then toward stairs stairs until statue then steps there by rectangular window
tgt: After you pass the stove turn left and then head toward the stairs. Go up the stairs until you get to the statue and then go up five more steps and stop there by the rectangular window.

src: exit kitchen stairs turn at landing up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Exit kitchen to stairs, go up stairs. Turn left at landing and go up more stairs. Stop at top of stairs.

src: exit kitchen turn up stairs past statue wall hanging turn steps wait there
tgt: Exit the Kitchen and turn left. Walk up the stairs past the statue and wall hanging. Turn left and walk 4 more steps. Wait there.

src: walk past kitchen area into first room on left just inside utility room
tgt: Walk past the kitchen area and go into the first room on the left and stop just inside the utility room.

src: walk across kitchen out right side doors turn door far left kitchen once pipes dryer
tgt: Walk across the kitchen and out the right side to where all the doors are. Turn and enter the door to the far left, closest to the kitchen. Stop once you enter facing the pipes and dryer.

src: walk around table pass by kitchen then at first doorway near water heater
tgt: Walk around the table and pass by the kitchen, then turn left at the first doorway. Stop near the water heater.

src: turn around down stairs left walk into kitchen left walk into exercise room wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Take a left and walk into the kitchen. Take another left and walk into the exercise room and wait there.

src: walk downstairs rug through hallway left of double doors through kitchen wait in workout room on left
tgt: Walk downstairs to the rug and through the hallway to the left of the double doors. Go through the kitchen and wait in the workout room on the left.

src: left at mirror hallway towards left hallway towards exercise room in front of rowing machine
tgt: Make a left at the mirror, go down the hallway towards the left, keep going down hallway towards the exercise room. Stop in front of the rowing machine.

src: with single door inside behind on pathway forward then right step building through double doors.once inside ninety degrees right kitchen
tgt: With the single door leading inside behind you and staying on the pathway, walk forward, then right, climbing 1 step and enter the building through the double doors.Once inside, turn ninety degrees to the right and enter the kitchen.

src: walk through large glass doors on left into house right into kitchen doorway
tgt: Walk through the large glass doors on the left and go into the house. Turn right into the kitchen doorway.

src: exit garden area right into house right in kitchen
tgt: Exit the garden area. Turn right and continue into the house. Turn right and stop in the kitchen.

src: walk through door then right hallway right at exit sign down hallway through third door on right
tgt: walk through door and then turn right. walk down hallway. turn right at exit sign. walk down hallway and go through the third door on the right.

src: through doorway into hallway right down hallway next available place right hall little wooden door with small desks in room wait there
tgt: Go through the doorway, and into the hallway.  Turn right and walk down the hallway.  When you get to the next available place, turn right.  Go down the hall a little more and stop when you see a wooden door with 2 small desks in the room.  Wait there.

src: walk through open doors into hallway with glass partition walls right hall exit sign right at exit sign hall first room with small desks office chairs inside
tgt: Walk through the open doors into the hallway with glass partition walls. Turn right down the hall and towards the exit sign. Turn right at the exit sign and continue down the hall to the first room with small desks and office chairs inside.

src: walk downstairs turn through library in office
tgt: walk downstairs, turn left, walk through library, stop in office.

src: down stairs left at foot of stairs through doorway into room with desk in middle bookcases on walls walk past desk with desk on right through doorway in doorway photocopy machine
tgt: Walk down the stairs.  Make a left at the foot of the stairs.  Go through the doorway into the room with the desk in the middle and bookcases on the walls.  Walk past the desk, with the desk on your right, and through the doorway.  Stop in the doorway, facing the photocopy machine.

src: stairs left into office on left left into room in copier room doorway
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. Go into the office on the left and take a left into he copier room. Stop in the copier room doorway.

src: walk out of bathroom out of door on right walk towards window first flight of stairs on left wait on landing
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and go out of the door on the right walk straight towards the window. Go down the first flight of stairs on the left and wait on the landing.

src: exit bathroom right straight stairs on left at bottom of stairs near window
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Walk straight and head down the stairs on the left. Stop at the bottom of the stairs near the window.

src: turn until theater room about degrees then head straight until door on right through door turn straight until stairs on left first flight of stairs
tgt: Turn around until you are facing the theater room, about 180 degrees, then head straight until you reach a door on the right. Go through the door, turn left, and go straight until you see stairs on your left. Go down the first flight of stairs.

src: exit bedroom turn at double doors wait in bathroom at end of hall
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left at the double doors. Wait in the bathroom at the end of the hall.

src: travel bedstand left of bed exit out door left turn down hallway bathroom sink
tgt: Travel to the bedstand left of the bed, and exit out the door to the left. Turn left and down the hallway to the bathroom sink.

src: bedroom left hallway walk straight into bathroom at end of hall in front of sink
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a left. Take a left down the hallway and walk straight into the bathroom at the end of the hall. Stop in front of the sink.

src: turn around pictures of sunsets on wall hallway corner near small figurine walk through open door near stairwell
tgt: Turn around and walk passed the pictures of sunsets hanging on the wall down the hallway. Turn the corner near the small figurine and walk through the open door near the stairwell.

src: turn around down hallway until stairs then into door past stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hallway. Follow it until you see stairs, then walk into the door past the stairs.

src: with counter on right straight hall room on left right hall straight past stairs on right into entry way once entry way before table
tgt: With the counter on your right go straight down the hall and pass the room on your left take a right down the hall and go straight past the stairs on your right and walk into the entry way and stop once you enter the entry way before you reach the table.

src: exit room past stairway fireplace then through doorway wait by door
tgt: Exit the room, walk past the stairway and the fireplace, then turn left. Proceed through the doorway and wait by the door.

src: bathroom past staircase turn at fireplace outside bear step in first doorway near blue chair stop
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk straight out and past the staircase.  Turn left at the fireplace and start to walk outside, passing the bear.  Step in the first doorway near the blue stuffed chair and stop.

src: exit bedroom straight towards blue chair turn after around black bear step into near front doorway stop
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go straight towards the blue chair, turn left after and around the black bear, step into the near front doorway and stop.

src: with christmas tree on right walk out of living room into entryway out of large main door with large oval window in straight through entry way out of next door up walkway out onto brick part of driveway on first quarter of brick
tgt: With the Christmas tree on your right walk out of the living room and into the entryway and out of the large main door with a large oval window in it and go straight through the entry way and  out of the next door and up the walkway out onto the brick part of the driveway stopping on the first quarter of the brick.

src: move through doorway right through front door building forward until brick-laid path then
tgt: Move through the doorway to your right and continue moving through the front door, exiting the building. Keep moving forward until you hit the brick-laid path and then stop.

src: right towards brown door with oval glass through through door front entrance outside walk towards road wait on red bricks
tgt: Make a right towards the brown door with an oval glass and go through it. Go through another door that leads to the to the front entrance and go outside. Walk towards the road and wait on the red bricks.

src: exit bathroom towards into kitchen next black chairs
tgt: Exit bathroom to bedroom, turn left and walk towards desk.Turn left and walk into kitchen, Stop next to two black chairs.

src: away from toilet turn at bed again at desk through doorway past red cabinets past chairs on right left once on carpet
tgt: walk away from the toilet, turn left at the bed, and left again at the desk. Continue through the doorway, past the red cabinets, and past the two chairs on the right. Turn left and stop once you are on the carpet.

src: bed desk black light switches sink chairs wicker chair
tgt: Go to the bed. Go to the desk. Go to the black light switches. Go to the sink. Go to the two chairs. Go to the wicker chair.

src: bed through door towards laundry then right in front of desk
tgt: Go passed the bed and through the door towards the laundry. Then turn right and stop in front of the desk.

src: walk towards washer dryer area once inside right towards area stove refrigerator area
tgt: Walk towards the washer and dryer area. Once inside, turn right and walk towards the kitchen area. Stop facing the stove and refrigerator area.

src: walk past foot of bed towards washer dryer right through doorway slightly left of of desk before in kitchen
tgt: walk past the foot of the bed towards the washer and dryer, turn right and walk through the doorway walk slightly to the left of of the desk and stop before you are in the kitchen.

src: turn around towards exercise bike walk door frame
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the exercise bike. Walk to the door frame.

src: exit bathroom walk straight across hall straight staircase exercise bicycle on right doorway ahead of bedroom by lamp next bed
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk straight across the hall.  Continue to walk straight.  You will pass a staircase and an exercise bicycle on your right.  Walk thought the doorway straight ahead of you.  You will enter a bedroom.  Stop by the lamp next to the bed.

src: turn bathroom hallway into next doorway in bedroom door
tgt: Turn around to exit the bathroom. Cross the hallway, and go into the next doorway. Stop in the bedroom door.

src: stairs turn at bottom of stairs into bedroom stop by door
tgt: go down stairs, turn left at the bottom of the stairs, walk into the bedroom and stop by the door.

src: downstairs turn bedroom
tgt: go downstairs and turn left, enter bedroom.

src: stairs first left bedroom just inside room
tgt: Go down the stairs, take the first left and enter the bedroom, stopping just inside the room.

tgt: Turn left and go past the light blue chairs. Turn left and go up the stairs. Wait at the top.

tgt: Turn around and walk past the chairs. Turn left and go up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: area left stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Leave the sitting area, and go to the left. Go up the stairs, and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: fireplace on right staircase on left then forward past double doors on right then archway on right near end of room
tgt: Put the fireplace on your right and the staircase on your left, then walk forward. Continue past the double doors on your right, and then enter the archway on your right near the end of that room.

src: turn hall past tables right wait in front of water fountain
tgt: Turn around and move down the hall past the tables. Turn right and wait in front of the water fountain.

src: walk past stairs on left past buffet table on right right opposite round table on left wait at water fountain
tgt: Walk past stairs on the left. Walk past buffet table on the right. Make a right opposite the round table on the left. Wait at the water fountain.

tgt: Enter the building, turn right and enter the kitchen, stopping at the breakfast bar.

tgt: Go into the living room and and walk to the kitchen on the right. Stop next to the counter once you enter the kitchen.

src: walk into building walk right past chairs walk behind couch just inside kitchen area
tgt: Walk into the building and walk right past the chairs. Walk behind the couch and stop just inside the kitchen area.

src: stairs on left then into second room on left wait there in laundry room
tgt: Go up the stairs on your left and then go into the second room on your left. Wait there in the laundry room.

src: walk way up top of stairs head at second room laundry room enter inside laundry room there
tgt: Walk all the way up to the top of the stairs. Head straight, and turn left at the second room that is a laundry room. Enter inside the laundry room, and stop there.

tgt: Go up all of the stairs, and then go towards a framed picture of a ship, but turn left when you see a laundry room.

src: walk past door turn behind chairs by glass table black chairs
tgt: Walk past the door and turn left. Walk behind the chairs and stop by the glass table and black chairs.

src: inside able past foot separate flights of fives steps on left then near round table with chairs around
tgt: Go inside and turn left when you're able to. Walk past the foot two separate flights of fives steps on your left. Then wait near a round table with eight chairs around it.

src: inside toward kitchen area next round glass table
tgt: Go inside and turn left toward the kitchen area. Stop next to the round glass dining table.

src: walk through doorway right hallway once exit sign
tgt: Walk through the doorway, and take a right down the hallway. Stop once you reached the exit sign.

src: exit room hard right hallway beside red chairs
tgt: Exit the room and do a hard right. Continue down the hallway and stop beside the red chairs.

src: exit room right into hall under exit sign close near red chair
tgt: Exit the room and turn right into the hall. Stop under the exit sign, close to the near red chair.

tgt: Turn and walk down the hallway past the staircase. Continue down the hall around the corner near the potted plant. Walk up to the next open door on the wall with a bathroom inside.

src: walk straight ahead right stairs past potted plant into first doorway on left wait
tgt: Walk straight ahead, veering to the right to avoid the stairs.  Go past the potted plant and into the first doorway on the left.  Stop there and wait.

src: walk forward right towards stairs right stairs n't down stairs past staircases forwards towards room with double doors horizontal openings turn while still in hallway n't through double doors just past double doors large potted plant slightly right towards small paneled door visible right of potted plant just outside room small half bath with vessel sink
tgt: Walk forward staying to the right and moving towards the stairs. Turn right when you reach the stairs (don't go up or down the stairs). Go past the staircases and forwards towards the room with the double doors that have the horizontal openings. Turn left while you are still in this hallway (Don't go through the double doors). You will be just past the double doors and facing a large potted plant. You should go slightly right towards the small two paneled door that is visible to the right of the potted plant. Stop when you are just outside this room, which is a small half bath with a vessel sink.

src: hallway first right turn hallway into first door on right wait in doorway
tgt: Go down the hallway and make your first right turn. Go down that hallway and turn into the first door on your right. Wait in the doorway.

src: turn right in hallway right into first office there
tgt: Turn right in the hallway. Turn right into the first office #360 and wait there.

src: straight then right straight again then at first door on right
tgt: Go straight and then right. Go straight again and then stop at first door on the right.

src: turn house once inside forward past large column walk past large stairs then on small set of wood steps hallway
tgt: Turn left and enter the house. Once inside walk forward and turn left past the large column. Walk past the large stairs and then turn left and stop on the small set of wood steps leading to a hallway.

src: turn down stairs then house past stairs on left hallway hallway wait near stairs
tgt: Turn left and walk down the stairs, then enter the house. Walk past the stairs on the left and turn down the hallway.  Enter the hallway and wait near the stairs.

src: stairs house forward first set of stairs left first of small stairs before office
tgt: Go down the stairs, and enter the house. Go forward and go down the first set of stairs. Take a left and go up the first of the small three stairs before you enter the office.

src: face open door right into dining area next turn past wooden lattice structure wait by thermostat on wall
tgt: Face the open door. Turn right and walk into the dining area. Next, turn left and walk past the wooden lattice structure. Wait by the thermostat on the wall.

src: turn right then past wall with holes wait there
tgt: Turn right then turn left and go past the wall with the holes and wait there.

src: exit little hall into main room stand at end of room divider
tgt: Exit the little hall into the main room and stand at the end of the room divider.

tgt: Turn toward the exit past the ropes.  Walk out of the exit doors down the red carpet.  Stop facing the stairs.

tgt: Walk past round mirror. Make hard left at rectangular mirror. Walk past fire extinguisher. Wait at top of marble stairs.

tgt: Leave the massage room and take a right. Go into the first door on the right with a tanning bed. Stop and the foot of the tanning bed.

src: exit beginning room open area right right room right in front of table
tgt: Exit the beginning room and enter the open area.  Turn right and enter the farthest right room.  Stop right in front of the table.

src: turn left between massage tables out of door straight just little way right big bathtub-like thing right there
tgt: Turn to the left, walk between the massage tables.  Go out of the door, and straight just a little way and turn right.  You'll see a big bathtub-like thing.  You'll stop right there.

tgt: Exit the house Turn right. Walk straight then turn right. Go past the fountain and wait near the first bush in the pot on the left.

tgt: Walk onto the balcony, turn right, walk past the fountain, and wait near the stone cross statue.

src: left hall past christmas tree turn into garden room setee then
tgt: Go to the left and head down the hall past the Christmas tree.  Turn left and go into the Garden room.  You'll go till you get to the setee.  Then you need to wait.

src: walk out of glass door walk through hall past hanging tapestry walk along hall over floor rug corner walk into bedroom
tgt: Walk out of the glass door nearest to you. . Walk through the hall past the hanging tapestry. Walk along the hall over the floor rug. Turn the corner and walk into the bedroom.

src: through door right then out double door right right before stairs between pillars
tgt: Go through the door and turn right and then walk out the double door to your right. Wait right before the stairs between the two pillars.

tgt: Walk through the doorway, turn right into the foyer. Walk through the foyer to the door. Walk out of the door and onto the porch.

src: through doorway right head through double doors on porch
tgt: Go through the doorway and turn right.  Head through the double doors and stop on the porch.

src: in front of couch walk outside door in front of after outside right inside house now left inside bedroom ahead wait
tgt: When you are standing in front of the couch walk to the outside door in front of you. After you go outside make a right and go inside house. Now make a left and go inside the bedroom straight ahead, and wait.

tgt: Turn around and to towards the couch that is outside, go around it, take the first hallway to the left to the doorway, enter the bedroom with the picture of gold lips, and stop.

tgt: Exit the house to the patio using the large glass sliding doors straight ahead. Turn right and go into the house using the large glass sliding doors.  Turn left and go straight into the hallway then the room straight ahead. Wait near the TV.

tgt: Exit the bedroom, go straight up the stairs and continue straight through to the kitchen area and stop.

Go up the stairs and walk straight until you reach the opening of the kitchen counters.  Stop in the middle opening next to the counter on your right and left in line with the two bar stools.

src: right through door up stairs straight by high chairs on right next counter
tgt: take a right go through the door and up the stairs. go straight and stop by the high chairs on the right, next to the counter.

tgt: Leave the bathroom go through the bedroom door turn right and stand on the second step.

tgt: Walk towards the narrow doorway, directly to the right of the wall painting and wait near the first door that you see on your left.

tgt: Walk past the couches and the television. Stop just inside the hallway.

tgt: Walk through the living room and enter the hallway. Wait near the glass door.

tgt: Head down hallway, make a left, enter bedroom and wait.

tgt: Walk straight, turn left and go into the room. Wait at the entrance.

src: stairs then in middle
tgt: Go down the stairs and then wait in the middle.

tgt: Go past the bed to the door on the left. Go through the door and to the first recliner.

tgt: Go down the stairs, and take a left. Take a left and enter the kitchen. Stop in front of the fireplace.

tgt: Walk to the left of the desk past the plywood storage bin. Walk past the desk and chairs. Walk down the Stairs to the right. Walk around the easel and stop.

tgt: Go towards the desks and make an immediate left, go straight passed the desks on the right, go through the doorway on the right, down the stairs, and then make a right and wait near the entrance to the toilet.

src: up circular stairs wait on third step from top landing
tgt: Walk up the circular stairs. Wait on the third step from the top landing.

src: spiral staircase at third step from top
tgt: Go up the spiral staircase. Stop at the third step from the top.

src: stairs on third step from top
tgt: Go up the stairs. Stop on the third step from the top.

tgt: Walk right up the stairs and turn right. Stop to the right of the top of the stairs.

tgt: Walk out the door and turn left. Wal down the hall and turn left. Walk down the hall and go through the door on your left.

tgt: Go down the stairs the turn slightly right and to into the room straight ahead. Wait near the wardrobe.

tgt: Walk down the stairs and to the right. Walk into the room and stop in front of the white panel doors.

tgt: exit lobby to the left, turn hard left and enter first door continue straight to bathroom, turn slight left and stop in front of bathroom stalls.

tgt: With the desk to your right, walk straight a few steps and then turn left and go through the door to the left of the circle shaped lights.  Enter the locker room area and walk straight through until you get to an area with toilet stalls on the left.  Stop in front of the first toilet stall.

tgt: Exit the room, pass the hallway and at turn left. Wait at the top of the stairs.

tgt: Walk straight down hallway, turn left at stairs, stop at top of stairs.

tgt: Walk through the office area out through the sliding barn door. Turn and walk into the kids bedroom next to the bathroom.

tgt: Walk through the doorway to the left of the kitchen. Go down the hallway and turn left. Enter the door there.

tgt: Turn left and go past the doorway.  Turn left and into a kid's bedroom.  Stop at the foot of the bed and wait.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk past the television. Exit the bedroom, turn left, then right and go toward the front door. Wait next to the grey rug.

tgt: Turn to your left and go passed the guitar. Go into the hall and turn left. Continue through the archway and turn right. Stop near the table.

tgt: While facing toilet turn left and exit bathroom. Continue straight and exit bedroom to the hallway. Turn left and then make a hard right. Walk toward the front door and stop near the rug.

tgt: With the opening for the double wood and glass doors immediately behind you, go forward and enter the second room on your left. Go into the room and stop in front of the display of the sword.

tgt: Walk through the hallway and walk left past the glass sculpture. Stop just inside the doorway.

tgt: Walk down hall into living room stopping at two chairs with lilacs.

tgt: Walk up the stairs and go straight down the hall. Enter the bedroom through the first door on the right. Stop before you reach the rug.

tgt: Go upstairs. Turn right and go through the double doors to the room with the exercise machine and bed.

tgt: walk up stairs, turn slight right and walk down hallway, walk passed laundry room, turn right into bedroom with elliptical machine. Stop at elliptical machine.

src: enter adjoining room stand on blue dot
tgt: Enter the adjoining room and stand on the blue dot.

tgt: Walk through the boiler room passed the large iron machine with pipes feeding out. Pass the water cooler and go through the open doorway. Walk through the next room towards the stairwell passing by the cardboard boxes stacked in the room. Walk up the first few steps of the stairwell.

tgt: Turn slight left and walk through the two doorways. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

tgt: Leave the boiler room passing the water cooler. Walking into the main room and take a left, go up the stairs and stop on the fourth stair.

tgt: walk off the balcony into the bedroom. Go through the bedroom and out into the hall and take a left. Go down the hall, and take the first left into the bedroom stopping in the doorway.

tgt: Walk into the bedroom from the balcony and exit out the door to your right. Make an immediate left down the hallway and wait in the doorway to the first room on your left.

tgt: Exit the patio, exit the bedroom, turn left, walk down the hall, wait at the first door on the left.

tgt: Go up steps, turn left, walk down stairs to end of hall, enter bedroom, wait by chair.

src: stairs in front of right stairs around corner straight chair stop
tgt: Go up the three stairs in front of you. turn right and Go down the stairs around the corner. Go straight to the chair and stop.

src: up steps at top turn right then steps right way until bedroom then
tgt: Walk up the steps, at the top turn right. Then walk down the steps to the right and keep going all the way until you enter the bedroom and then stop.

src: upstairs in entrance kitchen
tgt: Go upstairs and stop in the entrance to the kitchen.

src: turn around up stairs top at top turn right next set of stairs on right top room
tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs to the top. At the top turn right and go up the next set of stairs on your right. Stop when you reach the top and enter the room.

src: up stairs right towards set of stairs up steps at top of steps
tgt: Walk up the stairs, and turn right towards another set of stairs. Walk up the steps, and stop at the top of the steps.

src: walk around bed with bed on right drawer on around bed closets left open door stationary bycicle
tgt: walk around the bed, with bed being on your right and the drawer on you left. keep walking around the bed passing the closets to your left and go to the open door, and stop when you see the stationary bycicle.

src: walk around bed exit bedroom through door next lamp turn slightly wait by stationary bike
tgt: Walk around the bed and exit the bedroom through the door next to the lamp. Turn left slightly and wait by the stationary bike.

src: walk around bed through door on right wait near exercise bike
tgt: Walk around the bed and through the door on the right. Wait near the exercise bike.

src: toward couches then right steps up second set of stairs midway up stairs
tgt: Go toward the two couches and then turn right going up the steps.  Continue up to the second set of stairs and stop midway up those stairs.

src: forward into living room right small flight of stairs head up stairs ahead foyer on fourth stair from bottom
tgt: Walk forward into the living room. Take a right and go up the small flight of stairs. Head up the stairs ahead which lead to the foyer. Stop on the fourth stair from the bottom.

src: down stairs straight at stairs on right turn up stairs straight up stairs stop
tgt: walk down the stairs, straight, stop at the stairs on your right, turn and walk up the stairs, continue straight, walk up three more stairs and stop.

src: up stairs wait at top
tgt: Walk up the stairs.  Wait at the top.

src: up stairs top at very top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs to the top, stop at the very top of the stairs.

src: up staircase nearest at top in front of door
tgt: Walk up the staircase that is nearest and stop at the top, in front of the door.

src: office right past stairs veer right next statue of creature on bike
tgt: Leave the office and take a right. Go past the stairs, and veer right. Stop next to the statue of the creature on the bike.

src: bathroom walk glass table right past stairs bookshelves right in front of statue of animal on bicycle
tgt: leave the bathroom and walk to the glass dining table.  Turn right and walk past the stairs to the bookshelves.  Go right and stop in front of the statue of an animal on a bicycle.

src: walk into dining area right past clear table chairs walk past bottom of staircase stop near opening statue on bicycle
tgt: Walk into the dining area and go right past the clear table and chairs. Walk past the bottom of the staircase and stop near the opening that leads to the statue on a bicycle.

src: walk past tub right out of door right of pool table right in doorway
tgt: Walk past the tub and turn right. Walk out of the door and to the right of the pool table. Turn right and stop in the doorway.

src: exit bathroom tub room door on right slightly right pool table chair on right into door on right wait at entrance of bathroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom, pass the tub exit the room using the door on your right. Turn slightly right and pass the pool table. Pass a chair on your right and go into that door on your right. Wait at the entrance of the bathroom.

src: from bathroom bathroom by around left side of bathtub right at end of bathtub right end of pool table small bathroom in right corner of room opposite stairs
tgt: From the bathroom, exit the bathroom by walking around the left side of the bathtub and turn right at the end of the bathtub. Continue walking to the right end of the pool table and enter the small bathroom in the right corner of the room opposite the stairs leading down.

src: walk out of bedroom into hallway corner down stairwell ahead stairs floor of home walk towards glass doors out patio area
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom into the hallway. Turn the corner and walk down the stairwell ahead. Continue down the stairs to the lower floor of the home. Walk towards the glass doors leading out to the patio area.

src: bedroom stairs on left in o'clock position at bottom of stairs turn into kitchen area just after into kitchen area
tgt: Leave the bedroom and go down the stairs on the left in your 11 o'clock position.  At the bottom of the stairs, turn left into the kitchen area.  Stop just after stepping into the kitchen area.

src: exit bedroom descend stairs wait at stair landing
tgt: Exit bedroom and descend stairs, wait at stair landing.

src: down bottom of stairs forward into hallway painted pictures of crabs down hall along banister banister towards staircase
tgt: Walk down to the bottom of the stairs. Walk forward into the hallway passing the painted pictures of crabs. Walk down the hall along the banister railing. Turn around the banister and continue towards the staircase.

src: stairs walk past crab art right hallway past painting of ship wait at top of stair landing
tgt: Walk down stairs. Walk past crab art. Make right down hallway. Walk past painting of ship. Wait at top of stair landing.

src: stairs down hallway at end of turn right towards stairs next corner of railing
tgt: Go down the stairs and down the hallway. At the end of the railing turn right towards the stairs. Stop next to the corner of the railing.

src: bathroom around room into dining room left stairs on second stair from bottom
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go around the room into the dining room. Take a left and go up the stairs and stop on the second stair from the bottom.

src: walk through hallway into bedroom with large glass wall outside walk through bedroom along glass wall past bed walk through open entry on other side of room through room sofa area walk towards stairwell behind couches
tgt: WALK THROUGH THE HALLWAY INTO THE BEDROOM WITH A LARGE GLASS WALL TO THE OUTSIDE. WALK THROUGH THE BEDROOM ALONG THE GLASS WALL PAST THE BED. WALK THROUGH THE OPEN ENTRY ON THE OTHER SIDE OF THE ROOM. CONTINUE THROUGH THE ROOM PASSED THE SOFA AREA AND WALK TOWARDS THE STAIRWELL BEHIND THE COUCHES.

src: exit work area in right through bedroom exit out door past red recliner on right left before sink up second step of stairs
tgt: Exit the work area you are in and walk to the right.  Walk through the bedroom and exit out the door.  Continue walking past the red recliner on your right.  Turn left before reaching the sink and walk up to the second step of the stairs.

src: turn through hallway into first room through living room kitchen in front bedroom in hallway
tgt: Turn around and go left through the hallway and left  into the first room, keeping going left through the living room and kitchen and stop in the front the bedroom in the hallway.

src: exit room turn then into room next door right straight sink on left with birds into room ahead wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and then turn left into the room next door. Turn right go straight and pass the sink on the left with the birds. Go into the room straight ahead. Wait at the entrance.

tgt: Turn around and enter the hallway behind you. Once in turn left and walk forward. Turn left at the end to enter the double wood doors. Walk across the room to the right side and enter the door beside the sink. Stop once you enter the bedroom and the plant and mirror are to you right.

src: at top of stairs right turn walk hallway beside other stairs next walk end of hall into doorway of bedroom wait
tgt: When you are standing at the top of the stairs make a right turn and walk to the hallway beside the other stairs. Next walk to the end of the hall into the doorway of the bedroom and wait.

tgt: Go straight toward the two round tables. When you get to the first round table make a right u turn and to into the room your left. Go straight into the room and wait near the bed.

src: look in direction of stairs across rightmost on opposite side of stairs through opening by left of stairs continue through passage way until large room bed ahead of left
tgt: Look in the direction of the stairs and across to the rightmost arched opening on the opposite side of the stairs. Go through that opening by walking to the left of the stairs. Continue straight through that passage way until you enter a large room. There will be a bed ahead of you and to your left.

src: walk small stairs turn at very first white column at second stairs
tgt: Walk straight passing the two small stairs. Turn left at the very first white column. Stop at the second stairs.

src: forward with stairs behind straight second left on second from bottom stair
tgt: Walk forward with the stairs behind you. Walk straight and take the second left. Stop on the second from the bottom stair.

src: turn left forward past dresser entrance on left across from piano walk bottom step of stairs
tgt: Turn to your left and walk forward past the the dresser to the entrance on your left which is across from the piano.  Walk to the bottom step of the stairs.

src: walk through display room left into brown double doorway stop
tgt: Walk through the display room, make a left into the brown double doorway and stop.

src: walk forward past dining table on right living room through last door on left in doorway
tgt: Walk forward past the dining table on your right. Enter the living room through the last door on the left. Stop in the doorway.

src: travel past long dining table until tub door on left wait near entrance
tgt: Travel past the long dining table until you reach the tub, enter the door on the left and wait near the entrance.

tgt: Exit the closet and enter the hallway. Walk past the Marilyn Monroe picture and enter the first door on the left. Enter the room and stop in front of the bed.

tgt: Leave the room and walk towards the stairs. walk past the stairs and down the hall to the first door on your left. Enter the bedroom and stand at the balcony door.

tgt: Turn left, move forward through door, move forward down hallway, turn left at first doorway, move forward through doorway, move forward to balcony.

tgt: Walk out of the bedroom. Walk across the hall into the kitchen. Turn right and stop by the sink.

tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bedroom. Take a right and wait in the kitchen.

tgt: Turn around and walk past the foot of the bed.  Go out the doors and continue straight.  Then turn right when you get to an indoor/outdoor kitchen.  Then stand by the stove and wait.

tgt: Walk down the stairs and enter the bedroom room and wait by the chair.

src: hallway stairs towards grey sofa chair just after bedroom
tgt: Go down the hallway following the stairs going down.  Keep going towards the grey sofa chair and stop just after entering the bedroom.

src: walk then at front of arm chair
tgt: walk straight then stop at the front of the arm chair.

tgt: Go right through the archway, go straight passed the stairs on the left and into the archway on the left, make a left, make a right passed the table and go inside the doorway and stop.

tgt: Walk past the couch and television into the hallway. Walk into the room across on the left and turn left. Walk past the table and chairs and turn right. Walk into the room to the right of the stick decoration and stop.

tgt: Walk through the doorway on the right of the TV. In the foyer go through the door on the left. Enter the kitchen and take a right into the bathroom. Stop once you pass the door.

tgt: Go right until you hit a wall then go left and take a hard right into the bedroom then go into the bathroom.

src: turn through left straight through bed stop in doorway
tgt: Turn around and go through the left and go straight through passed the bed and stop in the doorway.

tgt: Turn left. Turn right and go into the room. Go straight until you go into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

Enter the doorway with the words to the left wall of it of "#downtown".  Stop inside the room when you reach the first pipe going up the wall to your right.

tgt: Walk past table, turn right, and exit room. Turn left and go through doorway. Stop in front of chairs.

tgt: Facing the big mirror on the wall go left, go towards the stairs, go passed the stairs on the left and go straight until you reach the left of the beige couch and an end-table and then stop.

tgt: Walk down the hall past the fireplace. Walk past the staircase towards the sofa. Stop between the sofa and the vase.

tgt: Exit the room. Walk straight across the open room with the blue and white design in the floor into the open hall on the opposite side. Stop in the entrance to the room with three white lounging chairs, next to the table with cups on it.

tgt: Leave the massage room and go straight. Go into the room at end of the hall and stop in the entryway.

tgt: Go down the two steps, pass the bathtubs. Go down two more steps, turn left, and wait there.

tgt: Go down stairs asking man blocking path to move. Wait for man to move. Proceed to bottom of stairs and turn left. Take immediate left down small hallway past painting. Go down small flight of stairs stopping at the bottom.

tgt: Exit room through the doorway near the fireplace. Keep right and walk through the hallway, turn right, enter the bedroom and wait near the bed.

tgt: Turn to the left and walk past the white chair. Turn right and walk past the double doors into the doorway. Walk in the hallway past the wooden cabinets. Enter the bedroom to your left and stop.

tgt: Walk through the doorway to the left of the fireplace, Walk right down the hallway, and walk into the first room on your left. Stop before you reach the small carpet.

tgt: Walk through the hall and into the bedroom with purple pillows on the bed. Walk through the bedroom and out of the door on the open other side of the room. Walk down the hall past the metallic wall. Turn to walk up the first few stairs of the stairwell.

tgt: Walk towards the windows and then turn right. Go around the bed and walk through the door past the main entrance. Keep walking until you see a steps to your left. Take two steps and wait on the stairs.

tgt: Walk towards the large window and turn left.  Walk across the room and past the elevator.  Walk to the stairs.  Stop on the second stair.

tgt: Exit the bathroom into the workout room then exit the workout room and head straight until you get to a mirror in the hallway with two lamps on each side. Wait near there.

tgt: Walk through the gym area and out the open door. Continue down the hall, turn, and stop in the open double doorway on the left.

tgt: Walk around the pool on the side closest to the building.  Turn right when you see an open glass door going inside and stop just before stepping into the doorway.  There will be an urn with some plants in it on your right.

tgt: Go along the pool to the right of the pool and stop at the doorway to the inside.

tgt: Walk straight between the house and swimming pool.  Continue until you reach the glass doors leading inside.  Wait here.

tgt: Turn around and turn right. Wait next to the counter with the bamboo plant.

tgt: Walk out of the closet and turn right. Walk across the hall and stop just inside the hallway.

tgt: Walk through the room passed the wooden piano. Walk up the small steps and through the tiled room past the reception desk and out through the front door.

tgt: Go out the room on you right. Pass the table and chairs. Turn right and go out the room. Wait there.

tgt: Turn left and exit the room.  Walk through the dining room and stand at the edge of the kitchen.

tgt: Turn around and walk out the men's locker room and enter the lobby. Wait near the door.

src: down hallway past water cooler lockers in doorway past lockers into lobby
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the water cooler and lockers. Stop in the doorway past the lockers that enters into the lobby,.

src: walk way forward mirrors on right open door straight ahead of there
tgt: Walk all the way forward passing both the mirrors on the right. Enter the open door that is straight ahead of you, and stop there.

src: pantry/closet room right in hallway next hall down stairs into bedroom wait at landing
tgt: You need to leave the pantry/closet room and make a right in the hallway. Next, you should go down the hall and down the stairs into the bedroom, wait at the landing.

src: exit room right stairs wait there by bed
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Go down the stairs and wait there by the bed.

src: closet in hallway right stairs on bottom step
tgt: Leave the closet. In the hallway take a right. Go down the stairs and stop on the bottom step.

tgt: With the door at your back walk to your right. Walk through the kitchen and stop in front of the bedroom door on the right.

tgt: Walk forward and turn left. Walk forward again and stop at the painting.

src: living room right
tgt: Facing the living room to the right.

src: exit room into kitchen turn left then right wait near bar stool
tgt: Exit the room into the kitchen and turn left. Then turn right and wait near the bar stool.

src: walk into kitchen left right next first bar stool
tgt: Walk into the kitchen, and go left. Take a right, and stop next to the first bar stool.

src: turn exercise room turn right stove wait near chairs at counter
tgt: Turn around and exit the exercise room and turn left. Turn right when you get to the stove and wait near the 2 chairs at the counter.

src: walk inside around bed right stairs up down stairs down on second step from top
tgt: Walk inside and around the bed to the right.  When you see stairs going up and down, take the stairs going down and stop on the second step from the top.

src: walk into house down stairs wait there
tgt: Walk into the house and walk down two stairs. Wait there.

src: enter building through folding glass doors head right towards stairs steps then
tgt: Enter the building through the folding glass doors and head to the right towards the stairs. Go down two steps and then stop.

src: exit bathroom bedroom right hallway master bathroom wait near shower
tgt: Exit the bathroom and enter the bedroom.  Turn right and proceed down the hallway and enter the master bathroom.  Wait near the shower.

src: as bathroom right through door right again into large bathroom in front of shower on left
tgt: As you exit the bathroom, turn right and go through the door, turn right again and continue into the large bathroom. Stop in front of the shower on your left.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and take an immediate right into the bedroom. Upon entering the room, take an immediate right and follow the short hallway into the bathroom.

tgt: Exit the room. Go forward toward the plant right of the staircase. Turn right after passing the double doors. Turn into the first door on the left leading to a restroom. Stop there.

tgt: Exit the pantry and head right, past the stairs. Continue following the hall to the right, past the outside entry and table. Turn right, before the tree, and wait in the bathroom entry on the left.

tgt: Exit the pantry, walk past the stairs and stop in the bathroom doorway.

tgt: Go upstairs and stop in the hallway, near the thermostat.

Curve slightly to your right and stop next to the next thermostat. The thermostat should be toward your left slightly above the light switches.

tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs all the way to the top. At the top, turn right and then when you reach the wall turn left and then stop.

tgt: turn hard right and walk toward the double glass doors.

src: walk past glass table on right lattice wall wait at opening in lattice wall
tgt: Walk past the glass table on your right, walk to the lattice wall, wait at the opening in the lattice wall.

tgt: turn around and go towards the door down the hall and the windows stop as soon as you hit the wine holders.

tgt: Walk across the patio toward the building and into the doorway on the left and stop.

src: walk far end of deck in doorway garage
tgt: Walk to the far end of the deck and stop in the doorway to the garage.

tgt: Go straight and into the house using the door on the slight left. Wait there.

tgt: Go past the table with the chairs. Pass the bar with the stools and the couches then go into the room on the slight left and wait by the large table with the chairs and the chandelier.

tgt: Walk past the dining table and take a right behind the couch. Leave the living room and go into the hall. Enter the formal dining room across from the living room. Stop nest to the end table.

tgt: Go between the sink and the wooden table on the right. Stop at the couch. Turn left and travel to the archway ahead. Enter the archway and continue going forward to the dining room with the large table and chairs.

src: between couches tv room
tgt: Go between the couches and TV, entering the nearest room.

tgt: Turn left and then walk straight ahead through the living room. Stop and wait, once you exit the living room.

tgt: Go down the hallway and past a large gold-framed mirror and through the entryway into a large room with a kitchen and seats and outside through the large back exit.

tgt: Leave the barroom and take a left, and another left. Walk straight down the hall and take a right into the bedroom. Stop once you pass the door in the bedroom.

tgt: Walk out of the brown door. Take a left at the open hallway. Take another left and walk down the hall until your reach a picture on the wall. Make a right through the brown door.

src: walk around table way up stairs wait
tgt: Walk around table. Walk half way up stairs and wait.

src: walk towards stairs on fourth from bottom stair
tgt: Walk towards the stairs and go up them. Stop on the fourth from the bottom stair.

src: right of wooden table turn stairs on fourth stair
tgt: Go to the right of the wooden table. Turn left and go up the stairs. Stop on the fourth stair.
