src: turn around down stairs down stairs just up ahead there
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Walk down two more stairs just up ahead and wait there.

src: downstairs through door stop near top of stairs
tgt: Go downstairs, through the door and stop near the top of the stairs.

src: downstairs then straight at top of stairs
tgt: Go downstairs, then go straight and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs walk around table chairs at bottom stand in front of doorway in wall on right before through doorway
tgt: Go down the stairs and walk around the table and chairs at the bottom and stand in front of the doorway in the wall on your right.  Stop before going through the doorway.

src: descend stairs wait at table
tgt: Descend stairs, Wait at dinning table.

src: stairs on left straight wait near couches
tgt: Go down the stairs on the left. Walk straight and wait near the couches.

src: walk through doorway away from couch right at next doorway right again down hallway room with blue ottoman stop
tgt: walk through the doorway away from the couch, turn right at the next doorway and right again down the hallway. Enter the room with the blue ottoman and stop.

src: exit room hard right into adjacent hallway down hallway room before rug big blue ottoman
tgt: exit sitting room to hall, turn hard right into adjacent hallway, continue straight down hallway to perfume room. stop before rug and big blue ottoman.

src: turn through entryway right through entryway right again through doorway wait in bedroom
tgt: Turn left, walk through the entryway, turn right, walk through the entryway, turn right again, walk through the doorway and wait in the bedroom.

src: straight right
tgt: GO STRAIGHT AND TURN RIGHT.

src: steps right up small set of stairs hall right at first doorway on right into doorway stop
tgt: Go up the three steps and to the right and up the small set of stairs, go down the hall and make a right at the first doorway on the right, go into the doorway and stop.

src: head up op short set of steps right hallway then right into bathroom
tgt: Head up and go op the short set of steps to the right. Continue down that hallway, then turn right into the bathroom.

src: with bathroom on left forward hallway stairs left into office first door on left just past doorway in office
tgt: With the bathroom on your left go forward down the hallway and go down the stairs and take a left into the office which is your first door on your left and stop just past the doorway in the office.

src: down hallway past bathroom painting on wall walk into office left near table with armchairs
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the bathroom and painting on the wall. Walk into the office to the left and stop near the table with two armchairs.

src: hallway wait in office at bottom of steps on left
tgt: Go down the hallway and wait in the office at the bottom of the steps on the left.

src: walk into room ahead around sofa on left past piano dining table through doorway into kitchen wait just inside entry way
tgt: Walk into the room ahead and walk around the sofa on the left. Continue past the piano and the dining table, through the doorway and into the kitchen. Wait just inside the entry way.

src: turn around past piano kitchen on right wait near counter top
tgt: Turn around and walk past the piano and enter the kitchen on your right.  Wait near the counter top.

src: turn right forward through hallway enter far door on left enter kitchen
tgt: Turn right. Go forward through hallway. Enter far door on left. Enter kitchen.

src: turn bathroom closet wait near bench
tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom and enter the closet. Wait near the bench.

src: past tub then straight into hallway right straight into closet wait there
tgt: Go past the tub and then go straight into the hallway. Turn right and go straight into the closet. Wait there.

src: turn right bathroom hallway right stop outside of doorframe
tgt: Turn right and exit the bathroom. Follow the hallway, turn right and stop outside of the doorframe.

src: bathroom closet in bedroom next first arm chair
tgt: Leave the bathroom and closet. Stop in the bedroom next to the first arm chair.

src: exit bathroom through door nearest bathtub into first bedroom on left next chair by fireplace
tgt: Exit the bathroom through the door nearest the bathtub. Turn into the first bedroom on the left and stop next to the nearest chair by the fireplace.

src: with bathtub left bathroom into next room on left
tgt: With the bathtub to your left, exit the bathroom, and turn left into the next room on your left.

src: walk through doorway directly opposite of window right after doorway walk towards stair case around stair case on door on left stop
tgt: Walk through the doorway, directly opposite of the window. Turn right after the doorway and walk towards the stair case, walk around the stair case on the farthest door on your left and stop.

src: through door right walk towards stairs turn at stairs left by bench then right at bench wait by doorway
tgt: Go through the door and make a right and walk towards the stairs. Turn left at the stairs and make another left by the bench then make a right at the bench and wait by the doorway.

src: walk through door into hallway into open room walk around banister rail into room walk towards round table then across room towards first set of chars near against wall along wall banister on other side of stairwell stop near arched doorway
tgt: Walk through the door and into the hallway. Continue out into the open room and walk around the banister rail into the room. Walk towards the nearest round table and then continue across the room towards the first set of two chars near against the wall. Continue along the wall to the banister on the other side of the stairwell and stop near the arched doorway.

src: head indoors turn into office stop by desk chair
tgt: Head indoors, turn left, walk into the office and stop by the desk chair.

src: walk through doorway that towards room table left through doorway into office stop at desk with black chair
tgt: Walk through doorway that leads towards dining room table, take a left, walk through doorway that leads into office, stop at the desk with a black chair.

src: walk straight through doorway left past stairs into office wait in office
tgt: Walk straight and through the doorway and take a left. Walk past the stairs and into the office. Wait in the office.

src: from bathroom walk across bedroom room at base of stairs
tgt: From bathroom walk across bedroom to dining room to stairs. Stop at base of stairs.

src: exit bathroom walk around front of bed bedroom through door on right walking past couch table wait on first few steps of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk around the front of the bed. Exit the bedroom through the door on the right and continue walking, past the couch and table. Wait on the first few steps of the stairs.

src: straight tub bed door on right then straight table chairs then straight toward stairs steps stop
tgt: Go straight and pass the tub and the bed. Go out the door on your right and then go straight. Pass the table and chairs then go straight toward the stairs. Go up four steps and stop.

src: walk out of kitchen right right out onto deck left deck stop of top stair of deck
tgt: Walk out of the kitchen and take a right and another right out onto the deck. Take a left and head down the deck. Stop of the top stair of the deck.

src: turn right through doorway right left at bottom of first set of stairs
tgt: Turn  right and go through the doorway to your right. Take a left and stop at the bottom of the first set of stairs.

src: sharp turn right outside walk past chairs down steps stop
tgt: Make a sharp turn right and walk outside. Walk left past the chairs. Walk down the steps and stop.

src: white door at end of hallway
tgt: Go to the white door at the end of the hallway.

src: turn degrees around down hallway until end of hallway unfinished room
tgt: Turn 180 degrees around. Walk down the hallway until you get to the end of the hallway. You should see an unfinished room.

src: down hallway closed door straight ahead wait at door
tgt: Walk down the hallway to the closed door straight ahead, wait at the door.

src: walk furniture on porch right paces turn into house walk across living room
tgt: walk passed furniture on porch, turn right and walk 2 paces, turn left into house walk across living room to hallway and stop.

src: indoors straight television right around picture outside door bathroom
tgt: Go indoors, go straight passed the television, go right around the picture, stop outside the door to the bathroom.

src: turn right outdoor seating walk towards house slightly right into house t.v while hallway into hallway towards open bathroom door
tgt: TURN RIGHT TO FACE THE OUTDOOR SEATING AND WALK TOWARDS THE HOUSE, TURN SLIGHTLY RIGHT AND WALK INTO THE HOUSE, WALK TO THE T.V. WHILE FACING THE HALLWAY, WALK INTO THE HALLWAY TOWARDS THE OPEN BATHROOM DOOR.

src: turn right into room walk between table couch walk on right small room with long blue drapes wait there
tgt: Turn to the right and walk into the room.  Walk between the table and the couch.  Walk on to the right and enter a small room with long blue drapes. Wait there.

src: exit empty room walk slightly
tgt: Exit the empty room and walk slightly left.

src: turn right walk through open doorway up round wooden table walk towards far right corner of room walk through narrow hallway into next room
tgt: Turn to the right and walk through the open doorway.  Walk up to the round, wooden table. Walk towards the far right corner of the room. Walk through the narrow hallway and into the next room.

src: walk forward dining table recreation room through first door on left on rug once doors
tgt: Walk forward to the dining table. Enter the recreation room through the first door on the left. Stop on the rug once you pass the doors.

src: walk past columns on right past long wood pew on left through open french door right of lamp on end table wait at pool table
tgt: Walk past the columns on the right. Walk past the long wood pew on the left. Walk through the open french door to the right of the lamp on the end table. Wait at the pool table.

src: then through wooden door at end of hallway once pool table
tgt: Go left and then proceed through the wooden door at the end of the hallway. Stop once you reach the pool table.

src: turn right steps right door wait outside
tgt: Turn right and go up the steps. Turn right and go out the door and wait outside.

src: exit stairwell steps wait outside
tgt: Exit the stairwell, go up the steps and wait outside.

src: stairs right in living room stairs right house once house
tgt: Go down the stairs, and to the right. In the living room go up the two stairs, and take a right. Exit the house. Stop once you exit the house.

src: turn past couch right stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn around and go past the couch. Turn right and go up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: room through doorway right of big windows stairs at top near white end table
tgt: Leave the room through the doorway to the right of the big windows.  Go up the stairs and stop at the top near the white end table.

src: walk between couch painting on wall upstairs at top of stairs near table
tgt: Walk straight between the couch and the painting on the wall. Go upstairs.  Stop at the top of the stairs near the table.

src: right hall exit through door on left outside straight on tile once hot tub
tgt: Take a right, and go down the hall. Exit through the door on the left and go outside. Go straight, and stop on the tile once you reach the hot tub.

src: walk out of bathroom right straight until large double glass doors on left outside wait near jacuzzi
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom. Turn right and go straight until you get to large double glass doors on the left. Go outside and wait near the jacuzzi.

src: walk into hallway right left outside walk towards pool straight until in front of circular hot tub
tgt: Walk into the hallway and turn right.  Turn left and go outside and walk towards the pool.  Walk straight until you are standing in front of the circular hot tub.

src: walk around left of air hockey table other end of in corner of room
tgt: Walk around the left of the air hockey table to the other end of it, and stop in the corner of the room.

src: by air hockey table stop by netting
tgt: Go by the air hockey table and stop by the netting.

src: walk between hammock game table in front of window
tgt: Walk between the hammock and the game table. Stop in front of the window.

src: study towards stairway stairs turn stairs straight across
tgt: Leave study towards stairway. Go up stairs, turn left and continue up stairs, walk straight across to bedroom.

src: walk out of study towards staircase up stairs turn at first landing stairs at top of staircase through open double doors right after through double doors
tgt: walk out of the study, towards the staircase. walk up the stairs. turn left at the first landing and continue up the stairs. At the top of the staircase, walk through the open double doors to the right. Stop after passing through the double doors.

src: walk out of library up stairs left staircase top slight right walk doorway there bedroom wait there
tgt: Walk out of the library and up the stairs. Go to the left staircase and go to the top.  Make a slight right and walk to the doorway there to the bedroom and wait there.

src: up stairs wait in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Walk up the stairs and wait in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: stairs walk past glass door wait at threshold of bathroom
tgt: Walk up stairs. Walk past glass door. Wait at threshold of bathroom.

src: up stairs left into bathroom at top of stairs at bathroom door
tgt: Walk up the stairs to your left and straight into the bathroom at the top of the stairs. Stop at the bathroom door.

src: exit bathroom forward room turn forward room wait in room with basketball painting
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk forward. Exit the room and turn left. Walk forward and turn left and enter the room. Wait in the room with the basketball painting.

src: bathroom office in hall left past stairs bedroom through first door on left at foot of bed
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and office. In the hall take a left. Go past the stairs and enter a bedroom through the first door on your left. Stop at the foot of the bed.

src: straight into room right into hallway hallway left into first bedroom on left
tgt: Go straight into the sitting room and right out into the hallway. Take a left down the hallway and go left into the first bedroom on the left.

src: upstairs left wait near rug
tgt: Go upstairs and to the left. Wait near the rug.

src: stairs then at top of stairs forward until table wait
tgt: Go up the stairs and then turn left at the top of the stairs. Walk forward until you get to the table and wait.

src: up stairs turn straight wait near dining table
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn left. Walk straight and wait near the dining table.

src: aisle of church through nave towards altar between second row of pews front wait there
tgt: Go down the aisle of the church through the Nave towards the altar.  Stop between the second row of pews to the front. Wait there.

src: walk front of church aisle row of second pews from front
tgt: Walk to the front of the church aisle and stop when you get to the row of the second pews from the front.

src: down aisle toward front wait at second row of pews
tgt: Walk down the aisle toward the front.  Wait at the second row of pews.

src: with shower on left out of bathroom through door on left right in bedroom right out of bedroom into hallway straight left into door into bedroom onto patio stopping in doorway patio
tgt: With the shower on your left go out of the bathroom through the door on the left and take a right in the bedroom and a right out of the bedroom into the hallway and go straight taking a left and going into the door into the bedroom and a left out onto the patio stopping in the doorway to the patio.

src: walk through door on wall next bathroom sink walk into hallway corner past painting on wall hall past red abstract painting walk into bedroom door near painting walk through bedroom out onto deck area on other side of rooom
tgt: Walk through the door on the wall next to the bathroom sink. Walk into the hallway and turn the corner past the painting on the wall. Continue down the hall past the red abstract painting and walk into the bedroom door near the painting. Walk through the bedroom and out onto the deck area on the other side of the rooom.

src: exit bathroom into bedroom right doorway into hallway by large red white picture into bedroom on right past white chair on left out door onto patio
tgt: exit bathroom into bedroom.  go right to bedroom doorway.  step out into hallway by the large red and white picture.  go into the bedroom on the right.  go past the white chair on the left and out the sliding door onto patio.

src: turn around through next room then doorway on left next fireplace
tgt: Turn around and walk through the next room.  Then enter the doorway on your left. Stand next to the fireplace.

src: head towards door with fire extinguisher beside through seating area through double doors on left in front of fireplace wait there
tgt: Head towards the door with the fire extinguisher beside it.  Pass through the seating area and go through the double doors on your left. Stop in front of the fireplace and wait there.

src: turn around through small hallway once in next room walk other side door on far left before double doors on right
tgt: Turn around and walk through the small hallway. Once in the next room, walk to the other side and enter the door on the far left. Stop before you reach the double doors on your right.

src: laundry room right kitchen in front of refrigerator
tgt: Leave the laundry room and turn right to enter the kitchen.  Stop in front of the refrigerator.

src: laundry room right until kitchen then
tgt: Leave the laundry room and turn right.  Walk until you enter the kitchen and then stop.

src: laundry room right walk into kitchen
tgt: Leave the laundry room, turn right, and walk into the kitchen.

src: exit bathroom room walk across room on stair
tgt: exit bathroom to sitting room. Walk across room to stairs and stop on 3rd stair.

src: out of bathroom right toward stairs stairs first landing stop
tgt: Go out of the bathroom and turn right heading toward the stairs.  Go up the stairs to the first landing and stop.

src: turn around out of bathroom door into seating area immediately right walk between red blue chairs towards stairs up stairs steps first landing stained glass window
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom door and into the seating area. Immediately turn right and walk between the red and blue chairs and towards the stairs. Walk up the stairs 3 steps and to the first landing and stop. You will be facing a stained glass window.

src: exit room stop in bedroom doorway near exit
tgt: Exit the room and stop in the bedroom doorway, near the exit.

src: exit bathroom room turn room door on left right into room next door on right wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the bathroom to the room. Turn left and exit the room using the door on the left. Turn right and go into the room next door on the right. Wait at the entrance.

src: exit bathroom bedroom right down hall last right into bedroom in doorway bedroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom and bedroom. Go right, and down the hall. Take the last right into the bedroom. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: exit bathroom right at end of hallway turn then right into bedroom wait by entryway
tgt: Exit the bathroom, turn right, at the end of the hallway turn left. Then turn right into the bedroom and wait by the entryway.

src: exit bathroom right hallway left at first doorway left into room right into doorway stop
tgt: Exit the bathroom, make a right and go down the hallway and make a left at the first doorway to the left, go into the room and make a right into the doorway and stop.

src: walk out of bathroom right left into bathroom right into bedroom just inside door
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right. Turn left and walk into the bathroom and turn right into the bedroom and stop just inside the door.

src: stairs right walking in front of recliners straight through doorway bedroom right past foot of bed in front of bathtub
tgt: continue down the stairs and turn right walking in front of two recliners, continue straight through the doorway to a bedroom and turn right to walk past the foot of the bed. Stop in front of the bathtub.

src: stairs right way across room past fireplace doorway wait next bathtub
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn right. Walk all the way across the room past the fireplace. Enter the doorway and wait next to the bathtub.

src: down stairs past fireplace walk through open door left of floor lamp right at dresser wait at tub
tgt: Walk down the stairs, and past the fireplace. Walk through the open door to the left of the floor lamp. Make a right at the dresser, and wait at the tub.

src: left through doorway then into bedroom past bed then pool outside just right at doorway
tgt: Go to the left and through the doorway.  Then go into the bedroom, and past the bed.  Then turn left You'll see a pool outside.  Just wait right at the doorway.

src: enter door left into bedroom toward bed turn at bed walk edge of pool wait
tgt: Enter the door to your left. Turn left into the bedroom. Walk toward the bed. Turn left at the bed. Walk to the edge of the pool and wait.

src: head inside building turn once inside opening on left through opening once outside
tgt: Head inside the building, turn left once inside, go to the opening on the left, go through the opening, stop once outside.

src: stairway with handrail until bathroom through bathroom into bedroom
tgt: go up the stairway with the handrail until you get to the bathroom.  Go through the bathroom and into the bedroom.

src: first steps turn on landing stairs right on landing walk through bathroom in doorway of bedroom
tgt: go up the first 5 steps and turn left on the landing, continue up the stairs, make a right on the 2nd landing, walk straight through the bathroom, stop in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: stairs hard left at stair up stairs hard right window past tub on right wait at threshold of open bedroom door
tgt: Walk up stairs. Make hard left at stair landing. Walk up stairs. Make hard right window. Walk past tub on right. Wait at threshold of open bedroom door.

src: exit bathroom turn left stairs left into room stop near table
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left, go down the stairs, take a left into the room and stop near the table,.

src: turn down hallway hallway into first double wood doors on left once office desk
tgt: Turn left and walk down the hallway.  Continue down the hallway and turn into the first double wood doors on your left. Stop once you enter the office and reach the desk.

src: turn forward stairs turn room wait in front of table
tgt: Turn left and go forward down the stairs. Turn left and enter the room. Wait in front of the table.

src: straight hallway into room at end turn into bathroom stop
tgt: Go straight down the hallway and into the room at the end. Turn left into the bathroom and stop.

src: from top of stairs straight ahead until inside bathroom
tgt: From the top of the stairs go straight ahead until getting inside the bathroom.

src: walk through hallway into room ahead once inside slight left bathroom wait here
tgt: Walk straight through the hallway and into the room straight ahead.  Once inside, make a slight left to enter the bathroom.  Wait here.

src: walk into laundry area turn past kitchen wait outside
tgt: Walk into the laundry area, turn left, walk past the kitchen, and wait outside.

src: exit bathroom turn through kitchen out door wait near chair on patio
tgt: Exit the bathroom, turn left and walk through the kitchen out the door, wait near the chair on the patio.

src: bathroom turn through kitchen in doorway porch mats
tgt: Leave the bathroom and turn left.  Walk through the kitchen and stop in the doorway going to the porch.  It is where the two mats meet.

src: walk into room at end of hall right through doorway just inside door
tgt: Walk into the room at the end of the hall and turn right. Walk through the doorway and stop just inside the door.

src: turn straight into large room walk in front of bed door on wall left of bed walk through door as soon as next room
tgt: Turn and walk straight into the large room.  Walk in front of the bed and go to the door that is on the wall, to the left of the bed.  Walk through that door and stop as soon as you enter the next room.

src: walk into room with red curtains past bed in through next doorway wait there
tgt: Walk into the room with red curtains.  Continue past the bed, and in through the next doorway.  Wait there.

src: light switch bed ottoman mirror
tgt: Go to the light switch. Go to the bed. Go to the ottoman. Go to the mirror.

src: with stairs towards back turn right through doorway once through doorway turn bedroom across bedroom then bathroom door left
tgt: With the stairs towards your back, turn right and go through the doorway. Once through the doorway, turn left and enter the bedroom. Continue across the bedroom, then enter the bathroom whose door you'll see to the left.

src: turn left through door then bed left door enter
tgt: Turn to your left and go through the door, then go passed the bed and go to the left door and enter.

src: exit room out glass door right once out turn head towards door right outside through door
tgt: Exit the room out the glass door to your right. Once out, turn left and head towards the door leading out. Stop right outside when you exit through the door.

src: exit bedroom entry turn left through glass door next red art piece
tgt: Exit bedroom to entry and turn left. Go through glass door and stop next to red art piece.

src: exit room door on left then head straight until large room then that glass door wait by red statue
tgt: Exit the room using the door on your left then head straight until you get to a large room then turn left and head out that glass door. Wait by the red statue.

src: turn hallway at second door on left
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallway. Stop at the second door on the left.

src: turn hallway third door on left
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallway. Stop when you reach the third door on your left.

src: down hall at door on left
tgt: Walk down hall, stop at 2nd door on the left.

src: up first flight of stairs at top
tgt: Walk up the first flight of stairs, and stop at the top.

src: walk past long table towards stairs set of stairs wait by window
tgt: Walk straight past the long table towards the stairs.  Go up one set of stairs.  Wait by window.

src: head forward up stairs on landing
tgt: Head forward and up the stairs. Stop on the landing.

src: walk out of bathroom right out of bedroom up steps at top of stairs
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right. Walk out of the bedroom and up the steps. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: head out of bathroom right up stairs on first landing wait in balcony area near stairs
tgt: Head out of the bathroom and to the right, up the stairs, stop on the first landing. Wait in the balcony area near the stairs.

src: exit bathtub bathroom bedroom right stairs after bedroom wait there at top
tgt: Exit the bathtub and leave the bathroom. Enter the bedroom and turn right. Go up four stairs after leaving the bedroom and wait there at the top.

src: kitchen area left of patio walk through kitchen few steps after frosted glass door just area
tgt: Go to the kitchen area to the left of the patio.  Walk straight through the kitchen and stop a few steps after passing the frosted glass door.  You will have just entered the dining area.

src: turn past bar with stools/chairs on right wait near glass table with chairs on right
tgt: Turn left and go past the bar with the stools/chairs on the right. Wait near the glass table with the chairs on the right.

src: left past balcony kitchen walk through into dining area outside of door bathroom
tgt: Take a left past the balcony, and enter the kitchen. Walk through, and into the dining area. Stop outside of the door to the bathroom.

src: exit empty room left next exit sign
tgt: Exit the empty room and take a left. Wait next to the exit sign.

src: head in hall down corridor on left wait by fire extinguisher
tgt: Head in to the hall and down the corridor on the left. Wait by the fire extinguisher.

src: exit office then al way down hallway until exit sign stop
tgt: Exit the office then turn left and go al the way down the hallway until you get to the exit sign and stop.

src: stairs doorway right
tgt: Descend up the stairs and enter the doorway to your right.

src: walk base of stairs up top of stairs in doorway right in front of
tgt: Walk to the base of the stairs and go up to the top of the stairs.  Stop in the doorway that is right in front of you.

src: upstairs in bedroom doorway across hall
tgt: Go upstairs and stop in the bedroom doorway across the hall.

src: exit kitchen through doorway by black shelves right past dining table table on left as next painting of sailboats
tgt: Exit the kitchen through the doorway by the black shelves.  Make a right and walk past the dining table.  The table will be on the left as you pass.  Stop next to the painting of sailboats.

src: turn dining room than turn right patio area next chair
tgt: Turn around and enter the dining room. Than turn right and enter the patio area.  Wait next to the chair.

src: walk out of kitchen right past table chairs turn behind white chair
tgt: Walk out of the kitchen and turn right. Walk past the table and chairs and turn left. Stop behind the white chair.

src: walk forward slightly walk near fountains next lounge chairs wait near pool steps
tgt: Walk forward and slightly left. Walk near the fountains, next to the lounge chairs. Wait near the pool steps.

src: walk towards pool right alongside left of lounging chairs wait after last round
tgt: Walk towards pool and continue to the right alongside it. Stay to the left of the lounging chairs and wait after you pass the last one, which is larger and round.

src: walk straight along pool wait next small waterfall
tgt: Walk straight along side the pool and wait next to the small waterfall.

src: walk into living room stairs on left
tgt: Walk into the living room and go down the stairs on the left.

src: walk end of hall downstairs wait at base of stairs
tgt: Walk to the end of the hall, go downstairs and wait at the base of the stairs.

src: walk forward past large painting turn down staircase wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk forward past the large painting and turn left. Walk down the staircase and wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk inside hallway walk into room at end with globe in after room walk into bathroom in front of sink mirror
tgt: Walk inside and go left down the hallway.  Walk into the room at the end with the globe in it and turn left after entering the room.  Walk into the bathroom and stop in front of the sink and mirror.

src: head indoors turn through hallway turn bathroom wait there
tgt: Head indoors, turn left, go through the hallway, turn left, enter the bathroom and wait there.

src: inside turn hallway straight into room turn into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Go inside. Turn left and go down the hallway. Go straight into the room. turn left and go into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: walk out of bedroom turn down of hall turn into bedroom walk bathroom wait there
tgt: Walk out of bedroom and turn left. Walk down to end of hall. Turn left into bedroom. Walk to bathroom and wait there.

src: exit bedroom left into next bedroom on left in entrance bathroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go to your left. Go into the next bedroom on your left. Stand in the entrance to the bathroom.

src: turn approximately degrees then toward wooden support pillar in front of slight left into open wooden door frame slightly into bathroom after right wait in front of open shower curtain
tgt: Turn around approximately 90 degrees, then move toward the wooden support pillar in front of you. Hang a slight left and move into the open wooden door frame. Turn slightly left and move into the bathroom. After you've entered, turn right and wait in front of the open shower curtain, facing it.

src: walk through doorway with draped curtains next wardrobe with mirror on
tgt: Walk through the doorway with draped curtains. Go stand next to the wardrobe with a mirror on it.

src: turn around towards bed turn exit out dark curtains walk at white door on left wood cabinet with mirrors
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the bed. Turn left and exit out where the dark curtains are. Walk and stop at the white door on your left and face the wood cabinet with mirrors.

src: turn left after stool left after chair wait in front of mirror on other side of open door
tgt: Turn around and take a left after the stool. Take another left after the chair. Wait in front of the mirror on the other side of the open door.

src: around couch up wooden stairs turn stairs before first flight ends
tgt: Go around the couch and up the wooden stairs. Turn left and head up the stairs.  Stop before the first flight ends.

src: face black couches up wood stairs behind left through doorway up stairs on right
tgt: face the two black couches and walk up the three wood stairs behind them. Turn left and walk through the doorway and up 6 stairs on your right.

src: walk behind couch steps at top of steps hall right at steps at first landing
tgt: Walk behind couch to stairs, go up steps. At top of steps turn left and go down hall. Turn right at steps and go up them. Stop at first landing.

src: walk past sink on right into living room straight ahead in living room left through door into hallway straight in hall straight with buffet on left

tgt: Go down the hallway to the left, and take a right into the doorway on the right and stop.

tgt: Walk towards the wide open door that looks into the bedroom.  Looking at the bed, walk forward and turn right when you are on the brown and grey carpet.  Follow that carpet forward until you reach the tall tapestry on the wall in a frame.  Turn to the left and walk through the open brown wooden door.  Take two steps through the door and stop.

tgt: Exit the room, turn right and walk through the glass doorway, continue down the corridor pass the partition and turn left. Proceed to the end of the hallway, then wait by the wall art on the right.
