src: up stairs right stairs at top take left stairs stop
tgt: Walk up the stairs, take a right and go up the stairs. At the top take a left and go up three stairs and stop.

src: walk into open area of building with office on perimeter walk towards red lounge chair area corner right near red chair lounge area hall with glass partition walls at first intersecting hallway
tgt: Walk into the open area of the building with office on the perimeter. Walk towards the red lounge chair area. Turn the corner to the right near the red chair lounge area. Continue down the hall with glass partition walls and stop at the first intersecting hallway.

src: exit office turn towards red sofas right hallway wait near first doorway on left
tgt: Exit the office and turn left. Walk towards the red sofas and turn right. Continue down the hallway and wait near the first doorway on the left.

src: turn right at exit sign hall door on left stop
tgt: Turn left and and turn right at the exit sign. Follow the hall to the door on the left and stop.

src: exit through bedroom door walk straight until hallway turn down stairs wait here
tgt: Exit through the bedroom door.  Walk straight until you reach a hallway.  Turn left, and walk down the stairs.  Wait here.

src: exit bedroom turn stairs wait there
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Turn left and go down the stairs. Wait there.

src: walk past bathroom into hall turn stairs wait at bottom of stairs near circles on wall
tgt: Walk past the bathroom, go into the hall and turn left to go down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs near the circles on the wall.

src: turn until stove top in front of towards stove top doorway left
tgt: Turn left until you see the stove top in front of you. Walk towards the stove top and exit the doorway you your left.

src: walk through kitchen toward stove patio left of stove wait at table
tgt: Walk through the kitchen toward the stove, enter the patio to the left of the stove, wait at the table.

src: walk past refrigerator doorway on left outside through door stand in front of next doorway on balcony
tgt: Walk past the refrigerator to the doorway on the left. Go outside through the door stand in front of the next doorway on the balcony.

src: hard right hard right past fireplace on left past round table on right past fireplace on left wait at wall mirror right of french doors with green glass
tgt: Make a hard right. Make a hard right. Walk past the fireplace on the left. Walk past the round table on the right. Walk past the fireplace on the left. Wait at the wall mirror to the right of the french doors with green glass.

src: straight past fireplaces on left wait near chairs on left
tgt: Go straight past the two fireplaces on the left. Wait near the three chairs on the left.

src: turn degrees room with fireplace forward past fireplace red carpet past stanchions in front of double doors
tgt: Turn 180 degrees to face the room with the fireplace. Walk forward past the fireplace. Continue down the red carpet past the stanchions. Stop in front of the double doors.

src: up stairs next floor at top of stairs left forward into bedroom in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk up the stairs to the next floor. At the top of the stairs take a left and walk forward into the bedroom. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: turn stairs first left once bedroom
tgt: Turn around, go up the stairs. Take the first left and stop once you entered the bedroom.

src: stairs hard at top of stair landing wait at threshold of bedroom door
tgt: Walk up stairs. Make hard left at top of stair landing. Wait at threshold of bedroom door.

src: walk through doorway turn up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk through the doorway. Turn left and walk up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk out of elevator left stairs flights of stairs wait at top
tgt: Walk out of the elevator and make a left to go up the stairs. Go up both flights of stairs and wait at the top.

src: exit elevator by through doorway left then again stairs stair past landing wait at top of staircase
tgt: Exit the elevator by moving through the doorway. Go left, then left again to head up the stairs. Continue up the stair past the landing and wait at the top of the staircase.

src: last few stairs right next flights of stairs wait
tgt: Go up the last few stairs and turn right. Go up the next two flights of stairs and wait.

src: up rest of stairs then next set of stairs at top of stairs near potted plant
tgt: Walk up the rest of the stairs, then continue up the next set of stairs.  Stop at the top of the stairs near the potted plant.

src: stairs then right other stairs on right then right other stairs on right at top of stairs
tgt: Go up the stairs then turn right and go up the other stairs on the right then turn right and go up the other stairs on the right and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: pass table chairs right left large green vase turn wait in hallway
tgt: Pass the table and chairs and turn right. Turn left and pass the large green vase. Turn left and wait in the hallway.

src: past dining room table right door turn head for large glass bottle turn then in hallway right before stone walls
tgt: Go past the dining room table and turn right entering the door. Turn left and head for the large glass bottle. Turn left and then wait in the hallway right before the stone walls.

src: conference room left left before stone wall
tgt: Leave the conference room and take a left. Take another left. Stop before you reach the stone wall.

src: exit shower then bathroom toward bedroom stand near bed
tgt: Exit the shower and then turn left and exit the bathroom toward the bedroom. Stand near the bed.

src: walk towards bathtub turn straight until bedroom then once room
tgt: Walk towards the bathtub and turn left.  Walk straight until you get to the bedroom and then stop once you have entered the room.

src: exit area corner of tub turn forward till under doorway of bedroom stop wait here
tgt: Exit the shower area. When you get to the corner of the tub turn left. Continue moving forward till you're under the doorway of the bedroom. Stop and wait here.

src: walk table area then right turn flights of stairs living room area before golden sculpture end table
tgt: Walk left to exit the table area and then take a right turn to descend down two flights of stairs.  Enter the living room area and stop before reaching the golden sculpture end table.

src: walk past table first left then first right straight past chairs at light switch
tgt: Walk straight past the table and take your first left and then take your first right. Walk straight past the two chairs and stop at the light switch.

src: walk out of dining room head left.stay right down stairs into living room next end table next couch
tgt: Walk out of the dining room and head to the left.Stay right and walk down the stairs into the living room. Stop next to the end table next to the couch.

src: walk forward through front door wait in front of second door
tgt: Walk forward and go through the front door. Wait in front of the second door.

src: away from brick driveway straight towards door walk through front door closet on left in front of door with oval window
tgt: walk away from the brick driveway, straight towards the door. Walk through the front door, there will be a closet on your left and stop in front of the door with an oval window.

src: head toward front door inside wait by door with oval glass in middle
tgt: Head toward the front door and go inside. Wait by the door with the oval glass in the middle.

src: walk towards piano turn though doorway steps right through doorway wait
tgt: Walk towards the piano and turn left though the doorway. Go up the steps. Turn right, go through the doorway, and wait.

src: pass by piano turn left stairs right
tgt: Pass by the piano and turn left. Go up the stairs and continue to the right and stop.

src: exit alcove turn past piano small steps wait in entrance room on right
tgt: Exit the alcove, and turn left past the piano. Go up the small steps and wait in the entrance to the room on the right.

src: enter bedroom balcony through door by bed wait right outside
tgt: Enter the bedroom, enter the balcony through the door by the bed, wait right outside.

src: exit bathroom walk through bedroom room towards glass doors bed wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Walk through the bedroom room towards the closest glass doors to the bed. Wait there.

src: walk past bed left outside doors outside just step then wait
tgt: Walk past the bed and go to the left to the outside doors.  Go outside just a step and then wait.

src: exit bedroom then right into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Exit the bedroom, then turn right into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: walk towards open door bedroom exit room down hallway until open bathroom door on right right twp steps into bathroom there in front of first sink in bathroom
tgt: Walk towards the open door to the bedroom and exit the room.  Walk down the hallway until you reach the open bathroom door on your right.  Turn right and take twp steps into the bathroom.  Stop there, you should be in front of the first sink in the bathroom.

src: forward right through open doorway down hall right into restroom
tgt: Go forward and make a right through the open doorway. Continue straight down the hall and make a right into the restroom.

src: down stairs at white flowers
tgt: Walk down stairs and stop at white flowers.

src: stairs by sculpture
tgt: Descend the stairs and stop by the sculpture.

src: stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk past glass table stairs at top
tgt: Walk past the glass dining table and go up the stairs.  Stop at the top.

src: turn right past table chairs right at stairs then staircase top funky piece of art with watermelon on there
tgt: Turn to the right and walk past the table and chairs.  Turn right at the stairs, and then climb up the staircase.  Go to the top.  When you see a funky piece of art, with a watermelon on it, stop and wait there.

src: walk in front of dinning table stairs left at staircase up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk in front of the dinning table and go to the stairs. Make a left at the staircase and walk up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: closet through fitness room once past fitness room first into bathroom next light switch
tgt: Leave the closet and go through the fitness room. Once past the fitness room take the first left into the bathroom and stop next to the light switch.

src: forward with shelves of shoes right right shelves with sweaters forward gym equipment left turn doorway bathroom on right forward just after light switches right
tgt: Move forward with the shelves of shoes to your right. Turn right when you reach the shelves with sweaters. Move forward and pass the gym equipment to your left. Turn left when you reach the doorway to the bathroom on the right. Move forward and stop just after you pass the light switches to your right.

src: walk other side of closet baskets right past exercise room turn into bathroom
tgt: Walk to the other side of the closet where the baskets are. Turn right and keep going past the exercise room. Turn left and go into the bathroom.

src: walk forward stairs then once first landing
tgt: Walk forward to the stairs and then climb up them and stop once you get to the first landing.

src: up steps turn up stairs on landing
tgt: Walk up the steps and turn left. walk up the stairs and stop on the landing.

src: bedroom walk straight hallway until stairs stairs in front of blue artwork on wall of landing
tgt: Leave the bedroom and walk straight down the hallway until you get to the stairs.  Go up the stairs and stop in front of the blue artwork on the wall of the landing.

src: towards black sofa right before then straight right past bar straight then right past door
tgt: go towards the black sofa. turn right before it then go straight.  take a right past the bar. go straight then left. stop right past the door.

src: walk across room right of couch walk behind counter turn room at room table
tgt: Walk across sitting room and to the right of the couch and walk behind counter. Turn left and enter dining room. Stop at dining room table.

src: through doorway right bar right then immediate left towards kitchen table stop
tgt: Go through doorway and turn right. Walk passed the bar and turn right and then take an immediate left and go towards the kitchen table and stop.

src: walk past rocking chair right walk past chairs right into building right in hallway
tgt: Walk past the rocking chair. Turn right and walk past both rocking chairs. Turn right and walk into the building. Turn right and stop in the hallway. .

src: walk in front of chairs turn right into building turn right beside washing machine
tgt: Walk in front of the chairs turn right, go into the building, turn right, stop beside the washing machine.

src: walk along wooden porch around corner past rocking chairs walk into entry way of home near couch floor lamp near entry door
tgt: Walk along the wooden porch around the corner and past the rocking chairs. Walk into the entry way of the home. Stop near the couch and floor lamp near the entry door.

src: walk just right ahead of across from small television stall
tgt: Walk just right ahead of you and across from the small television you will find the shower stall.

src: down hallway bathroom wait at door
tgt: Walk down the hallway, enter the bathroom, wait at the shower door.

src: turn degrees forward into bathroom turn shower wait at open door
tgt: Turn around 180 degrees and walk forward into the bathroom. turn left to the shower and wait at the open door.

src: turn stairs way top walk across room in front of door outside bathroom door stop
tgt: Turn around and go up the stairs all the way to the top. Walk across the room in front of the door to go outside and enter the bathroom door and stop.

src: turn stairs through bathroom door
tgt: Turn around and ascend the stairs. Go through the bathroom door.

src: up stairs forward wait near bathroom doorway
tgt: Walk up the stairs, step forward, wait near the bathroom doorway.

src: walk down hall right into bedroom at bookcase
tgt: Walk straight down hall turn right into bedroom, stop at bookcase.

src: walk forward hallway with paintings straight way end picture of children right bedroom
tgt: Walk forward and enter the hallway with the paintings. Keep walking straight all the way to the end when you reach the picture of 2 children. Turn right and stop when you enter the bedroom.

src: turn slightly hallway straight until door on right wait at entrance
tgt: Turn slightly left and continue down the hallway. Continue straight until you get to a door on the right. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk out of laundry room down stairs turn at bottom of stairs forward into living room wait next piano reclining chair
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room and down the stairs.  Turn left at the bottom of the stairs and go forward into the living room. Wait next to the piano and the reclining chair.

src: exit laundry room down stairs right at landing down stairs left at bottom of stairs then hard left into great room wait at piano
tgt: Exit the laundry room, and walk down the stairs. Make a right at the landing, and walk down the stairs. Make a left at the bottom of the stairs, and then a hard left into the great room. Wait at the piano.

src: exit room way down bottom of stairs turn again white chair in front of piano
tgt: Exit the room and walk all the way down to the bottom of the stairs. Turn left and again left passing the white chair and stop in front of the piano.

src: up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk forward let up stairs right up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Walk forward and talk a let. Walk up the stairs and turn right. Walk up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs wait at top of stair landing
tgt: Walk up stairs. Wait at top of stair landing.

src: turn bathroom bedroom hall in hall left then right next sofa
tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom. Continue to exit the bedroom and enter the hall. In the hall take a left and then stop right next to the sofa.

src: exit bathroom room turn go straight until couches wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Exit the room. Turn left go straight until you get to couches and wait there.

src: bathroom bedroom.take left in hallway living room area on left next tot large leather chair
tgt: Leave the bathroom and the bedroom.Take a left in the hallway, and enter the living room area on your left. Stop next tot he large leather chair.

src: stairs turn at top just before outside
tgt: Go up the stairs and turn left at the top.  Stop just before stepping outside.

src: head upstairs at top of steps turn outside through glass door wait here
tgt: Head upstairs.  At the top of steps, turn left and go outside through glass door.  Wait here.

src: staircase turn then wait at glass doors outside
tgt: Go up the staircase and turn left, then wait at the glass doors leading outside.

src: bedroom right out of glass doors into entry way in front of balcony before stairs
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Walk out of the glass doors and into the entry way. Stop in front of the balcony before you go down the stairs.

src: walk out of bedroom right through mosaic glass doors at top of stairs
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn right. Walk through the mosaic glass doors and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: exit bedroom walk through large double doors stand at top of split white stairs
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk through the large double doors. Stand at the top of the split, curving, white stairs.

src: down first flight of stairs right down next flight of stairs level of home through columns at bottom of stairs into large room ahead with open curtains on windows
tgt: Walk down the first flight of stairs. Turn right and walk down the next flight of stairs to the lower level of the home. walk through the columns at the bottom of the stairs and into the large room ahead with open curtains on the windows.

src: down stairs landing right stairs way bottom of stairs past columns
tgt: Walk down the stairs.  When you get to the landing, make a right, and continue to walk down the stairs.  Stop when you get all the way to the bottom of the stairs, past the two columns.

src: steps right then rest of stairs turn marble stairs carpet
tgt: Walk down four steps, turn right, then walk down the rest of the stairs.  Turn left and go down the marble stairs and stop when you reach the carpet.

src: stairs past christmas tree on right wiat room with fireplaplace
tgt: Go down the stairs, past the Christmas tree on your right, and wiat facing the room with the fireplaplace.

src: down stairs bottom stop at christmas tree
tgt: Walk down the stairs, when you reach the bottom stop at the christmas tree.

src: turn stairs forward stop in front of christmas tree
tgt: Turn around and go down the stairs. Walk forward and stop in front of the CHristmas Tree.

src: walk out of room past island turn past counter right by fireplace
tgt: Walk out of the room and past the island. Turn left and walk past the counter. Turn right and stop by the fireplace.

src: walk straight fridge on left turn straight until fireplace on right wait near fireplace
tgt: Walk straight and pass the fridge on the left. Turn left and walk straight until you see a fireplace on the right. Wait near the fireplace.

src: with half bath on right forward into kitchen after desk on left turn room immediately right in front of fireplace
tgt: With the half bath on your right, move forward into the kitchen. After passing the desk on your left, turn left and enter the room. Immediately turn right and walk to stand in front of the fireplace.

src: after bathroom left turn down hall end of hall right stairs wait on second step
tgt: After you leave the bathroom make a left turn and walk down the hall. When you get to the end of the hall make a right and go to the stairs, wait on the second step.

src: walk into hallway turn hall walk around corner at end of hallway hall walk first set of stair steps down level on first few stairs
tgt: Walk into the hallway and turn left to walk down the hall. Walk around the corner at the end of the hallway and continue down the hall. Walk to the first set of stair steps leading down to a lower level. Stop on the first few stairs.

src: exit bathroom quick left then immediate right wait near top of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom, make a quick left and then another immediate right and wait near the top of the stairs.

src: walk into house right into room with table through door left of painting stop after threshold
tgt: Walk into the house and turn right into the room with the dining table.  Go through the door left of the painting and stop after passing the threshold.

src: walk by table chairs toward sliding doors living area slight right into dining area through first door on left there
tgt: Walk by the table and chairs toward the sliding doors. Enter the living area. Take a slight right into the dining area. Enter through the first door on the left. Stop there.

src: walk across patio into house through door walk into dining room turn enter bathroom in middle of bathroom facing sink
tgt: Walk across patio and into house through sliding door. walk into the dining room. Turn left and enter bathroom. Stop in middle of bathroom facing sink.

src: up stairs walk towards hallway directly right of room across from stairs into first room on left in front of bed
tgt: Walk up the stairs, and walk towards the hallway directly right of the room across from the stairs. Walk into your first room on your left, and stop in front of the bed.

src: stairs right then left bedroom through last door on right at foot of bed
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a right, then a left.  Enter the bedroom through the last door on your right. Stop at the foot of the bed.

src: stairs right then right again into room wait there
tgt: Go up the stairs. Turn right and then right again to go into the room. Wait there.

src: exit bathroom past bed television until bedroom wait in doorway left
tgt: Exit the bathroom, continue past the bed and television until you exit the bedroom, wait in the doorway to your left.

src: exit bathroom walk straight across bedroom wait at door outside
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk straight across the bedroom. Wait at the door that leads outside.

src: exit bathroom walk through bedroom then near entrance of front door
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk through the bedroom. Then stand near the entrance of the front door.

src: stairs toward mirror turn toward rug door rug in front of wait outside in front of door
tgt: Go up the stairs toward the mirror, turn left toward the rug, and turn out the door the rug is in front of. Wait outside in front of the door.

src: stairs left hall left house through first door just after off welcome mat
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a left. Go down the hall and take another left. Leave the house through the first door and stop just after you are off the welcome mat.

src: finish stairs turn carpet turn again exit through door wait
tgt: Finish walking up the stairs. Turn left and walk to the carpet. Turn left again and exit through the door and wait.

src: walk around bed out door on left
tgt: Walk around the bed and out the door on your left.

src: walk foot of bed right turn slight left in hallway facing elevator
tgt: Walk to the foot of the bed, turn right and walk to hallway turn slight left and stop in hallway facing elevator.

src: turn right past bed past tv doorway just other side of bedroom door wait there
tgt: Turn to the right and walk past the bed.  Go past the tv and to the doorway.  You'll walk just to the other side of the bedroom door.  Wait there.

src: with bbq grill right forward then right grill right building through glass doors ahead of left
tgt: With the BBQ grill to your right, move forward and then turn to the right keeping the grill to your right. Enter the building through the sliding glass doors ahead of you and to the left.

src: bar into glass door on right
tgt: Go left passed the bar and into the glass door on the right.

src: turn bar with stools/chairs on right then right into door on left wait near light blue chair
tgt: Turn left and pass the bar with the stools/chairs on the right then turn right. Go into the door on the left and wait near the light blue chair.

src: turn around towards large green vase once vase turn room with words downtown beside door once black chair into room
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the large green vase. Once you reach the vase, turn left and enter the room with the words #downtown beside the door. Once you enter stop when you get to black chair looking into the room.

src: walk green vase turn enter work room stop at paper rolls
tgt: Walk straight to green vase, turn left and enter work room. Stop at paper rolls.

src: turn hall through white door stop by black chair
tgt: Turn around and go down the hall. Go left through the white door and stop by the black chair.

src: indoors couches steps straight hallway turn wait near entrance of bedroom
tgt: Go indoors. Pass the couches and go up the steps. Go straight down the hallway and turn left. Wait near the entrance of that bedroom.

src: enter house from patio across living room up steps through kitchen turn into bedroom through double doors
tgt: Enter house from patio, walk across living room up steps and through kitchen. Turn left into bedroom through double doors.

src: walk into house stairs down hall on left of kitchen first into bedroom in doorway
tgt: Walk into the house, and go up the stairs. Walk down the hall on the left of the kitchen. Take your first left into the bedroom. Stop in the doorway.

src: exit kitchen across living room with red bed at glass walls
tgt: Exit kitchen across living room to bedroom with red bed. Stop at glass walls.

src: exit room right of desk turn towards bedroom at entrance in between metal chairs
tgt: Exit the room to the right of the desk. Turn left and walk towards the bedroom. Stop when you are at the entrance and in between the 2 metal chairs.

src: black recliner phone semicircular divider aluminum chair
tgt: Go to the black recliner. Go to the phone. Go to the semicircular divider. Go to the aluminum chair.

src: walk out doorway closest bed walk down hallway past stairs walk in first room on right
tgt: Walk out the doorway, the one closest to the bed. Walk straight down the hallway, past the stairs and walk in the first room on the right.

src: exit bedroom straight room through archway then at first doorway right into doorway on right steps in then
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go straight the room through the archway and then at the first doorway to the right go into the doorway on the right and take two steps in and then stop.

src: exit room door on left right hallway couch on left hallway right on first door wait near entrance
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the left. Turn right and head down the hallway. Pass the couch on the left and head down the hallway. Turn right on the first door and wait near the entrance.

src: down hall right then forward by stairs
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn right, then walk forward and wait by the stairs.

src: walk straight table with phone in hallway straight until stairs wait there
tgt: Walk straight and pass the table with the phone in the hallway. Continue straight until you get to a stairs going up. Wait there.

src: walk forward right at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk forward. Turn right. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: left of wooden table turn into doorway turn into second doorway steps in stop
tgt: Go to the left of the wooden table, turn left into the doorway, turn left into the second doorway, take two steps in and the stop.

src: walk towards door walk onto porch walk indoors near door
tgt: Walk towards the door and walk onto the porch.  Walk indoors and stop near the door.

src: bit turn steel door enter inside turn again inside door enter inside there
tgt: Walk a bit, and turn left towards the opened steel door. Enter inside, and turn left again inside another door. Enter inside, and stop there.

src: exit room turn hallway right into brown double doorway step in
tgt: Exit the room, turn left and go down the hallway, turn right into the brown double doorway, take a step in and stop.

src: exit room turn hallway right into room wait near bed
tgt: Exit the room.  Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn right into the room and wait near the bed.

src: walk out of closet turn out of bedroom down hall right into room across from flowers by bed
tgt: Walk out of the closet and turn left. Walk out of the bedroom and walk down the hall. Turn right into the room across from the flowers and stop by the bed.

src: head stairs doorway on right toward kitchen sink right through doorway with wine fridge counter top on left
tgt: Head down the stairs to the doorway on the right.  Go toward the kitchen sink.  Turn right and go through the doorway.  Stop with the wine fridge and counter top on the left.

src: stairs through doorway on right past stove towards sink right through doorway onto brick floor once rug
tgt: continue down the stairs and through the doorway on your right. Walk past the stove towards the sink and turn right. Walk through the doorway onto the brick floor and stop once you reach the rug.

src: downstairs through door on right into kitchen walk sink right into room once rug in room
tgt: Go downstairs and go through the door on your right into the kitchen.  Walk to the sink and turn right to go into another room.  Stop once you reach the rug in the room.

src: turn around marble table right up stairs past pool at entrance showers
tgt: Turn left. Walk around the marble table. Turn right. Walk up the stairs past the pool. Stop at the entrance to the showers.

src: walk forward out of room right in hall up hot tub right in doorway shower
tgt: Walk forward and out of the room take a right in the hall. Walk up the hot tub and take a right. Stop in the doorway to the shower.

src: walk into hallway pool
tgt: Walk into the hallway and to the pool.

src: walk ahead into room on right wait at stairs
tgt: Walk straight ahead and into the room on the right. Wait at the stairs.

src: turn right hallway right on second door wait near stairs
tgt: Turn right and go down the hallway. Turn right on the second door and wait near the stairs going down.

src: turn right hallway beside mirror table doorway on right with stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn right and enter the hallway beside the mirror and the table. Enter the doorway on the right with the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk out of bathroom into bedroom then left out of bedroom wait right outside door
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and into the bedroom then make a left. Walk out of the bedroom and wait right outside the door.

src: out of shower stand in open doorway right walk banister
tgt: Turn around out of the shower and stand in the open doorway. Make a right and walk to the banister.

src: turn out of area out of bathroom into bedroom walk through bedroom door into hallway bed on way
tgt: Turn and walk out of the shower area. Walk out of the bathroom and into the bedroom. Walk through the bedroom door into the hallway, passing the bed on the way.

src: pass bed exit then tv wait there
tgt: Pass the bed and exit then pass the tv and wait there.

src: walk out of bedroom in hall near exterior door
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and stop in the hall near the exterior door.

src: walk past foot of bed towards exit of bedroom door directly in front of right just before room
tgt: Walk past the foot of the bed towards the exit of the bedroom. Stop when there's a door opening directly in front of you and another one to your right just before exiting the room.

src: walk out of bedroom turn left down steps through bathroom in doorway on other side
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom is turn left and walk down the steps. Walk through the bathroom and stop in the doorway on the other side.

src: exit bedroom door next turn down set of steps then straight into bathroom ahead straight until bedroom wait here
tgt: Exit bedroom door.  Next turn left, walk down one set of steps, then walk straight into the bathroom ahead.  Continue going straight until you reach the bedroom.  Wait here.

src: past bed turn head into door past sink tub in doorway before bed
tgt: Go past bed to doorway. Turn left. Head into door and go past the sink and tub. Stop in doorway before the bed.

src: with large mirror right down hallway toward large flower bouquet on end table close flowers turn slightly area in front of staircase so stairs back forward kitchen right of black topped island corner of island beside painting of mountain lake
tgt: With the large mirror to your right, walk down the hallway toward the large flower bouquet on the end table.  When you are close to the flowers, turn to the left slightly and walk to the area in front of the staircase.  Turn so the stairs are to your back, and walk forward entering the kitchen to the right of the black topped island.  Stop when you get to the corner of the island, beside the painting of a mountain and lake.

src: face mirror on wall turn towards stair case right into kitchen area next counter
tgt: Face the mirror hanging on the wall and turn left. Walk towards the stair case and turn right. Walk into the kitchen area and stop next to the counter.

src: walk past fireplace chair walk past staircase right into kitchen just inside kitchen
tgt: Walk past the fireplace and the chair. Walk past the staircase and turn right into the kitchen. Stop just inside the kitchen.

src: downstairs until few stairs
tgt: Go downstairs until there's a few stairs left to go and stop.

src: blue carpet until stairs change direction stairs down stairs until fifth stair from floor on fifth stair until again
tgt: Follow the blue carpet until you see the stairs going down. Change direction there and move down the stairs. Keep going down the stairs until you reach the fifth stair from the floor. Stand on that fifth stair until you are instructed to move again.

src: turn stairs wait on fifth step bottom
tgt: Turn left to go down the stairs. Wait on the fifth step to the bottom.

src: down hall right through hall in front of entryway living room
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn right. Walk through the hall and stop in front of the entryway to the living room.

src: walk straight then right straight into arch ahead near giraffe statue
tgt: Walk straight and then turn right. Walk straight into the arch ahead and wait near the giraffe statue.

src: down hall past bedroom stand near living room wait near end table
tgt: Walk down the hall past the bedroom and stand near the living room.  Wait near the end table.

src: walk through bedroom until hallway in hallway towards balcony glass window stand in window frame stop
tgt: Walk through the bedroom until you reach the hallway. In the hallway, walk towards the balcony and open the glass sliding window. Stand in the window frame and stop.

src: exit bathroom turn room right outside glass doors wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn left and exit the room. Turn right and go outside using the glass sliding doors. Wait there.

src: room adjacent room right wait in entrance balcony
tgt: Leave the room and leave the adjacent room.  Turn right and wait in the entrance to the balcony.

src: turn slight right into hallway right door just outside on mat
tgt: turn slight right into hallway and follow it straight.turn right to open door and stop just outside on mat.

src: exit bedroom walk past stairs on left right out open front door wait on door mat
tgt: Exit the bedroom, and walk past the stairs on the left. Make a right, and walk out the open front door. Wait on the door mat.

src: bedroom straight until foyer second opening on right out of large double wood doors on rug outside
tgt: Leave the bedroom. Go straight until you reach the foyer which is the second opening on your right. Step out of the large double wood doors, and stop on the rug outside.

src: stairs room at o'clock position step into doorway of bedroom stop
tgt: Go up the stairs and enter the room at your one o'clock position.  Step into the doorway of this bedroom and stop.

src: up set of stairs very top wait by bedroom doorway between sets of paintings
tgt: Walk up the set of stairs to the very top.  Wait by the bedroom doorway between the two sets of paintings.

src: walk towards stairs stairs at top of stairs straight towards open door in doorway
tgt: Walk towards the stairs and go up the stairs. At the top of the stairs walk straight towards the open door. Stop in the doorway.

src: stairs steps top
tgt: Go up the stairs, stop two steps to the top.

src: steps landing turn steps at top of stairs at beautiful chandelier
tgt: Come up steps to landing, turn left and continue up steps. Stop at the top of the stairs gazing at beautiful chandelier.

src: turn around up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk out of area past stairs down hallway outside on stoop
tgt: Walk out of the sitting area, past the stairs and down the hallway. Wait outside on the stoop.

src: walk past stairs on right hall turn outside between doors
tgt: Walk past the stairs, keeping them on your right. Continue down the hall and turn left to go outside. Stop there between the two doors.

src: walk from piano right out open door on left on porch outside
tgt: Walk from piano right to hallway. Walk out open door on left. Stop on porch outside.

src: forward towards steps stairs right end of hall wait just inside last door on left
tgt: Move forward towards the steps. go up the stairs and go right to the end of the hall. Wait just inside the last door on the left.

src: walk through large room table couch area towards small set of steps on other side up steps through doorway walk wall paintings small table against wall into hallway between hall end pool area
tgt: Walk through the large room passed the table and couch area towards the small set of steps on the other side. Walk up the steps and through the doorway. Walk passed the wall paintings and small table against the wall into the hallway between. Continue down the hall to the end where there is a pool area.

src: up stairs down hallway right of mirror jacuzzi room wait at doorway
tgt: Walk up the stairs, walk down the hallway to the right of the mirror, enter the jacuzzi room, wait at the doorway.

src: straight into room ahead then near sinks
tgt: Go straight into the room ahead and then wait near the two sinks.

src: through hallway opposite plants straight into doorway about steps in then
tgt: Go through the hallway opposite the plants and go straight into the doorway. Take about five steps in and then stop.

src: turn right through open doorway wait next sinks
tgt: Turn right and walk through the open doorway. Wait next to the sinks.

src: turn right through doorway with downtown walk past chairs turn at end of table forward at next table right forward at end of second table in front of table with pink box
tgt: Turn to the right to walk through doorway marked with #downtown. Walk past folding chairs. Turn left at end of table and walk forward. At next table, turn right and walk forward. Stop at end of second table, in front of table with pink box.

src: green decoration go through archway through room right around table at conference table turn right table stop
tgt: Facing the green decoration go left through the archway, go through the room, go right and around the table, at the conference table turn right, go passed the table and stop.

src: pass green vase into room table exit room right wait near bottom of stairs
tgt: Pass the green vase and to straight into the room. Pass the table and exit the room. Turn right and wait near the bottom of the stairs.

src: up stairs turn at carpet at top of stairs in middle of doorway
tgt: Walk up the stairs.  Turn left at the carpet at the top of the stairs, and stop in the middle of the doorway.

src: up first flight of stairs up next flights of stairs top of staircase walk along wall ahead through open glass doors near potted plant
tgt: Walk up the first flight of stairs. Continue up the next flights of stairs to the top of the staircase. Walk along the wall ahead and go through the open glass doors near the potted plant.

src: walk way up stairwell until rug on right bench in front of left in first doorway
tgt: Walk all the way up the stairwell until you see a rug on your right and a bench in front of you.  Take a left and stop in the first doorway.

src: exit kitchen wait in area between sofas
tgt: Exit the kitchen and wait in the sitting area, between the sofas.

src: sink turn counter chairs onto wood next small circle table stop
tgt: Facing the sink turn left, go passed the counter chairs, step onto the wood flooring next to the small circle table and stop.

src: kitchen living room next small round end table stop here
tgt: Leave the kitchen and go to the living room. Stand next to the small round end table. Stop here.

src: down hall left through doors down hall in front of double doors
tgt: Walk down the hall and to the left. Walk through the doors and down the hall. Stop in front of the double doors.

src: turn through doorway left of mirror wait in doorway on right
tgt: Turn left and walk through the doorway to the left of the mirror. Wait in the doorway on the right.

src: red carpet down hall past fire extinguishers on floor angle slightly through double doors ahead left red carpet end of ropes right in doorway
tgt: Follow the red carpet down the hall, past the fire extinguishers on the floor. Angle slightly left and walk through the double doors ahead and to the left. Follow the red carpet to the end of the ropes and turn right, waiting in the doorway.

src: turn next chair with white cushions left
tgt: Turn left. Wait next to the chair with the white cushions to the left.

src: turn toward left then forward table on right once past table forward few steps halt next chair with white cushions
tgt: Turn toward the left then walk forward keeping the table on your right. Once past the table keep going forward a few more steps and halt next to the chair with white cushions.

src: walk past black table chairs stand by first white chair rectangular coffee table couches
tgt: Walk past the black table and chairs and stand by the first white chair that is facing the rectangular coffee table and checkered couches.

src: turn room out last door on right once out turn then right hallway next white door on right hallway beside entrance storage room with drawers
tgt: Turn around and exit the room out the last door on your right. Once out, turn left and then right. Follow the hallway and enter the next white door on your right. Enter the hallway and stop beside the entrance to the storage room with drawers.

src: exit bedroom turn across hall through single door on left through door wait there
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left. Walk across the hall  and through the single door on the left. Go through the door and wait there.

src: turn bedroom walk into room picture of cheetah left of doorway wait there
tgt: Turn around and exit the bedroom. Walk into the room that has a picture of a cheetah to the left of the doorway and wait there.

src: exit building turn stairs turn wait at bottom of brick porch stairs
tgt: Exit the building, turn left, go up the stairs, turn left, wait at the bottom of the brick porch stairs.

src: walk outside head stairs way up at top after into gravel
tgt: Walk outside and head left to the stairs. Go all the way up and stop at the top after stepping into the gravel.

src: walk out onto patio stairs on left at top of stairs next bush before stairs on left
tgt: Walk out onto the patio and go up the stairs on your left. At the top of the stairs stop next to the bush before the stairs on your left.

src: left bathroom then left in hall steps now at bottom of steps in bedroom wait
tgt: You should make a left to leave the bathroom, then make a left in the hall to go down the steps. Now stand at the bottom of the steps in the bedroom and wait.

src: exit bathroom wait inside bedroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom and wait inside the nearest bedroom.

src: turn exit outside bathroom toilet bowl on left left outside door forward in front of small black chair white towel on side
tgt: Turn left and exit outside the bathroom passing the toilet bowl on your left. Turn left outside the door. Keep walking forward, and stop in front of the small black cushioned chair that has a white towel on its side.

src: turn door near sink then next hallway right enter room stop at edge of rug couch
tgt: Turn left and exit the door near the sink. Then turn left and enter the next hallway. Turn right and enter room, Stop at the edge of the rug facing the couch.

src: exit bathroom turn closet then right toward bed wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Pass the closet then turn right. Walk toward the bed and wait there.

src: exit bathroom left through open door right at hallway slight right into bedroom standing at edge of rug
tgt: exit bathroom to hallway, turn left and go through open door, turn right at hallway, turn slight right into bedroom standing at edge of rug.

src: exit closet then right room door on right left hallway until desk with with green chairs
tgt: Exit the closet then turn right and exit the room using the door on the right. Turn left and go down the hallway until you get to a desk with with two green chairs.

src: exit current room head toward bedroom right left then toward office area
tgt: Exit current room head toward bedroom, make a right, make a left then head toward the office area.

src: closet bedroom first left in hall straight toward green chairs office before rug
tgt: Leave the closet, and bedroom. take the first left in the hall, and go straight toward the green chairs. Enter the office, and stop before you reach the rug.

src: turn wood door once turn left down stairs way bottom at bottom turn right door left
tgt: Turn around and exit out the wood door. Once out turn left and walk down the stairs all the way to the bottom. At the bottom turn right and enter the door to your left and stop.

src: through door turn left stairs way floor then right in doorway of first door left
tgt: Go through the door and turn left. Go down the stairs. Continue all the way to the lower floor and then turn right  and stand in the doorway of the first door to your left.

src: turn around through door toward railing stairs way in doorway right of picture of marilyn monroe
tgt: Turn around and walk through the door toward the railing. Go down the stairs all the way. Stop in the doorway that's to the right of the picture of Marilyn Monroe.

src: walk so underneath fan then right door inside straight until head of dining room table behind first chair
tgt: Walk so you are standing underneath the fan and then turn right.  Enter the door going inside and walk straight until you reach the head of the dining room table.  Stop behind the first chair you encounter.

src: straight of chairs then right into glass doors wait by large table chairs
tgt: Go straight and pass one of the chairs then turn right into the glass doors and wait by the large table and chairs.

src: turn then right into house next table with chairs
tgt: Turn left and then turn right and walk into the house. Wait next to the table with four chairs.

src: exit bedroom move right past stairs into bedroom on left just inside room in between dressers
tgt: Exit the bedroom and move to the right, past the stairs, and into the bedroom on the left. Stop just inside the room, in between the two dressers.

src: turn walk through bedroom couch desk walk into hallway past stair well into bedroom on other side armchairs near glass doors near bed
tgt: Turn and walk through the bedroom passed the couch and desk. Walk into the hallway and continue past the stair well and into the bedroom on the other side, which has two armchairs near the glass doors. Stop near the bed.

src: turn around door out of doorway past stairs into bedroom just before bed
tgt: Turn around and walk to the door.  Go out of the doorway, past the stairs and into the bedroom.  Stop just before you get to the bed.

src: away from stairs right at double doors right hallway in front of fireplace on right
tgt: walk away from the stairs and turn right, turn left at the double doors and turn right down hallway stop in front of fireplace on the right.

src: turn right hallway left of doors with mirrors halfway down hallway into sitting room right in front of fireplace
tgt: Turn to your right and head down the hallway to the left of the doors with mirrors. Halfway down the hallway it opnes into a sitting room. Stop right in front of the fireplace.

src: right towards hallway left of double glass doors few steps hallway fireplace in alcove right
tgt: Go right towards the hallway to the left of the double glass doors. Take a few steps down the hallway. Go to the fireplace in the alcove to your right.

src: exit bathroom walk towards kitchen beside refrigerator
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Walk towards the kitchen and stop beside the refrigerator.

src: after bathroom left in hall wait in kitchen across hall
tgt: After you leave the bathroom make a left in the hall and wait in the kitchen across the hall.

src: exit bathroom walk through dining room white dining room table on left as in front of refrigerator in kitchen
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk through the dining room.  The white dining room table will be on your left as you pass.  Stop in front of the refrigerator in the kitchen.

src: turn past couch past couch on right through hallway through there stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn left, and go past the couch, when you get past the couch, go on to the right and go through the hallway.  Continue through there to the stairs.  You'll need to wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk along backside of couch in living room walk into arched entry way white tiled hall down hall first door walk through door stairwell
tgt: Walk along the backside of the couch in the living room. Walk into the arched entry way that leads to a white tiled hall. Walk down the hall to the first door. Walk through the door and towards the stairwell going down.

src: walk end of couch tree slight right down hall door on left enter there
tgt: Walk to the end of the couch and when you reach the tree take a slight right. Walk down that hall to the door on your left and enter there.

src: forward into kitchen right in kitchen in kitchen walk straight around counter on left right stairs once down stairs left at table
tgt: Walk forward into the kitchen and take a right in the kitchen. In the kitchen walk straight and go around the counter on your left. Take a right and go down the stairs. Once you are down the stairs take a left and stop at the table.

src: walk into kitchen walk past kitchen sink down stairs wait at built-in buffet
tgt: Walk into kitchen. Walk past kitchen sink. Walk down stairs. Wait at built-in buffet.

src: enter kitchen area right around island top of stairs stairs turn wait by dining table
tgt: Enter the kitchen area and turn right. Go around the island to the top of the stairs. Continue down the stairs. Turn left and wait by the dining table.

src: walk through wine closet through tall open door on other side ahead into room with wooden floor past round table by arm chairs past table through open entryway ahead door outside with decorative iron
tgt: Walk through the wine closet and through the tall open door on the other side ahead. Walk into the room with a wooden floor and past the round table surrounded by arm chairs. Continue past the table and through the open entryway ahead that leads to a door to the outside with decorative iron.

src: exit wine cellar straight past table chars toward front door wait there
tgt: Exit the wine cellar. Go straight past the table and chars. Walk toward the front door and wait there.

src: wine room walk around table opposite side down steps in front of wooden door underneath chandelier on far left corner of criss cross floor decoration
tgt: Leave the wine room and walk around the dining table to the opposite side.  Walk down the two steps and stop in front of the wooden door, underneath a chandelier.  You will be standing on the far left corner of the criss cross floor decoration.

src: walk straight wait in entryway of room on right
tgt: Walk straight and wait in the entryway of the room on the right.

src: down hallway along tall cupboards on wall walk along glass banister wall towards stairwell ahead past laundry room turn into next door hall paintings on side of walls
tgt: Walk down the hallway along the tall cupboards on the wall. Walk along the glass banister wall. towards the stairwell ahead. Walk past the laundry room and turn into the next door down the hall that has paintings on either side of the walls.

src: down hall right just before stairs in doorway
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn right just before the stairs. Stop in the doorway.

src: walk past dining table stairs at top of stairs near end table with potted plant on
tgt: Walk past the dining table and go up the stairs.  Stop at the top of the stairs near the end table with a potted plant on it.

src: walk around dining table up steps right into living room near black end table
tgt: Walk around the dining table and up the steps, to the right, into the living room. Stop near the black end table.

src: walk from view of pool staircase right before kitchen area right stairs wait right of stairs close table with black ash tray small white planter
tgt: Walk to your left away from the view of the pool. There will be a staircase right before the kitchen area to your right. Climb up those stairs and wait to the right of the stairs close to the table with the black ash tray and small white planter.

src: turn past doorway stairs way slightly little way in front of washer dryer
tgt: Turn left and walk past the doorway.  Go up the stairs, all the way.  Turn slightly left and walk a little way.  You'll stop when you are in front of the washer dryer set.

src: forward with desk on left walk into hallway in hallway right stair way top at top of stairs left into laundry room through first door on left side once inside laundry room just inside doorway
tgt: Walk forward with the desk on your left and walk into the hallway. In the hallway hang a right and go up the stair all the way to the top. At the top of the stairs hang a left and go into the laundry room through the first door on the left side. Stop once inside the laundry room and stop just inside the doorway.

src: walk out through open doors into hallway up stairwell ahead top walk through open door at top of stairs top of stairs with machines inside
tgt: Walk out through the open doors into the hallway. Walk up the stairwell ahead to the top. Walk through the open door at the top of the stairs straight closest the top of the stairs with the washing machines inside.

src: out of bathroom into bedroom past shelves bed couch out of bedroom door head toward door outside just outside door
tgt: Go out of the bathroom into the bedroom.  Go past the shelves and bed and couch out of the bedroom door.  Head toward the door going outside.  Stop just outside the door.

src: exit bathroom through bedroom exit house onto patio
tgt: exit bathroom, walk through bedroom to hall, exit house onto patio.

src: walk through bathroom through bedroom walk through open doors wait at grill
tgt: Walk through bathroom. Walk through bedroom. Walk through open sliding doors. Wait at grill.

src: walk through double doors turn through set of double doors wait in front of circle in front of stairs between large columns
tgt: Walk through the double doors and turn left. Continue through another set of double doors. Wait in front of the circle railing in front of the stairs and between the large columns.

src: red carpet right at chandileir wait at top of stairs
tgt: Follow red carpet, turn right at chandileir, wait at top of stairs.

src: away from semi circle of chairs through doorway red carpet left fire extinguisher on left red carpet until staircase on right at top
tgt: Walk away from the semi circle of chairs through the doorway, follow the red carpet to the left, pass the fire extinguisher on your left and follow the red carpet until there is a staircase on your right. Stop at the top.

src: down hall with marble flooring opening wood-floored hall right
tgt: Walk down the hall with marble flooring. Stop when there is an opening to a wood-floored hall to your right.

src: through marble floored hallway few feet from door
tgt: Go through the marble floored hallway and stop a few feet from the door.

src: turn next table with bamboo plant
tgt: Turn around and wait next to the table with the bamboo plant.

src: turn closet walk into closet slightly right out of closet into laundry room right into hallway turn into kitchen near refrigerator
tgt: TURN LEFT TO FACE THE CLOSET AND WALK INTO THE CLOSET, TURN SLIGHTLY TO THE RIGHT AND WALK OUT OF THE CLOSET AND INTO THE LAUNDRY ROOM, TURN RIGHT AND WALK INTO THE HALLWAY, TURN LEFT AND WALK INTO THE KITCHEN NEAR THE REFRIGERATOR.

src: walk into closet through open doors through closet door towards sink area corner near sink walk into kitchen area by refrigerator
tgt: Walk into the closet through the open doors. Walk through the closet door towards the sink area. Turn the corner near the sink and walk into the kitchen area and stop by the refrigerator.

src: with tub on left straight into closet right into closet right out of closet into laundry room right out of laundry room left into kitchen behind bench on right
tgt: With the tub on your left go straight into the closet and take a right into the closet and a right out of the closet into the laundry room taking a right out of the laundry room and a left into the kitchen stopping behind the bench on your right.

src: stairs left in sitting room left into changing room in doorway of changing room
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. In the sitting room take another left and go into the changing room. Stop in the doorway of the changing room.

src: down stairs left then left in sitting room straight back doorway of small room wait
tgt: Walk down the stairs and make a left then make a left in the sitting room. Go straight back to the doorway of a small room and wait.

src: stairs turn turn again through doorway room with white covered chairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Turn left again to go through the doorway to the room with the white covered chairs.

src: walk beside bed then door straight stairs then at middle of stairs
tgt: walk straight beside the bed then exit the door, walk straight to the stairs then stop at the middle of the stairs.

src: past bed exit bedroom through panel door straight towards staircase on far wall steps wait there
tgt: Go past the bed and exit the bedroom through the six panel door. Continue straight towards the staircase on the far wall. Go up 4 steps and wait there.

src: walk towards bed exit bedroom walk bottom of stairs up fourth step on stairs
tgt: Walk towards the bed and exit bedroom. Walk to the bottom of the stairs. Climb up to the fourth step and stop on the stairs.

src: turn couch on right
tgt: Turn around and pass the couch on your right.

src: walk back in blue couch right up door just past stairs on left
tgt: Walk back in keeping the blue couch to your right. Walk up to the door just past the stairs on your left.

src: walk into building behind couch by end table
tgt: Walk into the building and behind the couch. Stop by the end table.

src: right hall into room straight ahead in doorway
tgt: Go to the right, and continue down the hall. Go into the sitting room straight ahead. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn right straight until double doors into double doors wait there
tgt: Turn left and turn right and go straight until you get to double doors. Go into the double doors and wait there.

src: walk past chair cabinets in hallway across tiled marble flooring wait by double doors
tgt: Walk past the chair and cabinets in the hallway and across the tiled marble flooring.  Wait by the double doors.

src: exit closet into bathroom then bathroom into bedroom opposite side of room then bedroom
tgt: Exit the closet into the bathroom, then turn left and exit the bathroom into the bedroom. Go to the opposite side of the room, then exit the bedroom.

src: exit closet turn exit bathroom exit bedroom outside of doorway
tgt: Exit closet, turn left and exit bathroom. Exit bedroom, and stop outside of the doorway.

src: walk in bathroom turn into bedroom walk past bed right through door
tgt: Walk in to the bathroom and turn left into the bedroom. Walk past the bed and turn right. Walk through the door.

src: turn stairs first landing right again stairs forward towards hallway entrance turn hallway door on left bear into room
tgt: turn right up the stairs to the first landing and right again to continue up the stairs. Continue forward towards the hallway entrance. Turn left to proceed down the hallway. Choose the door on the left and bear left into the room.

src: upstairs down hallway on left wait in bedroom on left
tgt: Go upstairs, down the hallway on the left and wait in the bedroom on the left.

src: stairs then hallway until door on left room on left then
tgt: Go up the stairs, and then take a left down the hallway until you reach a door on the left. Enter the room on the left, and then stop.

src: exit bedroom straight hall wait in front of office on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go straight down the hall. Wait in front of the office on the right.

src: exit bedroom into hall in room through first door on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom into the hall and stop in the room through the first door on the right.

src: through bedroom turn through doorway through hallway couple of steps then right into black doorway stop
tgt: Go through bedroom, turn left through the doorway, go through the hallway a couple of steps and then turn right into the black doorway and stop.

src: enter house through doorway turn through doorway past piano wait
tgt: Enter house through doorway. Turn left and go through the doorway past the piano and wait.

src: turn right through open door piano stop by couch
tgt: Turn right and go through the open door. Go left passed the piano and stop by the couch.

src: walk in between couch fireplace through doorway inside of house turn at chair right at piano straight through doorway on left stop
tgt: walk in between couch and fireplace and through doorway to the inside of the house, turn left at the chair, right at the piano,straight and through the doorway on the left and stop.

src: stairs ahead left then right straight ahead turn through doorway right into game room
tgt: Go up the stairs, walk straight ahead and go left then right and continue walking straight ahead. Turn left and walk through the doorway. Turn right and walk into the game room.

src: stairs at top of stairs turn into hall down hallway right into billard room before pool table
tgt: Continue up stairs at top of stairs turn left into hall walk down hallway and turn right into billard's room. Stop before pool table.

src: up stairs forward towards hallway walk end of hallway right at pool table
tgt: Walk up the stairs, continue forward towards the hallway. Walk to the end of the hallway and take a right. Stop at the pool table.

src: walk past table into kitchen wait by counter
tgt: Walk past table, into kitchen and wait by counter.

src: walk past dining room table on right through doorway wait next kitchen counter
tgt: Walk past the dining room table on the right. Go through the doorway and wait next to the kitchen counter.

src: stay of table walk through door into kitchen marble kitchen counter
tgt: Stay left of the table and walk through the door into the kitchen and go to the marble kitchen counter.

src: walk into living room door then across living room foyer wait just inside foyer
tgt: Walk into the living room door.  Then walk across the living room to the foyer and wait just inside the foyer.

src: walk into house past white shag rug walk past vertical wall mirror wait at faux orchid
tgt: Walk into house. Walk past white shag rug. Walk past Vertical wall mirror. Wait at faux orchid.

src: into house off patio walk through living room into foyer just beyond gray line in foyer with table ahead of
tgt: Go into the house off the patio. Walk through the living room into the foyer. Stop just beyond the gray line in the foyer with the table ahead of you.

src: walk forward towards patterned glass door right there
tgt: Walk forward towards the patterned glass door. Turn right, and stop there.

src: with on left down hallway at top of double staircase right through glass double doors right after through doors
tgt: With the railing on your left, walk down the hallway.  At the top of the double staircase, turn right and go through the glass double doors.  Stop right after you step through these doors.

src: down hall right into double doors stop
tgt: walk down the hall that curves left. Turn right and step into the double doors and stop.

src: walk straight along brick right at bushes slight left walk towards door turn enter door way into living room at table chairs hard right walk straight between giant pillar chair
tgt: Walk straight along brick. turn right at bushes. turn slight left and walk towards door. turn left and enter door way into living room. At table and chairs turn hard right and walk straight. Stop between giant pillar and chair.

src: walk right balcony white chair on left sitting room in sitting room right in front of first large brown leather chair
tgt: Walk to the right down the balcony, passing the white chair on your left, and enter the sitting room. In the sitting room take a right and stop in front of the first large brown leather chair.

src: turn right enter side room right again near table chair
tgt: Turn right and enter left side room and turn right again near table and chair.

src: past table into bed room then into bathroom stand in front of sink
tgt: go past the table and into the bed room then turn left and go into the bathroom and stand in front of the sink.

src: walk straight across room small table bedroom right bathroom stand in front of sink wait
tgt: Walk straight across the room passed the small table. Enter the bedroom and turn right. Enter the bathroom stand in front of the sink and wait.

src: walk out of living room kitchen into bedroom on left of refrigerator in bedroom bathroom in doorway bathroom
tgt: Walk out of the living room and kitchen. Go into the bedroom on the left of the refrigerator. In the bedroom enter the bathroom. Stop in the doorway to the bathroom.

src: turn right then plant turn into room on right right into double door on right
tgt: Turn right and then turn left. When you get to the plant turn left and go into the room on the right. Turn right and go into the double door on the right.

src: turn around toward stairs at stairs right towards double wood doors turn walking until end with fake tree turn then right double white doors into bedroom right inside bedroom then into closet door right
tgt: Turn around and walk toward the stairs. At the stairs, turn right and walk towards the double wood doors. Turn left and keep walking until you reach the end with the fake tree. Turn Left and then right to enter the double white doors leading into the bedroom. Turn right inside the bedroom and then stop facing into the closet door to your right.

src: turn right steps enter right left forward turn enter bedroom right enter closet
tgt: Turn right to steps. Enter right. Turn left. Go forward. Turn left and enter bedroom. Turn right and enter closet.

src: exit bathroom right straight towards stairs wait at top of staircase
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Go straight towards the stairs that head down. Wait at the top of the staircase.

src: away from sink through doorway on left through doorway on right side of large clock walk down hallway towards staircase step stop
tgt: Facing away from the sink walk through the doorway on your left, walk through the doorway on the right side of the large clock. Walk straight down the hallway towards the staircase, step down one step and stop.

src: exit bathroom right hallway until stairs then on top of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Go down the hallway until you get to the stairs and then wait on the top of the stairs.

src: into dining room china cabinet
tgt: Go into the dining room. Go to the China cabinet.

src: walk across room hall stop before artwork on wall
tgt: Walk straight across dinning room hall and stop before artwork on wall.

src: fireplace right past timber pillars until next wall in front of abstract sculpture of wooden furniture pieces hardware
