tgt: Continue up the stairs and make a U-turn to the right.  Continue walking parallel with the stairs until you get to the end of the hallway.  Go right and stop on the mat on the deck outside.

src: up steps right walk up steps at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the steps and turn right Walk up the steps and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs wait at top
tgt: Go up the stairs and wait at the top.

src: up stairs on tiles at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs and stop on the tiles at the top of the stairs.

src: walk through kitchen on top step of stairs
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and stop on the top step of the stairs.

src: walk through kitchen past ovens sink at top of stairs without
tgt: Walk through the kitchen, past the ovens and sink, and stop at the top of the stairs without going down.

src: walk forward entire kitchen heading towards staircase right ahead right at top of staircase
tgt: Walk forward and pass the entire kitchen heading towards the staircase which is right ahead. Turn right and stop at the top of the staircase.

src: exit garage via door after steps then stairs right steps from top
tgt: Exit the garage via the door after climbing three steps. Then climb the stairs to your right, stopping two steps from the top.

src: go steps stairs in corner
tgt: Go left up the steps, and go up the stairs in the corner.

src: up steps outside door right way up stairs at third top stair
tgt: Walk up the three steps to exit outside the door. Turn right, and walk all the way up the stairs, and stop at the third top stair.

src: walk inside into bedroom walk past area turn at foot of bed inside doorway out of room
tgt: Walk inside and into the bedroom.  Walk past the sitting area and turn left at the foot of the bed.  Stop inside the doorway leading out of the room.

src: door plant ottoman wardrobe
tgt: Go to the door. Go to the plant. Go to the ottoman. Go to the wardrobe.

src: enter house through double doors across bedroom at right of fireplace.stop at light switch intercom
tgt: Enter house through double doors. Walk across bedroom to exit at right of fireplace.Stop at light switch and intercom.

src: through laundry room exit room right step into dining room stop
tgt: Go through the laundry room and exit the room, make a right and step into the dining room and stop.

src: pass sink right next room right again in front of table
tgt: Pass the sink and go to the right. Enter the next room and turn right again and stop in front of the table.

src: walk past sink out door on right into doorway room right once into dining room
tgt: Walk past the sink and out the door on your right.  Go into the doorway to the room to the right and stop once you have stepped into the dining room.

src: walk straight along path away from plants with guardrail on right through door ahead once inside turn next sink
tgt: Walk straight along the path away from the plants, with the guardrail on your right. Go through the door straight ahead. Once inside, turn left. Stop next to the sink.

src: porch door enter house turn at green counter top with sink
tgt: Walk down porch to front door, enter house, turn left and stop at green counter top with sink.

src: turn right into house turn wait by sink
tgt: Turn to the right and walk into the house. Turn left and wait by the sink.

src: exit living room stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the living room and go up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: exit living room walk into foyer up stairs wait at top of landing
tgt: Exit the living room, and walk into the foyer. Walk up the stairs, and wait at the top of the landing.

src: exit room by straight up stairwell at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the room by going straight. Head up the stairwell. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: up stairs turn through doorway sharp turn hall right up stairs at fourth step
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Turn left and walk through the doorway. Make a sharp turn left down the hall. Turn right and walk up the stairs. Stop at the fourth step.

src: stairs forward left second set of stairs of stairs wait
tgt: Go up the stairs and forward and to the left towards the second set of stairs you see.  Go up three of those stairs and wait.

src: stairs turn through door on left stairs on right before landing
tgt: go up stairs, turn left, go through door on left, go up stairs on right, stop before landing.

src: exit through door outside sidewalk first right turn off of sidewalk onto stone flooring step just past white columns then
tgt: Exit through the door to go outside.  Follow the sidewalk and take the first right turn.  Step off of the sidewalk onto the stone flooring.  Step just past the white columns and then stop.

src: outside first right on wood right outside doorway
tgt: Go outside, take the first right and stop on the wood right outside the doorway.

src: house down path at end of path right onto porch on porch between pillars
tgt: Leave the house and walk down the path. At the end of the path take a right and step onto the porch. Stop on the porch between the pillars.

src: exit bathroom right hall turn into kitchen area once kitchen area turn right immediately right again wait in kitchen area in front of sink
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Continue down the hall and turn left into the kitchen area. Once you enter the kitchen area turn right. Immediately turn right again. Wait in the smaller kitchen area in front of the sink.

src: turn right exit in hall turn end turn right into kitchen then right in front of sink
tgt: Turn to the right and exit. In the hall turn left and go to the end and turn left. Turn right into the kitchen and then take another right and stop in front of the sink.

src: exit bathroom turn hall kitchen right mini kitchen
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Proceed down the hall and enter the kitchen. Turn right and enter the mini kitchen.

src: turn until other house then across deck through open door few steps then on rug
tgt: Turn around until you are facing the other house, then walk across the deck, go through open door, take few steps, then stop on the rug.

src: down steps through door of building just inside doorway
tgt: Walk down the steps and through the door of the building. Stop just inside the doorway.

src: turn stairs through screen door once wicker chairs
tgt: Turn around and go down the stairs and through the screen door. Stop once you reach the wicker chairs.

src: turn toward pool right in front of pool wait by plants
tgt: Turn around and go toward the pool. Turn right in front of the pool and wait by the plants.

src: walk out onto walk outside house straight right wait near plants
tgt: Walk out onto the walk outside the house, and go straight, make a right and wait near the plants.

src: down walkway towards pool right on walkway near door
tgt: Walk down the walkway towards the pool and turn right. Stop on the walkway near the door.

src: walk inside left piano wait at set of stairs immediate left of piano
tgt: Walk inside and take a left towards the piano.  Wait at the set of stairs to the immediate left of the piano.

src: into building down steps wait behind wall near bottom of stairs
tgt: Go into the building and down the steps. Wait behind the wall near the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk into doorway turn down steps walk corner turn up second step stop
tgt: Walk into the doorway and turn left. Walk down the steps and walk left around the corner. Turn left and walk up the second step and stop.

src: right into office right again between bookshelves then quick left into second doorway on left near toilet
tgt: Turn right into the office, make a right again between the bookshelves and then a quick left. Turn into the second doorway on the left. Stop and wait near the toilet.

src: straight room right door turn through hallway until second door on left room wait near toilet
tgt: Go straight and enter the room. Turn right and go out the door. Turn left and go through the hallway until you get to the second door on the left. Enter the room and wait near the toilet.

src: with long corridor behind door left double door in front of through double door in front of room through opening in corner of room ahead of right after bookcase on left also concealed door that just through ninety degrees left second toilet area left
tgt: With the long corridor behind you, there will be a door to your left and a double door in front of you. Go through the double door in front of you. Exit this room through the opening in the corner of the room that's ahead of you and to the right. After passing the bookcase on your left (which is also a concealed door that you just went through), turn ninety degrees to the left and enter the second toilet area to your left.

src: walk past zebra painting into room walk in front of animal print bench
tgt: Walk past the zebra painting and into the room. Walk left and stop in front of the animal print bench.

src: turn hallway with painting of zebra room stop between sofa table
tgt: Turn and go down the hallway with the painting of a zebra. Enter the room and stop between the sofa and dining table.

src: turn left forward into hallway walk through double doors forward on striped rug
tgt: Turn around to your left and move forward into the hallway. Walk through the double doors, move forward and wait on the striped rug.

src: walk out of office right past stairs turn in front of piano
tgt: Walk out of the office and turn right. Walk past the stairs and turn left. stop in front of the piano.

src: walk past desk walk of stairs left opposite front door rug wait at piano
tgt: Walk past desk. Walk to bottom of stairs. Make left opposite front door rug. Wait at piano.

src: walk past table through double doors right continue straight turn towards area wait by piano
tgt: Walk past table and through double doors. Turn right And continue straight. Turn left and walk towards the sitting area. Wait by the piano.

src: walk forward foot of beds hallway n't forward anymore degrees right forward until kitchen just inside kitchen
tgt: Walk forward, passed the foot of both beds.  Enter the hallway, when you can't go forward anymore, turn 90 degrees to the right and walk forward until you enter the kitchen.  Stop just inside the kitchen.

src: beds through door black chair right hall in entryway kitchen
tgt: Go passed the beds and through the door. Go passed the black chair and turn right. Go down the hall and stop in the entryway to the kitchen.

src: walk across through door at other end of bedroom right head towards rectangle glass table after table
tgt: Walk across through the door at the other end of the bedroom. Turn right and head towards the rectangle glass table. Stop after passing the table.

src: through grand room right into doorway immediately after victorian east lake chairs
tgt: Go through the grand room and take a right into the doorway that is immediately after the two Victorian east lake chairs.

src: turn left walk on rug past few chairs end table hallway right then door on left on right there wait
tgt: Turn to the left and walk on the rug, going past a few chairs and a end table.  When you get to the hallway, you can turn right and then go to where there is a door on the left and on the right.  Stop there.  Wait.

src: turn around towards end of hall last entrance on right between doors in hallway
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the end of the hall. Take the last entrance on the right and stop between the two doors in the hallway.

src: exit kitchen walk past stairs wait in sitting room
tgt: Exit the kitchen and walk past the stairs. Wait in the sitting room.

src: turn left walk towards stairs across room past stairs into next room right before small table beside loveseat
tgt: Turn to your left and walk towards the stairs across the room. Go past the stairs and into the next room. Stop right before you get to the small table beside the loveseat.

src: walk out of area past center counter top sink into next room dining room table with chairs walk past stair well through room into living room area on other side stop near couches
tgt: Walk out of the kitchen area past the center counter top and sink. Continue into the next room and pass the dining room table with chairs. Walk past the stair well and continue through the room into the living room area on the other side. Stop near the couches.

src: walk door then right little bit then straight small stair then at mini bar
tgt: go walk to the door then turn right walk a little bit then turn left go straight to the small stair then stop at the mini bar.

src: turn head inside through patio doors walk past living room stairs wait in kitchen
tgt: Turn around and head inside through the patio doors.  Walk past the living room and go up the stairs.  Wait in the kitchen.

src: pass table chairs into house glass door on right straight up steps wait there
tgt: Pass the table and chairs and go into the house using the glass door on the right. Go straight and up the steps. Wait there.

src: dining room walk through washroom into room wait in doorway near couch
tgt: Leave the dining room and walk through the washroom into the sitting room. Wait in the doorway near the couch.

src: with table behind room through double doors ahead of left across room through double doors on opposite wall
tgt: With the table and chandelier behind you, exit the room through the double doors ahead of you and to the left. Continue across the room and through the double doors on the opposite wall.

src: dining room through door right of dining table walk past doorway on opposite from in doorway into room with round couch
tgt: Leave the dining room through the door to the right of the dining table.  Walk past the but and enter the doorway on the opposite from where you started.  Stop when you are standing in this doorway into the room with the round couch.

src: walk towards kitchen turn into dining room through dining area right into living room walk through living room toward fireplace slight right into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Walk towards the kitchen and turn left into the dining room. Continue through the dining area and turn right into the living room. Walk through the living room toward the fireplace and make a slight right into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: walk into kitchen first right into dining room walk end of room first right into room in sitting room in sitting room right into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Walk into the kitchen and take the first right into the dining room. Walk to the end of the room and take your first right into the sitting room. In the sitting room. In the sitting room take a right into the bathroom, stop in front of the sink.

src: turn right walk across dining table area room right towards blue chair right again bathroom
tgt: Turn right walk across the dining table area room. Turn right and walk towards the blue chair. Turn right again and enter the bathroom.

src: walk past stairs right past dining room table chairs in entryway outside
tgt: Walk past the stairs and turn right. Walk past the dining room table and chairs and stop in the entryway to the outside.

src: straight staircase on left right room glass table step near glass doors stop
tgt: Go straight passed the staircase on the left, turn right and cross the room passed the glass table, step near the glass sliding doors and stop.

src: walk forward right side of stairs.when room right past tables chairs exit large door outside behind first chair on right
tgt: Walk forward to the right side of the stairs.When the room opens up, turn right and walk past all the tables and chairs. Exit the large door leading outside and stop behind the first chair on the right.

src: walk past dual ovens refrigerator forward wait in front of bedroom door
tgt: Walk past the dual ovens and refrigerator and continue forward.  Wait in front of the bedroom door.

src: walk through kitchen past stove bedroom
tgt: Walk through the kitchen past the stove and enter the bedroom.

src: walk through doorway on left side of fridge straight until bedroom in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk through the doorway on the left side of the fridge and keep going straight until you enter a bedroom.  Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: exit bedroom straight down hallway on left enter stop in doorway
tgt: exit bedroom to hallway. Go straight down hallway to staircase, turn left to bedroom on left and enter, stop in doorway.

src: walk past stairs left at guitar wait at bedroom door threshold
tgt: Walk past stairs. Make left at guitar. Wait at bedroom door threshold.

src: walk through door out of bedroom walk past steps turn into bedroom stop
tgt: Walk through the door out of the bedroom. Walk past the steps and turn left. Walk into the bedroom and stop.

src: exit bathroom right into bedroom stop wait near dresser
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right into the bedroom. Stop and wait near the dresser.

src: exit bathroom right through door at end of hall turn next skis on wall
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right. Go through the door at the end of the hall. Turn left and stop next to the two skis on the wall.

src: exit bathroom hall wait in room at end of hall
tgt: Exit the bathroom and go down the hall. Wait in the room at the end of the hall.

src: exit room right down hallway over rug at very end of hallway after stairs
tgt: Exit the room and turn right and walk down the hallway over the rug.  Stop at the very end of the hallway after passing the stairs.

src: exit room then right straight until door on right there
tgt: Exit the room then turn right. Go straight until you get to a door on the right. Wait there.

src: exit room walk end of hallway wait past stairs in corner
tgt: Exit the room and walk to the end of the hallway. Wait past the stairs, in the corner.

src: down cement walkway through door into building walk through door entrance bedroom
tgt: walk down the cement walkway and through the door into the building.  Walk through the door and to the entrance to the bedroom.

src: turn behind hot tub in front of left little head toward walkway right of hot tub path pool on left heading way until through door through door very tall painting right in front of at painting in front of at bedroom with bed chaise lounge right in front of here
tgt: Turn behind you. There will be a hot tub in front of you to the left a little. Head toward the walkway to the right of the hot tub. Continue up the path. The pool is on your left and keep heading that way until you go through a door. When you go through the door there will be a very tall painting right in front of you. Turn left at the painting in front of you and you will be looking at a bedroom with a bed and chaise lounge right in front of you. Stop here.

src: walk ahead on boards left at left column walk through into building with tall cloth
tgt: Walk ahead on the boards. Make a left at the left column. Walk straight through into the building with the tall framed cloth.

src: steps in front of at top walk straight forward down next set of steps at bottom kitchen outside
tgt: Continue up the steps in front of you. At the top walk straight forward and down the next set of steps. At the bottom, stop facing the the kitchen and outside.

src: up stairs straight until set of stairs down stairs bottom
tgt: Walk up the stairs and continue walking straight until you reach another set of stairs.  Go down these stairs and stop when you reach the bottom.

src: stairs then white stairs ahead at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go up the stairs, and then go down the white stairs straight ahead. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: out of bathroom closet left bathroom once in bedroom walk around bed through door bedroom after bedroom immediate left turn then left into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: You should walk out of the bathroom closet and make a left to leave the bathroom. Once you are in the bedroom walk around the bed and go through the door to leave the bedroom. After you leave the bedroom make an immediate left turn, then make another left to go into the bathroom and wait by the sink.

src: into bathroom turn into bedroom around bed out into hall turn into dark bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Go into the bathroom and turn left into the bedroom.  Go around the bed and out into the hall.  Turn left and go into the dark bathroom. Stop in front of the sink.

src: turn right bathroom turn bedroom bedroom door on right walkout into hallway turn into bathroom on left in front of sinks
tgt: Turn to your right and enter the bathroom. Turn left and enter the bedroom. Cross the bedroom and exit the door on the right. Walkout into the hallway. Turn left and walk into the bathroom on your left. Stop in front of the sinks.

src: walk past stairway towards long glass table room perpendicular glass table by beside table
tgt: Walk past the stairway, towards the long glass table.  Enter the room perpendicular to the glass table by turning left.  Wait beside the table.

src: walk past stairs wait in office across from area
tgt: Walk past the stairs and wait in the office, across from the dining area.

src: with sofa behind right until little black desk on left in front of black desk
tgt: With the sofa behind you, take a right until you see a little black desk on your left. Go and stand in front of the black desk.

src: turn right hallway until end then right hall door brown doors on right right after second door right into office room
tgt: Turn right, go down the hallway until you come to the end and then make a right, go down the hall passed the door brown doors on the right, right after the second door go right into the office room.

src: head past exit sign right past open doors on right walkway.. turn right at exit sign walkway at open door kitty-corner from office
tgt: Head past the exit sign and turn right. Go past the open doors on the right and left, continuing down the walkway.. Turn right at the exit sign. Go down the walkway. And stop at the open door kitty-corner from the "enerskin" office.

src: right out of room head before right at doorway room with desk chairs
tgt: Turn right out of room. Head straight before turning right. Stop at doorway to room with desk and chairs.

src: walk towards door outside in front of door turn right across room once in front of stairs turn room once in door
tgt: Walk towards the door going outside. In front of the door turn right. Walk across the room. Once you are in front of the stairs, turn left and enter the room. Stop once in the door.

src: living room by right stairs on left bedroom in doorway bedroom
tgt: Leave the living room by taking a right, and going up the stairs. On the landing take a left and enter the bedroom. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: past couch first part of stairs left bedroom at landing in bedroom
tgt: Go past the couch, and go up the first part of the stairs. Take a left and enter the bedroom at the landing. Stop in the bedroom.

src: walk straight exit room right then into room wait near entrance
tgt: Walk straight and exit the room. Turn right and then turn left into the room. Wait near the entrance.

src: turn around past plant on left trash on right out of bathroom doors right forward left through open door at end of hallway after through door stop
tgt: Turn around and walk past the plant on the left and the trash can on the right. Continue out of the bathroom doors and take a right. Continue going forward and take a left through the open door at the end of the hallway. After walking through the door stop.

src: left bathroom forward left in room with double window doors in doorway
tgt: Go left and exit the bathroom. Go forward to the left in the room with double window doors and stay in the doorway.

src: walk toward bedroom right right just inside bathroom door
tgt: Walk toward the bedroom and turn right. Turn right and stop just inside the bathroom door.

src: straight then right right again into bathroom wait near first sink
tgt: Go straight then turn right. Turn right again and go into the bathroom. Wait near the first sink.

src: down hall right inside bathroom
tgt: Walk down the hall and to the right. Stop inside the bathroom.

src: turn slightly right straight across area set of tables set of tables against wall between wait
tgt: Turn slightly to your right. Walk straight across the dining area, passing one set of tables. When you come to another set of tables, which are against the wall, stand between them and wait.

src: in room doorway on same wall as doorway line of round tables between tables nearest doorway
tgt: In this room there is one doorway. On the same wall as the doorway there is a line of round tables. Go stand between the two tables nearest to the doorway.

src: walk between tables wall on other side of room
tgt: Walk between the tables to the wall on the other side of the room.

src: up stairs then through doorway down hall toward brown chair
tgt: walk up the stairs. Then go through the doorway. Walk down the hall. Go toward the brown chair.

src: stairs turn straight hard right through open double doors straight right into area by chair
tgt: Go up stairs, turn left, go straight, make a hard right through the open double doors, go straight and make a right into the sitting area and stop by the chair.

src: stairs left right hallway in hall right into living room behind black leather chair
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a left. Take a right and go down the hallway. In the hall take a right into the living room. Stop behind the black leather chair.

src: exit bathroom through door opening across hall then right head top of stairs on right steps down stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom and go through the door opening across the hall, then turn right and head to the top of the stairs on your right. Take two steps down the stairs.

src: exit bathroom hallway into room opposite bathroom right slightly top of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom and cross the hallway into the room opposite the bathroom. Turn right slightly and continue to the top of the stairs.

src: bathroom door door hinges wicker chair stairs
tgt: Go to the bathroom door. Go to the door hinges. Go to the wicker chair. Go to the stairs.

src: down stairs bottom then hallway right bedroom wait by closet door
tgt: Walk down the stairs to  the bottom.  Then walk down the hallway to your right and enter the bedroom. Wait by the closet door.

src: staircase walk past brown chair right room with bed
tgt: Go down the staircase. Walk past the brown chair to the right and enter the room with the bed.

src: head downstairs right room with double doors
tgt: Head downstairs and merge right, entering the room with the double doors.

src: bathroom right outside of bathroom door
tgt: Leave the bathroom and stop right outside of the bathroom door.

src: exit shower turn forward until bedroom wait by chair
tgt: Exit the shower and turn left.  Proceed forward until you enter the bedroom. Wait by the chair.

src: walk right side of bathroom wood door past sinks right outside of wood door
tgt: Walk to the right side of the bathroom and exit the wood door past the sinks. Stop right outside of the wood door.

src: walk past barber chair turn in front of plants
tgt: Walk past the barber chair and turn left. Stop in front of the plants.

src: walk down hallway left at end of hallway wait by doorway
tgt: walk straight down the hallway. Take a left at the end of the hallway. Wait by the doorway.

src: straight by chair into left inside door
tgt: Go straight and by the chair, go into the left and stop inside the door.

src: walk towards bedroom turn then through door left of black desk immediately right house wait here
tgt: Walk towards bedroom.  Turn left, then walk through the door to the left of the black desk.  Immediately turn right, and exit the house.  Wait here.

src: exit bathroom exit bedroom turn right at door
tgt: Exit bathroom to bedroom, Exit bedroom turn right and stop at sliding door to outside.

src: exit bathroom bedroom turn past closet exit bedroom right walk end of walkway wait at glass door
tgt: Exit the bathroom  and enter the bedroom and turn left. Walk past the closet and exit the bedroom. Turn right and walk to the end of the walkway and wait at the sliding glass door.

src: exit bedroom turn right before steps right behind couch
tgt: Exit bedroom turn right before steps and stop right behind the couch.

src: turn head bottom of wooden short staircase right staircase there same direction room just in front of white couch
tgt: Turn left and head to the bottom of the wooden short staircase you see. Turn right and head down the staircase there, continuing the same direction, stopping and waiting when you enter the room and you're just in front of the white couch.

src: exit toilet door right right again at small corner wall in front of white sofa
tgt: Exit the toilet door and turn right. Turn right again at the small corner passing the wall. Stop in front of the white sofa.

src: down hallway past stairs stop at doorway on right chairs desk
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the stairs and stop at the doorway on your right where there's three chairs and a desk.

src: walk down hallway towards staircase stop at first door on right after staircase
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway towards the staircase, stop at the first door on the right after the staircase.

src: hallway then in front of last door on right
tgt: Go down the hallway, then stop in front of the last door on the right.

src: stairs straight in living room veer in front of tree in large planter on left
tgt: Go down the stairs, and go straight. In the living room veer left. Stop in front of the tree in the large planter on the left.

src: stairs walk straight ahead until room with couches other ahead of then thirty degrees left until wooden flooring on brick paving
tgt: Continue down the stairs and walk straight ahead until you enter the room with two couches facing each other ahead of you. Then turn about thirty degrees to the left and continue moving until you leave the wooden flooring and are standing on brick paving.

src: walk downstairs room right of mirror next spiral trees wait here
tgt: Walk downstairs.  Enter the room to the right of the mirror.  Walk next to spiral trees.  Wait here.

src: turn around out door swirl on left into room directly next door end of room by mirror
tgt: Turn around and walk out the door that has the swirl on it. Make a left into the room directly next door. Go to the end of the room by the mirror.

src: walk through locker room left in open area immediate left into locker room into bathroom on right in doorway
tgt: Walk through the locker room and take a left in the open area. Take an immediate left into the locker room. Go into the bathroom on the right and stop in the doorway.

src: exit toilet room enter next room turn again adjoining room enter room walk slight right door behind bench at shower
tgt: exit toilet to dressing room and enter next room. Turn left and left again to reach adjoining room. Enter room and walk slight right to open door behind bench. Stop at shower.

src: bathroom bedroom in doorway
tgt: Leave the bathroom. Exit the bedroom. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn toilet forward bathroom forward bed walk past bed door on right in doorway on right side
tgt: Turn to face toilet. Move forward to door. Turn left to exit the bathroom. Walk forward to the bed. Walk past the bed to the door on the right. Stop in the doorway on the right side.

src: exit bathroom then in doorway of bedroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom and then wait in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: turn stairs then right down hall at bedroom entrance
tgt: Turn around and head up the stairs, then turn right and walk down the hall. Stop at the bedroom entrance.

src: at top of stairs right straight hallway in doorway of bedroom at very end
tgt: At the top of the stairs turn right and keep going straight down the hallway.  Stop in the doorway of the bedroom at the very end.

src: stairs right bedroom through double doors wait by entryway
tgt: Proceed up the stairs, turn right and enter the bedroom through the double doors. Wait by the entryway.

src: walk past tv through living room right behind far couch behind couch in front of mottled painting
tgt: Walk past the TV through the living room. and take a right behind the far couch. Stop behind the couch in front of the mottled painting.

src: turn past television couches look behind second couch on right
tgt: Turn left and walk past the television and two couches, look behind the second couch on the right.

src: turn room in front of tv once across turn right behind couch large picture on wall
tgt: Turn left and cross the room in front of the TV. Once across turn right and stop behind the couch and the large picture on the wall.

src: turn entire staircase stop at top of stairway on second floor
tgt: Turn around and head up the entire staircase, Stop at the top of the stairway on the second floor.

src: up stairs immediatly once reach top
tgt: Walk up the stairs, and stop immediatly once your reach the top.

src: stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Go up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: turn room out of curtains on left once turn left white door once through right steps first turn in steps
tgt: Turn around and exit the room out of the curtains on your left. Once out turn left and enter the white door. Once through, turn right and go down the steps. Stop when you reach the first turn in the steps.

src: walk through doorway with black curtains immediately sharp left enter through door left of mirror quick right forward until stairs down stairs wait by red flowers in left corner
tgt: Walk through the doorway with black curtains.  Immediately take a sharp left, and enter through the door left of the mirror.  Make a quick right, and walk forward until you reach stairs.  Walk down the stairs.  Wait by red flowers in the left corner.

src: exit bedroom right into double doors few steps stairs stop
tgt: Exit the bedroom, turn right into the double doors, take a few steps down the stairs and stop.

src: walk out of bedroom across hall walk past table chairs walk into bedroom right just inside bathroom
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and across the hall. Walk past the table and chairs. Walk into the bedroom and turn right. Stop just inside the bathroom.

src: stand in doorway of bathroom walk straight ahead area past chairs bicycle bedroom once in bedroom turn right into bathroom in doorway of bathroom

tgt: Go through the doorway to the room with the red blinds ahead. Travel to the white door. Go through the door and into the bathroom with towels on the shelf.

tgt: Walk straight ahead. Stop and stand at the clear banister that looks over the rest area.

tgt: walk out of the elevator and go straight and into the kitchen. In the kitchen go down the stairs into the living room and stop next to the polka dotted chair next to the end table.

src: along railing stairs on left straight until in middle of hallway then
tgt: Go along the railing passed the stairs on your left and keep going straight until your in the middle of the hallway, then stop.

tgt: Turn left and walk down the hallway. Wait just inside the bedroom.

tgt: Walk forward towards the glass barrier and turn left to walk down the hallway past the laundry area. Continue straight down the hallway passing the smaller bedroom (on the left) and two double doors (on the right). Proceed straight through the other double doors and into the larger bedroom. Walk a short distance through the doors, stop a few feet inside the doorway before you pass the black sculpture.

tgt: Turn around and exit the wood door  behind you and enter the kitchen. Once inside turn slightly right and walk through the kitchen and head down the hallway. Turn into the 2nd room on the right and stop in front of the washer and dryer.

tgt: Exit the small kitchen then turn slightly right and go straight until you get to the glass sliding doors.When you pass the glass sliding doors on the left turn right and wait by the washer and dryer.

tgt: Leave the kitchen and walk through the dining room and kitchen. Go straight and exit the kitchen. take the second right and enter the laundry room. Stop in front of the machines.

tgt: Pass the bed and stop by the patio window.

tgt: Walk past the foot of the bed and the tub and stand between the two chairs in front of the glass doors to the deck.  Stop just before stepping onto the deck.

tgt: Leave the bedroom, and take a right. Go up the stairs and stop at the top of the stairs outside of the bathroom.

tgt: Go up the stairs. Turn right and go into the room on the right. Turn right and go into the bathroom. Wat at the entrance.

tgt: Walk up the steps and turn right. Walk into the second door on the right and stop.

tgt: Turn left, and walk forward, and enter the room next to the refrigerator. Walk and turn right towards the laundry room, and stop there.

src: through doorway turn left through next doorway left of refrigerator right laundry room
tgt: Go through the doorway and turn left. Go through the next doorway to the left of the refrigerator. Turn right and enter the laundry room.

src: past checkered couches black chairs with dining room table statue of women colorful stairs right wait by office desk
tgt: Go past the checkered couches and the black chairs with the dining room table. Pass the statue of a women and when you get to the colorful stairs turn right and wait by the office desk.

src: head towards table with multiple black leather seats slightly head towards staircase staircase stop right office room
tgt: Head towards the table with multiple black leather seats. Turn slightly left and head towards the staircase. When you reach the staircase stop and turn right and enter the office room.

src: walk past tables onto blue red rug beside long black table towards stairs at bottom of stairs right inside office next desk
tgt: Walk past the tables and onto the blue and red rug.  Keep walking beside the long black table, towards the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs, and turn right. Walk inside the office and wait next to the desk.

src: exit laundry room down stairs left at bottom of stairs walk into open room next with pillow
tgt: Exit laundry room and walk down stairs to the left. At bottom of the stairs walk into open room and stop next to chair with pillow.

src: turn way down stairs left at bottom of stairs into room right stopping before desk
tgt: Turn around and go all the way down the stairs to your left. At the bottom of the stairs, go into the room to your right stopping before you reach the desk.

src: room down stairs into office with entrance right of bottom of stairs once inside office
tgt: Leave the room and walk down the stairs.  Go into the office with the entrance to the right of the bottom of the stairs.  Stop once inside the office.

src: turn around across living room past chair lamp right hallway first door on right stop
tgt: Turn around and walk across the living room, past the chair and the lamp. Take a right when you reach the hallway, enter the first door on your right, and stop.

src: walk out of dining room into living room steps out of leaving room right in hallway down hallway into second room on right wait in doorway of bedroom
tgt: Walk out of the dining room and into the living room. Go up the two steps leading out of the leaving room and make  a right in the hallway. Walk down the hallway go into the second room on the right. Wait in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: down steps past couch into hallway right into hallway then right at first door inside bedroom
tgt: Walk down the steps past the couch into the hallway. Turn right into the hallway, then turn right at the first door. Stop when you step inside the bedroom.

src: with widescreen display on left forward towards full height windows right forward then room via opening on opposite wall into bedroom
tgt: With the widescreen display on your left, move forward towards the full height windows and turn right. Continue forward and then exit the room via the opening on the opposite wall into the bedroom.

src: walk past television right around railing into first door on left just inside door
tgt: Walk past the television and turn right. Walk around the railing and into the first door on the left. Stop just inside the door.

src: turn right after couch left into bedroom wait there
tgt: Turn around and take a right after the couch. Take a left into the bedroom and wait there.

src: turn in hall down hall up steps wait at top of steps
tgt: Turn left in hall. Continue straight down hall and up steps. Wait at top of steps.

src: enter hallway end up steps wait inside bathroom left of steps
tgt: Enter the hallway, walk to the end and up the steps. Wait inside the bathroom to the left of the steps.

src: after stairs down long hallway steps then by bathroom sink
tgt: After you go up the stairs turn left and head down the long hallway, go up the steps then turn left and wait by the bathroom sink.

src: walk out of laundry room turn right into first door on right just inside bathroom door
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room and turn left. Turn right and walk into the first door on the right. Stop just inside the bathroom door.

src: walk out of laundry room into hallway turn towards bedroom right hallway right into bathroom next first bathroom sink
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room into the hallway and turn left. Walk towards the bedroom and turn right continuing down the hallway. Turn right and walk into the bathroom. Stop next to the first bathroom sink.

src: turn until open door with laundry unit on right out of door hallway hallway as right in cabinet on left right into bathroom across from in cabinet
tgt: Turn around until you face and open door with a laundry unit on the right. Walk out of the door and left to face a hallway. Follow the hallway as it turns right and walk to a built in cabinet on the left. Turn right and walk into the bathroom across from the built in cabinet.

src: straight hall off left little bit first double door on right into bedroom turn at bed nightstand littler by wooden cabinet wait there
tgt: Go straight down the hall, veer off to the left a little bit.  Enter the first double door on the right and go into the bedroom. Turn left at the bed and nightstand, go a littler further and stop by the wooden cabinet.  Wait there.

src: forward toward plant left hall first right into room left into bathroom in doorway bathroom
tgt: Walk forward toward the plant. Take a left and go down the hall. Take the first right into the room, and take a left into the bathroom. Stop in the doorway to the bathroom.

src: hallway slight left room on right enter bedroom turn at bed.walk bathroom at doorway
tgt: walk down hallway and turn slight left to open room on your right. enter bedroom and turn left at bed.walk to bathroom. Stop at doorway.

src: exit room through archway right of picture of sailboat straight through hallway then near brown picture with sconce next
tgt: Exit the room through the archway to the right of the picture of the sailboat, go straight through the hallway and then stop near the brown framed picture with the sconce next to it.

src: turn toward picture of boat walk into hallway walk end of hallway sconce picture right of light
tgt: Turn toward the picture of the boat and walk into the hallway. Walk to the end of the hallway where there is the sconce and a picture to the right of the light.

src: slightly by patterned chair through door way down long hall
tgt: Go slightly left by the patterned chair and through the door way. Continue down the long hall.

src: staircase walk towards blue chair wait on carpet
tgt: Walk down staircase.  Walk towards blue chair.  Wait on carpet.

src: down stairs right down stairs right down rest of stairs straight towards red chair before
tgt: walk down stairs, curve right walk down more stairs, curve right and walk down the rest of the stairs, walk straight towards red chair, stop before you reach it.

src: stairs lounge wait in front of red chair on right
tgt: Go down the stairs and enter the lounge. Wait in front of the red chair on the right.

src: turn hallway first intersection turn wait in middle of hallway
tgt: Turn left, go down the hallway to the first intersection, turn left and wait in the middle of the hallway.

src: walk through doorway turn left hall turn
tgt: walk through doorway and turn left, go down hall and turn left, stop.

src: walk out of room into hallway corner left down hall past glass towards exit sign turn into next hallway at exit sign down towards open office doors ahead
tgt: Walk out of the room and into the hallway. Turn the corner to the left and walk down the hall past the glass walls towards the exit sign. Turn left into the next hallway at the exit sign and walk down towards the open office doors ahead.

src: exit closet turn into bathroom turn into toilet room stop
tgt: Exit the closet and turn left into the bathroom, the turn left into the toilet room and stop.

src: walk through door in front of left bathroom door left towards sink before wait by toilet
tgt: Walk straight through the door in front of you.  Stay left and enter the bathroom door to your left.  Move towards the sink, but turn left before you reach it.  Wait by the toilet.

src: exit closet turn into bathroom into toilet room stop
tgt: Exit the closet and turn into the bathroom. Go into the toilet room and stop.

src: exit bedroom head towards down stairs ahead right down bottom of stairs then through opening of wooden door ahead of slightly left
tgt: Exit the bedroom and head towards the down stairs ahead and to your right. Go down to the bottom of the stairs, then through the opening of the wooden door ahead of you and slightly to the left.

src: exit bedroom down stairs walk through open wood door past table on right wait at painting of guitarist
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Walk down the stairs. Walk through the open wood door, past the mirrored table on the right. Wait at the painting of the guitarist.

src: exit bedroom stairs through doorway left of plant with white flowers next painting of man with guitar
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go down the stairs. Go through the doorway to the left of the plant with white flowers. Stop next to the painting of a man with a guitar.

src: turn hallway.stop near plant
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallway.stop near the plant.

src: way down hallway at door left bedroom
tgt: Go all the way down the hallway, stopping at the door to the left leading to the bedroom.

src: walk straight after big door plant bed
tgt: Walk straight, after the two big door you can see a plant when you turn left you can see a bed.

src: continue staircase through doorway on right straight hallway once in front of white rug
tgt: Continue walking up the staircase, and through the doorway on the right. Walk straight down the hallway and stop once in front of the white rug.

src: walk upstairs through door on right through door on left right hall just inside door of bedroom ahead
tgt: Walk upstairs and walk through the door on your right.  Walk through the door on your left and continue right down the hall. Stop when you get just inside the door of the bedroom straight ahead.

src: up staircase at top of stairs hall until doorway on right through doorway then quick left walking towards bathroom walk past bathroom down hallway with picture on wall left through doorway of bedroom ahead of just as room
tgt: Walk up the staircase.  At the top of the stairs, keep following the hall until you get to the doorway on your right.  Go through that doorway and then make a quick left walking towards the bathroom.  Walk past the bathroom, down the hallway with a picture hanging on the wall to your left. Keep walking through the doorway of the bedroom ahead of you, and stop just as you enter the room.

src: walk towards living room through living room on wooden area just outside sliding windows
tgt: Walk towards the living room. Continue through the living room and stop on the wooden area just outside the sliding windows.

src: straight through hallway between couch stairs chairs once entryway outside
tgt: Go straight through the hallway and between the couch and stairs. Go passed the chairs and stop once you reach the entryway to the outside.

src: walk toward stairs past couch just outside on patio
tgt: Walk toward the stairs and left past the couch. Stop just outside on the patio.

src: walk past palm tree into building stop in front of couch
tgt: Walk past the palm tree and into the building. Stop in front of the couch.

src: inside through glass doors in between palm trees wait beside couch with honeycomb design
tgt: Go inside through the glass doors in between the palm trees.  Wait beside the couch with a honeycomb design.

src: straight passe water feature large entry living room couch stop near
tgt: Go straight passe the water feature and enter the large entry. Go to the living room couch and stop near it.

src: walk pass bed between bed dresser straight pass closet on left out into hallway straight left stairs on second stair from top
tgt: Walk pass the bed and between the bed and dresser going straight pass the closet on the left and out into the hallway going straight and taking a left to go down the stairs stopping on the second stair from the top.

src: turn left around bed then out door past exercise bike at top of staircase wait there
tgt: Turn to the left, go around the bed, and then out the door and past the exercise bike.  You'll stop at the top of the staircase.  Wait there.

src: around bed open doorway bedroom stop at top of stairs
tgt: Go around the bed to the open doorway. Exit the bedroom and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: up stairs turn outside by gate
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn left. Walk outside and stop by the gate.

src: stairs turn left through doorway ahead once barred door
tgt: Go straight up the stairs and turn left. Go through the doorway that is straight ahead and stop once you reach the barred door.

src: up towards stairs with closed cabinets on left up stairs turn at table with glass vase as along path storage table with shelves with sculptures on top gate right exit out gate in pathway with brick walls
tgt: Walk up towards the stairs with the closed cabinets on your left. Walk up the stairs and turn left at the table with the glass vase. As you walk along the path there will be a storage table with shelves to your left with sculptures on top. Open the gate to your right and exit out the gate. Stop in the pathway with the brick walls.

src: exit bathroom door on right bedroom across hall enter on left beside recliner
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Take the door on the right to exit the bedroom. Go across the hall. Enter on the left and stop beside the recliner.

src: exit bathroom bedroom bedroom right door forward turn living room there
tgt: Exit the bathroom, and enter the bedroom. Pass the bedroom, and turn right to exit the door. Keep walking forward, and turn left entering the living room, and stop there.

src: turn through door past bed hard right then slight left into living room area at opening
tgt: Turn around and go through the door, walk past the bed and make a hard right and then a slight left into the living room area, stop at the opening to it.

src: turn left doorway rockers at bottom of stairs stop
tgt: Turn around and go to the left. Enter the doorway to outside and pass the rockers. At the bottom of the stairs stop.

src: at washer dryer turn right out of short hallway through open door as soon as possible right through door outside from bedroom once outside right past blue chairs down wooden stairs on landing
tgt: Looking at the washer and dryer, turn to the right and walk out of the short hallway through the open door.  As soon as possible, turn right and walk through the door that leads outside from the bedroom.  Once outside, turn right and walk past the two blue rocking chairs.  Walk down the three wooden stairs and stop on the landing.

src: walk through doorway right of washer dryer turn house then chairs steps on deck
tgt: Walk through the doorway to the right of the stacked washer and dryer. Turn left and exit the house, then turn left and pass the two rocking chairs. Go down four steps and stop on the deck.

src: walk out of bathroom into hallway ahead corner right past open doors through doorway ahead at end of hall walk into room couch with stools around coffee table turn at circular statue walk through open double doors outside area near couches
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom into the hallway ahead. Turn the corner to the right and walk past the open doors and through the doorway straight ahead at the end of the hall. Walk into the room, which contains a couch with stools around a coffee table. Turn at the circular statue and walk through the open double doors to the outside area near the couches.

src: right into hall through door toward pool through door right by chair
tgt: Turn right into the hall and go left through the door toward the pool. Go out through the door to the right and stop by the chair.

src: walk out of bathroom turn walk until near table metal art right outside wait near furniture
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn left.  Walk until near the table and metal art.  Turn right and walk outside.  Wait near the furniture.

src: exit bedroom through hallway right at stairs into bedroom wait in doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom, walk through the hallway and turn right at the stairs into the bedroom. Wait in the doorway.

src: turn bedroom down hall past movie posters on wall right at first doorway after posters inside doorway
tgt: Turn around to exit the bedroom. Walk down the hall past the movie posters on the wall. Turn right at the first doorway after the  posters. Stop inside the doorway.

src: down hall right by stairs in doorway of bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn right by the stairs. Stop in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: walk straight with door on left through doorway round counters right into room on right just inside doorway
tgt: Walk straight with the door on your left. Walk through the doorway and pass the round counters and take a right into the room on the right and stop just inside the doorway.

src: down hall through double doors wait in doorway right
tgt: Walk down the hall through the double doors and wait in the doorway to the right.

src: hall toward purple sign on ground through door straight in first doorway on right
tgt: Move down the hall toward the purple sign on the ground. Go through the door. Continue straight and stop in the first doorway on your right.

src: stairs veer right living room right before piano right library area just inside entry library
tgt: Go up the stairs and veer right. Enter the living room and take a right before the piano. Take another right and enter the library area. Stop just inside the entry to the library.

src: up stairs walk past end table walk in front of piano right walk in front of shelves stop
tgt: Walk up the stairs and walk past the end table. Walk in front of the piano and turn right. Walk in front of the shelves and stop.

src: stairs straight right at piano right into small room
tgt: Go up the stairs, continue straight and take a right at the piano. Take another right into the small room.

src: walk past wine fridge on left right in front of round table down stairs right wait at bottom landing
tgt: Walk past the wine fridge on the left. Make a right in front of the round table. Walk down the stairs to the right. Wait at the bottom landing.

src: turn into large room stairs on right
tgt: Turn left into the large room and go down the stairs on the right.

src: exit kitchen living area hard right stairs then stairs bottom wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Exit the kitchen and enter the living area. Turn hard right and go to the stairs and then down the stairs to the bottom. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk by stairs enter door at end of hall
tgt: walk by stairs, enter door at end of hall.

src: down hallway past stairs towards bedroom stop wait just before into next room
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the stairs towards the bedroom. Stop and wait just before crossing into the next room.

src: pass stairs on left walk straight hallway walk into door way bedroom stop by door
tgt: Pass the stairs on the left and walk straight down the hallway. Walk into the door way to the bedroom and stop by the door.

src: down entire hallway inside of doorway zebra painting
tgt: Walk down the entire hallway and stop inside of the doorway facing a zebra painting.

src: turn hallway at door
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallway. Stop at the door.

src: walk end of hall stop by painting
tgt: Walk to the end of the hall and stop by the painting.

src: forward out of bedroom with bed at back in hallway walk forward through hall into main room walk past living room on right stairs on bottom step
tgt: Walk forward out of the bedroom with the bed at your back. In the hallway walk forward through the hall and into the main room. Walk past the living room on your right and take a left up the stairs. Stop on the bottom step.

src: exit bedroom walk straight toward area turn at stairs wait on stairs
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk straight toward the dining area. Turn left at the stairs and wait on the stairs.

src: walk out door down hall red chair turn at red chair stairs
tgt: Walk out the door and down the hall to the red chair. Turn left at the red chair and go up those stairs.

src: from stairs hallway right into bedroom
tgt: From stairs, walk down hallway turn right into bedroom.

src: up steps veer left down hall right in front of bathroom
tgt: Walk up the steps and veer left. Walk down the hall and to the right. Stop in front of the bathroom.

src: stairs dogleg left forward until laundry room ahead of corridor right right forward stop in front of entrance bathroom on left
tgt: Continue up the stairs and take a dogleg to the left. Continue forward until the laundry room is ahead of you and a corridor to the right opens up. Turn right and continue forward and stop in front of the entrance to the bathroom on your left.

src: walk across room turn right then by striped rug
tgt: Walk across the room, turn left, turn right, then turn left and wait by the striped rug.

src: with sink on right down hall into living room walking through doors at end of room into hall right in hall hall into dining room left on rug in front of giraffe chaise lounge
tgt: With the sink on your right walk down the hall and into the living room walking and taking a left through the doors at the end of the room into the hall and take a right in the hall going down the hall and into the dining room taking a left and stopping on the rug in front of the giraffe printed chaise lounge.

src: walk through open door bedroom out of bedroom door on opposite side of room through open double doors down hallway into living room on striped floor rug
tgt: Walk through the open sliding door to the bedroom. Walk out of the bedroom door on the opposite side of the room through the open double doors. Walk down the hallway into the living room. Stop on the striped floor rug.

src: turn outside through patio doors
tgt: Turn left and walk outside through the patio doors.

src: walk straight ahead past staircase toward pillar right around pillar walk into bedroom towards balcony wait on balcony near foot of bed
tgt: Walk straight ahead, past the staircase, toward the pillar. Move right around the pillar. Walk into the bedroom and go towards the balcony. Wait on the balcony near the foot of the bed.

src: walk past stairs through bedroom outside by opening outside
tgt: Walk past the stairs and through the bedroom outside. Stop by the opening to the outside.

src: move towards kitchen before kitchen turn right path straight until dining table wait here
tgt: Move towards the kitchen.  Before you reach the kitchen turn right.  Follow this path straight until you reach a dining table.  Wait here.

src: walk past dining table towards kitchen before kitchen at column right walk over circle decoration on floor into room beyond after into dining room
tgt: Walk past the dining table towards the kitchen.  Before entering the kitchen, at the column, turn right and walk over the circle decoration on the floor and into the room beyond it.  Stop after stepping into this dining room.

src: walk forward right at very first corner forward granite counter on right area room there
tgt: Walk forward and turn right at the very first corner. Keep walking forward passing the granite counter on your right. Enter another area or room, and stop there.

src: turn past brown couch straight towards fireplace turn towards open wooden doors pause inside doorway dining room
tgt: Turn left and walk past the brown couch. Walk straight towards the fireplace and turn left. Walk towards the open wooden doors. Pause inside the doorway that leads to a dining room.

src: exit room turn toward fireplace turn then right into room by fireplace wait near large double doors
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and walk toward the fireplace. Turn left and then turn right into the room by the fireplace. Wait near the large double doors.

src: walk towards room with fireplace left walk towards first set of lights right into doorway of double doors
tgt: Walk towards the room with the fireplace. Make a left and walk towards the first set of hanging lights. Make a right and walk into the doorway of the double doors.

src: exit room right right again into room next door wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room. Turn right. Turn right again to go into the room next door. Wait at the entrance.

src: exit bedroom right then sharp right into brown doorway stop
tgt: Exit the bedroom, turn right and then take a sharp right into the brown doorway and stop.

src: exit bathroom right other right enter bedroom wait
tgt: Exit bathroom, make a right, make a other right and enter bedroom and wait.

src: walk into room walk along right side of room walking in direction of stairs through last door on right just side first door on left
tgt: walk into the room and walk along the right side of the room walking in the direction of the stairs. Walk through the last door on the right. Stop just out side the first door on the left.

src: walk towards staircase right beside staircase outside first door on left
tgt: Walk straight towards the staircase, turn right beside the staircase, stop outside the first door on the left.

src: walk though large open room with round in middle walk towards stairwell through hallway right down hall large open room at end with red floor rug under chandelier
tgt: Walk though the large open room with the round tables in the middle. Walk towards the stairwell and through the hallway to the right. Walk down the hall towards the large open room at the end with a red floor rug under a chandelier.

src: bathroom walk straight hall right right into bedroom first on right right into bathroom in bathroom doorway
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk straight down the winding hall sticking to your right. Take a right into the bedroom that is first on your right and another right into the bathroom and stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: exit bathroom forward slight right hall then into first room on right into doorway of room bathroom stop
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Continue forward and make a slight right to continue down the hall. Then go into the first room on your right. Go into the doorway of that room's bathroom and stop.

src: through doorway into hallway right into bedroom with geometric picture on wall wait into bathroom
tgt: Go through the doorway into a hallway, veering to the right. Go into a bedroom with a geometric picture on the wall and wait looking into the bathroom.

src: walk along patio area past wicker chair potted plants walk in through open door with single hanging wall lamp on side into interior of home walking through large room past chairs around coffee table towards leather arm chairs in far corner of room
tgt: Walk along the patio area past the wicker chair and potted plants. Walk in through the open door with a single hanging wall lamp and windows on either side. Continue into the interior of the home walking through the large room past the chairs around the coffee table. Continue towards the leather arm chairs in the far corner of the room.

src: turn into house straight past green chairs then wait near brown chair/couches
tgt: Turn left and go into the house. Go straight past the green chairs then turn left. Wait near the brown chair/couches.

src: head indoors walk through archway in corridor wait near leather chairs
tgt: Head indoors, walk straight through the archway and stop in the corridor and wait near the leather chairs.

src: walk past tables hallway left wait by giant vase
tgt: Walk past the tables and go down the hallway to the left. Wait by the giant vase.

src: across room turn at bookshelf straight in front of large vase
tgt: go across the room and turn left at the bookshelf. Go straight and stop in front of the large vase.

src: turn white set of shelves pass by left hallway towards very large green glass vase in front of vase
tgt: Turn towards the white set of shelves, Pass by it to your left and go down the hallway towards a very large green glass vase.  Stop in front of the vase.

src: walk around bed toward balcony turn walk straight through door straight stop inside second doorway
tgt: Walk around the bed toward the balcony. Turn left and walk straight through the door. Go straight and stop inside the second doorway.

src: walk out past bed left at railing move through doorway straight ahead in doorway immediately across hallway
tgt: Walk out past the bed and make a left at the railing. Move through the doorway straight ahead. Stop in the doorway immediately across the hallway.

src: walk into bedroom past bed turn at balcony walk across patio walk into building stop in doorway across hall
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and past the bed. Turn left at the balcony and walk across the patio. Walk into the building and stop in the doorway across the hall.

src: bathroom right room stop at white planter
tgt: Leave bathroom to hallway and turn right, Walk to living room and stop at white planter.

src: turn bathroom once turn right towards chair right again down hallway double doors on end once rug
tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom. Once out turn right and walk towards the chair and turn right again and down the hallway. Enter the double doors on the end and stop once you reach the rug.

src: bathroom right towards kitchen short hallway through wooden double doors on throw rug
tgt: Leave the bathroom. Go right towards kitchen, but stop short and go down hallway. Go through wooden double doors, and stop on the throw rug.

src: bathroom right in living room then left in living room walk dining room wait
tgt: Leave the bathroom and make a right to go in the living room. Then make a left in the living room and walk to the dining room and wait.

src: bathroom right into living room in living room walk towards dining room table behind first chair on right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and take a right into the living room. In the living room walk towards the dining room table and stop behind the first chair on the right.

src: exit bathroom slight right room turn towards room slight right enter dinning room stop between table counter
tgt: exit bathroom to hall, turn slight right to living room, turn left and walk towards dinning room, turn slight right and enter dinning room, stop between table and counter.

src: turn slightly right past bed right wait in hallway with portrait items on wall
tgt: Turn slightly right, walk past the bed. Turn right and wait in the hallway with portrait items on the wall.

src: away from balcony into bedroom around bed past bed right in front of light switch on wood wall
tgt: Walk away from the balcony into the bedroom, and around the bed. Past the bed take a right, and stop in front of the light switch on the wood wall.

src: walk in building walk past chair walk around bed out of bedroom stop
tgt: Walk in the building and walk past the chair. Walk around the bed and out of the bedroom and stop.

src: walk forward away from pool room second on right at between massage next cloth
tgt: Walk forward away from the pool and and enter the room that is second on the right. Stop at the between the massage beds next to the checkered cloth.

src: walk straight slightly right door immediately right door crash-bar pass that door until picture frame on right immediately after picture quick right into door wait there
tgt: Walk straight but slightly to the right. There will be a door immediately to your right, the door has a crash-bar attached to it, walk pass that door until you pass a picture frame on your right. Immediately after that picture frame make a quick right into that door and wait there.

src: pool area right massage room enter room stop at foot of beds
tgt: Leave the pool area, and to your right there is a massage room. Enter room and stop at the foot of the beds.

src: bedroom right in hallway attic in middle of room
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right in the hallway. Enter the attic and stop in the middle of the room.

src: exit bedroom wait in unfinished room on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom, and wait in the unfinished room on the right.

src: walk into bedroom out of bedroom right into unfinished room wait in unfinished room
tgt: Walk into the bedroom. Walk out of the bedroom and take a right into the unfinished room. Wait in the unfinished room.

src: walk past bed in front of hammock
tgt: Walk straight past the bed, and stop in front of the hammock.

src: forward of bed at door exit
tgt: Go forward to edge of bed. Stop at door exit.

src: forward on rug walk past bed just bed
tgt: Go forward, walking on the rug.  Walk past the bed and stop just bed.

src: straight room turn stairs on left steps top
tgt: Go straight to exit the room. Turn left and go up the stairs on the left. Wait three steps to the top.

src: with bed immediate left forward bedroom after bedroom head stairs on left first flight on last step prior first landing
tgt: With the bed to your immediate left, walk forward to exit the bedroom. After leaving bedroom, head to the stairs on your left and climb the first flight, stopping on the last step prior to the first landing.

src: turn right room once out turn up stairs in front of once last step from top
tgt: Turn right and exit the room. Once out, turn left and walk up the stairs in front of you. Stop once you reach the last step from the top.

src: enter house wait at couch inside door house
tgt: Enter the house, wait at the couch inside the door to the house.

src: walk towards house between patio into living room once past doorway in living room
tgt: Walk towards the house, between the patio couches into the living room. Stop once you are past the doorway in the living room.

src: walk forward up steps onto patio door step inside wait
tgt: walk forward up the two steps onto the patio.  go to open door and step inside and wait.

src: turn degrees down hallway turn right into entryway stand in big circle in front of doors restaurant
tgt: Turn around 180 degrees walk down the hallway turn right into the entryway and stand in the big circle in front of the doors to the restaurant.

src: walk down hall past large glass windows wait on large rug in front of glass doors
tgt: Walk straight down the hall and past the large glass windows. Wait on the large rug in front of the glass doors.

src: walk down hallway slight right towards door on circle art on floor
tgt: walk straight down hallway , turn slight right towards entry door, stop on circle art on floor.

src: turn around past table wait in front of large double doors at end of table
tgt: Turn around and walk past the table. Wait in front of the large double doors at the end of the table.

src: turn across room large wooden entry way on opposite side

tgt: Go past the big clock on the wall and through the door on the left, go down the hallway and enter the room on the left just before the stairs.

tgt: Walk into the office and exit. In the hall go straight and enter the theater through the first door on your left. Stop on the carpet nest to the ottoman table.

tgt: Walk straight and turn left to exit the door. Walk and then make another left to enter a theater room. Stop at the entrance of the room.

tgt: Walk out of the room and straight across the hall. Turn right at the stairs and walk down the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

tgt: Walk out of the unfinished room past the construction supplies in the closet and continue into the hallway. Walk down the hallway past the bedrooms and closet doors. Turn and begin to walk down the stairway.

src: room walk straight hallway until stairs on right stairs on with stairs in front of
tgt: Leave the room and walk straight down the hallway until you get to some stairs on your right.  Go down the stairs and stop on the landing with two more stairs in front of you.

tgt: Exit the bathroom from the door closest to the sink. Turn left and go straight down the hallway, entering the first door into the study. Go through the study to the door on the right, then take the door into the bathroom.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and make a sharp turn right. Then turn left and walk out of the small room. Turn left in the hallway and walk into the room with the shelves. Walk right past the table and chairs into the bedroom. Walk left into the bathroom and stop.

tgt: Exit the bathroom through the doorway on the right, go straight through the next doorway, make a left and go through the brown double doors, go through the opening in the bookshelves on the right, make a left into the bathroom, take a step in and then stop.

tgt: Go straight and turn right. Head up the staircase. At the top of the staircase, stop.

tgt: move down the hallway to the left of the stairs.

tgt: Turn around 180 degrees, go down the hallway.  Stop next to the minifridge.

tgt: Walk out of the kitchen near the pie plates. Turn into the hall before the stairs, and go into the first door, looking in the doorway of the restroom.

tgt: Exit the kitchen using the door on the left then turn right and go through the door and then turn left and go into the bathroom and stop at the entrance.

tgt: Walk out of the bedroom, and go straight. Go into the room straight ahead. Stop once you pass the doorway.

tgt: Walk past the foot of the bed out the door into the hallway.  Keep walking straight until you enter a room with a dark round footstool on a white rug in the center of the room.  Stop when you have stepped into this room.

tgt: Exit the kitchen into the living room. Go past the couches then turn right after you pass the rug and the stairs turn left and wait by the wooden wardrobe.

Walk into the next room, walk across the rug and past the white overstuffed chair, heading for the front door. Walk through the entryway, over the rug, slightly to the left, towards the umbrella stand by the front door. Take a couple more steps towards the living room.Stop when you get to the white chair.

In the hallway, turn right leaving the mirror on your left and continue down the hallway until the floor changes from stone tile to carpet at the entrance to the exercise room.

There is a doorway with stairs on your right off the hallway.  Walk past that doorway.  Enter the room with the wood floor in front of you and stop in front of the grey couch.

Pass by the curtained divider on your left and the bed on your left until you have to take a step upwards, leaving the purple floor and standing on a light grey floor of a bathing area.

tgt: Walk outside and past the four chairs on the deck.  When you get to the table, turn left and stop in the doorway of the room with the fur rug.
