tgt: Go outside and walk to the left of the pool. Turn into the last room on the left. It's the room with a glass desk and two gray rugs. Stop in the doorway.

src: onto patio walk past pool office through door on far left in doorway
tgt: Go out onto the patio and walk past the pool. Enter the office through the door on the far left. Stop in the doorway.

src: walk top of stairs wait by lamp
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs and wait by the lamp.

src: turn up stairs beside table with lamp
tgt: turn left, walk up stairs, stop beside the table with the lamp.

src: stairs then
tgt: Go up the stairs then stop.

src: door ahead of straight until steps wait there
tgt: Go out the door straight ahead of you and wall straight until you get to steps. Wait there.

src: walk out double wooden doors in front of once out right straight at bottom of steps
tgt: Walk out the double wooden doors in front of you. Once out, turn right. Keep walking straight and stop at the bottom of the steps.

src: through open doorway straight ahead right wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go through the open doorway straight ahead. Turn right. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit room right of tv hall turn towards bathroom right wait in entrance bedroom
tgt: Exit the room to the right of the TV and go down the hall. Turn left and walk towards the bathroom. Turn right and wait in the entrance to the bedroom.

src: head through doorway into small hallway turn toward stairs past stairs toward bathroom right into bedroom stop at side of bed
tgt: Head through the doorway into the small hallway and turn left toward the stairs.  Go past the stairs and toward the bathroom.  Turn right into the bedroom and stop at the side of the bed.

src: living room through door on right past door on left turn towards bathroom right bedroom
tgt: Leave the living room through the door on the right, walk past the door on the left, turn left, walk towards the bathroom, turn right, and enter the bedroom.

src: exit den right past dining table wait in area by chairs
tgt: Exit the den, turn right and walk past the dining table. Wait in the sitting area by the chairs.

src: turn right exit out of office left wait by white chair
tgt: Turn to the right and exit out of the office. Take a left and wait by the white chair.

src: home office immediate left ahead in front of coffee table sofas
tgt: Leave the home office and take an immediate left.  Continue ahead and wait in front of the coffee table and sofas.

src: enter building turn up staircase on left as up top of stairs
tgt: Enter the building and turn left.  Walk up the staircase on your left.  It curves around as you walk up it.  Stop when you get to the top of the stairs.

src: walk into front entrance of home walk towards stairs upper level up staircase stop at top near wall with wall art of people
tgt: Walk into the front entrance of the home. Walk towards the stairs leading to the upper level. Walk up the staircase and stop at the top near the wall with wall art of people sitting.

src: forward into house left walk stairs on stair second from top
tgt: Walk forward into the house and take a left. Walk to the stairs and go up them. Stop on the stair second from the top.

src: through hallway right wait at light switch
tgt: Go through the hallway, make a right and wait at the light switch.

src: at top of stairs turn into hallway right as hallway before dining room at plant pictures
tgt: At top of stairs turn left into hallway, turn right as hallway turns. Stop before entering dining room at plant and pictures.

src: walk forward right at photographs
tgt: Walk forward and turn right. Stop at the photographs.

src: stairs until paintings
tgt: Go down the stairs until you reach the paintings.

src: turn around stairs as soon as not stairs stop on landing in hallway wall with several pictures in black frames
tgt: Turn around to walk down the stairs. As soon as you cannot go down any more stairs, Stop. You will be on a landing, in a hallway and facing a wall with several pictures in black frames.

src: stairs stop at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk around railing of staircase turn continue railing stop at next flight of stairs
tgt: Walk around the railing of the staircase, turn left continue following the railing, stop at the next flight of stairs.

src: walk along upstairs banister rail corner along banister rail through open door walk base of stairwell upstairs
tgt: Walk along the upstairs banister rail. Turn the corner and continue along the banister rail through the open door. Walk to the base of the stairwell leading upstairs.

src: walk straight turn left walk past banister hall other set of stairs steps then wait
tgt: Walk straight. Turn to the left and walk past the banister.  Keep walking down the hall the other set of stairs.  Go up 3 steps and then wait.

src: exit bathroom toward room then room door on right side straight past pool table past stairs wait there by light switches
tgt: Exit the bathroom toward the room then exit the room using the door on the right side. Go straight past the pool table and past the stairs and wait there by the three light switches.

src: walk over long hallway with windows just past pool table
tgt: Take a walk over the the long hallway with all the windows that is just past the pool table.

src: walk out of bathroom through bedroom turn outside bedroom walk past stairs walk through entryway stop
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and through the bedroom. Turn left outside the bedroom and walk past the stairs. Walk through the entryway and stop.

src: down stairs stop in front of first doorway on left
tgt: Walk down the stairs, stop in front of the first doorway on the left.

src: down stairs landing right then next set of stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the stairs to the landing and make a right.  Then go down the next set of stairs and wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs once off stairs on next floor at bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs. Stop once you are off the stairs and on the next floor at the bottom.

src: toward round desk left down hallway through glass doors on right desk on left
tgt: Go to the left toward passed the round desk. Go left, down the hallway, through the glass doors on the right, and stop passed the desk on the left.

src: exit bathroom walk straight past front desk turn at end of desk into hallway walk past black urns until large black urn in front of right in next room wait in center of
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk straight past the front desk. Turn left at the end of the desk into a hallway. Walk straight past two black urns until you see large black urn in front of you. Turn right in to the next room and wait in the center of it.

src: turn towards reception desk past desk down hallway open glass doors right into room just inside
tgt: Turn left and walk towards the reception desk.  Go past the desk and down the hallway entering the open glass doors to your right.  Walk into that room and stop just inside.

src: walk along hall with guardrail past stairs into first doorway into bedroom on left between bed double closet doors
tgt: Walk along the hall with the guardrail past the stairs. Turn into the first doorway into the bedroom on the left. Stop between the bed and double closet doors.

src: with banister on right hallway past stairs on left bedroom last room on left at foot of bed
tgt: With the banister on your right, head down the hallway past the stairs on your left and enter the bedroom, which is the last room, on your left. Stop at the foot of the bed.

src: with railings on right down hallway into bedroom on left after stairs room stop at foot of bed
tgt: With the railings on your right, walk down the hallway and turn into the bedroom on the left after passing the stairs.  Enter the room and stop at the foot of the bed.

src: walk along low glass wall down hallway.continue hallway along glass wall past laundry room walk through next open door into bedroom with armchair near foot of bed
tgt: Walk along the low glass wall down the hallway.Continue down the hallway along the glass wall and past the laundry room. Walk through the next open door which leads into a bedroom with an armchair near the foot of the bed.

src: walk down hallway turn on room right after dryer in doorway
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway, turn left on room right after washer and dryer, stop in doorway.

src: down hallway turn left wait in doorway of bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hallway turn to your left and wait in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: turn right straight then at near sofa
tgt: turn right go straight then stop at near sofa.

src: move through room with bed right through entry way outdoor patio area few feet behind long couch
tgt: Move through the room with the bed to your right. Pass through the entry way and enter the outdoor patio area. Stop a few feet behind the long couch.

src: walk out of bedroom onto patio on patio stop behind couch
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom onto the patio. On the patio stop behind the couch.

src: walk over mat inside once inside room through door on right wall in hallway turn just before outside
tgt: Walk over the mat and inside.  Once inside, leave the room through the door on the right wall.  In the hallway, turn left.  Stop just before going outside.

src: walk through sitting room wait by front door
tgt: Walk through the sitting room and wait by the front door.

src: walk into house right past chair through entryway into hallway turn by door
tgt: Walk into the house. Walk right past the chair through the entryway and into the hallway. Turn left. and stop by the door.

src: turn right towards kitchen into hallway walk into room
tgt: Turn right towards kitchen. Go into hallway and walk into dining room.

src: walk through archway with thermostat on wall toward piano just before
tgt: walk through the archway with the thermostat on the wall.  Walk toward the piano and stop just before it.

src: turn toward kitchen through doorway right of breakfast bar down hall bathroom on right side as straight piano
tgt: Turn toward the kitchen, and walk through the doorway to the right of the breakfast bar.  Walk down the hall, passing the bathroom on your right side as you walk.  Walk straight and stop when you get to the piano.

src: room ropes at top of stairs toward chandelier
tgt: leave sitting room, jump the ropes and stop at top of stairs looking toward chandelier.

src: walk out of area stairs stair second from top stop
tgt: Walk out of the sitting area and go the stairs. Go down one stair to the second from the top and stop.

src: around table head towards that down little forward towards chandelier wait at stairs before
tgt: Go around the table and head towards stairs that lead down. Walk a little forward towards the chandelier and wait at the stairs before going down.

tgt: Turn around to leave the room. Walk down the hall and turn right at the large doorway across from the water fountain. Walk towards the stars. Walk past the stairs to the space on the right. Walk under the stairs. Turn right and stop halfway down the hall.

src: bathroom right into main room walk past service buffet table stairs first right in front of bench below bridal room sign
tgt: Leave the bathroom and take a right into the main room. Walk past the service buffet table  and stairs, and take the first right. Stop in front of the bench below the bridal room sign.

src: exit bathroom right enter main lobby turn towards room with stairs on right lights slight right white table on right right hallway at bench
tgt: Exit bathroom to hallway. turn right and enter main lobby. Turn left and walk towards room with stairs on the right and hanging lights. Turn slight right walking passed white table to hallway on right. Turn right and walk down hallway. Stop at the bench.

src: walk straight until lounge chairs right hallway through glass double doors wait there
tgt: Walk straight until you see three lounge chairs. Turn right and continue down the hallway. Go through the glass double doors and wait there.

src: walk past lounge chairs down hallway wait in room near snack bar
tgt: Walk past the lounge chairs and down the hallway. Wait in the room near the snack bar.

src: turn left hallway on right past water dispense hallway until set of wooden doors with glass panes enter through doors right before large column in center
tgt: Turn to your left and go down the hallway on your right. Walking past the water dispense. Continue down that hallway until you hit a set of wooden doors with glass panes. Enter through those doors and wait right before the large column in the center.

tgt: Walk up the stairs, and take a left towards the dresser. Stop right after you walk through the door that leads to the bathroom.

tgt: Turn to your right 90 degrees and walk into the bedroom.  Go to the right of the bed and walk forward.  Walk in the open bathroom door and stop just inside the bathroom.

src: up stairs into bedroom turn into bathroom stop
tgt: Walk up the stairs into the bedroom. Turn left and walk into the bathroom and stop.

src: shower turn around end of shower room black cabinet turn right down hall hallway past laundry baskets open door on right right into room walk table in middle of room
tgt: FACING THE SHOWER TURN AROUND AND WALK TO THE END OF THE SHOWER ROOM, FACING A BLACK CABINET TURN RIGHT AND WALK DOWN THE HALL, CONTINUE DOWN THE HALLWAY PAST THE LAUNDRY BASKETS TOWARDS THE OPEN DOOR ON THE RIGHT, TURN RIGHT AND WALK INTO THE ROOM, WALK TO THE TABLE IN THE MIDDLE OF THE ROOM.

src: from showers walk straight right hallway straight baskets on floor right after baskets room stop
tgt: Turn away from the showers, walk straight, turn right down the hallway, go straight passed the baskets on the floor, turn right after the baskets, enter the room and stop.

src: walk into hallway right down hall right into room stop
tgt: Walk into the hallway and turn right. Walk down the hall and turn right. Walk into the room and stop.

src: enter door into bedroom past foot of bed right into bathroom wait just inside bathroom in front of open door
tgt: Enter the door and go into the bedroom past the foot of the bed. Turn right and go into the bathroom. Wait just inside the bathroom in front of the open door.

src: turn around in bedroom right int bathroom wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk in the bedroom. Turn right int the bathroom and wait there.

src: indoors bed right straight into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Go indoors. Pass the bed and turn right. Go straight into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: through bedroom doorway across from mirror in bedroom through first door on left bathtub
tgt: Go through the bedroom doorway across from the mirror. In the bedroom go through the first door on the left. Go to the bathtub.

src: mirror on right turn turn straight until into bathroom wait near entrance
tgt: When you pass the mirror on the right turn left. Turn left and walk straight until you go into the bathroom. Wait near the entrance.

tgt: Turn around and walk past the mirror. Then turn left and enter the bedroom. Then turn left and walk into the master bathroom.

src: exit bathroom turn on white rug
tgt: Exit the bathroom, turn left, stop on the white rug.

src: into hallway turn wait in room at end of hallway
tgt: Go into the hallway and turn left. Wait in the room at the end of the hallway.

src: exit bathroom turn hallway towards bedroom before white carpet
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Proceed down the hallway towards the bedroom and stop before you make it to the white carpet.

src: stairs at top red path splits
tgt: Go up the stairs and stop at the top, where the red path splits.

src: stairs wait near chandelier
tgt: Go up the stairs. Wait near the chandelier.

src: up wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs at bottom turn right head towards chairs in front of left bathroom at sink
tgt: Continue down the stairs. At the bottom turn right and head towards the two chairs in front of you. Turn left and enter the bathroom. Stop at the sink.

src: down stairs right down at bottom of stairs right past christmas tree walk past chairs left doorway through doorway on left bathroom stopping in front of sink
tgt: Walk down the stairs and take a right to keep going down. At the bottom of the stairs take a  right and go past the Christmas tree. Walk past the chairs o the left and go to the doorway. Go through the doorway on the left and enter the bathroom stopping in front of the sink.

tgt: Turn left and walk down the stairs.  Walk past the Christmas tree.  Walk between a blue and red chair.  Then you'll see a doorway to the bathroom.  Walk through that and then wait.

tgt: Walk towards the desk with burnt orange chair, take a sharp left at the window, walk straight towards the kitchen and stop in front of the ridge.

src: bathroom by left with toilet behind straight through foyer into kitchen next white pillar in kitchen
tgt: Leave the bathroom by taking a left with the toilet behind you. walk straight through the foyer into the kitchen. Stop next to the white pillar in the kitchen.

src: exit bathroom enter kitchen at outside door
tgt: exit bathroom, enter kitchen, stop at outside door.

src: walk past workout equipment turn into bedroom right out of bedroom in front of desk
tgt: Walk past the workout equipment and turn left. Walk into the bedroom  and turn right. Walk out of the bedroom and stop in front of the desk.

tgt: Turn towards the left and walk out of the gym room. Turn left again and walk down the hall. Enter the bedroom, then turn right. Enter the office and stop next to the desk.

src: turn towards hallway picture on wall correct way left hall hallway dead into bedroom right room wait next corner of desk
tgt: Turn around and move towards the hallway. There is a picture hanging on the wall to let you know your going the correct way. You are going to turn left and travel down the hall. When the hallway dead ends into a bedroom, turn right.  Enter the room and wait next to the closest corner of the desk.

src: walk across room wait through second door on right in bathroom
tgt: Walk across the room and wait through the second door on the right, in the bathroom .

src: turn right door on right stairs once door at bathroom
tgt: Turn right and walk to the door on the right 2nd closest to the stairs. Stop once you enter the door and are looking at the bathroom .

src: straight into fourth door from right wait by sink
tgt: Go straight and go into the fourth door from the right. Wait by the sink.

src: walk forward through hallway left at first door on right
tgt: Walk forward through the hallway, make a left, stop at the first door on the right.

src: walk down hall turn into first doorway on right
tgt: Walk straight down the hall and turn left. walk into the first doorway on the right and stop.

src: walk in direction of windows let at next hallway right into first office in doorway
tgt: Walk in the direction of the windows. Take a let at the next hallway. Take a right into the first office, and stop in the doorway.

tgt: Exit bedroom to hallway, turn left and follow hallway straight to beach painting. Turn right into bedroom. Turn left into closet, stop in middle of closet.

tgt: Turn around and exit the door behind you beside the white cabinets beside it. Turn right into the bedroom. Turn left into the walk in closet. Stop inside the closet facing the corner with the wicker basket.

tgt: Exit and turn left. Keep walking towards the big painting on the wall, and turn towards the room that is placed on its right. Enter the bedroom, and turn left, and enter the empty closet, and stop there.

src: walk through bathroom doorway straight hallway straight ahead walk through bedroom just of bathroom around out room straight into first door on left stop
tgt: Walk through bathroom doorway, walk straight down hallway to bedroom straight ahead, walk straight through bedroom to just infront of the bathroom, turn around and walk out the room, walk straight into first door on the left and stop.

tgt: Exit the bathroom, walk down the hallway toward the stairs, turn hard left to enter the bedroom to the left of the closet, wait at the foot of the bed.

src: bathroom out of bedroom into hall in hall sharp left into bedroom on left of double door closet in bedroom stop at foot of bed
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go out of the bedroom into the hall. In the hall take a sharp left and go into the bedroom on the left of the double door closet. In the bedroom stop at the foot of the bed.

src: turn degrees hallway first doorway on right into bathroom just inside door
tgt: Turn around 180 degrees and go down the hallway.  Take the first doorway on the right and walk into the bathroom. Stop just inside the door.

src: with cabinets on left corridor towards stairs before stairs right bathroom next shower
tgt: With the cabinets on your left, move down the corridor towards the stairs. Before you reach the stairs, turn right and enter the bathroom, stopping next to the shower.

src: turn around down hallway until opening on right door on right in bathroom door ahead of
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hallway until you see an opening on your right. Enter the door on your right, and stop in the bathroom door ahead of you.

src: up stairs into open bedroom
tgt: Walk up the stairs and into the open bedroom.

src: turn up steps office area bedroom area by closes left wait there
tgt: Turn left walk up the steps and leave the office area. Exit the bedroom area by the closes door to your left. Wait there.

tgt: Walk up the small stairs through the doorway, then walk straight through till you reach the open on the left. Walk towards the doorway, and stop directly in the middle of it.

tgt: Walk past the picture and out of the kitchen and turn right. Walk through the doorway on the right and down the stairs. Stop next to the end of the hand rail.

src: turn small kitchen through doorway on right down stairs midway stairs wait there
tgt: Turn left and enter the small kitchen. Go through the doorway on the right and walk down the stairs. Stop midway down the stairs and wait there.

tgt: Exit the kitchen through the doorway next to the bananas. Turn right and head down the stairs. Stop about halfway down the stairs.

tgt: Walk out of the room and turn right. Walk out of the bathroom and walk to the right of the bed. Turn right and walk into the closet and stop.

tgt: Leave toilet to bathroom, turn slight right enter bedroom, Walk to right side of bed. Turn right into closet and stop.

tgt: Walk through the bathroom and exit from the door on the right. Walk straight until you get to the bed, then turn right and wait inside the closet.

tgt: Walk up the steps and turn right out of the garage. Walk over to the stairs and walk up. Turn left at the top of the stairs and stop just inside the bedroom.

src: turn around into house then stairs top then near door
tgt: Turn around and walk into the house. Then walk up the stairs to the top then turn left and stand near the door.

src: walk into house.. stairs room on left in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk into the house.. Go up the stairs. And enter the room on the left. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: walk in direction of purple orange chairs stairs around silver wall exit into patio once
tgt: Walk in the direction of the purple and orange chairs, and keep going stairs. Walk around the silver wall, and exit into the patio. Stop once you exit.

src: turn right red purple furniture right hall outside then next red sculpture
tgt: Turn right and go passed the red and purple furniture. Go to the right and follow the hall outside. Then stop next to the red sculpture.

tgt: Go past the glass table and chairs. Then go past the red and purple couches. Go past the large stainless steel wall. Turn right and go out the large glass door. Wait near the red statue.

tgt: Exit the closet and go through the doorway on your left.  Enter the bedroom then walk to the double doors on your right.  Walk down the hallway to your right and stop under the archway behind the blue chair.

tgt: Exit walk-in closet through door. Take a slight left and walk through doorway. Walk into the bedroom. Take a slight right and walk through double doors. Take a left upon exiting the bedroom. Walk to the doorway to the right. Wait there.

src: walk into room with clock through bench mirror by light switches towards very large living room with front doors
tgt: Walk into the room with the clock through it, bast a bench and a mirror, and stop by some light switches facing towards a very large living room with front doors.

tgt: Leave the room and walk down the hallway until you pass two chairs.  Stop in the doorway of the room on the left (it is directly after the second chair).

tgt: Exit the bathroom by walking forward down the wooden-floored hallway. Continue ahead until you pass the first chair on your left. Bear left around the second brown leather chair. Stop just short of the open doorway. Then wait here.

src: exit bathroom go forward til by second chair
tgt: exit the bathroom go. Move forward til you are by the second chair.

src: walk past gold garbage under crystal lighting
tgt: Walk past gold garbage can. Wait under crystal lighting.

tgt: Walk straight ahead past the elevators.  When you get to the "staff only" door, stop there and wait.

tgt: Walk straight down the hallway with the elevators on your right. Stop in front of the last elevator on the right.

tgt: Leave bar area across sitting room through double doors. Turn right into hallway and enter main room. Stop on antelope rug.

tgt: Go out the double doors on the left then turn right and go down the hallway all the way down until you get to a room with a rug that has an antelope and stop there.

tgt: Walk straight across the room and exit out the double wood and glass doors on the left. Once out the doors, Turn right and walk down the hallway and enter the door at the end. Stop once inside the room facing the large windows.

src: from bedroom down hall turn at stairs on top of stairs
tgt: From bedroom walk down hall and turn left at stairs. Stop on top of stairs.

src: hallway turn again few steps downstairs then
tgt: Go down hallway, turn left and left again and take a few steps downstairs, and then stop.

src: turn after banister on left stairs wait there
tgt: Turn left after the banister on the left and walk down three stairs. Wait there.

tgt: Exit the room and turn left. Walk toward the pool. Stop between the pool and treadmill.

src: turn room turn at exercise bikes walking in front of pool
tgt: Turn around and leave the room. Turn left at the exercise bikes. Keep walking and stop in front of the pool.

src: massage room left next brown door left of lounge chairs
tgt: Leave the massage room, and take a left. Stop next to the brown door to the left of the lounge chairs.

tgt: Exit bedroom, move toward swinging doors, and enter bedroom bathroom, Wait at entrance.

src: bedroom hall straight enter through swinging doors bedroom on left stop
tgt: Leave the bedroom and enter the hall. Go straight and enter through the swinging doors. Enter the bedroom on the left, and stop.

tgt: Exit the bedroom, go straight through the room and step through the swivel doors and step in and stop.

tgt: Turn right and go outside using the large glass doors. Walk toward the pool. Wait near the BBQ.

tgt: Walk and turn right towards the outside through the glass door. Keep walking forward passing the sofas on your left, and stop in front of the pool.

tgt: Turn right towards the glass door, and exit outside. Walk forward passing the entire sofa set with a coffee table on the left. Walk forward and stop near the pool area.

tgt: Exit bathroom to bedroom and continue through to hallway into kitchen. Stop at microwave.

src: exit bathroom left bedroom walk past built-in desk on right wait at built-in microwave
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Make a left, and exit the bedroom. Walk past the built-in desk on the right. Wait at the built-in microwave.

src: exit bathroom into bedroom right through door forward into kitchen wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom into the bedroom. Turn right and walk through the door. Walk forward into the kitchen. Wait there.

src: stairs on fifth step from bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop on the fifth step from the bottom.

src: down stairs wait just before bottom
tgt: Walk down the stairs and wait just before the bottom.

src: stairs on fifth step from bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs. Stop on the fifth step from the bottom.

src: path in front of large cactus
tgt: walk down path to left and stop in front of large cactus.

src: down walkway wait by entrance
tgt: Walk down the walkway and wait by the entrance.

tgt: Walk along the patio past the purple chairs along the glass barrier wall. Continue towards the open door at the end of the wall that leads inside.

tgt: Walk up the set of steps to the right. Walk right past the black chair and table. Walk past the glass conference room wall and stop by the plywood trunk.

tgt: Go up the stairs, go through the room to the right of the desks and turn right into the hallway and then stop.

tgt: Go up the stairs. Turn right and walk about twenty steps down the hallway then stop.

tgt: Walk up stairs,  turn right walk down hall, and wait by light switch.

tgt: Walk into the room and right past the table and chairs. Stop just past the grate wall.

src: through door straight right table then on other side of wooden lattice
tgt: Go through the door and go straight. Turn right to go passed the table and then stop on the other side of the wooden lattice.

src: walk towards room with dining room table walk past on left past doorway with wooden wall on right immediatly after
tgt: Walk towards the room with the dining room table, and walk past it on your left. Walk past the doorway with the wooden wall on your right, and stop immediatly after it.

src: through archway ahead rug hallway right of stairs through hallway right around bookcase hall exercise room with treadmill
tgt: Go through the archway ahead.  Pass the rug and enter the hallway to the right of the stairs. Go through the hallway go right around the bookcase and continue down the hall to the exercise room with the treadmill.

src: walk out of large passageway over oriental rug into doorway just past right into room left tall bookshelf straight into room with treadmills in
tgt: Walk out of the large passageway, over the oriental rug, and into the doorway just past it. Make a right into the room. Make a left around the tall bookshelf. Walk straight into the room with the treadmills in it.

src: walk right little veer right in big room in kitchen route doorway in kitchen through in little workout room right there by tv wait
tgt: Walk to the right a little. Veer to the right when you get in the big room.  Keep going and you'll be in the kitchen.  Take the route to the doorway in the kitchen and go through it.  You'll be in a little workout room.  Stop right there by the tv.  Wait.

src: exit room walk straight hall wait in entrance laundry room on left
tgt: Exit the room and walk straight down the hall. Wait in the entrance to the laundry room on the left.

src: indoors through black door then into second door on left wait by washer
tgt: Go indoors and straight through a black door and then go into the second door on your left and wait by the washer.

src: into hallway andgo nect washing machine wait there
tgt: Go into the hallway andgo nect to the washing machine and wait there.

src: exit room turn into room next door turn after stairs way until door outside wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go into the room next door. Turn left after you pass the stairs and go all the way down until you exit the door and go outside. Wait there.

src: walk out door straight ahead right of tv once turn left door walk other side of railing turn hallway along railing in doorway at end outside
tgt: Walk out the door straight ahead to the right of the TV. Once out turn left and enter the door. Walk to the other side of the railing and turn left. Continue down the hallway along the railing and stop in the doorway at the end leading outside.

src: exit playroom turn past stairs next patio door
tgt: Exit the playroom and turn left . Walk past  the stairs  and stand next to the patio door.

src: turn door behind once turn left across room before pool with wood door left
tgt: Turn around and exit the door behind you. Once out turn left and go across the room. Stop before you reach the pool with the wood door to your left.

src: exit room then head straight treadmills then right before pool
tgt: Exit the room then turn left and head straight. Pass the treadmills then stop right before getting to the pool.

src: head toward pool between treadmill pool
tgt: Head toward the pool. Stop between the treadmill and the pool.

src: walk between couch chair around counter right past refrigerator wait there
tgt: Walk left between couch and chair to kitchen, turn left and walk around counter, go right past the refrigerator, wait there.

src: walk straight toward kitchen stand near fridge
tgt: Walk straight toward the kitchen. Stand near the fridge.

src: walk towards refrigerator left of refrigerator
tgt: Walk towards the refrigerator. Stop to the left of the refrigerator.

src: down stairs hallway ahead left past stairs turn wait near doorway bathroom in next hallway
tgt: Walk down the stairs and continue down the hallway that is ahead and to the left. Walk past the stairs and turn left. Wait near the doorway to the bathroom in the next hallway.

src: turn around down remainder of steps slightly left then way through door until door hard left door stop
tgt: Turn around and walk down the remainder of the steps, head slightly to the left and then make your way through the door, continue to walk until you see a door, turn hard left towards the door and stop.

src: stairs then dogleg left corridor forward past stairs downwards on right left bathroom step through opening then
tgt: Continue down the stairs, then take a dogleg to the left to continue down the corridor. Keep going forward past the stairs leading downwards on your right. When you can go to the left towards the bathroom, step through the opening and then stop.

src: leave bar area down stairs landing stop
tgt: Leave bar area to stairs going down, go down stairs to first landing and stop.

src: stairs on left about steps bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs on the left. Wait about five steps to the bottom.

src: down stairs second landing stop wait near banister
tgt: Walk down the stairs to the second landing. Stop and wait near the banister.

src: hallway turn into laundry room at laundry machines
tgt: Walk down hallway and turn left into laundry room. Stop at laundry machines.

src: down hallway walk past chair railing right into laundry room stop
tgt: Walk down the hallway. Walk past the chair and the railing. Turn right and walk into the laundry room and stop.

src: walk forward then at doorway
tgt: walk forward then turn left, stop at the doorway.

src: exit bathroom right bedroom walk past backside of green sofa turn forward on edge of gray carpet next cowhide cube
tgt: Exit the bathroom.  Turn right and exit the bedroom. Walk past the backside of the green sofa and turn left. Walk forward and wait on the edge of the gray carpet next to the cowhide cube.

src: walk towards right on carpet door on right past back of couch turn at plant on right side on cow seat next patterned stool on right
tgt: walk towards bed, turn right on carpet and walk out door on right, straight past back of couch, turn left at plant, walk on right side on cow patterned seat, stop next to cow patterned stool on your right.

src: exit bathroom walk past bed on left bedroom door walk between grey green couches wait at cowhide ottoman
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Walk past the bed on the left. Exit the bedroom door. Walk between the grey and green couches. Wait at the cowhide ottoman.

src: down hallway until bedroom way down hallway wait near bed
tgt: Walk down the hallway until you get to a bedroom all the way down the hallway. Wait near the bed.

src: hallway in bedroom end wait next bed
tgt: Go down the hallway and go in the bedroom the end. Wait next to the bed.

src: forward way until bedroom visible white bed visible in front of very end of corner enter inside there
tgt: Keep walking forward all the way until you see a bedroom visible. A white bed should be visible in front of you towards the very end of the corner. Enter inside, and stop there.

src: through hall right after tub inside gym
tgt: Go through the hall. Turn right after you pass the tub. Stop inside the gym.

src: walk towards room with bath from bathroom walk towards room with gym equipment just inside gym room
tgt: Walk towards the room with the bath. From the bathroom walk towards the room with gym equipment and stop just inside the gym room.

src: straight into bathroom around bathtub into right doorway exercise room
tgt: Go straight into the bathroom, around the bathtub, and into the right doorway to the exercise room.

src: pass grand piano green chair straight into room wait near fireplace
tgt: Pass the grand piano. Pass the green chair and go straight into the room. Wait near the fireplace.

src: turn around hallway dining area then right center doorway wait near fireplace
tgt: Turn around to walk down the hallway, pass the dining area, then veer right to enter the center doorway. Wait near the fireplace.

src: walk into foyer straight ahead into office in office doorway
tgt: Walk into the foyer. Go straight ahead into the office. Stop in the office doorway.

src: stairs way top floor at top of stairs right in front of first panel of banister
tgt: Go up the stairs all the way to the top floor. At the top of the stairs take a right and stop in front of the first panel of the banister.

src: up stairs onto deck
tgt: Walk up the stairs and onto the deck.

src: up stairs right at top wait near glass guardrail
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Turn right at the top and wait near the glass guardrail.

src: down stairs through white door on right down steps stop
tgt: Walk down the stairs and through the white door on your right. Walk down two more steps and stop.

src: stairs at bottom right before table right into doorway few steps stairs then
tgt: Go down the stairs and at the bottom make a right before the table, make a right and go into the doorway, take a few steps down the stairs and then stop.

src: stairs right right past desk through doorway wait in front of statute
tgt: Go down stairs and turn right. Turn right past desk and go through doorway. Wait in front of statute.

src: exit room through door in opposite corner from kitchen then through door immediate into laundry room
tgt: Exit the room through the door in the opposite corner from where you started and enter the kitchen. Then go through the door opening to your immediate left into the laundry room.

src: walk past dining room table chairs turn through doorway turn by sink
tgt: Walk past the dining room table and chairs and turn left. Walk through the doorway and turn left. Stop by the sink.

src: pass table chairs then door on right left into room next door wait by sink
tgt: Pass the table and chairs then turn left and go out the door on the right. Turn left and go into the room next door. Wait by the sink.

src: towards stairs stairs towards back glass door at seaing before doors
tgt: Go towards the stairs  Pass the stairs and go towards the back glass door.  Stop at the seaing that is before the doors.

src: walk forward until stairs on left turn stairs step
tgt: Walk forward until you have reached stairs on your left. Turn to face the stairs and go up one step.

src: exit living room past dining table past stairs sitting room wait at white couch
tgt: Exit the living room, walk past the dining table, walk past the stairs, enter the sitting room, wait at the white couch.

src: walk into bedroom right right into closet wait there
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and turn right. Turn right into the closet and wait there.

src: exit closet toward room then room second door on right into other closet
tgt: Exit the closet toward the room then exit the room using the second door on the right and go into the other closet.

src: closet right through second door on right into closet once inside
tgt: Leave the closet and take a right. Go through the second door on the right. Step into the closet and stop once inside.

src: walk past round table on right hard left after library on left wait in threshold of open french doors
tgt: Walk past round table on the right. Make a hard left after the library on the left. Wait in the threshold of the open french doors.

src: walk past table on right bookcase on left then wait in hallway
tgt: Walk straight past the table on the right and the bookcase on the left then turn left. Wait in the hallway.

src: walk past red sofa on right past bookshelves on left turn wait in doorway with double doors
tgt: Walk past the red sofa on the right and continue past the bookshelves on the left. Turn left and wait in the doorway with the double doors.

src: turn bathroom once forward past stairs across living area past fireplace then right into hallway first door on left with handicap sign beside door
tgt: Turn left and exit the bathroom. Once out walk forward past the stairs. Go across the living area, past the fireplace and then turn right into the hallway.  Enter the first door on the left with the handicap sign beside the door.

src: exit bahtroom right out of bedroom into main living space area infront of until doorway on right hand side of plaid chairs once in doorway right carpeted hallway into second door on left wait there
tgt: Exit the bahtroom and make a right out of the bedroom and into the main living space. Continue walking to the area infront of you until you can see the doorway on the right hand side of the two plaid chairs. Once in the doorway make a right down the carpeted hallway and into the second door on your left. Wait there.

src: exit bedroom through door on right forward past stairs on left fireplace on right right at curio cabinet first door on left wait in bedroom doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door on the right. Continue forward past the stairs on the left and the fireplace on the right. Turn right at the curio cabinet and enter the first door on the left. Wait in the bedroom doorway.

src: forward slightly left through door way hard left in bathroom
tgt: Walk forward slightly to the left. Walk through the door way, make a hard left, stop in the bathroom.

src: after area walk towards hall by living room walk inside hall go first room on left next go inside bathroom wait
tgt: After you leave the dinning area walk towards the hall by the living room. Walk inside the hall and make go to the first room on the left. Next go inside the bathroom and wait.

src: turn around across room small hallway then bathroom stand by sink
tgt: Turn around and walk across the room to the small hallway. Then turn left and enter the bathroom.  Stand by the sink.

src: move towards bed once between bed television
tgt: Move towards the bed and stop once you are between the bed and the television.

src: walk down hall into bed room between bed desk
tgt: walk straight down hall into bed room. Stop between bed and desk.

src: down hallway into bedroom wait
tgt: Walk down the hallway and go into the bedroom and wait.

src: face pool walk around clockwise palm trees column opposite side from in front of empty urn in between windows on right side of door
tgt: Face the pool and walk around it clockwise, passing two palm trees and a column.  Stop when you have reached the opposite side from where you started and are in front of an empty urn that is in between the two windows on the right side of the door.

src: walk slightly right before right turn then extremely sharp right turn way around pool near window
tgt: Walk slightly to the right before making a sharper right turn and then an extremely sharp right turn, making your way around the pool and stopping near the furthest window.

src: walk around pool pool right glass doors left right walk middle of pool
tgt: Walk around the pool and keep the pool to your right and the sliding glass doors to the left. Make a right and walk to the middle of the pool.

src: stairs landing bottom floor in front of television at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs to the landing and continue to the bottom floor. Stop in front of the television at the bottom of the stairs.

src: downstairs sharp right downstairs until bottom of stairs then
tgt: Go downstairs, make a sharp right and go downstairs more, until you reach the bottom of the stairs then stop.

src: down stairs right at bottom of stairs right next set of stairs even with edge of tv on right
tgt: Walk down the stairs to your right. At the bottom of the stairs turn right and go down the next set of stairs. Stop when even with the edge of the TV on the right.

src: walk towards area left on walkway stop before stairs
tgt: Walk towards door that leads to out area, take a left on walkway, stop before the two stairs.

src: walk through living room toward patio walk on patio left next bush next walkway before stairs
tgt: Walk through the living room toward the patio. Walk on the patio and take a left. Stop next to the bush next the walkway before the stairs.

src: turn around right along beige sectional sofa walk through wide open doorway left onto stone path in front of stairs outside
tgt: Turn around and walk to your right, along the beige sectional sofa. Walk through the wide open doorway. Take a left onto the stone path in front of the stairs outside.

src: out of room right towards stairs stairs bar room on left
tgt: Make a left out of the room. Go right, towards the stairs. Pass the stairs and the bar. The room will be on your left.

src: area left hall stairs stairs area near fireplace next round end table
tgt: Leave the sitting area and take a left. Go down the hall towards the stairs. Pass the stairs and go to the sitting area near the fireplace. Stop next to the round end table.

src: turn right along hall right doorway walk towards stairs then sofas wait by white gold sofa
tgt: Turn right and walk along the hall. Turn right and cross the doorway. Walk towards the stairs and then towards the sofas. Wait by the white and gold sofa.

src: walk out of bathroom stall past sink area through open door at end of bathroom walk across hall open double doors directly ahead into large dining room stop near armchairs around fireplace
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom stall and past the sink area. Continue through the open door at the end of the bathroom. Walk across the hall towards the open double doors directly ahead. Walk into the large dining room and stop near the armchairs around the fireplace.

src: exit bathroom then straight into double doors wait near chairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom then go straight into the double doors. Wait near the chairs.

src: bathroom doorway across hall near wooden table
tgt: Leave the bathroom and enter the doorway across the hall. Stop near the wooden table.

src: past sculpture house down hallway turn just before orange leather chair
tgt: Go past the sculpture and enter the house. Walk down the hallway and turn left. Stop just before reaching the orange leather chair.

src: forward right of red art piece through doors straight until in between chairs turn in between red chair big silver cylinder stop
tgt: Go forward and to the right of the red art piece, go through the doors and straight until you are in between the chairs, turn left and go in between the red chair and the big silver cylinder and stop.

src: walk past red sculpture into building walk past metal chair turn behind red leather chair
tgt: Walk past the red sculpture and into the building. Walk past the metal chair and turn left. Stop behind the red leather chair.

src: walk across room glass wall on right right at stone pillar next box
tgt: Walk across room following glass wall on right, turn right at stone pillar and stop next to OSB box.

src: walk towards desk on right side of room pass behind desk chair walk past behind next desk at wooden box
tgt: Walk towards the desk located on the right side of the room. Pass behind the desk and chair. Walk past behind the next desk. Stop at the wooden box.

src: walk past conference room wait in hallway on right
tgt: Walk past the conference room and wait in the hallway on the right.

src: walk sharp right turn corridor before slight right turn top of steps
tgt: Walk straight, take a sharp right turn and continue down the corridor before making a slight right turn to the top of the steps.

src: walk past fireplace right into next room walk middle of room right walk edge of stairs
tgt: Walk past the fireplace, turn right and walk into the next room.  Walk to the middle of the room and turn right and walk to the edge of the stairs.

src: pass fireplace on right right hall room top of stairs
tgt: Pass the fireplace on your right. Take a right. Go down the hall. Cross the room and go to the top of the stairs.

src: head stairs into kitchen right head towards recliner right into bedroom wait
tgt: Head up the stairs and into the kitchen. Turn right and head towards the recliner and take a right into the bedroom and wait.

src: turn top of steps at top turn right way other end of table right door left of tall table with chairs once door bed
tgt: Turn around and go to the top of the steps. At the top turn right and walk all the way to the other end of the table. Turn right and enter the door to the left of the tall table with 2 chairs. Stop once you enter the door and are facing the bed.

src: turn right up stairs then right past dinning room table bedroom on right wait by bed
tgt: Turn right and walk up the stairs. Then turn right and walk past the dinning room table.  Enter the bedroom on your right and wait by the bed.

src: down stairs at bottom
tgt: walk down the stairs. stop at the bottom.

src: stairs that spiral left at bottom of stairs
tgt: walk down stairs that spiral left. stop at bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs right wait by lamp
tgt: Go down the stairs. Turn right and wait by the lamp.

src: finish stairs then straight u turn wait near couches
tgt: Finish going down the stairs then go straight and U turn left. Wait near the couches.

src: walk along hallway into theater room wait at back between sofa recliner
tgt: Walk along the hallway and into the theater room. Wait at the back, between the sofa and the recliner.

src: turn around away from steps wood way around until blue furniture walk through furniture up right of single recliner
tgt: Turn around and walk away from the steps. And follow the wood railing all the way around until you reach the blue furniture. Walk through the furniture and step up and stop to the right of the single recliner.

src: straight opposite white door until pillar then few steps pillar towards table stop
tgt: Go straight opposite the white door until you reach the pillar and then take a few steps passed the pillar towards the table and stop.

src: straight until dining room table chairs
tgt: Go straight until you get to the dining room table and chairs.

src: walk forward down hallway kitchen behind stools
tgt: Walk forward down the hallway and go to the kitchen. Stop when you are behind the stools.

src: walk past piano wait in front of middle pillar
tgt: Walk past the piano and wait in front of the middle pillar.

src: walk forward in direction of piano on left of second last pillar
tgt: Walk forward in the direction of the piano. Stop on the left of the second to last pillar.

src: next middle white column on same side as piano
tgt: Go stand next to the middle white column, on the same side as the piano.

src: through door next bed turn around straight hall right outside bathroom
tgt: Go through the door an stand next to the bed the turn around and got straight down the hall and stand right outside the bathroom.

src: exit bathroom toward room then right room then into room next door wait near bed
tgt: Exit the bathroom toward the room then turn right and exit the room and then turn left and go into the room next door and wait near the bed.

src: bathroom into bedroom beside bed right in doorway in doorway into first bedroom on left next stand beside lamp wait
tgt: You need to leave the bathroom and go into the bedroom, when you are beside the bed make a right and stand in the doorway. When you are in the doorway go into the first bedroom on the left. Next stand beside the lamp and wait.

src: way up stairs into first door on left outside of bathroom first door on left in long hall
tgt: Go all the way up the stairs and turn into the first door on the left. Stop outside of the bathroom, the first door on the left in the long hall.

src: upstairs right upstairs into doorway few steps then
tgt: Go upstairs, turn right and go upstairs, turn into the leftmost doorway, take a few steps and then stop.

src: finish stairs then into hallway wait there
tgt: Finish going up the stairs then go left into the hallway and wait there.

src: stairs in garage walk across foyer past front door left hard right walk past tv walk past dining table left through door patio wait near outdoor table
tgt: Walk up stairs in garage. Walk across foyer, past the front door to the left. Make a hard right, and walk past the TV. Walk past the dining table to the left, and through the sliding door to the patio. Wait near the outdoor dining table.

src: up stairs out of garage through doorway towards couches right walk in front of tv towards dining table out glass door next table
tgt: walk up the stairs out of the garage, straight through the doorway towards the couches, turn right and walk in front of the TV towards the dining table, and out the sliding glass door, stop next to the table.

src: steps garage straight into living room right head toward dining room table with chairs glass door wait in patio near black patio table chairs
tgt: Go up the steps to exit the garage. Continue straight into the living room and turn right. Head toward the dining room. Pass the table with chairs and go out the glass sliding door. Wait in the patio near the black patio table and chairs.

src: right down stair case next stair case at landing
tgt: Go the right and down the stair case. go to the next stair case and go up it. Stop at the landing.

src: set of stairs stair continue straight right stairs next room wait by door
tgt: Walk down one set of stairs.  When you reach the stair landing continue straight, and turn right to walk up the stairs.  Enter the next room.  Wait by the door.

src: walk top of stairs down stairs up set of stairs past metal gate at top of stairs
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs and stop. Walk down the stairs and up the set of stairs past the metal gate. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: turn right straight until room on right just inside room
tgt: Turn right and go straight until you see a room on your right, stop just inside that room.

src: walk past stairs walk into first room on right on staircase beside long rug
tgt: Walk past the stairs and walk into the first room on your right.  Wait on the staircase beside the long rug.

src: straight stairs on left straight then right right again stairs.. steps then
tgt: Go straight and pass the stairs on the left. Continue straight and then turn right and turn right again to go down the stairs.. Go down three steps then stop.

src: bathroom into room in sitting room forward towards christmas tree left into dining room in dining room next small serving trolley on right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go into the sitting room. In the sitting room walk forward towards the Christmas tree, and take a left into the dining room, In the dining room stand next the small serving trolley on your right and stop.

src: move through bathroom door turn left forward around red chair turn beige chair left of christmas tree move through entryway stop at little table with golden tea set
tgt: Move through bathroom door and turn left. Go forward, moving around the nearest red chair. Turn left when you get to the beige chair to the left of the Christmas tree. Move through the entryway and stop at the little table with the golden tea set.

src: exit bathroom turn into main room head towards christmas left forward dinning room on left before table
tgt: Exit the bathroom turn left into the main room and head towards the christmas tree.on the left. walk forward and enter the dinning room on your left. Stop before the table.

src: exit bedroom right straight across glass floor into narrow hallway wait in front of bedroom on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right. Continue straight across the glass floor into the narrow hallway. Wait in front of the bedroom on the right.

src: exit bedroom into hallway right after forward over transparent glass section of floor into narrow hallway on opposite wall at end of hallway into room on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom into the hallway, turning to the right after you exit. Continue forward, walking over the transparent glass section of the floor and continue into the narrow hallway on the opposite wall. At the end of the hallway, go into the room on your right.

src: exit bedroom through door on left right forward landing forward little corridor bedroom on right there
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door on the left. Turn right and go forward to the landing. Continue forward and enter the little corridor. Enter the bedroom on the right. Wait there.

src: exit bedroom by middle door turn down hall enter bedroom by first doorway on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom where you start by the middle door.  Turn left, and walk down the hall.  Enter another bedroom by the first doorway on your right.

src: exit room through door turn into hallway enter first room on right
tgt: Exit room through door, turn left. Walk into hallway and enter first room on right.

src: exit bedroom down hall left of stairs first door on right past cabinet bedroom wait at foot of bed
tgt: Exit the bedroom, walk down the hall to the left of the stairs to the first door on the right past the cabinet, enter the bedroom, wait at the foot of the bed.

src: straight in through doors down hall bit turn right by planter step at top of stairs wait right there
tgt: Go straight in, through the doors, and down the hall a bit.  Turn to the right by the planter.  Go another step or two and you'll be at the top of the stairs.  Wait right there.

src: enter house through door first right at top of descending staircase
tgt: Enter the house through the door and take your first right. Stop at the top of the descending staircase.

src: walk along patio stone open entry doorway ahead into home down hallway ahead first corner walk top of stairwell in hallway
tgt: Walk along the patio stone to the open entry doorway ahead. Walk into the home and down the hallway ahead. Turn the first corner and walk to the top of the stairwell in the hallway.

src: walk into house up stairs in living room walk past kitchen down hall on left of refrigerator at tree left next hall stand in doorway first door on left
tgt: Walk into the house and up the stairs in the living room. Walk past the kitchen and down the hall on the left of the refrigerator. At the tree take a left to go down the next hall. Stand in the doorway to the first door on your left.

src: enter building steps walk past kitchen down hallway second hallway wait in bathroom on left
tgt: Enter the building and go up the steps. Walk past the kitchen, down the hallway to the second hallway. Wait in the bathroom on the left.

src: inside large glass doors then steps fridge on right straight toward plant in pot on hallway pot hallway right of pot turn into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Go inside using the large glass sliding doors then go up the steps. Pass the fridge on the right and continue straight toward the plant in the pot on the hallway. When you get to the pot continue down the hallway that is to the right of the pot and turn left into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: turn hallway right laundry room wait by desk
tgt: Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn right, enter the laundry room and wait by the desk.

src: turn hallway right in open doorway
tgt: Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn right and stop in the open doorway.

src: walk through doorway step into laundry room
tgt: walk left through the doorway. step into the laundry room.

src: down wood hallway past open doors photographs on walls stairwell at end of hall first few steps
tgt: Walk down the wood floored hallway past the open doors and framed photographs on the walls. Continue down the stairwell at the end of the hall down the first few steps.

src: straight until stairs steps then
tgt: Go straight until you get to the stairs. Go down three steps then stop.

src: down hall top of stairs walk second step down
tgt: Walk down the hall to the top of the stairs. Walk to the second step down and stop.

src: enter past thermostat through left opening walk past beds into bathroom wait in front of sink
tgt: Enter past the thermostat and go through the left opening. Walk past the beds into the bathroom and wait in front of the sink.

src: direction degrees through doorway right of door outside walk past chair into leftmost door walk through bedroom into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Reverse your direction 180 degrees. Walk through the doorway to the right of the door leading outside. Walk past the chair and straight into the leftmost door. Walk through the bedroom into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: head left at glass door into room with ironing boards into bathroom with white towels on sink
tgt: Head left and make another left at the glass door into the room with the ironing boards and go into the bathroom with white towels on the sink.

src: walk upstairs into kitchen in archway dining room
tgt: Walk upstairs, into the kitchen and stop in the archway to the dining room.

src: stairs turn into dining room turn again near large table with chairs
tgt: Go up the stairs. Turn left and go into the dining room. Turn left again and wait near the large table with chairs.

src: up staircase at corner forward turn again towards long dining table there
tgt: Walk up the staircase, and turn left at the corner. Walk forward, and turn left again towards the long dining table, and stop there.

src: exit bathroom walk staircase wait here
tgt: Exit the bathroom.   Walk to the staircase.  Wait here.

src: turn left bathroom walk towards stairs on third stair
tgt: Turn to the left and exit the bathroom. Walk towards the stairs and stop on the third stair.

src: bathroom tv room stairs on third stair from bottom
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and the TV room. Go up three stairs. Stop on the third stair from the bottom.

src: turn right stairs turn up large flight of stairs up left side at fork in stairs at stair just before
tgt: Turn right to walk up stairs. Turn left. Walk up large flight of stairs. Walk up left side at fork in stairs. Stop at stair just before landing.

src: stairs left marble stairs at left stairs on left at stair third from top
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a left to go up the marble stairs. At the landing take a left and go up the stairs on the left. Stop at the stair that is third from the top.

src: turn up carpeted staircase next level turn up main flight of stairs at entry of home at platform midway up stair turn at flower vase next flight of stairs top
tgt: Turn and walk up the carpeted staircase to the next level. Turn and walk up the main flight of stairs at the entry of the home. At the platform midway up the stair turn left at the flower vase and continue up the next flight of stairs to the top.

src: up stairs at fourth stair from top
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Stop at the fourth stair from the top.

src: up stairs wait on fourth step from top
tgt: Walk up the stairs and wait on the fourth step from the top.

src: stairs in middle of second set of stairs
tgt: Go up the stairs, stopping in the middle of the second set of stairs.

src: down hallway bathroom picture with worded text through open door ahead hall into bedroom at end with couches arm chairs around fireplace
tgt: Walk down the hallway passing the bathroom and picture with worded text. Continue through the open door straight ahead. Continue down the hall and into the bedroom at the end with couches and arm chairs around a fireplace.

src: walk down hallway wait in bedroom at end
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway and wait in the bedroom at the end.

src: down hallway past mirror on right into living room
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the mirror on the right and into the living room.

src: walk right of fireplace into first room after on blue carpet walk through bedroom past green counter top walk through door bedroom on left after into second bedroom
tgt: Walk to the right of the fireplace and go into the first room after stepping on the blue carpet.  Walk through the bedroom and past the green counter top.  Walk through the door to the bedroom on the left.  Stop after stepping into this second bedroom.

src: walk right of fireplace into first room on right wait in doorway second bedroom
tgt: Walk to the right of the fireplace and into the first room on the right. Wait in the doorway to second bedroom.

src: straight slightly right into hallway right into room turn into room next door wait near wardrobe
tgt: Go straight and slightly right to go into the hallway. Turn right and go into the room. Turn left and go into the room next door. Wait near the wardrobe.

src: walk straight hallway head until picture frame on wall
tgt: Walk straight. Enter the hallway. Head straight until you get to a picture frame on the wall.

src: bedroom walk straight hallway in front of framed artwork on wall at end just after bathroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and walk straight down the hallway and stop in front of the framed artwork on the wall at the end, just after you pass a bathroom.

src: walk through doorway down hall in front of picture
tgt: Walk through the doorway and down the hall. Stop in front of the picture.

src: after out of building walk railing right steps pool area wait
tgt: After you walk out of the building walk to the railing and make a right, walk to the steps leading to the pool area and wait.

src: along balcony once near top of stairs stop
tgt: Go along the balcony, once near the top of the stairs stop.

src: start door building turn so sidewalk towards pool railing on left pillar tables on right forward until steps pool destination right before steps pool wall with light right railing left
tgt: Start facing the door to enter the building. Turn left so you are facing the sidewalk towards the pool. The railing should be on your left and the pillar and tables should be on your right. Continue moving forward until you reach the steps to go down to the pool. The destination you are trying to reach is right before the steps to do gown to the pool. There will be a wall with a light to your right and a railing to your left.

src: pass beds straight out of room door ahead through laundry room steps then right into room wait by bed
tgt: Pass the beds and go straight out of the room using the door straight ahead. Go through the laundry room. Go up the steps then turn right and go into the room. Wait by the bed.

src: walk around beds bathroom walk through bathroom into hallway bedroom through first door on right on far side of bed between windows
tgt: Walk around the beds to the bathroom. Walk through the bathroom, into the hallway. Enter the bedroom through the first door on the right. Stop on far side of the bed between the windows.

src: walk past beds into bathroom walk straight through bathroom onto wooden floor straight up few stairs room on right on right side of bed in between windows on far wall
tgt: Walk past the two beds into the bathroom and walk straight through the bathroom onto the wooden floor.  Keep going straight up a few stairs and enter the room on the right.  Stop on the right side of the bed in between two windows on the far wall.

src: up stairs into first room on right into closet once inside
tgt: Walk up the stairs and go into the first room on the right.  Walk into the closet and stop once inside.

src: up stairs right at top walk through bedroom door right wait near closet
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn right at the top. Walk through the bedroom door to the right and wait near the closet.

src: stairs right bedroom first door on right into closet in closet
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a right. Enter the bedroom that is the first door on your right and go into the closet. Stop in the closet.

src: straight until table chairs then stairs right steps then
tgt: Go straight until you get to the table and chairs then turn left and go down the stairs. Turn right and go down three steps then stop.

src: step down forward then stairs down first landing turn right steps wait there
tgt: Step down and go forward and then turn left. Proceed to the stairs and go down to the first landing. Turn to the right and go down two more steps. Wait there.

src: stairs landing stairs on right stop
tgt: Go down the stairs to the landing. Go down three stairs on your right, and stop.

src: exit bedroom left straight down hall door in doorway christmas tree
tgt: exit bedroom to hallway, turn left and go straight down hall to open door, stop in doorway facing christmas tree.

src: turn hall through door at end of hall in doorway
tgt: Turn left and go down the hall. Go through the door at the end of the hall and stop in the doorway.

src: exit bedroom hallway past fire extinguisher christmas tree forward in doorway master suite
tgt: Exit the bedroom and move down the hallway, past the fire extinguisher and Christmas tree. Continue forward and stop in the doorway that is marked Master Suite.

src: turn right then right again hallway little set of stairs now in dining room wait there
tgt: Turn to the right and then to the right again.  Go down the hallway.  Go up the little set of stairs.  You're now in the dining room.  Wait there.

src: turn after second chair right wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn around and after the second chair take a right and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: forward with living room on left last flight of stairs on right dining area right at top of stairs
tgt: Walk forward with the living room on the left. Go up the last flight of stairs on the right and enter the dining area. Stop right at the top of the stairs.

src: straight right hallway until hallway
tgt: Go straight down the right hallway until it intersects another hallway.

src: at end of hall left hall end of hall exit sign near ceiling next walk past exit sign wait in front of office in center of floor
tgt: At the end of the hall you need to make a left and go down the hall. When you get to the end of the hall you will see an exit sign that is near the ceiling. Next walk past the exit sign and wait in front of an office and in the center of the floor.

src: turn right hallway glass on right forward past end of glass wall forward until under exit sign near ceiling stop wait
tgt: Turn to your right, enter that hallway, keeping the glass on your right. Keep walking forward, past the end of the glass wall. Continue moving forward until you're under the exit sign that is near the ceiling. Stop and wait.

tgt: Enter the massage room that is straight ahead and to the left. Wait there.

src: walk across open room room with massage tables before massage tables next mirror on wall
tgt: Walk across the open room. Enter the room with the two massage tables. Stop before the massage tables, next to the mirror on the wall.

src: into room with square pattern on floor doorways mirrored hangings into one on left few steps into massage room stop
tgt: Go into the room with the square pattern on the floor, and see the two doorways to the left the mirrored hangings, go into the one on the left, take a few steps into the massage room and stop.

src: walk towards fireplace turn walk straight through doorway straight past bench in first doorway on right
tgt: walk towards fireplace, turn left and walk straight through doorway, walk straight past bench, stop in first doorway on your right.

src: walk towards fireplace once fireplace turn hallway with light hardwood straight until room on left wait here
tgt: Walk towards fireplace.  Once you reach fireplace, turn left, and enter the hallway with the light colored hardwood.  Continue straight, until you reach a room on the left.  Wait here.

src: exit room door on left turn wait near entrance of room
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the left. Turn left and wait near the entrance of that room.

src: turn around towards left stairs at bottom
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the left. Descend the stairs and stop at the bottom.

src: room turn in hallway stairs at bottom
tgt: Leave the room and turn left in the hallway.  Go down all the stairs and stop at the bottom.

tgt: Put the double doors directly behind you. Then walk straight across the main hallway. Go past the cheetah painting on your right. Turn right, and enter the laundry room with a sink.

src: right hallway then right at chair wait once laundry room
tgt: Go right down the hallway, then right at the chair wait once you enter the laundry room.

src: walk forward then right turn at doorway
tgt: walk forward then make a right turn and stop at the doorway.

tgt: Make left at exit sign, walk down the hall to second office on the left. This office has a  bulletin board full of notices. Stop in front of desk with green chair.

src: move into area hallways meet then left turn down hallway second doorway on left
tgt: Move into the area where the two hallways meet and then make a left turn. Move down the hallway and enter the second doorway on your left.

src: through door right enter second room on right
tgt: go through door and turn right, enter second room on right.

src: exit laundry room turn hallway stop near counter
tgt: Exit the laundry room, turn left and go down the hallway and stop near the counter.

src: exit laundry room turn hallway until dining room wait there
tgt: Exit the laundry room. Turn left and go down the hallway until you get to the dining room. Wait there.

src: exit through door next bathroom sink turn down hallway until kitchen counter wait here
tgt: Exit through the door next to the bathroom sink.  Turn left and walk down the hallway until you reach the kitchen counter.  Wait here.

src: downstairs wait in bathroom doorway
tgt: Go downstairs and wait in the bathroom doorway.

src: down stairs enter bathroom at shower
tgt: Walk down the stairs and enter bathroom. Stop at shower.

src: stairs facing into bathroom
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop facing into a bathroom.

src: stairs stop
tgt: go down the stairs and stop.

src: down stairs just ahead wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the stairs just ahead. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop when you reach the bottom.

tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn right. Walk into the bedroom and turn left. Stop by the rug.

tgt: Exit room, turn right, turn left and wait near the bed.

tgt: Exit the bedroom. Walk past the pool table on the right. Walk through the archway to the left of the stair railing. Wait at the alcove on the stair landing.

tgt: Exit the bedroom on the right and pass the pool table. Take the next right and then stop on the left by the railing.

tgt: Walk straight out the door ahead. Once out, walk past the pool table and turn left and follow the walkway. Stop once you pass a hallway on your left.

tgt: Go straight until you go out two double doors that lead to outside. Wait there.

src: toward exit walk long white banquet table plant in corner pass through first set of double doors before second set of double doors with fire extinguisher upper right
tgt: Heading toward the exit walk passed the long white banquet table and the plant in the corner. Pass through the first set of double doors. Stop before the second set of double doors with the fire extinguisher to the upper right.

src: walk past cloth table toward entryway outside in entryway
tgt: Walk past the cloth table and toward the entryway to the outside. Stop in the entryway.

tgt: Make a right around the corner of the first lounger on the right. Walk to the end of the hall with the three pieces of wall art. Make a right into the bathroom, facing the sinks.

tgt: Follow the edge of the spa to the other side of the room, turn left and exit. go straight passed the equipment and chair to a door on the slight right. enter the  bathroom and stop near the sink.

src: past stairs through doorway
tgt: Go past the stairs and through the doorway.

src: move through room with marble staircase left through doorway next glass vase pass across hallway stop at doorway of room directly across from first doorway through
tgt: Move through the room with the marble staircase to your left. Move through the doorway located next to the glass vase. Pass across the hallway and stop at the doorway of the room directly across from the first doorway you passed through.

tgt: Go around the table and through the entryway on the left to the kitchen. Walk straight and go through the doorway across the kitchen. Stop next to the chair on your right.

tgt: Go through the wide arched opening at the opposite corner of the dining area you're in and go into the kitchen. Continue past the kitchen island and through the door opening just to the right of the small build in desk. Stop once you're fall enough into that area to be able to turn right.

tgt: Walk upstairs and wait at the top of the stairwell.

tgt: Turn left and go between the stairs and the wall. After a few steps turn left again towards the living room. Enter the living room.  Turn right and go between the breakfast table and the wall.

tgt: Exit the room, turn left, walk all the way down the hallway to the open door, wait in the doorway.

tgt: Exit the door to your right and walk past the entire railing.  Stop in the middle of the first doorway you enter.

src: room left in hallway down hall in doorway bedroom ahead at end of hallway
tgt: Leave the room, and take a left in the hallway. Walk down the hall and stop in the doorway to the bedroom straight ahead at the end of the hallway.

src: around bed stand in doorway on left
tgt: Go around the bed and stand in the doorway on the left.

src: walk around bed bedroom in doorway outside of bedroom
tgt: Walk around the bed and leave the bedroom. Stop in the doorway outside of the bedroom.

src: right after bed left wait in doorway
tgt: Take a right after the bed. Take a left and wait in the doorway.

tgt: Go along the bookshelf, turn left along the table, turn right along the table and wait near the second black chair.

tgt: Walk forward past the bookshelves on the right. Then wait by the two black chairs on the left.
