tgt: Step forward and turn left, walking around the desk. Continue forward past the two black lounge chairs. Walk down the stairs and wait at the bottom of them.

src: stairs way up down hallway before door on left
tgt: Go up the stairs. Continue all the way straight up and down the hallway. Stop before you get to the door on the left.

src: stairs split straight then straight in hall between third fourth photos on wall
tgt: Start up the stairs. When the split, continue straight. Then walk straight in the hall. Stop between the third and fourth photos on the wall.

src: stairs up stairs hall next middle photo on right wall
tgt: Go up the stairs, and go straight up more stairs. Go down the hall. Stop next to the middle photo on the right wall.

src: stairs then behind chair door enter door bedroom
tgt: go up the stairs then behind the chair there is a door, enter that door you will see a bedroom.

src: stairs at top right then table on left door by black chair turn left near bed
tgt: Ascend the stairs. At the top, turn right and then follow the table on the left. Exit the door by the black chair and turn left and stop near the bed.

src: steps right pool table into second room on right wait near bed
tgt: Go up the steps. Turn right and pass the pool table. Go into the second room on the right. Wait near the bed.

tgt: Go to the top of the staircase. Go to the right side of the pool table.Go into the bedroom next to the slot machine.

tgt: Walk up the stairs and walk right past the pool table. Walk into the bedroom on the left and stop.

tgt: Walk forward towards the TV and take a right into the bedroom. Walk to the bathtub and stop right at the foot of the bathtub bear the bedpost.

tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and take a right. Wait next to the small white table.

tgt: Turn and walk past the bed and dresser out of the door on the other side. Walk through the laundry room and into the living room. Walk passed the couch area and up to the door to outside.

src: leave bedroom in slight left straight enter living room behind couch
tgt: leave bedroom in to hall, turn slight left. continute down hall straight and enter living room, stop behind the couch.

src: walk out of bedroom through open door into hallway down hall bathroom laundry room .walk through wood double doors with glass panes into lounge area with couches near sword mantle peice on table
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom through the open door into the hallway. Walk down the hall  passed the bathroom and laundry room .Walk through the wood double doors with glass panes and into the lounge area with couches. Stop near the sword mantle peice on the table.

src: exit room straight until chairs wait there
tgt: Exit the room, go straight until facing two chairs, wait there.

src: turn house hallway open room with couches right walking towards large table beside door outside right before middle table
tgt: Turn left and enter the house. Go down the hallway. When you reach the open room with all the couches , turn right. Keep walking towards the large table beside the door leading outside. Stop right before you reach the middle table.

src: down hallways into living room right at couch heading towards table in middle of room with plant
tgt: Walk down the hallways into the living room and make a right at the couch heading towards the table in the middle of the room with the plant.

tgt: Exit the garage and go straight when you get to a room with beige sofas. Turn right and pass the beige sofas and stand near the round table with the clear vase that has green plants.

src: hall then stairs turn right past table chairs till in hallway then wait there
tgt: Continue down the hall.  And then proceed up the stairs.  Turn to the right and go past the table and chairs.  Go till you are standing in the hallway and then stop.  Wait there.

tgt: Go up the winding staircase. At the top of the stairs take a right, and another right going past the dining table. Stop in the hallway outside of the bedroom.

src: up stairs.and right between elevator bedroom doors
tgt: Walk up the stairs.and take a right. Stop between the elevator and bedroom doors.

src: turn around across room living room walk through living room dining room wait near table
tgt: Turn around and walk across the room and enter the living room.  Walk through the living room and enter the dining room. Wait near  the table.

tgt: Go down the stairs, and straight into the sitting room. Go through the sitting room into the dining room. Stop once you enter the dining room.

src: down stairs into room in front right around of furniture through entryway
tgt: Walk down the stairs and straight into the room in front. Go right around all of the furniture, and through the entryway.

tgt: Go through the bathroom and through the doorway on your left then make a right and stop at the nearest doorway.

src: right into bathroom out of bathroom right wait in doorway
tgt: Take a right into the bathroom and walk straight out of the bathroom. Take a right and wait in that doorway.

tgt: Leave the bathroom.  Walk straight through the room with the mirror until you enter a room with a giant clock.  Stop in the doorway to the right of the clock.

tgt: Turn left at fridge. Walk down hallway. Turn right at second skylight. Walk into bedroom. Wait at bookshelf.

src: turn so kitchen island on right refrigerator on left with cabinet pantry in front of forward cabinet pantry turn until hallway with glass door onto patio on left down hallway until set of glass doors on left with recessed door on right turn door walk though though room until bookcase
tgt: TURN TO THE LEFT SO THE KITCHEN ISLAND IS ON THE RIGHT AND A REFRIGERATOR  IS ON THE LEFT WITH CABINET PANTRY IN FRONT OF YOU, WALK FORWARD TO THE CABINET PANTRY, TURN LEFT UNTIL YOU FACE A HALLWAY WITH A SLIDING GLASS DOOR LOOKING ONTO A PATIO IS ON THE LEFT, WALK DOWN THE HALLWAY UNTIL YOU COME TO ANOTHER SET OF SLIDING GLASS DOORS ON THE LEFT WITH A RECESSED DOOR ON THE RIGHT, TURN TURN TO THE DOOR AND WALK THOUGH IT, WALK THOUGH THE ROOM UNTIL YOU COME TO A BOOKCASE.

tgt: Walk forward with the refrigerator on your left. Take a left and go into the hallway. Go straight and take the third right into a bedroom. Stop in front of the bookcase.

tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom.  Continue past the closet area.  When you get into the bedroom and are next to the bed, on the side, stop.  Wait there.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and keep going straight past the closet. Wait near the nightstand.

src: bathroom into bedroom in front of bench across from bed
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go into the bedroom. Stop in front of the bench across from the bed.

tgt: Exit the living room and walk up the stairs, at the first landing turn left. Walk to the stair that is second from the landing and wait there by the banister.

tgt: Go through the archway and up the stairs, at the level make a left and two steps from the top stop.

tgt: Walk through the doorway that leads to the stairs and walk up the stairs. Take a left at the second set of stairs, and stop at the second step from the top.

tgt: Walk forward, and go through the gate. Enter the house and take the second right. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

tgt: Wall through the door comprised of an open grate of vertical metal bars and then enter through the wooden door to your left. Continue forward to the short flight of five stairs and climb to the bottom of them.

tgt: Enter through the white gate.  Turn left and go inside.  Pass the wooden shelving and go down brick steps to the right.  Wait here.

src: turn around towards bed turn dining table straight ahead toward small refrigerator under counter on right
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the bed, turn left, pass the dining table, look straight ahead and walk toward the small refrigerator under the counter on the right.

src: exit room walk straight ahead toward bed turn bed straight toward small fridge there
tgt: Exit the room and walk straight ahead to toward the bed. Turn left and pass the bed. Walk straight toward the small fridge and stop there.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and go into the bedroom directly across. Go left and pass between the foot of the bed and dresser. Go into the little kitchen and stop in front of the dishwasher.

tgt: Walk straight along the gray path on the floor.  Walk past the two benches on your right and then enter the doorway after them.  Stand a couple steps in from the door in front of the rounded edging of the table.

tgt: Go straight down the hallway and past the seating area.  Turn right at the double doors.  Continue until you're at this marble looking table and wait.

tgt: Walk toward the chairs and turn right. Walk past the chairs and up the stairs into the kitchen. Stop at the top of the stairs.

tgt: Leave the media area, and walk past the orange recliner. Walk up the stairs and stop one you are the top of the stairs.

tgt: Leave the TV area, and go up the stairs on the right into the kitchen. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs then in doorway outside
tgt: Go up the stairs and then go left.  Stop in the doorway leading outside.

src: forward stairway just white chair right sets of stairs until on second floor of building turn forward then at entryway of door outside
tgt: Move forward to the stairway just pass the white chair to your right. Ascend both sets of stairs until you arrive on the second floor of the building. Turn left, move forward, and then stop at the entryway of the door leading outside.

src: from back door walk stairs then stairs at top of stairs at balcony door
tgt: From the back door walk to the stairs then walk up the stairs. At the top of the stairs turn left and wait at the balcony door.

src: walk past table with flowers bed out of bedroom down hall in front of railing
tgt: Walk past the table with the flowers and the bed out of the bedroom. Walk down the hall and stop in front of the railing.

src: walk foot of bed with foot of bed left walk through hallway through middle door railing
tgt: Walk to the foot of the bed.  With the foot of the bed to your left, walk straight through the hallway through the middle door.  Stop when you get to the railing.

src: turn degrees head towards bed enter door next bed at banisters
tgt: Turn 80 degrees left. Head towards bed. Enter door next to bed. Stop at banisters.

src: hallway turn door pass pot with plant before second turn on second entrance table chairs right head into living room wait by fireplace
tgt: Go down the hallway and turn left when you get to a door. Pass one pot with a plant and before you get to the second one turn left on the second entrance. Pass the table and chairs and turn right. Head into the living room and wait by the fireplace.

src: light switch right forward on stone floor on stone floor pivot left onward past butter churns on left then again veer left dining room traverse right side of table on right doorway living room advance until even with corner of cabinet on left here
tgt: Keeping the light switch to your right, move forward on to the stone floor. Remaining on the stone floor, pivot to the left and continue to move onward. Walk past the two butter churns on the left, then again veer to the left. Enter the dining room and traverse it, keeping to the right side of the table. On your right is a doorway to the living room. Advance until you're even with the corner of the cabinet on your left. Remain standing here.

src: walk out of small room into hallway with brick floor down brick hallway past wooden equipment turn into dining room walk past dining room table right into next room stop wait in next room next tall cabinet fireplace
tgt: Walk out of the small room, into the hallway with the brick floor.  Walk down the brick hallway, past the wooden equipment and turn left into the dining room. Walk past the dining room table and turn right into the next room.  Stop and wait in the next room, next to a tall cabinet and the fireplace.

src: turn dining room forward through dining room past bottom of staircase just past end of stairs
tgt: Turn around and face the dining room.  Go forward through the dining room, past the bottom of the staircase and stop just past the end of the stairs.

src: kitchen area right right stairs stop at bottom
tgt: Leave the kitchen area, going to the right. Turn to the right when you reach the stairs and stop at the bottom.

src: turn right towards brown table/desk walk towards stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn right and walk towards the brown table/desk. Walk towards the stairs and wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit room walk up steps on right wait in hallway outside weight room
tgt: Exit the room a walk up the steps on the right. Wait in the hallway outside the weight room.

src: door on right steps landing walk middle of landing then
tgt: Go out the door on your right. Go up the steps to the landing. Walk to the middle of the landing, then stop.

src: room right first few stairs in hallway outside fitness room
tgt: Leave the room and take a right. Go up the first few stairs and stop in the hallway outside the fitness room.

src: walk past dining room table left hallway then into office wait by desk
tgt: Walk past the dining room table and enter the left hallway. Then turn left and walk into the office. Wait by the desk.

src: walk past dining room table chairs past stairs into hallway turn down hallway into study just inside doorway
tgt: Walk past the dining room table and chairs and past the stairs into the hallway. Turn left and walk down the hallway into the study. Stop just inside the doorway.

src: walk past table chairs on right past stairs on left turn straight into room wait near desk
tgt: Walk past the table and chairs on the right and past the stairs on the left. Turn left. Continue straight into the room. Wait near the desk.

src: stairs left left into foyer past round table right into living room stop at edge of couch closest
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. Take a left and go into the foyer. Past the round table take a right into the living room. Stop at the edge of the couch closest to where you entered.

src: stairs walk left slightly right through entryway wait by couch
tgt: Go down the stairs and walk to the left. Walk slightly to the right and go through the entryway. Wait by the couch.

src: down stairs then wand walk table in middle of room then right right behind right side of couch wait there
tgt: Walk down the stairs and then turn left.  Turn around wand walk to the table in the middle of the room.  Then turn right and stand right behind the right side of the couch.  Wait there.

src: up stairs sharp left walk behind stairs left wait in laundry room
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Take a sharp left. Walk behind the stairs and take a left. Wait in the laundry room.

src: head upstairs sharp left through landing door on left wait in laundry room
tgt: Head upstairs and turn sharp left. Walk through the landing to the door on the left. Wait in the laundry room.

src: stairs turn walk over black rug turn into room with washer dryer just before washer dryer
tgt: Go up the stairs, turn left, and continue walking. Walk over the black rug, turn left into the room with the washer and dryer. Stop just before reaching the washer and dryer.

src: forward towards wall then towards living room forward until couch then right on steps
tgt: Move forward towards the wall then turn left to head towards the living room. Keep going forward until you reach the couch, then turn right and wait on the steps.

src: walk behind couch right steps on third step
tgt: Walk behind couch, turn right and go up steps, stop on third step.

src: head toward red chairs little bit right behind chairs sets of stars right up stairs on left there
tgt: Head toward the red chairs a little bit to your right. Standing behind the chairs there will be two sets of stars to your right. Head up the stairs on the left and stop there.

src: walk around bed chairs bathroom on left near shower
tgt: Walk around the bed and chairs and enter the bathroom on your left. Stop near the shower.

src: move end of bed stand on blue dot
tgt: Move to the end of the bed and stand on the blue dot.

src: turn past bed right at dresser then right again into bathroom by door sink
tgt: Turn left and walk past the bed, turn right at the dresser, and then turn right again and walk into the bathroom.  You'll stop by the shower door and the sink.

src: turn straight until bed on right right past ottoman straight until near dresser then right towards door on far right enter door stall on left
tgt: Turn left and go straight until you pass the bed on the right, turn right past the ottoman. keep straight until you are near the dresser, then turn right and go towards the door on your far right, enter the door and stop where the shower stall is on your left.

src: turn house through living room into foyer onto steps on right wait near bottom
tgt: Turn around and enter the house.  Walk through the living room and into the foyer.  Walk onto the steps on your right. Wait near the bottom.

src: inside through room into room with white walls tiles walk round table with white flowers on skylight staircase on right on second step from bottom
tgt: Go inside and walk through the room into the bigger room with white walls and tiles.  Walk to the round table with white flowers on it, underneath the skylight.  Go up the staircase on the right and stop on the second step from the bottom.

src: head inside past table couches into entryway past couches right at bottom of stairs
tgt: Head inside. Go past the table and couches. Go into the entryway and past the two couches. Turn right and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit room then right pass chair with sink then left hallway room on left stairs wait there by desk
tgt: Exit the room then turn right pass the chair with the sink then turn left to go down the hallway. Enter the room on the left. Pass the stairs and wait there by the desk.

src: walk out of room right past barber chair turn walk past plants by stairs
tgt: Walk out of the room and turn right. Walk past the barber chair and turn left. Walk left past the plants and stop by the stairs.

src: exit room right toward sink area left turn exit through double doors wait in reception area near elevators
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Walk toward the sink area to your left. Turn left and exit through the double doors. Wait in the Reception area near the elevators.

src: walk inside immediately straight towards room in front of inside at door
tgt: Walk inside and turn left immediately. Keep walking straight towards the room in front of you. Enter inside, and stop at the door.

src: enter home from side door then hallway into next room before door on left bathroom
tgt: Enter the home from the side door then go down the hallway straight into the next room, stopping before reaching the door on the left to the bathroom.

src: inside through open door immediately left forward through hallway room ahead beside table giant clock
tgt: Go Inside through the open door, and immediately turn left.  Continue forward through the hallway, and enter the room straight ahead.  Wait beside the table and giant clock.

src: enter house through front door walk straight after wooden dresser near wall right down stairs next hard left walk until bathroom on left into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Enter the house through the front door and walk straight. After you reach the wooden dresser near the wall, turn right and walk down the stairs.  Next make a hard left, and walk until you reach the bathroom on your left.  Continue into the bathroom, and wait by the sink.

src: enter building through wooden doorway straight passing by room left short flight of steps ahead of then narrow hallway turn into second room on left bathroom in front of shower
tgt: Enter the building through the wooden doorway staying straight and passing by the room to the left and taking the short flight of five steps ahead of you. Then continue down the narrow curving hallway and turn left into the second room on the left which will be a bathroom. Stop in front of the shower.

src: enter building walk past shelves down steps second doorway wait in bathroom
tgt: Enter the building, walk past the shelves and down the steps. Enter the second doorway and wait in the bathroom.

src: exit bedroom via door left then bedroom door right there
tgt: Exit the bedroom via the door. Take a left then enter the bedroom door to the right. Wait there.

src: out of bedroom with rabbit mirror toward large picture of people at beach in doorway of bedroom with green chair mirror with white frame seats in front of bed
tgt: Go out of the bedroom with the rabbit ears mirror, toward a large picture of people at the beach, and stand in the doorway of another bedroom with a green chair, a mirror with a white frame,and three seats in front of the bed.

src: exit room turn then right into other bedroom wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room and turn left then turn right and go into the other bedroom. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk out of laundry room right walk end of hallway right into bedroom in front of bed
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room and turn right. Walk to the end of the hallway and turn right. Walk into the bedroom and stop in front of the bed.

src: exit laundry room right through hallway until end then right into bedroom then wait
tgt: Exit the laundry room, make a right and go through the hallway until the end and then make a right into the bedroom and then wait.

src: turn right door once turn right end of hallway right bedroom stop
tgt: Turn right and exit the door. Once out turn right and go to the end of the hallway and turn right. Enter the bedroom and stop.

src: towards pool then left of pool straight towards diamond shape on wall turn right through way then near plant
tgt: Go towards the pool and then go to the left of the pool, go straight towards the diamond shape on the wall, turn right through the way and then left, and stop near the plant.

src: head in towards pool turn by pool with pool towards right forward dogleg right alcove with door left other door right massage room
tgt: Head in towards the pool and turn left, to pass by the pool with the pool towards your right. Continue forward and take a dogleg to the right to enter an alcove with a door to your left and an other door to your right, both leading to a massage room.

src: turn pool on right forward then right towards pool corner bit immediately in front of big rectangular mirror
tgt: Turn left, and pass the pool on your right. Keep walking forward, and then turn right towards the pool corner. Walk a bit, and turn left immediately. Stop in front of the big rectangular mirror.

src: bottom of staircase in dining room into office
tgt: Go to the bottom of the staircase in the dining room. Go into the office.

src: walk across room past stairs wait in office by desk
tgt: Walk across the room, past the stairs and wait in the office, by the desk.

src: step outside of room walk through doorway on opposite side past stairs after into office
tgt: Step outside of the room and walk through the doorway on the opposite side past the stairs.  Stop after stepping into the office.

src: straight hallway then left past bed veer right through white door in doorway
tgt: Go straight to the hallway and then turn left.  Go past the bed.  Veer to the right and go through the white door.  Stop when you're in the doorway.

src: forward turn forward past bed on platform walk forward past green sofa stop in doorway
tgt: Move forward. Turn left. Walk forward past bed on platform. Walk forward past green sofa. Stop in doorway.

src: walk past bed through lounge area wait in doorway
tgt: Walk past the bed through the lounge area and wait in the doorway.

src: stairs towards living room fire place on right in front of large round fireplace
tgt: Go down the stairs and go towards the living room fire place on the right. Stop in front of the large round fireplace.

src: down stairs around glass lamp at bottom turn wait by fireplace
tgt: Walk down the stairs and around the glass lamp at the bottom. Turn left and wait by the fireplace.

src: stairs past floor lamp wait at fireplace
tgt: Walk down stairs. Walk past floor lamp. Wait at fireplace.

src: turn right room way until white couch at table in front of white couch
tgt: Turn right and cross the room all the way until you reach the white couch. Stop at the table in front of the white couch.

src: walk between desk copy machine turn walk between desk bookshelf walk between desks wait near coffee table
tgt: Walk between the desk and the copy machine, turn left and walk between the desk and the bookshelf. Walk between the desks and wait near the coffee table.

src: walk toward copier turn past shelves toward middle of room in front of pallet table
tgt: Walk toward the copier and turn left. Walk past the shelves and toward the middle of the room. Stop in front of the pallet table.

src: walk into bedroom once inside right straight into bathroom walk wait here
tgt: Walk into bedroom.  Once inside, turn right, and walk straight into the bathroom.  Walk to shower.  Wait here.

src: enter bedroom next hallway bathroom wait in en suite bathroom next shower
tgt: Enter the bedroom next to the hallway bathroom. Wait in the en suite bathroom, next to the shower.

src: lamp in bedroom sink in bathroom shower
tgt: Go to the lamp in the bedroom. Go to the sink in the bathroom. Go to the shower.

src: continue rest of stairs turn at top walk towards closet turn hallway bedroom down at end of hallway turn in front of beds
tgt: continue walking up the rest of the stairs, turn left at the top and walk towards the closet. Turn left down the hallway and enter the bedroom straight down at the end of the hallway, turn left and stand in front of the two beds.

src: down stairs
tgt: Walk down the stairs.

src: stairs until hard right hallway parallel stairs room at end of hallway move until at foot of beds
tgt: Continue up the stairs until you can turn a hard right and go down the hallway parallel to the stairs. Enter the room at the end of the hallway and move left until you're standing at the foot of the two beds.

src: steps inside then stairs level next blue art on wall
tgt: Go up the steps and inside. Then start up the stairs and stop where it becomes level, next to the blue art on the wall.

src: up circular stairs inside stairs inside on landing in front of blue art on wall
tgt: Walk up the circular stairs and go inside.  Go up the stairs inside.  Stop on the landing in front of the blue art on the wall.

src: walk forward stairs house stairs on first landing
tgt: Walk forward, and go up the stairs. Enter the house, and go up the stairs. Stop on the first landing.

src: down hallway turn at guitar wait in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hallway, turn left at the guitar, wait in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: pass glass wall right into bedroom stop by head of bed
tgt: pass glass wall. turn right into bedroom, stop by head of bed.

src: straight hallway first into bedroom in doorway of bedroom
tgt: Go straight down the hallway and take the first left into a bedroom. Stop in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: turn left past hose towards entrance of house right through doorway stairs couple of stairs then wait
tgt: Turn to the left and past the hose.  Go towards the entrance of the house and turn right.  Go through the doorway.  Proceed to the stairs. Go down a couple of stairs and then wait.

src: walk placemat right into doorway.walk right of flowerbed staircase third step of stairs
tgt: Walk to the placemat and turn right into the doorway.Walk to the right of the flowerbed and go down the staircase. Stop when you reach the third step of the stairs.

src: walk through rock way down outside patio towards front door walk into home through open door walk towards tile steps ahead on first few steps
tgt: Walk through the rock arched way down the outside patio towards the front door. Walk into the home through the open door. Walk towards the tile steps ahead and stop on the first few steps.

src: turn around down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: turn stairs towards door turn rest of stairs down stairs bottom of stairs stop wait there
tgt: Turn around and go down the stairs, towards the door.  Turn to go down the rest of the stairs.  Walk down the stairs.  When you get to the bottom of the stairs, stop and wait there.

src: down flights of stairs stop at end of stairs
tgt: Walk down the two flights of stairs, stop at the end of the stairs.

src: walk through kitchen outside wait on porch next chair
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and outside. Wait on the porch next to the chair.

src: turn around across hotel room exit through back door at second welcome mat
tgt: Turn around and walk across the hotel room. Exit through the back door. Stop at the second welcome mat.

src: walk forward through kitchen out of door outside on balcony on welcome mat once kitchen
tgt: Walk forward through the kitchen and out of the door. Go outside on the balcony. Stop on the welcome mat once you exit the kitchen.

src: down hallway right wait near entrance bathroom
tgt: Walk down the hallway and turn right. Wait near the entrance to the bathroom.

src: turn around down hallway then right by bathroom door
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hallway. Then turn to your right and stop by the bathroom door.

src: walk down hallway right at first doorway wait there
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway, take a right at the first doorway and wait there.

src: head toward room with white couch left toward kitchen then front door turn hall in front of stairs
tgt: Head toward the room with the white couch.  Go left toward the kitchen and then to the front door.  Turn left down the hall and stop in front of the stairs.

src: exit room head right hallway towards front door from front door turn at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the room and head right down the hallway towards the front door. From the front door, turn left and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: through doorway other doorways behind couch grey chairs entryway with rug turn left of stairs
tgt: Go through the doorway and passed the other doorways. Go behind the couch and the grey chairs. Go to the entryway with the rug and turn left. Stop to the left of the stairs.

src: enter glass door turn stairs down stairs midway at staircase
tgt: Enter the glass door. Turn left towards the stairs, and walk down the stairs, and stop midway at the staircase.

src: walk inside stairs on third step from top
tgt: Walk inside and start to go down the stairs.  Stop on the third step from the top.

src: enter house immediately right steps down
tgt: enter house and immediately turn right, take 3 steps down and stop.

src: stairs left in doorway across from stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. Stop in the doorway across from the stairs.

src: stairs left pair of doors into room with many faucets on pedestals
tgt: Go down these stairs and make a left and you will see a pair of doors leading into a room with many faucets on pedestals.

src: down stairs turn down stairs then at base of stairs wait
tgt: Walk down the stairs, turn left, walk down more stairs, then stop at the base of the stairs and wait.

src: walk past bed bedroom hard right in bathroom by shower
tgt: Walk past the bed to exit the bedroom and turn hard right. Stop in the bathroom by the shower.

src: walk around bed bedroom first right into bathroom in front of shower
tgt: Walk around the bed, and leave the bedroom. Take the first right into the bathroom. Stop in front of the shower.

src: through doorway on right of bedroom into hallway right in bathroom near sink
tgt: Go through the doorway on the right of the bedroom. Go into the hallway and turn right and stop in the bathroom near the sink.

src: exit room through glass door on right through room television at door on left past television turn room walk bottom of spiral staircase stop
tgt: Exit the room through the glass door on your right. Walk through the room to the television.  At the door on the left past the television, turn left and exit the room.  Walk to the bottom of the spiral staircase and stop.

src: head inside through glass door walk towards couches turn into hallway then immediately hard right wait by steps
tgt: Head inside through the glass door. Walk towards the couches.  Turn left into the hallway, then immediately turn hard right.  Wait by steps.

src: indoors table chairs tv then wait near stairs on left
tgt: Go indoors. Pass the table and chairs. Pass the tv then turn left. Wait near the stairs on the left.

src: exit room straight past couches on right way table chairs wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Go straight past the couches on the right. Walk all the way to the table and chairs and wait there.

src: walk towards couch in living room across from kitchen past couch dinning table at first dinning chair at table
tgt: Walk towards the couch in the living room that's across from the kitchen. Go past the couch and continue to the dinning table. Stop at the first dinning chair at the table.

src: exit through door way forward white sofa on right way forward until long table with white chairs there
tgt: Exit through the door, and walk all the way forward passing the white sofa on your right. Keep walking all the way forward until you see a long table with six white cushioned chairs, and stop there.

src: stairs turn wait in open doorway down hall on right
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Wait in the open doorway down the hall on the right.

src: turn bottom of stairs at bottom turn room past fireplace once room right hallway turn into first bedroom stop
tgt: Turn around and go to the bottom of the stairs. At the bottom, turn left and cross the room walking past the fireplace. Once you cross the room, turn right to enter the hallway. Turn left into the first bedroom and stop.

src: stairs after room turn past fireplace out of room into hall right first doorway stop
tgt: Go down the stairs.  After you reach the room, turn left. Walk past the fireplace, out of the room and into the hall. Turn right, walk to the first doorway, and stop.

src: walk around bed stop in doorway near painting
tgt: Walk around the bed and stop in the doorway near the painting.

src: walk around bed right through door into hallway
tgt: Walk around the bed and turn right. Go through the door and into the hallway.

src: closet towards bed right around bed past lounge on left out of room into hallway just outside of room in doorway hallway
tgt: Leaving the closet and going towards the bed take a right to go around the bed and past the lounge on your left go out of the room into the hallway and stop just outside of the room in the doorway to the hallway.

src: turn up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Turn left and walk up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: turn right at picture up stairs left at top of stairs
tgt: Turn right at the picture and walk up the stairs to the left. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: into room right of guitar art stairs at top of stairs with animal head sculpture in front of
tgt: Go into the room right of the guitar art and go up the stairs.  Stop at the top of the stairs with the animal head sculpture in front of you.

src: walk out of massage room left of pool in front of massage table
tgt: Walk left out of the massage room and to the left of the pool. Stop in front of the massage table.

src: walk into open room with exercise equipment turn past exercise machine towards pool walk into hallway near pool past potted plants near open door small room with massage bed
tgt: Walk into the open room with the exercise equipment. Turn left and walk past the exercise machine towards the pool. Walk into the hallway near the pool past the potted plants. Stop near the open door to a small room with a massage bed.

src: exit room with mural twin beds turn at doorway walk along narrow pathway on left enter into room directly in front of at end of path room bed painted fan on wall in doorway
tgt: Exit the room with the mural and two twin sized beds. Turn left at the doorway and walk along the narrow pathway on your left. Enter into the room directly in front of you at the end of the path. The room has one bed and a painted fan on the wall. Stop in the doorway.

src: face window right hallway right at banister turn towards pool table right before pool table again past pool table right through doorway
tgt: face window to outside, turn right to walk down hallway, turn right at banister, turn left and walk towards pool table, turn right before you pass the pool table, and left again, walk past the pool table, turn right and walk through doorway to bedroom, stop.

src: turn until black railing right walk other side of pool table door on far left right of tv bedroom
tgt: Turn left and walk until you reach the black railing and turn right. Walk to the other side of the pool table and enter the door on the far left to the right of the TV.  Stop when you enter the bedroom.

src: face window turn right straight hallway split in walk way right stairs on right pool table on left end of pool table first bedroom on left inside doorway
tgt: Face the window and turn to the right. Walk straight down the hallway. When you come to the split in the walk way go right. Walk passed the stairs on the right and the pool table on the left.  A the end of the pool table enter the first bedroom on the left. Stop inside the doorway.

src: enter room next door table chairs right into kitchen then into laundry room wait by sink
tgt: Enter the room next door. Pass the table and chairs. Turn right into the kitchen then turn left and go into the laundry room. Wait by the sink.

src: living room through dining room walk straight last right into kitchen in kitchen left into laundry room right past counter in laundry room
tgt: Leave the living room through the dining room. Walk straight and take the last right into the kitchen. In the kitchen take a left into the laundry room. Stop right past the counter in the laundry room.

src: turn right then laundry room wait there
tgt: Turn right and then turn left to enter the laundry room. Wait there.

src: walk past outdoor chairs on right home through open door left in front of round foyer table wait in dining room door threshold
tgt: Walk past outdoor chairs on the right. Enter the home through the open door. Make a left in front of the round foyer table. Wait in the dining room door threshold.

src: straight into house large door walk toward round table turn table wait at entrance of room on left
tgt: Go straight into the house using the large door and walk toward the round table. Turn left when you get to the table and wait at the entrance of the room on the left.

src: inside house through black archway then into ornate archway then
tgt: Go inside the house through the black archway, then turn left into the ornate archway and then stop.

src: walk through dining room with table on right past doorway on left table on right in between faucet marble cylinder on left
tgt: walk through the dining room with the table on your right, continue past a doorway on your left, a table on your right and stop in between the faucet and marble cylinder on your left.

src: turn around other end of room
tgt: Turn around and walk to the other end of the room.

src: straight until extra large table with chairs then by fake sink
tgt: Go straight until you pass the extra large table with chairs then stop by the fake sink.

src: walk past metal chairs into room with red bed head of right side of bed right through passageway walk into bathroom area past mirror in doorway shower
tgt: Walk past the two metal chairs into the room with the red bed.  Go to the head of the right side of the bed and turn right.  Walk through the passageway and walk into the bathroom area.  Walk past the mirror and stop in the doorway to the shower.

src: walk past metal chairs right past bed right hall into bathroom walk just inside shower
tgt: Walk past the metal chairs and right past the bed. Walk right down the hall and left into the bathroom. walk left and stop just inside the shower.

src: through doorway between chairs walk into bedroom right through doorway down hall into bathroom sinks into shower stop
tgt: Go through the doorway between the chairs. Walk into the bedroom and take a right. Go through the doorway and walk down the hall into the bathroom. Pass the sinks and go into the shower. Stop.

src: exit bathroom by straight then right straight second door on right enter that room wait at door
tgt: Exit the bathroom by walking straight then turn right and go straight and enter the second door on the right. Enter that room and wait at the door.

src: exit bathroom right in hall walk through doorway at end stop in bathroom doorway on right
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right in the hall. Walk through the doorway at the end and stop in the bathroom doorway on the right.

src: exit bathroom right narrow hallway just past sink on right just after through door opening stop at door opening at immediate right
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right down the narrow hallway just past the sink on your right. Just after you pass through a door opening, stop at the door opening that will be at your immediate right.

src: turn hallways with pictures on wall left into bedroom through open door turn degrees walk towards bathroom right outside door
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallways with the pictures on the wall.  They will be to your left.  Go into the bedroom through the open door.  Turn left 90 degrees and walk towards the bathroom stopping right outside the door.

src: right hallway with of paintings into bedroom turn next bed once bathroom
tgt: Go right down the hallway with all of the paintings and into the bedroom. Turn left next to the bed and stop once you reach the bathroom.

src: turn pictures on wall into bedroom at end of hall turn hall left of bed stop
tgt: Turn around and go passed the pictures on the wall. Go into the bedroom at the end of the hall and turn left. Enter the hall to the left of the bed and stop.

src: turn stairs wait there
tgt: Turn left and walk down three stairs. Wait there.

src: walk forward end of hallway turn down alongside railing until then turn down stairs once step
tgt: Walk forward to the end of the hallway and turn left. Walk down alongside the railing until it stops. Then turn and walk down the stairs. Stop once you get to the 3rd step.

src: exit bedroom turn left then hard left down third stair wait on stairs by banister
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left. Then turn hard left and walk down the third stair. Wait on the stairs by the banister.

src: walk through door left of fireplace slight right stairs wait on first landing of red stairs
tgt: Walk through the door to the left of the fireplace. Take a slight right to walk up the stairs. Wait on the first landing of the red stairs.

src: walk out door right once turn right white stairs once at top of white stairs turn right red stairs at top of first set of red stairs
tgt: Walk out the door to your right. Once out turn right and go up the white stairs. Once at the top of the white stairs turn right and go up the red stairs. Stop at the top of the first set of red stairs.

src: walk through open door right up stairs up stairs right wait at first landing
tgt: Walk through the open door and turn right. Walk up the stairs. Walk up more stairs to the right. Wait at the first landing.

src: exit bedroom stairs straight television on right at door

tgt: Go down the stairs and make a right and through the doorway, go into the bedroom a step, and turn left. Take a few steps into the bathroom and stop.

tgt: With the windows showing the pool outside to your left, walk forward, through the opening at the end of the hallway, then take a sharp right turn through a doorway onto carpeting. After you step onto the carpeting, enter the bedroom towards your immediate left.

src: walk past pool through doorway hall on right in bedroom on left
tgt: Walk past the pool and through the doorway. Go down the hall on the right and stop in the bedroom on the left.

tgt: Pass the pool and go indoors using the double glass doors. Pass the large table with chairs and turn left and wait by the wine bottles that have grapes by them.

tgt: Walk straight through the room and exit out the door on the left. Keep going past the large table and turn left. Walk down the hallway and stop when you reach the 2 entry ways. One in front of you and one to your right. The bar area is to your left.

src: continue straight until large marble pot then
tgt: Continue walking straight until you pass a large marble pot then turn left and stop.

tgt: Walk to the far end of the room and through the doorway. Wait to the left, at the beginning of the hallway.

Stop as soon as you are at the bottom of the stairs. The front door to the house will be slightly ahead of you and to the right.

src: turn stairs
tgt: Turn around and go down the stairs.

src: down stairs wait at sink
tgt: Walk down hall passed stairs to bathroom, wait at sink.

tgt: Walk down the hall and to the left of the end table. Walk past the brick wall and into the doorway to the left of the dining room and stop.

tgt: Exit the bedroom and wait at the top of the second set of steps in the kitchen.

tgt: Walk past floor runner. Wait at top of stairs.

tgt: Walk around the table towards the hallway and stop in the doorway.

Head forward and past the chair on your right and head through the doorway on your right, immediately after the chair.  Stop here you are at your destination.

src: kitchen left next left straight hallway into bathroom through third door on right in doorway
tgt: Leave the kitchen and take a left. Take the next left and go straight down the hallway. Go into the bathroom through the third door on your right and stop in the doorway.

src: exit kitchen hard left down hallway right at brown door down hallway bathroom wait at sink
tgt: Exit the kitchen, turn hard left, walk down hallway, turn right at the brown door, walk down the hallway, enter the bathroom wait at the sink.

src: door out of kitchen through small hallway left of dining room with large table into door as soon as painting of boy on beach
tgt: Go to the door out of the kitchen. and through the small hallway to the left of the dining room with the large table.  Turn into the door as soon as you pass a painting of a boy walking on a beach.

tgt: Exit the nook and walk past the piano. Go up the steps and to the left. wait in the hallway at the bottom of the steps.

tgt: Walk past the bookshelves and out through the open entry way to the next room with a piano. Walk along the wall past the piano and up the small set of steps. Turn the corner and walk past the dresser with a glass vase on top. Turn the corner and walk down the hallway with wooden cabinets against the wall.

src: left walk towards piano left at piano up steps down stairs on left wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Take a left and walk towards the piano. Take a left at the piano and walk up the steps. Walk down the stairs on the left and wait at the bottom of the stairs.

tgt: turn around and go straight towards the pool then take a right and walk past the couches to the next doorway and  then stop right under the doorway.

tgt: Walk towards the pool on the right side. Walk into the seating area on the patio and enter the house. Stop inside the house before you reach the carpet.

tgt: Turn around and walk towards the pool. Walk around the pool to your right, keeping the barbeque grill area to your left. When you get to the grill area make a right back towards the house. Go through the black double doors and wait just inside in front of the foosball table.

src: through doorway by pictures of new york yankees player into living by tan support column
tgt: Go through the doorway by the pictures of the New York Yankees player. go into the living and stop by the tan support column.

src: movie room across hall into living room wait
tgt: You need to leave the movie room and go across the hall into the living room and wait.

src: exit room door on right then down hallway until living room with tv couches wait there
tgt: Exit the room using the door on your right then turn left and walk down the hallway until you get to the living room with tv and couches. Wait there.

src: walk out of closet into bathroom then left bathroom walk on right side of bedroom room left in hall then right stairs walk past steps wait in hall on far left
tgt: Walk out of the closet and into the bathroom then make a left to leave the bathroom. Walk on the right side of the bedroom and leave the room. Make a left in the hall then make a right to go to the stairs. Walk past the steps and wait in the hall on the far left.

src: straight ahead into bathroom then into bedroom door walk past pool table past top of stairs straight start of windows wait there
tgt: Go straight ahead and into the bathroom.  Then turn left and go into the bedroom.  Go out the door and walk past the pool table.  Go past the top of the stairs.  Go straight to the start of the windows.  Wait there.

src: closet bathroom out of bedroom into hallway in hallway past pool table stairs straight through archway in front of light switch
tgt: Leave the closet and the bathroom and go out of the bedroom into the hallway. In the hallway go past the pool table and stairs and go straight through the archway, and stop in front of the light switch.

src: slight left into large area with tables by table with black chairs
tgt: Take a slight left. Walk into large area with tables. Stop by table with black chairs.

src: walk table left past desk stop by white shelf
tgt: Walk pas the table and to the left. Walk past the desk and stop by the white shelf.

src: stand between white shelf long wooden table black tan white chairs empty aside from single plant
tgt: Stand between the white shelf and the long wooden table that has black, tan, and white chairs and is empty aside from a single plant.

src: turn past living room outside next outdoor kitchen
tgt: Turn left and walk past the living room and go outside. Stop next to the outdoor kitchen.

src: walk between grey couch on left wall with blue painting on on right doorway directly in from of house outside next marble-topped bar with sink in
tgt: Walk between the grey couch on your left and the wall with the blue painting on it on your right.  Walk thought the doorway directly in from of you to exit the house.  Stop when you are outside, next to the marble-topped bar with the sink in it.

src: walk forward through doorway onto patio wait in front of sink
tgt: Walk forward through the doorway, onto the patio, and wait in front of the sink.

src: exit room by door left of bed linen closet on right hand wall just past bathroom
tgt: Exit the room by the door to the left of the bed and enter the linen closet on the right hand wall just past the bathroom.

src: exit room then right on second door wait in closet
tgt: Exit the room then turn right on the second door and wait in the closet.

src: exit bedroom forward toward first doorway on right inside door way
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk forward toward the first doorway on your right.  Stop inside the door way.

src: walk across room right until grey chairs turn up short stairs leftmost room
tgt: Walk across the room staying to the right until you reach some grey chairs. Turn left and walk up the short stairs and enter the leftmost room.

tgt: Move forward and turn left once past the white couch. Continue up the first set of stairs and turn left, moving past the bar area into the home theater. Stop just inside the doorway.

tgt: Walk past the couch, turn left, walk to the stairs, go up the stairs, turn left, enter the room, wait at the chair.

tgt: Walk through the hallway away from painting of the man to your right. Walk passed the sitting area and continue through the hallway toward a sculpture of two animals in a niche to your right. Once you get to the animal sculptures in the niche on your right, wait there. You should also see a tapestry hanging on the wall to your left.

tgt: Turn around and walk down the hallway. Go past the front door and continue until you reach the shelf on the right side with an animal statue and stop.

tgt: Walk past the living room on the right. Walk past the wall tapestry on the left. Wait under the round skylight.

tgt: Exit the room. Turn left then turn left again and wait near the pool table.

tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left.  Walk until you see a pool table and then stop at the end with the triangle.

tgt: Exit the bathroom. turn left and to until you see a pool table. Go to the pool table.

src: walk past dining table right staircase stop at top
tgt: Walk past the dining table and go right.  Go up the staircase and stop at the top.

tgt: Go across the wooden floor to the left of the table, go up the stairs to the right, at the top of the stairs stop.

tgt: walk past the table and then turn right.  Then walk up the stairs to the top.  Stay there.

tgt: ascend the stairs and then go to your left and go down the hallway and then turn left again and stop right before the kitchen table.

tgt: Walk across main workroom, turn left at stone hallway and stop.

tgt: Walk straight and slightly right. Turn left and go into the hallway. Wait there.

Wait by the lamp on your left.

Turn the corner and walk through the first open door on the right into a bedroom with floral bedspread blanket.

tgt: walk away from movie room towards couch, turn right before hardwood floor and walk down hallway, take first left, stop in doorway to bedroom.
