src: walk along brick path left up steps past hot tub on right down steps on left through rock garden wait near patio chairs
tgt: Walk along the brick path to the left. Walk up the two steps and go past the hot tub on the right. Walk down the two steps on the left and go through the rock garden. Wait near the patio chairs.

src: path on patio steps across rocks first patio chair on left
tgt: Go down the path on the patio, go up the steps, go across the rocks to the first patio chair on the left.

src: brick walkway towards brick stairs into large room on left before stairs.wait
tgt: Go down the brick walkway towards the brick stairs.  Go into the large room on the left, before you get to the stairs.Wait.

src: walk open double doors walk along patio woven lounge chairs walk into open double doors on other side of lounge chairs into home
tgt: Walk passed the open double doors. Walk along the patio passing the woven lounge chairs. Walk into the open double doors on the other side of the lounge chairs and into the home.

src: walk straight along path past table chairs turn on first open doors
tgt: Walk straight along the path past the table and chairs and turn left and enter on the first open doors you see.

src: walk through open door ahead into lounge area with small beds then through door on opposite end of room into wooden floored room up counter area near plate on counter
tgt: Walk through the open door ahead into the lounge area with two small beds. Then walk through the door on the opposite end of the room. Into the wooden floored room and walk up to the counter area near the plate on the counter.

src: exit sauna through door at other side of room stop in lobby by elevator
tgt: exit sauna, walk through door at other side of room stop in lobby by elevator.

src: step out of sauna turn past massage tables glass shelf out of room straight straight ahead into room walk past stairs stop by desk
tgt: Step out of the sauna and turn left. Walk past the massage tables and the glass shelf. Walk out of the room and go straight. Walk straight ahead into the room. Walk past the stairs and stop by the desk.

src: walk forward towards gray chair right hallway up stairs wait near bathroom on left
tgt: Walk forward towards the gray chair. Turn right and continue down the hallway. Walk up the stairs and wait near the bathroom on the left.

src: exit bedroom head for staircase stop at landing
tgt: Exit bedroom and head for staircase, stop at the landing.

src: bedroom hall stairs outside of bathroom on left
tgt: Leave the bedroom, and go down the hall. Go up the stairs, and stop outside of the bathroom on the left.

src: straight stairs head toward stairs down steps after turn left wait by table chairs
tgt: Go straight and pass the stairs going up. Head toward the stairs going down and go down the steps. After you go down turn left and wait by the table and chairs.

src: walk around circular glass panels right stairs at bottom of stairs turn wait in front of glass table
tgt: Walk around the circular glass panels to the right and continue down the stairs. At the bottom of the stairs, turn left and wait in front of the glass table.

src: with window right forward stairs down bottom of stairs then at bottom turn steps downwards
tgt: With the window to your right, head forward to the stairs leading down. Climb down to the bottom of those stairs and then at the bottom, turn left and take three more steps downwards.

src: turn body right up stairs stairs in stair area by light switch set of stairs
tgt: Turn body right and walk up the stairs. Continue up the stairs in the smaller stair area. Take a left by the light switch and continue up the smaller set of stairs.

src: walk upstairs living room walk next set of stairs wait
tgt: Walk upstairs to the living room.  Walk halfway up the next set of stairs and wait.

src: up first set of stairs then second step of stairs at fourth top step
tgt: Walk up the first set of stairs. Then walk up the second step of stairs, and stop at the fourth top step.

src: step forward turn kitchen left doorway wait near sink
tgt: Step forward, turn left and enter the kitchen. Keep to your left, enter the doorway, and wait near the sink.

src: forward with wooden chairs on left at end of hall through door turn again through door in kitchen
tgt: Walk forward with three wooden chairs on your left. Turn left at the end of the hall, and go through that door. Turn left again, and go through that door. You will end up in a kitchen.

src: past chairs on left turn into room turn into room on left wait near sink
tgt: Go past the three chairs on the left. Turn left. Go into the room. Turn left and go into the room on the left. Wait near the sink.

src: straight then into last room from left turn into closet wait there
tgt: Go straight and then go into the last room starting from the left. Turn left and go into the closet. Wait there.

src: away from musical instruments.turn corner walk through door bedroom closest stairs then into room closet
tgt: Walk away from the musical instruments.Turn the corner and walk through the door to the bedroom closest to the stairs. Then go into that room's closet.

src: walk forward then door right once in door left once closet
tgt: Walk forward and then turn left when it opens up. Enter the door the right Once in, enter the door to your left and stop once you enter the closet.

src: exit bathroom steps wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom and go up the steps. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit bathroom bedroom up steps stand at bottom of stairs next art with blue lines
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Exit the bedroom. Walk up the steps. Go stand at the bottom of the stairs, next to the art with blue lines.

src: bathroom up stairs turn at base of stairs
tgt: Leave bathroom to bedroom, walk up stairs, turn left and stop at base of stairs going up.

src: exit conference room right hallway left into first open door wait just inside room
tgt: Exit the conference room. Make a right and go down the hallway. Make a left into the first open door and wait just inside the room.

src: turn right around office table door turn
tgt: Turn right and go around the office table. Exit the door labelled 01. Turn left and stop.

src: conference room right down hall classroom through first door on left once door
tgt: Leave the conference room and go right. Walk down the hall, and enter the classroom through the first door on the left. Stop once you pass the door.

src: walk out of room with mechanical devices down hall over mosaic tile through first open door massage beds inside
tgt: Walk out of the room with the mechanical devices. Walk down the hall over the mosaic tile and through the first open door to left that has the two massage beds inside.

src: exit room first door on left wait at end of massage tables
tgt: Exit the room, enter the first door on the left.  Wait at the end of the massage tables.

src: walk forward past table right then through doorway forward then in first room on left at end of massage table
tgt: walk forward past the table.  Take a right then walk through the doorway.  Continue forward, then go in the first room on the left.  Stop at the end of the massage table.

src: exit room right then hallway walk straight until front room wait near christmas trees
tgt: Exit the room. Turn right then continue down the hallway. Walk straight until you get to the front room. Wait near the two Christmas trees.

src: exit room right corridor christmas tree room ahead wait by mirror
tgt: Exit room, and make a right to go down corridor.  Pass the Christmas tree, and enter the room straight ahead.  Wait by mirror.

src: exit right way forward towards very end room in front of inside room in front of small christmas tree
tgt: Exit, and turn right. Walk all the way forward towards the very end room that is in front of you. Enter inside the room, and stop in front of the two small Christmas tree.

src: into room right into room next door table chairs then bed into bathroom on right wait near sink
tgt: Go into the room. Turn right and go into the room next door. Pass the table and chairs then pass the bed and go into the bathroom on the right. Wait near the sink.

src: bathroom bedroom bedroom through door on right in bedroom bathroom through door on left of bed in front of sink
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and bedroom. Enter the bedroom through the door on the right in the bedroom. Enter the bathroom through the door on the left of the bed. Stop in front of the sink.

src: straight into bedroom right through next door into bathroom in back right corner
tgt: Go straight into the bedroom and turn right. Go through the next door and into the bathroom in the back right corner.

src: walk along edge of house house through patio door
tgt: walk along the edge of the house and enter the house through the patio door.

src: walk along outside of house underneath glass overhang entrance with glass double doors building wait
tgt: Walk along the outside of the house underneath the glass overhang. You will come to an entrance with glass double doors. Enter the building and wait.

src: walk toward area harbor through doors building next birdcage
tgt: Walk toward the sitting area that overlooks the harbor and go left through the doors to enter the building.  Stop next to the birdcage.

src: exit bathroom right through second door on right
tgt: Exit bathroom and turn right. Go through second door on the right and stop.

src: forward bathroom through door in front of as through doorway move forward past chair left wait in between open doors right
tgt: Move forward to exit the bathroom through the door in front of you. As you walk through the doorway move forward past a chair and sink to your left. Wait in between the two open doors to your right.

src: exit bathroom door hard right straight wait by second door on right
tgt: Exit the bathroom door. Turn hard right and continue straight.  Wait by the second door on the right.

src: right into hallway turn into room with rug
tgt: Turn right into the hallway. Turn left and and go into the room with the rug.

src: exit bedroom turn hall into room ahead before desk with green chairs
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left. Continue down the hall and into the room straight ahead and stop before the desk with two green chairs.

src: exit closet right bedroom hallway in hallway first door on left then straight hallway until light wood table with green chairs
tgt: Exit the closet and make a right to exit the bedroom and enter the hallway.  In the hallway, take the first door on your left.  Then walk straight down that hallway until you get to the light wood table with the two green chairs.

src: walk into bedroom right right into closet turn into bathroom in bathroom
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and turn right. Turn right and walk into the closet. Turn left and walk into the bathroom. Stop in the bathroom.

src: walk towards room with red bed right right before room down hallway second hallway once into room
tgt: Walk towards the room with the red bed, turn right - right before you get to the room. Walk down the hallway, take a left down the second hallway and stop once you walk into the room.

src: walk past silver chairs into bedroom right then right again past glass bookshelf turn wait near desk
tgt: Walk past the two silver chairs and into the bedroom. Turn right and then right again. Walk past the glass bookshelf and turn left. Wait near the desk.

src: exit kitchen dining room walk into office ahead in office next stairs
tgt: Exit the kitchen  and enter the dining room. Walk into the office straight ahead and wait in the office that is next to the stairs.

src: around bar doorway straight ahead once room towards stairs door right of stairs once inside office
tgt: Go around the bar to exit out the doorway straight ahead. Once out, cross the room towards the stairs. Enter the door to the right of the stairs. Stop once inside the office.

src: kitchen into dining room past foot of stairs through archway wait by desk in home office
tgt: Leave the kitchen and go into the dining room. Go past the foot of the stairs and Walk through the archway. Wait by the desk in the home office.

src: turn around out of bathroom right through doorway wait next lockers
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom and take a right. Walk through the doorway and wait next to the lockers.

src: out of bathroom exercise room right hallway slight right
tgt: Go out of the bathroom to the exercise room.  Turn right and go down the hallway.  Make a slight right and stop.

src: exit bathroom right then into door on right right wait near basket
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Then go into the door on the right and turn right. Wait near the basket.

src: pool right forward until just end of pool walk around planter on left then forward up step straight ahead until next third of planters planters on right next third planter await further orders
tgt: Keeping the swimming pool to your right, move forward until you just pass the end of the pool. Walk around the planter on your left, then go forward and up the one step. Move straight ahead until you are next to the third of the three planters. Keep the planters on your right, Stop next to the third planter and await further orders.

src: turn around past pool next block wall near patio doors
tgt: Turn around and walk past the pool and stand next to the block wall near the patio doors.

src: walk towards end of pool with steps in pool straight steps of pool double doors indoors near door small plants on ground
tgt: Walk towards the end of the pool with the steps to get in the pool. Walk straight passed the steps of the pool to the double doors to go indoors. Stop near the door and the three small plants on the ground.

src: pass couch dining table towards bar turn left then in hall next thermostat
tgt: Go pass the couch and the dining table. Go towards the bar and turn left. Then stop in the hall next to the thermostat.

src: along white couch room circle table towards front door before front door right straight left at counter with chair stop at thermostat
tgt: Go along the white couch and cross the room passed the circle table, go towards the front door and before the front door make a right, go straight, and make a left at the counter with the chair and stop at the thermostat.

src: after sitting room through dinning area left at kitchen now into hallway wait next glass door outside
tgt: After you leave the sitting room walk through the dinning area and make left at the kitchen. Now go into the hallway and wait next to the glass door going outside.

src: into bathroom across bathroom turn right in doorway at bed
tgt: Leave closet into bathroom, walk across the bathroom turn right and stop in the doorway looking at the bed.

src: walk past bathroom vanity wait at bedroom door threshold
tgt: Walk past bathroom vanity. Wait at bedroom door threshold.

src: straight past double sinks turn right bedroom wait right there
tgt: Go straight, past the double sinks.  Turn to the right and there will be a bedroom.  Wait right there.

src: walk out of bedroom right railing stop after american flag
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and make a right. Follow the railing and stop after passing the American flag.

src: exit bedroom right hallway forward until end of paisley carpet turn forward toward american flag then few steps forward into room about feet from corner of fireplace
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right to face the hallway.  Walk forward until you reach the end of the paisley carpet and turn left.  Walk forward toward the American flag, then take a few steps forward into the room and stop about 2 feet from the corner of the fireplace.

src: behind stairs american flag stop near
tgt: Go behind you and walk passed the stairs and go passed the american flag and stop near it.

src: enter kitchen walk railing on balcony past table on right
tgt: Enter the kitchen. Walk to the railing on the balcony past the table on the right.

src: walk between kitchen counter table stop at glass partition into family room below wait
tgt: Walk between the kitchen counter and dining table and stop at the glass partition.  Look into the family room below and wait.

src: into kitchen then at end turn right then at stairs turn at bottom of stairs towards fireplace wait behind couches
tgt: Go into the kitchen and then at the end turn right. Then turn left at the stairs and go down. Turn left at the bottom of the stairs and go towards the fireplace. Wait behind the couches.

src: walk opposite side of area wait there
tgt: Walk to the opposite side of the dining area and wait there.

src: straight until many round tables with chairs large table on left head until round tables with chairs
tgt: Go straight until you pass many round tables with chairs. When you pass the large table on the left. Head straight until you get to more round tables with chairs.

src: turn around middle of dining room open once area other side of dining room left of last column on right once first table stop
tgt: Turn around and walk to the middle of the dining room where it is open. Once you reach this area, enter the other side of the dining room to the left of the last column on the right. Once you pass the first table, stop.

src: exit bathroom right kitchen bar with stools/chairs straight glass door balcony wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Pass the kitchen bar with stools/chairs and continue going straight. Go out the glass sliding door to the balcony and wait there.

src: exit bathroom through open doorway right into kitchen area past island forward until first light grey couch with pillows on about foot away from corner of grey couch
tgt: Exit the bathroom through the open doorway.  Turn right and walk into the kitchen area.  Walk past the island and continue forward until you reach the first light grey couch with three striped pillows on it.  Stop about a foot away from the corner of the grey couch.

src: turn right doorway room room by first opening on right through kitchen walk past kitchen island toward balcony in front of chaise on balcony
tgt: Turn right to enter doorway to dining room. Leave dining room by first opening on the right. Walk through kitchen. Walk past the kitchen island toward balcony. Stop in front of the closest chaise on the balcony.

src: bottom of stairs right down bottom of stairs turn toward open door right through open doors in front of shrub
tgt: Go down to the bottom of the stairs. Turn right and walk down to the bottom of the stairs. Turn left and walk toward the open door. Turn right and go through the open doors and stop in front of the shrub.

src: walk way down stairs at bottom turn forward towards black doors on right outside out doors once
tgt: Walk all the way down the stairs. At the bottom turn left and walk forward towards the 2 black doors on your right leading outside. Walk out the doors and stop once out.

src: stairs floor turn at bottom of stairs forward toward double glass doors on right through double glass doors outside wait there
tgt: Go down the stairs to the lower floor. Turn left at the bottom of the stairs. Go forward toward the double glass doors on the right. Go through the double glass doors leading outside. Wait there.

src: exit bathroom floor changes from white
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Stop where the floor changes from white to wooden.

src: walk around tub through door at end left through little room with sink cabinets into bedroom on other side just after bedroom
tgt: Walk around the tub and go through the door at the end to the left.  Walk through the little room with the sink and cabinets and into the bedroom on the other side.  Stop just after entering the bedroom.

src: walk between bathtub chair through bathroom walk through archway right of towel ring through archways stop wait next trophy
tgt: Walk between the bathtub and the chair through the bathroom. Walk through the archway to the right of the towel ring. Walk through two archways. Stop and wait next to the trophy.

src: stand behind first of chairs at kitchen bar
tgt: Go stand behind the first of three chairs at the kitchen bar.

src: sink through archway right of sink candelabra travel along candelabra wall brown chair at end of counter
tgt: Locate the sink. Go through the archway to the right of the sink. locate the candelabra. Travel along the candelabra wall to the brown chair at the end of a counter.

src: bar area left left behind couch behind first chair at table
tgt: Leave the bar area and take a left. Take a left behind the couch. Stop behind the first chair at the table.

src: stairs turn left towards kitchen stop near sink
tgt: Go up the stairs and turn left. Go towards the kitchen and stop near the sink.

src: step right way up steps straight until hallway right down steps before near kitchen counter
tgt: Take a step, turn right and walk all the way up the steps, walk straight until you've reach a hallway, turn right and walk down the steps before stopping near the kitchen counter.

src: stairs then straight steps right toward kitchen next kitchen island with sink
tgt: Go up the stairs then walk straight and go down the steps and turn right toward the kitchen. Stop next to the kitchen island with the sink.

src: hall first doorway on left in area in front of door
tgt: Go down the hall to the first doorway on the left and stop in the sitting area in front of the door.

src: exit office room quick left wait near black leather bench on left
tgt: Exit the office room, make a quick left and wait near the black leather bench, located on your left.

src: exit room turn left into room with stairs stop between large wooden door seating area
tgt: Exit the room and turn left. Go into the room with stairs. Stop between the large wooden door and the seating area.

src: into living room patio exit covered part of patio on cris cross stone
tgt: Go into the living room and towards the patio. Exit the covered part of the patio, and stop on the cris cross stone.

src: walk out backyard around couches outside once down steps
tgt: Walk out to the backyard. Go around the couches outside and wait once you walk down the two steps.

src: move through living room towards patio doors through patio doorway move straight across patio wait at step
tgt: Move through living room towards patio doors. Move through patio doorway. Move straight across patio and wait at step.

src: exit bedroom mirror at top of stairs foyer wait at front door of house
tgt: Exit the bedroom, walk to the mirror at the top of the stairs, enter the foyer, wait at the front door of the house.

src: walk out of bedroom right into hallway down on rug in front of doorway
tgt: Walk out of bedroom and turn right into hallway. Walk down and wait on rug in front of doorway.

src: exit bedroom hallway left straight mirror on rug
tgt: exit bedroom to hallway. follow hallway to the left, walk straight passed mirror and stop on rug.

src: exit room into through room with white chairs next set of white art peices on wall square piece in middle between taller peices
tgt: Exit the room, going into and through the room with three white lounging chairs. Stop next to the set of three white art peices on the wall, one square piece in the middle between two longer and taller peices.

src: step out of bathroom straight left after beverage bar
tgt: step out of the bathroom and go straight. take a left after the beverage bar.

src: exit ladies room walk straight past wicker basket on floor walk past metal wall art wait at end of bed of river rocks
tgt: Exit the ladies room, and walk straight past the wicker basket on the floor. Walk past the metal wall art, and wait at the end of the bed of river rocks.

src: walk past bed first right into bathroom forward into toilet closet in doorway
tgt: Walk past the bed and take the first right into the bathroom. Walk forward into the toilet closet. Stop in the doorway.

src: walk through bedroom walk through door on right side into bathroom straight wait in doorway toilet room
tgt: Walk through the bedroom and walk through the door on the right side, into the bathroom. Continue straight and wait in the doorway to the toilet room.

src: walk into bedroom exit through door left of tv after through door bathroom straight until in front of toilet then
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and exit through the door to the left of the TV.  After going through this door to the bathroom, keep going straight until you stand in front of the toilet and then stop.

src: exit room through swinging doors bedroom on right in front of bed
tgt: Exit the room through the swinging doors. Enter the bedroom on the right and stop in front of the bed.

src: walk through white swinging doorway across form area right into bedroom next blue wicker chair at foot of bed
tgt: Walk through the white swinging doorway across form the sitting area. Take a right into the bedroom. Stop next to the blue wicker chair at the foot of the bed.

src: head toward stairs stairs into room on right then right into bedroom wait near bed
tgt: Head toward the stairs when you pass the stairs go into the room on your right and then turn right and go into the bedroom. Wait near the bed.

src: tapestry on right then straight ahead.turn towards sofas walk behind far sofa
tgt: Put the tapestry on your right, then walk straight ahead.Turn left, walking towards the sofas. Walk behind the far sofa.

src: step forward turn forward wait behind couch
tgt: Step forward, turn left and walk forward, wait behind the couch.

src: walk past tapestry on right past glass coffee table on right past french doors on right wait behind chesterfield sofa
tgt: Walk past the tapestry on the right. Walk past the glass coffee table on the right. Walk past the french doors on the right. Wait behind the chesterfield sofa.

src: through open door in room other rooms in house doorway so across hallway through open brown wooden door room with large carpets through room across first carpet across doors on other side of white table doors just other side of doorway that outside patio there
tgt: Go through the one open door in the room that leads to other rooms in the house.  When you exit that doorway, so across the hallway through the open brown wooden door that leads to a room with two large carpets.  Walk through the room, across the first carpet and across to the doors on the other side of the white table.  Open the doors to outside and step just to the other side of the doorway that looks outside to a patio.  Stop there.

src: straight through sets of doors into big room with table in middle around left of table stop at door in back of room
tgt: Go straight through both sets of doors and into the big room with the table in the middle. Go around the left of the table and stop at the door in the back of the room.

src: walk through white classdoors then through class brown doors walk pas table with vase in right of white chair
tgt: Walk through the two white classdoors, and then continue to walk through the class brown doors. Walk pas the table with the vase in it, and stop to the right of the white chair.

src: stairs u turn right straight turn on second door wait at entrance
tgt: Go up the stairs. U turn right. Go straight and turn left on the second door. Wait at the entrance.

src: stairs right down hallway past paintings bedroom through second door on left in doorway
tgt: Go up the stairs and go right. Walk down the hallway past the paintings. Enter the bedroom through the second door on the left. Stop in the doorway.

src: walk top of stairs right down hallway past paintings at bedroom door
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs and turn right. Walk down the hallway past the paintings. Stop at the bedroom door.

src: step onto wooden deck right forward right again building wait in doorway of first room on left
tgt: Step onto the wooden deck and turn right. Walk forward and turn right again, entering the building. Wait in the doorway of the first room on the left.

src: walk around corner right into building walk into opening on left stop
tgt: Walk around the corner and right into the building. Walk into the opening on the left and stop.

src: walk into building first doorway on left stop
tgt: Walk into the building. Go to the first doorway on the left. Stop.

src: after stairs slightly right between fake sink marble pot turn into hallway then right into bedroom bed then into bathroom wait by white chair
tgt: After you go up the stairs turn slightly left and go right between the fake sink and the marble pot. Turn left into that hallway and then turn right and go into the bedroom. Pass the bed then go left into the bathroom. Wait by the white chair.

src: head between white drinking fountain floor decoration left hallway first bedroom on right past bed into bathroom by towel rack
tgt: Head between the white drinking fountain and the floor decoration. Make a left and go down the hallway. Enter the first bedroom on the right. Walk past the bed and into the bathroom. Stop by the towel rack.

src: walk towards faucet sculpture past on left side walk right of marble cylinder doorway walk through doorway right of long rug around foot of bed through doorway on left in front of towel rack
tgt: walk towards the faucet sculpture, continue past it on left side and walk to the right of the marble cylinder to the doorway. Walk through the doorway to the right of the long rug, around the foot of the bed, and through the doorway on the left. Stop in front of the towel rack.

src: exit closet toward bed turn door right hallway past kitchen steps wait near couch
tgt: Exit the closet toward the bed. Turn left and go out the door. Turn right and go down the hallway and past the kitchen. Go down the steps and wait near the couch.

src: exit bedroom turn right stairs wait at end of stairs by couch
tgt: Exit the bedroom turn right and go down the stairs.  Wait at the end of the stairs by the couch.

src: forward turn forward right
tgt: Go forward. Turn left. Go forward. Turn right. Go to couch and stop.

src: indoors walk straight until almost past stairs on left right into room wait at entrance
tgt: Go indoors. Walk straight until you almost past the stairs on the left and turn right into the room. Wait at the entrance.

src: enter house past fireplace right enter area wait
tgt: Enter house, walk past the fireplace and make a right and enter dinning area, and wait.

src: walk into building past fireplace walk through door on right in doorway
tgt: Walk into the building and past the fireplace. Walk through the door on the right and stop in the doorway.

src: turn past bar with chairs turn straight right into bedroom wait near bed
tgt: Turn left and go past the bar with the chairs. Turn left and go straight. Turn right and go into the bedroom. Wait near the bed.

src: walk around counter in front of into kitchen walk around seating wet bar area turn through doorway right of refrigerator first left first right into bedroom wait there
tgt: Walk around the counter in front of you into the kitchen. Walk around the seating wet bar area and turn left. Walk through the doorway to the right of the refrigerator make the first left and the first right into a bedroom. Wait there.

src: walk along granite counter around corner into kitchen area past central counter with chairs around through arched door on other end of counter near refrigerator corner right after hallway walk into first open door on right with painting on wall
tgt: Walk along the granite counter and continue around the corner into the kitchen area. Walk past the central counter with chairs around it. Continue through the arched door on the other end of the counter near the refrigerator. Turn the corner to the right after entering the hallway. Walk into the first open door on the right with a painting on the wall nearest to it.

src: exit bathroom walk past blue door through door house stop
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Walk past the blue chairs to the door. Go through the door and exit the house. Stop.

src: exit bathroom right across room with christmas christmas tree on left through doorway in front of door with oval glass window in after though door through second door directly in front of building outside on porch with white columns
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right.  Walk across the room with the Christmas three.  The Christmas tree will be on your left.  Walk through the doorway in front of you that has a door with an oval glass window in it.  After you walk though that door, walk through a second door that is directly in front of you.  You will be leaving the building.  Stop when you are outside on the porch with the white columns.

src: turn bathroom right towards blue chairs then through doorway behind right outside
tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom. Turn right and walk towards the blue chairs. Go passed them and then through the doorway behind them. Stop right outside.

src: walk past fireplace through arch way past arch way right bedroom right of photos of kids in doorway room
tgt: Walk past the fireplace and go through the arch way. Past the arch way take a right and enter the bedroom to the right of the photos of the kids. Stop in the doorway to the room.

src: walk right of couch slight left through archway hard right in hallway enter bedroom next too bench
tgt: Walk right to end of couch, turn left and walk to fireplace, turn slight left and walk through archway, turn hard right in hallway and enter bedroom, stop next too bench.

src: turn right up counter turn past fireplace walk over archway right at pictures on wall straight into door on by pictures
tgt: Turn to the right and walk up to the counter. Turn left and walk past the fireplace. Walk over to the archway. Turn right at the pictures on the wall and go straight. Go into the door on the left by the pictures.

src: turn right into room turn past wall with holes in glass doors on right outside then
tgt: Turn right and go into the room turn left and walk past the wall with holes in it. Go out the glass doors on the right to go outside and then stop.

src: turn then door right once out door turn past chairs on left table chairs on right wood petition right doors on left leading outside stop
tgt: Turn around. and then go out the door to your right. Once out the door turn left and walk past the chairs on the left and table and chairs on the right. Go out the wood petition and turn right. Go to the doors on your left leading outside and stop.

src: hall into dining area past table back door there outside
tgt: Go down the hall and into a dining area.  Go past the table and towards the back door, wait there facing outside.

src: stairs u turn past table chairs turn wait near stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs. U turn left and walk past the table and chairs. Turn left and wait near the stairs going down.

src: descend stairs sharp stair case toward table left at staircase downwards
tgt: Descend stairs,make sharp left around stair case toward dinning table, make a left and stop at staircase going downwards.

src: turn stairs turn way around beneath stairs just before door on left

When you get to the door go inside and make a left, you should now be by the kitchen and in front of a narrow doorway. Go through the doorway and into the doorway of the bedroom across the hall, stop in the bedroom doorway and wait.

After you enter the house, walk through the living room.  Walk between the couch and the television mounted on the wall, with the television on your left. Before you reach the end of the hall turn to the right towards the top of the stairs. Walk down the stairs to the first landing and turn to face the rest of the stairs leading down.

tgt: go down stairs. walk forward towards living room. Turn hard right and walk across living room to balcony outside. Top at the balcony.

tgt: Go to the post. Go down two stairs. Go to the light switch. Go to the plant. Go to the endtable. Go to the balcony.

src: door outside degrees left then forward left forward past dinning table on left then after chair on right right into hallway at door right
tgt: Facing the door to the outside, turn 90 degrees to the left, then go forward and to the left. Move forward past the dinning table on your left. Then after passing the 2nd chair on your right, turn right and step into the hallway, stopping at the door to your right.

src: in table with chandelier right on first door by door on right
tgt: Go in and pass the table with the hanging chandelier. Turn right on the first door you see and wait by the door on your right.

src: though opening left through room with table chairs through first door on right right once room
tgt: Go though the opening to your left and walk through the room with the table and chairs. Walk through the first door on your right and stop to the right once you enter the room.

src: walk into room spiral stairs wait there
tgt: Walk straight into the room. Go up the spiral stairs. Wait there.

src: exit stairs door directly ahead spiral staircase at top
tgt: Exit the stairs and open the door directly ahead. Climb up the spiral staircase. Stop at the top.

src: stand at top of stairs room with ceiling light in front of door circular stairs on last step from top
tgt: Stand at the top of the stairs and enter the room with the ceiling light in front of the door.  Go up the circular stairs and stop on the last step from the top.

src: bathroom move towards bed in center of wood floor next refrigerator
tgt: Leave the bathroom and move towards the bed. Stop in the center of the wood floor next to the refrigerator.

src: hall living area turn wait near refrigerator
tgt: Follow the hall to the living area and turn left. Wait near the refrigerator.

src: bathroom straight turn at foot of bed next chair
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go straight. Turn left and stop at the foot of the bed next to the chair.

src: through near doorway left through doorway then right top of stairs stairs midway level wait
tgt: Go through the near doorway and make a left through the doorway and then make a right and go to the top of the stairs, go down the stairs to the midway level and wait.

src: through doorway in front of left through wooden door turn hallway head towards staircase first entryway down stairs wait in awning at top of second set
tgt: Go through doorway in front of you. Turn left and enter through wooden door. Turn left down hallway and head towards the staircase. Take the first entryway down the stairs and wait in the awning at the top of the second set.

src: full length mirror travel toward through door left large staircase first set of stairs first landing at top of second set of stairs
tgt: Locate the full length mirror. Travel toward it and go through the door to the left. Continue to the large staircase and go down the first set of stairs to the first landing. Stop at the top of the second set of stairs.

src: turn right top of stairs through wood doors once through turn down hallway up small set of steps stop
tgt: Turn right and walk to the top of the stairs and through the wood doors. Once through, turn left and walk down the hallway. Walk up the small set of steps and stop.

src: stairs turn in hallway straight hallway stairs under first ceiling light after stairs
tgt: Go up the stairs and turn left in the hallway.  Keep going straight down the hallway and go up the stairs.  Stop under the first ceiling light after going up the stairs.

src: steps.turn hallway steps then there
tgt: Go up the steps.Turn left and go down the hallway. Go up the steps then wait there.

src: turn right into hallway turn down hallway wait by bedroom
tgt: Turn right, walk into the hallway, turn left, walk down the hallway, and wait by the bedroom.

src: exit room right down hallway blue white painting into door on left painting wait near bed
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Head down the hallway. When you get to a blue and white painting go into the door on the left that is closest to the painting and wait near the bed.

src: exit bedroom in hallway through hallway into room with television
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Go left in the hallway. Go through the hallway. Go into the room with the television.

src: bathroom out of bedroom into hallway forward stairs on fourth stair from top
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go out of the bedroom into the hallway.  Go forward and go down the stairs. Stop on the fourth stair from the top.

src: exit bathroom towards bed hard left forward bedroom into hallway slight right wait in middle of staircase
tgt: Exit the bathroom towards the bed. Make a hard left and continue forward to exit the bedroom into the hallway, make a slight right and wait in the middle of the staircase.

src: slight left head towards bed turn head towards open white door frame left of black table walk through slight right head halfway down first set of wooden stairs with metal railings wait there
tgt: Make a slight left and head towards the bed. Turn left and head towards the open white door frame to the left of the black table and walk through it. Make a slight right and head halfway down the first set of wooden stairs with metal railings. Wait there.

src: walk past bed right bathroom wait by toilet
tgt: Walk past the bed, turn right, enter the bathroom, wait by the toilet.

src: around bed bathroom turn wait by door
tgt: Go around the bed and enter the bathroom, turn left and wait by the door.

src: pass foot of bed into bathroom head into room with toilet sink
tgt: Pass the foot of the bed and go into the bathroom  Head into the room with the toilet and face the sink.

src: walk left of dining room table chairs past television turn across entryway inside garage
tgt: Walk to the left of the dining room table and chairs and past the television. Turn left and walk across the entryway and stop inside the garage.

src: pass table then tv on left turn straight into garage then
tgt: Pass the table then pass the TV on the left. Turn left and go straight into the garage then stop.

src: walk forward past dining table out of living room forward into garage stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk forward past the dining table. Take the left out of the living room. Walk forward into the garage. Go down the stairs, and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: past big chairs up short staircase into room hard left into bathroom stop
tgt: Go past the big chairs and up the short staircase. Go into the room and turn hard left. Go into the bathroom and stop.

src: walk past purple leather sofa small staircase with metal bannister on right past in bedroom door bathroom on left into bathroom there
tgt: Walk past the purple leather sofa  and go up the small staircase with the metal bannister on your right past.  This will put you in a bedroom.  There is a door to a bathroom on your left.  Go into the bathroom and stop there.

src: around counter up stairs turn into bathroom
tgt: Go left around the counter and up the stairs. Turn left and go into the bathroom.

src: stairs at bottom right
tgt: Descend the stairs and at the bottom, turn right and stop.

src: exit bedroom slight right down stairs way down stairs step near white brick painting stop
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go slight right and down the stairs, go all the way down the stairs, and step near the white brick painting and stop.

src: down stairs right wait by painting
tgt: Walk down the stairs, turn right and wait by the painting.

src: walk out of closet straight balcony wait
tgt: Walk out of the closet and go straight to the balcony and wait.

src: exit glass door straight round tub outside sliding door there
tgt: Exit the glass door. Walk straight passing the round tub. Walk outside the sliding door and stop there.

src: walk through doorway towards bathtub between tub sink right in front of window
tgt: Walk through doorway towards the bathtub, walk to window between the tub and the sink and stop right in front of the window.

src: walk through living room area past natural wooden table top walk past armchair around fireplace right through open double doors with plaque above around stairwell into hallway walk past rotary phone on wall walk into open door at end near elevator into bathroom
tgt: Walk through the living room area past the natural wooden table top. Walk past the armchair and around the fireplace to the right through the open double doors with a plaque above it. Walk around the stairwell and into the hallway. Walk past the rotary phone hanging on the wall. Walk into the open door at the end near the elevator and into a bathroom.

src: walk straight then into room on right of fireplace right into hallway turn on door right by elevator then at bathroom entrance
tgt: Walk straight and then go into the room on the right of the fireplace. turn right and go into the hallway. turn left on the door right by the elevator then wait at the bathroom entrance.

src: walk past fireplace right bathroom hallway stand near entrance of men room
tgt: Walk past the fireplace to the right and enter the bathroom hallway.  Stand near the entrance of the men's room.

src: walk out of blue wall bedroom into hallway in hallway turn left walk second of brown chairs
tgt: Walk out of the blue wall bedroom and into the hallway. In the hallway, turn to the left and walk to the second of the two brown chairs.

src: exit room then hallway until brown chairs on left then there
tgt: Exit the room then turn left and head down the hallway until you pass two brown chairs on the left then turn left and wait there.

src: bedroom walk hall until chairs then first room on left in doorway
tgt: Leave the bedroom and walk left.  Continue walking down the hall until you pass two chairs, then go to the first room on the left.  Stop in the doorway.

src: straight past pool turn into house large glass doors table wait near door room
tgt: Go straight past the pool. Turn left and go into the house using the large glass sliding doors. Pass the table and wait near the door to exit the room.

src: walk down patio past chairs then beds into room on left after beds through room stand in doorway on opposite wall from on left just past animal skin rug in doorway
tgt: Walk straight down the patio past the two chairs and then two beds.  Turn into the room on the left after passing the two beds.  Walk through the room and stand in the doorway on the opposite wall from where you entered on the left, just past the animal skin rug.  Stop in this doorway.

src: start at pool near long sofa chairs past then turn through glass door opening
tgt: Start at the pool near two long sofa chairs, go past them and then turn left through the glass door opening.

src: walk through room exit via door next giant clock down hallway right at top of stairs in doorway deck
tgt: Walk through the room and exit via the door next to the giant clock.  Walk down the hallway and turn right at the top of the stairs.  Stop in the doorway to the deck.

src: enter room with desks exit through door left head forward down corridor at second door right outside deck
tgt: Enter the room with the desks. Exit through the door to the left. Head forward down the corridor. Stop at the second door to the right that leads outside to the deck.

src: walk out door on right side of big clock walk down hallway stop at top of stairs right at top of stairs onto patio in doorway patio
tgt: Walk out the door on the right side of the big clock.  Walk straight down the hallway and stop at the top of the stairs.  Turn right at the top of the stairs and walk onto the patio.  Stop in the doorway to the patio.

src: walk through double glass doors into living area turn past dining table hallway right at first doorway wait in laundry room
tgt: Walk through the double glass doors into the living area and turn left. Walk past the dining table and towards the hallway. Turn right at the first doorway and wait in the laundry room.

src: inside turn past fancy chairs glass table then right hallway right into laundry room wait near sink
tgt: Go inside. Turn left and go past the fancy chairs and the glass table then turn right. Go down the hallway and turn right. Go into the laundry room. Wait near the sink.

src: enter house through glass doors across room right into laundry room wait here
tgt: Enter house through glass doors, walk across dinging room to hall, turn right into laundry room, wait here.

src: enter large lobby turn walk end of room at center through double doors on porch
tgt: Enter large lobby and turn left. walk to the end of the room at center through double doors and stop on porch.

src: straight toward round table then outside large double doors wait there
tgt: Go straight toward the round table  then turn left and walk outside using the large double doors. Wait there.

src: turn hall turn at table head towards other table through entryway on terrace stop
tgt: Turn around and head down the hall. Turn left at the table and head towards the other table. Go through the entryway on to the terrace and stop.

src: walk around big display turn left through entryway down hallway by other display on right
tgt: Walk around the big roped off display and turn left. Go through that entryway and down that hallway. Stop by the other roped off display on your right.

src: turn left climb over rope hallway jump over rope on right side at end of hallway wait right there by fireplace
tgt: Turn to the left and climb over the rope.  Go down the hallway.  Jump over the rope on the right side at the end of the hallway.  Wait right there by the fireplace.

src: go through second door by columns then next room right wait by table
tgt: Go left through the second door by the columns, then enter the next room and turn right, wait by the table.

src: room into room across hall then wait by bed in room
tgt: Leave the room and go into the room across the hall then wait by the bed in the room.

src: walk past massage with liquid pans above walk through open door on other side of room into open room with square tile mosaic floor walk into door on other side of mosaic right of paintings walk sink area small bed near bathtub
tgt: Walk past the massage tables with the hanging liquid dispensing pans above. Walk through the open door on the other side of the room and into the open room with a square tile mosaic floor. Walk into the door on the other side of the mosaic to the right of the paintings. Walk passed the sink area and towards the small bed near the bathtub.

src: move for open door on left through doorway room forward across hall room slight left wait near bed
tgt: Move for the open door on the left. Go through the doorway to exit this room and continue forward across the hall. Enter the room, make a slight left and wait near the bed.

src: walk forward towards couch between couch chair left at counter walk end of room left in hallway room on inside of room past doorway
tgt: Walk forward towards the couch, and between the couch and the chair. Take a left at the counter and walk to the end of the room and take a left in the hallway. Enter the room and stop on the inside of the room past the doorway.

src: between chair coffee table around couch by end table between table island turn after table into room
tgt: Go between the chair and coffee table. Go around the couch by the end table. Go between the table and island. Turn left after passing the table and go into the room.

src: walk kitchen towards refrigerator turn past table down hall just inside room
tgt: Walk to the kitchen, towards the refrigerator. Turn left past the table. Walk down the hall and stop just inside the room.

src: turn men room stand near sink
tgt: Turn around and enter the men's room.  Stand near the sink.

src: walk right of circular lights forward through entryway across room in front of bathroom
tgt: Walk to the right of the circular lights. Walk forward straight through the entryway and across the room and stop in front of the bathroom.

src: past circle lights on floor through door head straight past water tank near sinks
tgt: Go past circle lights on the floor. Go through the door and head straight. Continue past the water tank. Stop near the sinks.

src: walk towards chair at end of long table right towards brick wall walk until vase of white flowers stop
tgt: Walk towards the chair at the end of the long table. Turn right and begin walking towards the brick wall. Walk until you have reached the vase of white flowers and stop.

src: walk towards windows right in front of white flowers near couch
tgt: Walk towards the windows and go right.  Stop in front of the white flowers near the couch.

src: hard right walking then right at table with white flowers
tgt: Make a hard right. Keep walking. Then turn right and stop at the table with white flowers.

src: away from meeting room doors through tables wait at temporary wood/fabric wall towards very back of room
tgt: Walk away from the meeting room doors. Walk through the tables and wait at the temporary wood/fabric wall towards the very back of the room.

src: turn between tables past last tables wait by center of partitions
tgt: Turn left to walk between the tables. Proceed past the last tables and wait by center of the partitions.

src: towards brown tables towards room dividers near middle of
tgt: Go towards the brown tables, go towards the room dividers and when you are near the middle of them stop.

src: inside left into living room left into powder room on rug right next door
tgt: Go inside and take a left. Walk into the living room and take a left into the powder room. Stop on the rug right next to the door.

src: exit bedroom through doorway left of mirror bedroom makeup room left of bed wait at radiator
tgt: Exit the bedroom, walk through the doorway to the left of the mirror, enter the bedroom, enter the makeup room to the left of the bed, wait at the radiator.

src: walk through doors left straight ahead through door turn before fireplace walk through door wait just inside room
tgt: Walk through the doors and take a left. Walk straight ahead through the door. Turn left before the fireplace and walk through the door. Wait just inside the room.

src: turn then right small rug on floor turn outside next black rug
tgt: Turn left and then turn right. When you reach small rug on the floor turn left. Walk outside and wait next the black rug.

src: turn slightly left hallway hallway around stairs through first doorway on left after stairs in between large windows wait
tgt: Turn slightly to the left and go down that hallway. Follow the hallway around, passing the stairs and exiting through the first doorway on the left after the stairs. Stand in between the two large windows and wait.

src: hallway opposite of mirror at intersection right stairs on left on rug left turn into doorway few steps in then
tgt: Go down the hallway opposite of the sitting mirror, at the intersection make a right, go passed the stairs on your left and on the rug make a left turn into the doorway, take a few steps in and then stop.

src: exit room stairs right at top of stairs immediate left through opening
tgt: Exit the room and climb the stairs to your right. At the top of the stairs, take an immediate left through the opening.

src: exit bedroom turn stairs turn wait at entrance room by doors
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Turn left and go up stairs. Turn left and wait at the entrance to the sitting room by the two closed doors.

src: exit room stairs on right inside doorway on left
tgt: Exit the room and go up the stairs on your right.  Stop inside the doorway that is on your left.

src: step forward right up stairs at landing right second flight of stairs at top of stairs straight ahead until dining room table in front of table
tgt: Step forward, turn right, and walk up the stairs.  At the landing, turn right and continue up the second flight of stairs.  At the top of the stairs, walk straight ahead until you get to the dining room table.  Stop in front of the table.

src: start by right staircase at top of staircase straight into main dining area
tgt: Start by making a right up the staircase. At the top of the staircase, keep straight into the main dining area.

src: up stairs top walk carpet before table
tgt: Walk up the stairs, when you get to the top walk to the carpet before the table.

src: head stairs turn at top of stairs laundry room right before bedroom ahead into bathroom through first doorway on right there
tgt: Head up the stairs. Turn left at the top of the stairs. Pass the laundry room. Turn right before reaching the bedroom ahead. Turn into the bathroom through the first doorway on the right. Stop there.

src: upstairs end of hall right in bathroom
tgt: Go upstairs and to the end of the hall. Turn right and stop in the bathroom.

src: stairs turn down hallway right doorway walk right bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairs. Turn left and walk down the hallway. Turn right and enter the doorway. Walk straight, turn right, and enter the bathroom.

src: up stairs right at landing up next set of stairs wait at top
tgt: Walk up the stairs to your right. Turn left at the landing and walk up the next set of stairs and wait at the top.

src: up steps left turn then sharp right steps once top of steps
tgt: Walk up the steps, make a left turn and then a sharp right and continue up the steps. Stop once you've reached the top of the steps.

src: right stairs at top of stairs stop
tgt: Go right to go up the stairs. At the top of the stairs stop.

src: turn room once in pool room past pool right into doorway stairs elevator reception area
tgt: Turn left and exit the room. Once in the pool room, walk past the pool and turn right. Walk into the doorway and stop facing the stairs, elevator and reception area.

src: walk right of pool into room with elevators in doorway
tgt: Walk to the right of the pool and turn into room with the elevators and stop in the doorway.

src: head opening pool around right of pool then through double doors right floor changes from tile wood
tgt: Head to the opening leading to the pool and go around to the right of the pool then exit through the double doors to your right. Stop when the floor changes from tile to wood.

src: exit bathroom short dogleg right stop after room ahead
tgt: Exit the bathroom and take a short dogleg to the right, the stop after entering the room ahead.

src: exit bathroom walk straight across hall into mostly empty room next tv on wall
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Walk straight across the hall and into the mostly empty room. Stop next to the TV on the wall.

src: exit bathroom straight until bedroom wait near entrance
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Go straight until you enter a bedroom. Wait near the entrance.

src: walk across room past glass wood wall separator wicker basket down hall across mosaic floor enter door on opposite wall turn inside room in front of massage table
tgt: Walk across room past glass and wood wall separator and wicker basket. Walk down hall and across mosaic floor. Enter left door on opposite wall. Turn left. Stop inside room in front of massage table.

src: walk past lounge chairs room straight past hallway into fourth room on right wait near bed on left
tgt: Walk straight past the lounge chairs and exit the room. Go straight past the hallway. Go into the fourth room on the right and wait near the bed on the left.

src: lounge chairs left through way left of hangings on wall through hallway straight ahead doorways into left few steps towards massage table stop
tgt: Facing the lounge chairs go left and through the way to the left of the two hangings on the wall, go through the hallway and straight ahead there are two doorways go into the left one, take a few steps towards the massage table and stop.

src: exit office right straight toward clear table chairs right table wait near stairs up on right
tgt: Exit the office. Turn right. Walk straight toward the clear table and chairs. Turn right and pass the table. Wait near the stairs that go up on the right.

src: turn around forward few steps right room once out right until bottom of stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk forward a few steps. Turn right and exit the room. Once out, turn right and walk until you reach the bottom of the stairs. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit room stop at base of stairs
tgt: Exit the room and stop at the base of the stairs.

src: into large room marble counter with stools in direction until room with ovens stovetops long serving window oudside wait
tgt: Go into the large room and towards the marble counter with stools  Continue in the direction until you enter a room with ovens and stovetops and a long serving window that opens to the oudside and wait.

src: path by blue dots into kitchen
tgt: Follow the path marked by blue dots into the kitchen.

src: indoor porch area into living room right behind couch straight back kitchen left at end of kitchen wait in doorway of kitchenette
tgt: Leave the indoor porch area and go into the living room. Make a right when you get behind the couch and go straight back to the kitchen. Make a left at the end of the kitchen and wait in the doorway of the kitchenette.

src: walk into house past living room into kitchen in kitchen left into room with stove open window patio in front of sink
tgt: Walk into the house and past the living room hearing into the kitchen. In the kitchen take the left into the room with the stove and the open window to the patio. Stop in front of the sink.

src: exit pool room through door on right by tub
tgt: exit pool room through door on right, stop by tub.

src: with pool on left past window on right through first doorway on right through next doorway on right before bath tub
tgt: With the pool on your left. Walk past the window on your right and through the first doorway on your right. Walk through the next doorway on your right. Stop before you hit the bath tub.

src: walk along pool on left house through door on right left down hallway bathroom through first door on right
tgt: Walk along the pool on your left and enter the house through the door on the right. Take a left  and walk down the hallway. Enter the bathroom through the first door on the right.

src: down path past cactus past plants into room stop by door
tgt: Walk down the path past the cactus. Keep walking past the plants step into the room and stop by the door.

src: stay on walkway slightly path toward door walk through door wait
tgt: Stay on the walkway and follow the slightly curving path toward the door. Walk through the door and wait.

src: turn walk on pathway towards entrance of house doorway through then wait
tgt: Turn around.  Walk on the pathway towards the entrance of the house.  When you get to the doorway, walk through it and then stop.  Wait.

src: past second sink out door down hall into closet there
tgt: Go past the second sink and out the door. Walk down the hall into the closet and stop there.

src: walk through bathroom hall in front of closet
tgt: Walk through the bathroom and  the hall. Stop in front of the closet.

src: stand so toilet left walk straight bathroom area room in closet final doorway into closet with mirror at far end in doorway of last room near pegs on right side
tgt: Stand so the toilet is to your left.  Walk straight, passing the bathroom area, a room in the closet, and enter the final doorway into the closet with the mirror at the far end.  Stop in the doorway of this last room, near the pegs on the right side.

src: around staircase past bar through door just inside door at pool with bar on right
tgt: Go around the staircase, walking past the bar. Walk through the door, and stop just inside the door, looking at the pool with a bar on your right.

src: pass by staircase ahead forward elevators on right through doorway ahead pool area forward by plant
tgt: Pass by the staircase ahead. Go forward passing the elevators on the right. Go through the doorway ahead leading to the pool area. Go forward and wait by plant.

src: around front of stairs then past elevator through door on second tile in room
tgt: Go around the front of the stairs, then go past the elevator and through the door.  Stop on the second tile in to the room.

src: straight couches near windows in corner
tgt: Go straight passed the couches and stop near the windows in the corner.

src: walk past fireplace wait in front of windows next ottoman
tgt: Walk past the fireplace and wait in front of the windows next to the ottoman.

src: walk across living room past tv wait by mirror windows
tgt: Walk across the living room past the TV.  Wait by the mirror and windows.

src: move towards refrigerator right after kitchen island walk towards hallway in middle of hallway
tgt: Move towards the refrigerator. Turn right after the kitchen island. Walk towards the hallway and stop in the middle of the hallway.

src: through kitchen towards fridge right from fridge straight through into hallway there in front of door
tgt: Go through the kitchen towards the fridge. Turn right from the fridge and go straight through into the hallway, stopping there in front of a door.

src: walk past island right past refrigerator into hallway stop
tgt: Walk past the island and turn right. Walk past the refrigerator into the hallway and stop.

src: past main entrance hall with large tapestry into office with walnut table crystal vase on mantle
tgt: Go past the main entrance and travel down the hall with the large tapestry and into the office with the walnut table and crystal vase on the mantle.

src: turn towards hallway straight until end of hall then door right right in doorway
tgt: turn around and go towards the hallway and keep walking straight until you get to the end of the hall and then take the door right to your right and stop in the doorway.

src: walk past dining table door kitchen into hallway down hall past wall art front door of home hall past wall art into open door at end of hall office with bookshelves
tgt: Walk past the dining table and door to the kitchen into the hallway ahead.Walk down the hall past the wall art and front door of the home. Continue down the hall past more wall art and into the open door at the end of the hall which leads to an office with bookshelves.

src: walk towards sofa turn across door turn again next room walk across office area right room right wait by sink in bathroom
tgt: Walk towards the sofa. Turn left and walk across the door. Turn left again and enter the next room. Walk across the office area and turn right. Enter the room to your right. Wait by the sink in the bathroom.

src: bedroom out of room in hallway left enter office in office right through door into bedroom then bathroom on left in front of cabinet next sink
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a left out of the sitting room. In the hallway take a left an enter the office. In the office take a right and go through the door into the bedroom, then the bathroom on the left. Stop in front of the cabinet next to the sink.

src: enter lounge area with diamond-pattern rug left.go down hallway office continue through office until bathroom wait in front of light switches at bathroom entrance
tgt: Enter the lounge area with the diamond-pattern rug and turn left.Go down the hallway and enter the office continue through the office until you enter the bathroom. Wait in front of the light switches at the bathroom entrance.

src: through door opposite bathroom white bed through door on right straight through double doors
tgt: Go through the door opposite the bathroom. Continue to the white bed. Turn around and go through the door on the right. Go straight through the double doors.

src: walk into bedroom into hallway in hall walk straight white swinging doors bedroom on other side of door top in doorway on left
tgt: Walk into the bedroom, and into the hallway. In the hall walk straight and go to the white swinging doors. Enter the bedroom on the other side of the swinging door and top in the doorway on the left.

src: walk into bedroom immediate hard left through loft hallway through double doors wait near bathroom
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and take an immediate hard left. Walk through the loft hallway and go through the double doors. Wait near the bathroom.

src: turn right top of stairs down stairs then right stairs few steps near dining room then there
tgt: Turn right and go to the top of the stairs.  Walk down the stairs, and then take a right when you get down the stairs.  You'll go a few steps, near the dining room and then you'll stop and wait there.

src: stairs then painting stop
tgt: Go down the stairs, then walk to the painting and stop.

src: exit room right walk stairs stairs right at bottom of stairs in front of large piece of art right of bathroom
tgt: Exit the room, turn right, and walk to the stairs.  Descend the stairs.  Turn right at the bottom of the stairs, and stop in front of the large piece of art to the right of the bathroom.

src: exit bedroom turn right.walk past staircase door on right in front of entryway through door in office area
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right.Walk past the staircase and to the door on the right in front of an entryway. Go through the door and you'll be in an office area.

src: through doorway hall hall past teh landing first door on right in doorway
tgt: Go through the doorway to the hall.  Go down the hall past teh landing.  Take the first door on the right and stop in the doorway.

src: forward exit room upon right hallway past stairs on right side next doorway right
tgt: Move forward and exit the room. Upon exiting, turn to your right and move down the hallway, past the stairs on the right side. Enter the next doorway to your right and stop.

src: turn right exit out double wood doors once turn right end of hallway double wood doors once inside turn on rug in front of animal print chair
tgt: Turn right and exit out the double wood doors. Once out turn right and walk to the end of the hallway and enter the double wood doors. Once inside, turn left and stop on the rug in front of the animal print chair.

src: walk in front of wood chairs through double doors right before hardwood floor down hallway through doorway turn at leather chair on carpet in front of cheetah print bench
tgt: walk in front of two wood chairs, straight through double doors, turn right before the hardwood floor and walk down the hallway, walk through another doorway, turn left at the leather chair and stop on the carpet in front of cheetah print bench.

src: exit room down hall past zebra painting room at end on striped rug
tgt: Exit the room and walk down the hall, past the zebra painting. Enter the room at the end and stop on the striped rug.

src: exit bathroom right then toward kitchen wait near kitchen area
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and then turn left and walk toward the kitchen. Wait near kitchen area.

src: exit bathroom veer right next room once out of room left after corner on left
tgt: Exit the bathroom and veer right to exit the next room. Once out of that room, continue to the left and stop after you pass the corner on your left.

src: enter exit dining room turn wait in between counter grey chairs
tgt: Enter and exit the dining room and turn left. Wait in between the counter and the two grey chairs.

src: exit room through middle doorway wait at table
tgt: Exit the room through the middle doorway, and wait at the table.

src: cross room exit through middle door near table in middle of room
tgt: Cross the room and exit through the middle door. Stop near the table in the middle of the room.

src: exit room middle door on left toward round table straight ahead there
tgt: Exit the room using the middle door on the left. Walk toward the round table straight ahead and wait there.

src: turn on rug in front of bench with giraffe print
tgt: Turn left and wait on the rug in front of the bench with the giraffe print.

src: hall into living room on striped rug
tgt: Go down the hall into the living room. Stop on the striped rug.

src: turn down hall through double doors stand near large brown chair
tgt: Turn left and walk down the hall through the double doors. Stand near the large brown chair.

src: turn through kitchen then stairs on first landing
tgt: Turn left and walk through the kitchen.  Then walk up the stairs and stop on the first landing.

src: turn around through kitchen end of bar at end of bar right large stairs at first platform blue painting
tgt: Turn around and walk through the kitchen to the end of the bar. At the end of the bar, turn right. Go up the large stairs and stop at the first platform facing the blue painting.

src: walk into kitchen stairs on landing
tgt: Walk into the kitchen, and  go up the stairs. Stop on the landing.

src: turn right out of bedroom door turn once into hallway then right at first door into bathroom into doorway
tgt: Turn to the right and walk out of the bedroom door.  Turn left once you get into the hallway.  Then turn right at the first door.  You'll be looking into the bathroom.  Stop when you get into the doorway.

src: exit bedroom turn wait in bathroom on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left. Wait in the bathroom on the right.

src: walk forward past bed dresser into hallway outside of room left into hallway outside of bathroom right into bathroom in bathroom doorway
tgt: Walk forward past the bed and dresser and into the hallway outside of the room and take a left into the hallway outside of the bathroom and take a right into the bathroom and stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: walk into living room next red ottoman
tgt: Walk into the living room and stand next to the red ottoman.

src: glass door turn between white couch table right of orange ottoman
tgt: Go to the glass door. Turn left and go between the white couch and the table. Go to the right of the orange ottoman.

src: walk across room edge of couch between couch table right in front of red ottoman
tgt: walk across room to edge of couch, turn left and walk between couch and table, turn right and stop in front of red ottoman.

src: steps right at counter top
tgt: go up steps, turn right, stop at counter top.

src: walk towards stairs ad right stairs straight into kitchen in kitchen next cabinet under counter with colorful dishes
tgt: Walk towards the stairs ad take a right to go up the stairs. Go straight into the kitchen. In the kitchen stop next to the cabinet under the counter with the colorful dishes.

src: walk towards couch right steps sets of steps straight back kitchen wait by counter
tgt: Walk towards the couch and make a right to go up the steps. Go up the both sets of steps and go straight back to the kitchen and wait by the counter.

src: outside double doors turn into house again turn then right into bathroom wait near entrance
tgt: Go outside using the double doors. Turn left and go into the house again. Turn left and then turn right into the bathroom. Wait near the entrance.

src: exit office space left then other left forward then right bathroom wait
tgt: Exit office to outside living space, make a left,  then make a other left, go forward then make a right and enter the bathroom, and wait.

src: turn door outside once outside doorway once in turn door on left once sink right into bathroom before next sink
tgt: Turn around and exit out the door to go outside. Once outside, turn left and enter the doorway. Once in , turn and enter the door on your left. Once you reach the sink, turn right and walk into the bathroom and stop before you reach the next sink.

src: head long hallway turn at exit sign numbered lockers on left kitchenette on right
tgt: Head down the long hallway and turn left at the exit sign.  Stop where numbered lockers are on the left, and the kitchenette is on your right.

src: hallway turn at exit sign
tgt: Walk down hallway, turn left at exit sign, walk to sink.

src: turn hall turn in kitchenette
tgt: Turn around, go down the hall. Turn left and stop in the kitchenette.

src: walk along porch past bench table walk into entry door home into home walk into hallway past desk ahead forward through hall in next room near counter top area
tgt: Walk along the tiled porch past the bench and table. Walk into the entry door to the home. Continue into the home and walk into the hallway past the desk ahead. Continue forward through the hall and stop in the next room near the counter top and dining area.

src: indoors straight into hallway on slight left past stairs on right into room on right wait there
tgt: Go indoors. Walk straight into the hallway on the slight left. Go past the stairs on the right. Go into the room on the right and wait there.

src: walk across patio into house forward toward wall with stone tile walk past stone tile wall on left side walk past stair case at entrance area
tgt: Walk across patio into the house. Walk forward toward wall with stone tile. Walk past stone tile wall on left side. Walk past stair case. Stop at entrance to kitchen area.

src: exit bathroom door right walk bedroom door exit through left hallway step through door right dining room right there
tgt: Exit the bathroom door and turn right. Walk to the bedroom door and exit through it. Turn left and go down the hallway.  Take one step through the door to your right which is the dining room. Stop right there.

src: exit bathroom right walk across room door hallway turn left of hallway turn right enter dining room at room table
tgt: exit bathroom to bedroom, turn right and walk across room to open door, enter hallway and turn left. Go to end of hallway turn right and enter dining room. Stop at dining room table.

src: walk through doorway towards bed right past bed walk through door on right walk hall through double doors on right into kitchen stop
tgt: walk through the doorway towards the bed, turn right, walk past the bed and walk through the door on the right walk left down the hall, walk through the double doors on the right into the kitchen and stop.

src: exit bathroom toward bedroom then bedroom door on left then straight until into room wait by first green chair
tgt: Exit the bathroom toward the bedroom then exit the bedroom using the door on the left then turn left and head straight until you go into the room. Wait by the first green chair.

src: turn around out of bathroom into bedroom out of bedroom first in room straight ahead
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom into the bedroom. Walk out of the bedroom. Take your first left and wait in the room that is straight ahead.

src: exit bathroom bedroom first left in hall just inside room with desk with black chair side green chairs on other side
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Exit the bedroom. Take the first left in the hall and stop just inside the room with a desk with one black chair one one side and two green chairs on the other side.

src: dining table behind stairs at top of stairs right bedroom just after room
tgt: Put the dining table behind you and go up the stairs.  At the top of the stairs turn right and enter the bedroom.  Stop just after entering the room.

src: stairs right once bedroom
tgt: Go up the stairs. Take a right, and stop once you pass the bedroom.

src: exit room stairs on right right into room on right there
tgt: Exit the room and go up the stairs on your right. Turn right and go into the room on the right. Wait there.

src: with deck behind way down right side of room couches fireplace after final couch in front of white door
tgt: With the deck behind you, walk all the way down the right side of the room, passing couches and a fireplace.  Stop after you pass the final couch and are in front of the white door.

src: walk through living room fireplace on right in front of door after couch
