tgt: Walk straight through the living room and passing the fireplace on the right. Stop in front of the door after you pass the couch.

src: straight fireplace couches then at very end right in front of door
tgt: Go straight and pass the fireplace and all the couches then stop at the very end right in front of the door.

src: down stairs right stairs stop at bottom of stairs at sauna
tgt: Walk down stairs, turn right and continue down stairs, stop at bottom of stairs at sauna.

src: stairs stop at sauna door
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop at the sauna door.

src: down first flight of stairs turn right down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the first flight of stairs, turn right, walk down the stairs, wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: with pool back staircase second floor patio left of staircase covered archway with table under table towards blue basketball court off of tile floor of patio onto rock in between patio court
tgt: With the pool to your back, locate the staircase to the second floor patio.  To the left of the staircase a covered archway with a table under it.  Proceed to the table, walking passed it heading towards the blue basketball court.  Step off of the tile floor of the patio onto the rock, and stop in between the patio and the court.

src: towards stairs then left of stairs along walkway right then straight toward circle table circle table then just pillar onto stones stop
tgt: Go towards the stairs and then go to the left of the stairs along the walkway, going right and then straight toward the circle table, go passed the circle table, then go just passed the pillar onto the stones and stop.

src: stairs left walk around wait in rocks in front of basketball court
tgt: When you get to the stairs make a left and follow the walk around, wait in the rocks in front of the basketball court.

src: walk out of bedroom walk under stairs right
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom. Walk under the stairs. Turn right and stop.

src: left bedroom wait in door way on other side of light switch
tgt: Take a left and exit the bedroom. Wait in the door way on the other side of the light switch.

src: past foot of bed into hallway at top of staircase
tgt: Go past the foot of the bed.  Go into a hallway, and you will be at the top of the staircase.  That's where you will wait.

src: exit spa room walk into reception area through set of double doors wait there
tgt: Exit the spa room and walk into the reception area through the set of double doors.  Wait there.

src: exit sauna then room right straight into room ahead wait there
tgt: Exit the sauna and then Exit the room. Turn right and go straight into the room ahead. Wait there.

src: exit room straight through double doorway into room with wooden floor just inside next wicker chair
tgt: Exit the room, continue straight through the double doorway into the room with a wooden floor. Stop just inside, next to the wicker chair.

src: turn past table chairs into main part of house veer left in dining room through doorway into hallway bedroom door
tgt: Turn around, go past the table and chairs.  Go into the main part of the house and veer to the left in the dining room.  Go through a doorway and into a hallway.  You must stop when you get to the bedroom door.

src: walk through piano room walk through room walk through open door right of wall art walk into bedroom wait at side of bed
tgt: Walk through piano room. Walk through dinning room. Walk through open door to right of wall art. Walk into bedroom. Wait at side of bed.

src: walk through library room table out arched entry way on other side of table.. walk dining table area through hallway near mounted brass art
tgt: Walk through the library room passed the table and out the arched entry way on the other side of the table.. Walk passed the dining table area and through to the hallway near the mounted brass art.

src: dining area head kitchen enter area left of kitchen also stove in front of jar of marshmallows
tgt: Leave the dining area, and head to the kitchen. Enter area left of the kitchen which also has a stove. Stop in front of the jar of marshmallows.

src: turn kitchen area into room with cabinets cupboards wait there
tgt: Turn around and enter the kitchen area. Turn left into the room with the cabinets and cupboards and wait there.

src: past table chairs straight slightly right bar with stool/chairs then near stove
tgt: Go past the table and chairs and go straight slightly right. Pass the bar with the stool/chairs and then turn left and stand near the stove.

src: walk ahead past stove sink refrigerator washer dryer once bedroom door past washer dryer
tgt: Walk straight ahead past the stove, sink, refrigerator, washer and dryer. Stop once you reach the bedroom door past the washer and dryer.

src: walk through kitchen walk in doorway after washer dryer wait by dresser
tgt: Walk straight through the kitchen. Walk in the doorway after the washer and dryer. Wait by the dresser.

src: away from door outside past stove sink once in doorway past washer dryer
tgt: walk away from the door to the outside, past the stove and sink. Stop once you are in the doorway straight past the washer and dryer.

src: turn around past table right into den right into bathroom ahead in front of sink
tgt: Turn around and walk past the table and take a right. Walk into the den and take a right. Walk into the bathroom straight ahead and wait in front of the sink.

src: walk around dining room table right past tea on left into room right walk between sofa chairs slightly right into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Walk around the dining room table and take a right. Walk past the tea set on the left and into the sitting room. Turn right and walk between the two pink sofa chairs. Turn slightly right and walk into the bathroom and wait near the sink.

src: walk end of table right sitting room once sitting room turn right head into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Walk to the end of the table and turn right and enter the sitting room. Once you enter the sitting room turn right and head into the bathroom in front of the sink.

src: turn left around table left pass by next table as well between table last table stop
tgt: Turn to your left and walk around the table to your left. Pass by the next table as well and turn left between that table and the last table and stop.

src: walk between tables turn through chairs near last row
tgt: Walk between the tables, turn left and continue through the chairs. Stop near the last row.

src: walk forward past dinning tables wait by last table on by door
tgt: Walk forward past dinning tables, wait by last table on the left by the door.

src: turn left stone path past pool house wait by door
tgt: Turn to the left and follow stone path past the pool. Enter the house and wait by the door.

src: with pool on left walk forward house once inside bedroom on other side of door
tgt: With the pool on your left walk forward. Enter the house and stop once you are inside the bedroom on the other side of this door.

src: walk forward pool on left through door wait there
tgt: Walk forward passing the pool on the left. Go through the door and wait there.

src: with stairs behind forward at corner just before door ahead forward by glass door on right steps through wooden door ahead of just after room
tgt: With the stairs behind you, go forward and turn left at the corner just before the door straight ahead. Continue moving forward passing by the glass door on your right. Climb the two steps and go through the wooden door ahead of you. Stop just after entering that room.

src: walk past large mirror on wall turn at bathroom hallway wait just inside doorway garage
tgt: Walk past the large mirror on the wall and turn left at the bathroom. Continue down the hallway and wait just inside the doorway to the garage.

src: down hallway into garage wait by bench
tgt: Walk down the hallway and into the garage. Wait by the bench.

src: desk steps right toward bed turn enter closet
tgt: Leave desk and walk up steps. Turn right and walk toward bed. Turn left and enter closet.

src: climb small steps through double doors forward until door left then through opening
tgt: Climb up the three small steps and go through the double doors. Continue forward until there's a door opening to your left. Then go through that opening.

src: turn degrees small steps right into bedroom door on left outside of doorway
tgt: Turn around 180 degrees and go up the small steps to the right. Walk into the bedroom go out the door on the left and stand outside of the doorway.

src: exit room right stairs turn through doorway up stairs wait at foot of curved steps
tgt: Exit room, turn right and go up stairs. Turn left through the doorway and walk up the stairs. Wait at the foot of the curved steps.

src: exit room right up first set of stairs then up main stair case wait near bottom
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Walk up the first set of stairs. Then turn left and walk up to the main stair case and wait near the bottom.

src: turn right in hallway turn left after stairs walk towards circular staircase on right with iron railings just before first step
tgt: Turn right in the hallway and turn left after going up three stairs.  Walk towards the circular staircase on the right with the iron railings and stop just before taking the first step.

src: walk across room exit wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk across sitting room and exit, wait at bottom of stairs.

src: turn head towards door as coffee table outside towards hallway moving door once steps
tgt: Turn around and head towards the door as you pass the coffee table. Continue outside towards the hallway and keep moving. Exit the door and stop once you reach the steps.

src: turn door left of tv once walk across room out door ahead stairs on 2nd step
tgt: Turn around and exit out the door to the left of the TV. Once out walk across the room and out the door straight ahead. Go up the stairs and stop on the 2nd step.

src: picture of guitar through door on right stairs step into bedroom in o'clock position from top of stairs stop after into room
tgt: Facing the picture of the guitar, go through the door on the right.  Go up the stairs and step into the bedroom in the 1 o'clock position from the top of the stairs.  Stop after stepping into the room.

src: right from red white black picture walk stairs walk into doorway on right
tgt: Turn right from the red white and black picture. Walk left up the stairs. Walk into the doorway on the right and stop.

src: exit room right stairs slightly right straight into room wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room. Turn right and go up the stairs. Turn slightly right and go straight into the room. Wait at the entrance.

src: stairs then right wait near kitchen sink
tgt: Go down the stairs then turn right and wait near the kitchen sink.

src: stairs right of kitchen
tgt: Go down stairs,  Walk to kitchen and stop to the right of kitchen.

src: stairs right forward towards kitchen until in middle of arc with openings towards right
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn right and continue forward towards the kitchen until you're in the middle of an arc with five openings towards your right.

src: bathroom walk right massage room last door on right into room right inside room next door
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk to the right. Enter the massage room that is the last door on your right. Walk into the room that is the farthest right and stop inside, the room next to the door.

src: away from sinks exit through doorway once out of bathroom proceed towards right at end of hallway through last doorway on right turk hamami sauna straight through doorway with brown rug in front of in front of shoes towels
tgt: Walk away from the sinks and exit through the doorway. Once out of the bathroom proceed towards your right at the end of the hallway walk through the last doorway on your right that says Turk Hamami Sauna. Continue straight and walk through the doorway with a brown rug in front of it. Stop in front of the shoes and towels set out.

src: turn right through doorway down hall right last door on right through room in doorway on opposite side of room
tgt: Turn to the right. Walk through the doorway. Walk down the hall to the right. Enter the last door on the right. Walk through the room. Stop in the doorway on the opposite side of the room.

src: up stairs stop
tgt: Walk up the stairs and stop.

src: walk upstairs wait at top
tgt: Walk upstairs and wait at the top.

src: climb top of stairs blue dots
tgt: Climb to the top of the stairs following the blue dots.

src: stairs wait at top of stairs near area
tgt: Go up the stairs.  Wait at the top of the stairs  You'll stop near the roped off area.

src: into doorway bed past bed through door
tgt: Go into the doorway that leads to a bed. Go past the bed and through the door.

src: walk past round table on left through open door on right open bedroom door walk past foot of bed on right bathroom wait at towel warmer on wall left
tgt: Walk past the round table on the left. Walk through the open door on the right. Enter the open bedroom door. Walk past the foot of the bed on the right. Enter the bathroom. Wait at the towel warmer on the wall to the left.

src: walk towards door with table left through door into room with light picture on left side of wall walk past painting through doorway onto tile
tgt: Walk towards the door with the dining table to your left. Walk through the door and into the room with one handing light  and a picture on the left side of the wall. Walk past the painting and through the doorway onto the tile.

src: exit bathroom at bed turn into hallway at double doors on left
tgt: exit bathroom to bedroom at bed turn left and walk into hallway. Stop at double doors on your left.

src: exit bathroom then bedroom door on left wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom then when you get to the bedroom go out the door on your left and wait there.

src: bathroom hallway bedroom in bedroom left out door just outside bedroom doorway painting on wall also doorway on left
tgt: You should leave the bathroom and go down the hallway to get to the bedroom. When you are in the bedroom take a left and walk out the door. You should wait just outside the bedroom doorway and beside a painting on each wall; there is also a doorway on the left.

src: into room with staircase right between grey couch glass table after glass table right before left of thermostat
tgt: Go into the room with the staircase to the right, go between the grey couch and the glass table, after passing the glass table make a right, and stop before and to the left of the thermostat.

src: straight behind couch dining table then before bar next thermostat
tgt: Go straight and go left behind the couch and the dining table. Then stop before getting to the bar next to the thermostat.

src: place white black painting back forward towards staircase into room into room until left walk behind grey couch with glass table with blue chairs on right end of table right forward stop in middle of room same distance from white wall blue chairs black support beam clear metal bar stools in middle of room
tgt: Place the white and black painting to your back, and walk forward towards the staircase into the room.  Continue into the room until you can turn left and walk behind the grey couch, with the glass table with blue chairs on your right.  Walk to the end of the table and turn right.  Walk forward and stop in the middle of the room.  You should be the same distance from the white wall, blue chairs, black support beam, and clear metal bar stools in the middle of the room.

src: exit room right past living room area wait by column
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Walk past the living room and dining area. Wait by the column.

src: exit room right head until entrance next room wait
tgt: Exit room and make a right. Head straight until you reach the entrance to the next room and wait.

src: exit area th hallway past stairs towards dining table before area
tgt: Exit the waiting area, head down th hallway past the stairs towards the dining table.  Stop before entering this dining area.

src: bathroom walk through bedroom bedroom by door on left out of bedroom down hall end of hall by elevator right at foot of stairs from there
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk through the bedroom to exit the bedroom by the door on your left.  Make a left out of the bedroom and walk down the hall.  When you get to the end of the hall by the elevator, make a right and stop at the foot of the stairs ascending from there.

src: walk forward bathroom bedroom diagonally until doorway walk through doorway turn forward hall until just open doorway on left forward base of stairs stop wait
tgt: Walk forward to exit the bathroom and enter the bedroom. Walk diagonally to the left until you come to the doorway. Walk through the doorway and turn left. Walk forward down the hall until you just pass the open doorway on the left. Walk forward to the base of the stairs and stop and wait.

src: bathroom left bedroom then left in hall walk end of hall then slight right wait in front of stairs
tgt: Leave the bathroom and make a left to leave the bedroom then make another left in the hall. Walk to the end of the hall then take a slight right and wait in front of the stairs.

src: with bathroom right room then hallway passing by stairs on left eventually room at extreme end of hallway
tgt: With the bathroom to your right, exit the room, then turn left and go down the hallway, passing by the stairs on your left to eventually enter the room at the extreme end of the hallway.

src: walk past couch out door right down hall past stairs end of hall into room at end of hall stop
tgt: Walk past the couch, out the door, and turn right. Walk down the hall, past the stairs, and continue to the end of the hall. Go into the room at the end of the hall and stop.

src: stand with window behind room via door in front of railing turn hallway way room at very end step inside unfinished room once inside in middle of room
tgt: Stand with the window behind you and exit the room via the door in front of the railing.  Turn left down the hallway and walk all the way to the room at the very end.  Step inside the unfinished room and stop once inside in the middle of the room.

src: walk through doorway sharp turn right then behind couch walk past table with plants by dining room table chairs
tgt: Walk through the doorway and make a sharp turn right then left behind the couch. Walk past the table with the plants and stop by the dining room table and chairs.

src: straight hall on right right into living room before couch straight just of table chairs
tgt: Go straight and turn down the hall on the right. Turn right into the living room, and go left before the couch. Go straight and stop just left of the table and chairs.

src: room right living room on right behind first couch left walk area behind left bench
tgt: Leave the room, and go right. Enter the living room on the right. Walk behind the first couch and go left. Walk to the dining area, and stop behind the left bench.

src: up stairs turn up first section of stairs wait there
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Turn left and walk up the first section of stairs. Wait there.

src: with stove on left straight up step on right onto stair case stairs stairs at landing stairs left at fork stopping at window on next landing with steps on left
tgt: With the stove on your left go straight and up the one step on take a right onto the stair case and go up the stairs and left up the stairs at the landing going up the stairs and taking a left at the fork stopping at the window on the next landing with two steps on your left.

src: forward stairs right first landing left turn stairs at second landing
tgt: GO forward and go up the stairs to the right.  Go to the first landing and take a left turn.  Continue up the stairs and stop at the second landing.

src: bathroom left in hallway then right in other hallway inside room left room wait in hallway in front of first room on right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and make a left in the hallway then make a right in the other hallway. Go inside the room and make a left to leave the room. Wait in the hallway in front of the first room on the right.

src: exit bathroom slight through study into hallway in hall
tgt: Exit bathroom to bedroom, walk slight left through study into hallway. Stop in hall.

src: step out of bath tub walk door way on left walk through door way then right past book case after book case left walk past desk double glass doors through double glass doors wait by picture of mountain
tgt: Step out of the bath tub and walk to the door way on the left and walk through that door way.  Then make a right and walk past the book case.  After the book case make a left and walk past the desk to the double glass doors.  walk through the double glass doors and wait by the picture of a mountain.

src: turn hall turn bedroom walk past bed bathroom wait in front of sink
tgt: Turn around and enter the hall. Turn left and enter the bedroom. Walk past the bed, enter the bathroom and wait in front of the sink.

src: turn right then hallway bathroom
tgt: Turn around and turn right then left. Follow the hallway and enter the bathroom.

src: turn right into room on left past bed into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Turn right and go into the room on the left. Walk past the bed and straight into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: exit bathroom walk though adjacent room past black desk desk on left as in next room sink sink on left as
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk though the adjacent room past the black desk. The desk will be on your left as you pass.  In the next room, stop when you get to the sink.  The sink will be on your left as you approach.

src: walk past table into living room turn in front of counter
tgt: Walk past the table and into the living room. Turn left and stop in front of the counter.

src: exit bathroom right at dining room table tol kitchen wait by counter
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Turn left at the dining room table, walk tol the kitchen and wait by the counter.

src: around table near window on past ornate clock straight until large office
tgt: Go around the table near the window and continue on past the ornate clock and go straight until you find the large office.

src: walk across room wait by open door
tgt: Walk across the room and wait by the open door.

src: into room with piano through rectangular door on left into room with fireplace
tgt: Go into the room with the piano. Go through the rectangular door on the left and into the room with the fireplace.

src: with ping pong table behind down length of room staircases one on right on first stop
tgt: With the ping pong table behind you, walk down the length of the room.  When you see two staircases, take the one on the right and stop on the first stop.

src: walk past everything step down stairs then
tgt: Walk straight past everything and go down one step down the stairs then stop.

src: walk straight ahead toward stairs wait on second step
tgt: Walk straight ahead toward the stairs. Wait on the second step.

src: bookshelf door on same wall as bookshelf right travel past elephant photo left into next room with couch at bowl of apples
tgt: Locate the bookshelf. Enter the door that is located on the same wall as the bookshelf. Turn right and travel past the elephant photo, and go left into the next room with a couch. Stop at the bowl of apples.

src: walk through bedroom into hallway on other side right down hallway past picture on wall of elephant walk into next open door large theater screen couch area
tgt: Walk through the bedroom and into the hallway on the other side. Turn right and walk down the hallway past a picture on the wall of an elephant. Walk into the next open door that leads to a large theater screen and couch area.

src: room via door in middle of wall right of bed once in hallway turn right walking until top of stairs into entertainment room on instead of stairs just after room
tgt: Leave the room via the door in the middle of the wall to the right of the bed.  Once in the hallway turn right and keep walking until you get to the top of some stairs.  Turn into the entertainment room on the left instead of going down the stairs.  Stop just after entering this room.

src: closet room left right foyer right into office in doorway office
tgt: Leave the closet and the room. Take a left, and right. Enter the foyer and take a right into the office. Stop in the doorway to the office.

src: step out of closet walk left past bench right out of bedroom walk out of room past glass door right just inside doorway
tgt: Step out of the closet and walk left. Walk past the bench and right out of the bedroom. Walk left out of the room and past the glass door. Turn right and stop just inside the doorway.

src: doorway left of cabinet bedroom bedroom through double doors on right at mirror then sharp right living area walk double doors directly right there
tgt: Take the doorway left of the cabinet. Enter the bedroom. Exit the bedroom through the double doors on the right. Turn left at the mirror and then take a sharp right. Enter the living area. Walk to the double doors directly to the right. Stop there.

src: exit bedroom walk into next bedroom in hall stand in room bathroom doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk into the next bedroom in the hall. Go stand in that room's bathroom doorway.

src: right then right into bedroom with beds left wait in entrance bathroom
tgt: Take a right then take another right into the bedroom with two beds. Take a left and wait in the entrance to the bathroom.

src: exit bedroom right past double closet doors on right open bedroom door on right past bed on left past tv on right wait at threshold bathroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom, and make a right. Walk past the double closet doors on the right. Enter the open bedroom door on the right. Walk past the bed on the left. Walk past the TV on the right. Wait at the threshold to the bathroom.

src: flight of stairs on landing
tgt: Walk down one flight of stairs and stop on the landing.

src: walk between columns sharp turn right down steps on landing
tgt: Walk between the columns and make a sharp turn right. Walk down the steps and stop on the landing.

src: walk forward then right at stairs then stairs
tgt: walk forward then turn right at the stairs then go down the stairs.

src: turn straight left at wall straight
tgt: Turn around and go straight. Take a left at the wall and go straight.

src: head until wall with holes in then by glass table with white chairs
tgt: Head straight until you pass the wall with holes in it then turn left and wait by the glass table with the white chairs.

src: past room dividers toward glasstop desk into dining area next large glass table
tgt: Go down past some room dividers toward a glasstop desk, and turn into the dining area. Wait next to the large glass dining table.

src: walk into hallway through entrance kitchen area walk sink area between refrigerator table
tgt: Walk into the hallway and through the entrance to the kitchen area. Walk  Passed the sink and stove area and stop between the refrigerator and dining table.

src: walk through kitchen past sink stove stand in front of table on bench side
tgt: Walk through the kitchen. Go past the sink and stove stand in front of the dining table on the bench side.

src: walk into kitchen walk past refrigerator directly in front of wooden table
tgt: Walk into the kitchen.  Walk past the refrigerator.  Stop directly in front of the wooden table.

src: walk past chairs left walk in front of chair stop
tgt: Walk past the chairs and to the left. Walk in front of the chair and stop.

src: exit bedroom via left toward couch there
tgt: Exit the bedroom via the farthest left. Walk toward the couch. Stop there.

src: towards front door before front door left then through archway middle of middle room stop
tgt: Go towards the front door but before the front door make a left, then through the archway, go to the middle of the middle room and stop.

src: walk beside outside doors behind chairs across room right up stairs on seventh step
tgt: Walk beside the outside doors and behind the chairs across the room. Turn right and walk up the stairs. Stop on the seventh step.

src: turn through living room room right up stairs in th e middle of stairs
tgt: Turn left and walk through the living room. Exit the room, turn right and walk up the stairs. stop in th e middle of the stairs.

src: with windows on left through large room past areas through door left of tapestry wood paneled room with circle table in middle stairs on sixth step from bottom
tgt: With the windows on your left, walk through the large room past the sitting areas.  Go through the door left of the tapestry and enter a wood paneled room with a circle table in the middle.  Go up the stairs and stop on the sixth step from the bottom.

src: walk out of bathroom turn along hallway white painting other bathroom turn stairs down of stairs wait on there
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn left. Walk along the hallway passed the white painting and the other bathroom.  Turn left towards the stairs. Walk down three of the stairs and wait on there.

src: exit bathroom bedroom bedroom door on left then straight until stairs wait on second step
tgt: Exit the bathroom to the bedroom. Exit the bedroom using the door on the left then go straight until you get to the stairs and wait on the second step.

src: walk out of bathroom into bedroom turn bedroom door at top of stairs
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom into the bedroom and turn left. Continue out the bedroom door, turning left to wait at the top of the stairs.

src: exit room turn hallway slightly right down hallway right into room wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn slightly right to continue going down the hallway. Turn right and go into the room. wait at the entrance.

src: left past wall vent on left right just after bathroom right opposite console table left wait at threshold of open door
tgt: Make a left. Walk past the wall vent on the left. Make a right just after the bathroom. Make a right opposite the console table to the left. Wait at the threshold of the open door.

src: room left right at end of hall first right room in doorway
tgt: Leave the room, and take a left. Take a right at the end of the hall, and take the first right. Enter the room, and stop in the doorway.

src: turn right across hallway through doorway slightly middle hallway walk though wait at entrance
tgt: Turn right and walk across the hallway through the doorway. Turn slightly left and enter the middle hallway and walk though it. Wait at the entrance.

src: head out of room left first right little door just past that door wait in doorway
tgt: Head out of the room and go to your left. Make the first right where the little door is. Go just past that door and wait in the doorway.

src: walk through double doors left then small right near very small door walk into doorway past small door
tgt: Walk through the double doors make a left then a small right near the very small door. Walk into the doorway past the small door.

src: enter kitchen right by sinks between cabinets stairs turn wait by stool at end of counter
tgt: Enter the kitchen and turn right by the sinks. Go between the cabinets towards the stairs. Turn left and wait by the stool at the end of the counter.

src: walk towards black steps walk wait here
tgt: Walk towards black steps.  Walk to chalkboard.  Wait here.

src: turn around right of room walk towards stairs then in middle between sets of stairs at bottom
tgt: Turn around and walk to the right of the room. Walk towards the stairs and then stop in the middle between the 2 sets of stairs at the bottom.

src: red artwork on left into doorway then right after first silver chair straight through glass door step into bedroom stop
tgt: Go passed the red artwork on the left, go into the doorway and then make a right after the first silver chair. Go straight through the glass door and step into the bedroom and stop.

src: head inside right forward into room in front of bed
tgt: Head inside, turn right, walk forward into the room, stop in front of the bed.

src: head inside building turn right then inside bedroom
tgt: head inside the building. turn right, then wait inside the bedroom.

src: turn right room right end of hallway toward couches there by couches
tgt: Turn right to exit the room. Turn right when you get to the end of the hallway. Walk toward the couches and stop there by the couches.

src: through door right then straight stairs stairs back of couch
tgt: Go through the door to the right and then go straight to the stairs. Pass the stairs and go to the back of the couch.

src: turn right bedroom right wait at area with couches fireplace
tgt: Turn right and exit the bedroom. Take another right and wait at the sitting area with the couches and fireplace.

src: stairs right right suite on right once in doorway
tgt: Go up the stairs, and go right. Veer right, and enter the suite on the right. Stop once you are in the doorway.

src: up stairs right wait in entrance if kitchen wait there
tgt: Walk up the stairs and take a right. Wait in the entrance if the kitchen and wait there.

src: continue stairs at top right room though opening right of fireplace through door right with sign abe lincoln above
tgt: Continue to climb the stairs and at the top, turn right and exit the room though the opening to the right of the fireplace.  Go through the door opening to your right with the sign "ABE LINCOLN" above it.

src: turn until middle of arches with table by chairs behind through middle arch until long table with chairs on side fireplace further down in next room right door outside on left ninety degrees right walk towards fireplace with long table towards left just before carpet in front of fireplace
tgt: Turn around until you're facing the middle of three arches with a table surrounded by six chairs behind you. Walk through the middle arch until you see a long table with eight chairs on each side and a fireplace further down in the next room to your right. There will be a door leading to the outside on your left. Turn ninety degrees to the right and walk towards the fireplace with the long table towards your left, stopping just before reaching the carpet in front of the fireplace.

src: archways forward immediately right through rectangular archway into first room on left along table at chairs
tgt: Facing the three archways go forward and immediately right, go through the rectangular archway and go into the first room on your left, go along the table, and stop at the chairs.

src: office heading dining room walk through room into kitchen in doorway room
tgt: Leave the office heading to the dining room. Walk through the room and into the kitchen. Stop in the doorway to the sitting room.

src: turn right forward around bed bathroom wait there
tgt: Turn right and move forward around the bed, enter the bathroom and wait there.

src: walk around bed into bathroom stop
tgt: Walk around the bed and into the bathroom and stop.

src: turn around other side of bed stop in bathroom doorway
tgt: Turn around and walk to the other side of the bed and stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: exit room walk across hallway slightly right across kitchen towards sofas turn walkthrough doorway just right of portraits of family
tgt: Exit the room. Walk across the hallway. Turn slightly right and walk across the kitchen towards the sofas. Turn left and walkthrough doorway just right of the portraits of a family.

src: straight hallway right just after kitchen table pathway on left between kitchen island back of brown couch slight right through arch door way straight middle hallway at picture with prayer on
tgt: Go straight down hallway turning right just after the kitchen table. Follow pathway on the left between kitchen island and the back of the brown couch make a slight right passing through the arch door way. Continue straight using the middle hallway stopping at the picture with prayer on it.

src: walk out of bedroom into hall walk past bench then right past island walk through entryway into hallway on right in front of vent
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and into the hall. Walk past the bench and then right past the island. Walk through the entryway and into the hallway on the right. Stop in front of the vent.

src: exit room into corridor then third door on right wait by massage table
tgt: Exit the room into the corridor, then enter the third door on the right and wait by the massage table.

src: walk through bathroom door walk through foyer into room right of panel artwork step into room near massage chair
tgt: Walk through the bathroom door. Walk through the foyer and go into the room to the right of the three panel artwork. Step into the room near the massage chair.

src: exit room in room with square mosaic on floor wall on right through doorway room on left walk bed stop near foot
tgt: Exit the room you are in and enter the larger room with the square mosaic on the floor.  Face the wall on your right and go through the doorway to the room on the left.  Walk to the bed and stop near the foot.

src: walk hall walk end of hall right past small refrigerator in hall just outside door
tgt: Walk left down the hall. Walk to the end of the hall and go right. walk past the small refrigerator and in the hall. Stop just outside the door.

src: walk towards pictures on wall then left straight hall slight right down step into wooden doorway stop
tgt: Walk towards the pictures on the wall and then turn left, go straight down the hall and take the slight right further down, take a step into the wooden doorway and stop.

src: walk past dining room down hall wait in theater room at end of hall
tgt: Walk past the dining room and down the hall. Wait in the theater room, at the end of the hall.

src: exit bedroom then left stairs left of couch wait on third step
tgt: Exit the bedroom and then make a left. Go to the stairs located to the left of the couch and wait on the third step.

src: exit bedroom left walk bottom of stairs stairs in front of window
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go left.  Walk to the bottom of the stairs.  Go up two stairs to stop in front of the window.

src: exit room then then stairs on left steps then
tgt: Exit the room then turn left then go up the stairs on the left. Go up three steps then stop.

src: straight in house way mirror then left once first door right right in middle of doorway
tgt: Go Straight in the house all the way to the mirror then take a left and once you come to your first door take a right and stop right in the middle of the doorway.

src: into house left at end of entry way straight into dining groom through first wall on right in dining room doorway
tgt: Go into the house and take a left at the end of the entry way. Go straight and into the dining groom through the first wall on the right. stop in the dining room doorway.

src: walk through foyer left mirror walk past wall sconce wait at room door threshold
tgt: Walk through foyer. Make left mirror. Walk past wall sconce. Wait at dining room door threshold.

src: walk past dining room table television sharp turn through doorway stop at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk past the dining room table and the television. Make a sharp turn left through the doorway and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk past dining room table into living room out of living room stop at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk past the dining room table into the living room. Take a left out of the living room and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk through dining area table with blue vases on top through next room television through open entryway on other side corner stairs front door home
tgt: Walk through the dining area passed the dining table with blue vases on top. Continue through the next room passed the television and through the open entryway on the other side. Turn the corner and begin to walk up the stairs opposite the front door to the home.

src: while animal print sofa turn walking straight past spiderman statue off carpet through door right of pulp fiction poster door on left window on right
tgt: While facing the animal print sofa, turn left and keep walking straight past the Spiderman statue and off the carpet.  Go through the door to the right of the Pulp Fiction poster.  Stop when there is a door is on your left and a window is on your right.

src: walk past spider-man statue into hallway straight past wooden table pulp fiction poster walk through glass door wait by window
tgt: Walk past Spider-Man statue and into the hallway.  Continue straight past the wooden table and "Pulp Fiction" poster.   Walk through the glass door.  Wait by the window.

src: through hallway after glass door
tgt: Go through the hallway and stop after you have passed the glass door.

src: turn past bed doorway through doorway across hall into kitchen wait
tgt: Turn around and go past the bed to the doorway.  Go through the doorway and across the hall, into the kitchen and stop there and wait.

src: bedroom slight right way slight at counter
tgt: leave bedroom to hallway. turn slight right and enter hall way, turn slight left to kitchen, stop at counter.

src: turn around across hallway stop at entrance kitchen
tgt: Turn around and walk across the hallway, stop at the entrance to the kitchen.

src: turn head through hallway straight into room right at black chairs
tgt: Turn left and head through the hallway.  Walk straight into the room.  Turn right and stop at the black chairs.

src: turn hallway then next immediate left desks right by white bookshelves stop
tgt: Turn left to enter the hallway. Then take your next immediate left and continue to the desks. Turn right by the white bookshelves and stop.

src: walk towards large green vase then through rock hallway on other side turn right forward long wood table
tgt: Walk towards the large green vase and then turn left and walk through the rock hallway. On the other side turn right and walk forward and stop when you reach the long wood table.

src: walk out of doorway hard left couch hard left down hallway second pillar left wait by counter
tgt: walk out of the doorway take a hard left. when you get to the couch take a hard left. walk down the hallway to the second pillar and take a left. wait by the counter.

src: walk out of pantry left left behind couch left into kitchen next counter in kitchen
tgt: Walk out of the pantry and take a left. Take a left behind the couch, and take a left into the kitchen. Stop next to the counter in the kitchen.

src: straight then entryway then couch again straight outside of island
tgt: Go straight and then turn left. Enter the entryway and then turn left to pass the couch again. Keeping going straight and stop outside of the island.

src: straight into house large glass doors turn wait near kitchen area
tgt: Go straight into the house using the large glass doors. Turn left and wait near the kitchen area.

src: walk from patio into house living room walk island table
tgt: Walk from the patio into the house living room. Walk to kitchen island table.

src: enter house into kitchen next first counter on left
tgt: Enter the house, and go into the kitchen. Stop next to the first counter on your left.

src: walk out of bathroom into hallway walk cabinet wall mirror hall walk water cooler into next room ahead walk towards large circular desk area near pamphlets on desk
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom into the hallway. Walk passed the cabinet and wall mirror and continue down the hall. Walk passed the water cooler and into the next room ahead. Walk towards the large circular desk area near the pamphlets laid out on the desk.

src: walk through doorway right straight through next doorway forward then right wait by reception desk
tgt: Walk through doorway and turn right. Walk straight and go through the next doorway. Walk forward and then turn right. Wait by the reception desk.

src: turn around down part of floor next large dark-brown mirror door right towards reception desk
tgt: Turn around and walk down the part of the floor next to the large dark-brown framed mirror. Walk straight out the door and make a right towards the reception desk.

src: walk toward table chairs turn through door way walk through doorway walk through massage room walk through door on right in doorway
tgt: Walk toward the table and chairs, and turn left through the door way.  Walk straight through the doorway and walk through the massage room.  Walk through the door on the right and in the doorway.

src: stairs left through brown archway into first room on left through room into room on right
tgt: Go passed the stairs to your left and go through the brown archway, go into the first room on your left, go through the room and go into the room on the right and stop.

src: walk past stairs into hallway ahead first room on left walk through room past massage tables door ahead wait just inside doorway
tgt: Walk past the stairs and into the hallway ahead. Enter the first room on the left and walk through the room, past the massage tables and to the door ahead. Wait just inside the doorway.

src: turn slightly room right towards stairs wait by small chair
tgt: Turn slightly left and exit the room. Turn right and walk towards the stairs. Wait by the small chair.

src: exit bathroom through double-doors next plants stop
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Go through the double-doors next to the plants and stop.

src: walk around screens outside room once outside room left of large plants after into room
tgt: Walk around the screens and outside the room.  Once outside, go to the room to the left of the large plants.  Stop after stepping into this room.

src: through wooden door next windows straight ahead turn into bathroom at end of hall
tgt: go through wooden door next to windows, and straight ahead, turn left into bathroom at end of hall.

src: walk through doorway left of lighted sculptures on ground straight until long horizontal mirror on right right towards first toilet
tgt: walk through the doorway to the left of the lighted sculptures on the ground. Continue straight until you pass a long horizontal mirror on your right. Turn right and walk towards the first toilet.

src: walk through door left of glowing circles past mirror large cabinet on right left in doorway
tgt: Walk through the door to the left of the glowing circles. Continue past the mirror to the large standing cabinet on the right. Turn left and stop in the doorway.

src: down stairs walk towards red sofa turn bathroom
tgt: Walk down the stairs and walk towards the red sofa. Turn left and enter the bathroom.

src: down stairs way past christmas tree right turn walk past blue chair into room with white sink
tgt: Walk down the stairs all the way and past the Christmas tree. Make a right turn and walk past the blue chair into the room with the white sink.

src: down stairs into room with fireplace around chairs into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Walk down the stairs, walk into the room with the fireplace, walk around the chairs and turn left into the bathroom, stop in front of the sink.

src: walk across living room floor next far side of bar
tgt: Walk across living room to tile floor. Stop next to the far side of the bar.

src: past bed tv desk at mirror by entrance door
tgt: Go past the bed, the tv, and the desk. Stop at mirror by the entrance door.

src: walk past tv toward bathroom before through bathroom door
tgt: Walk past the TV and continue toward the bathroom.  Stop before walking through the bathroom door.

src: turn around left down hallway right down stairs toward kitchen at stair landing
tgt: Turn around, to the left and walk down the hallway. Turn right and walk down the stairs toward the kitchen. Stop at the stair landing.

src: down hall right down stairs right down stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk down the hall and to the right. Walk down the stairs and turn right. Walk down the stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: laundry room then right stairs level right rest of stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Facing the laundry room go left, and then make the right, go down the stairs to the level and turn right, go down the rest of the stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: turn around then straight once inside of house through doors
tgt: Turn around and then walk straight, stop once you're inside of the house through the doors.

src: turn head indoors through double glass doors at partition
tgt: Turn around and head indoors through the double glass doors. Stop at the partition.

src: enter house by doorway with glass doors by latticework inside house directly in front of door
tgt: Enter the house by the larger doorway with the two glass doors.  Stop by the latticework inside the house directly in front of the door.

src: hallway past double doors door open room right in there walk past base of beds few feet then at entrance bathroom wait by first sink
tgt: You'll see a hallway.  When you get past the double doors, there will be a door open and you'll enter that room. Turn right and go in there.  Walk past the base of the beds.  Walk a few more feet and then stop at the entrance to the bathroom.  Wait by the first sink.

src: hall through second door on right on other side of bedroom in bathroom doorway
tgt: Go down the hall and through the second door on the right. Wait on the other side of the bedroom in the bathroom doorway.

src: straight down hallway right into open door turn beds into bathroom in doorway
tgt: Go straight down hallway, turn right into the open door, turn left, walk passed the beds into the bathroom and stop in the doorway.

src: walk past island chair up stairs turn inside doorway
tgt: Walk past the island and the chair. Walk up the stairs and turn left. Stop inside the doorway.

src: walk past bar staircase turn by green vase with white flowers
tgt: Walk past the bar and go left up the staircase. Turn left and stop by the green vase with white flowers.

src: turn along glass railing once at end turn black stairs at top of stairs forward then small room stop
tgt: Turn left and follow along the glass railing. Once at the end turn left and go up the black stairs. At the top of the stairs walk forward and then turn left to enter a small room and stop.

src: turn around out of office into great room forward past staircase on right dining table on left toward kitchen through doorway with kitchen counter on left walk towards island at island turn through kitchen towards kitchen table that part of room before kitchen table
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the office into the great room.  Keep walking forward, past the staircase on your right and the dining table on your left, toward the kitchen.  Go through the doorway with the kitchen counter on your left and walk towards the island.  At the island turn left and walk through the kitchen towards the kitchen table.  Stop when you enter that part of the room, before you get to the kitchen table.

src: turn around out of office walk straight through doorway kitchen left at kitchen island wait on rug just ahead
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the office. Walk straight and through the doorway that leads to the kitchen. Take a left at the kitchen island and wait on the rug just ahead.

src: exit office black table on left into kitchen area turn into dining room then next television
tgt: Exit office, go passed the black table on the left, go into the kitchen area, turn left and go into the dining room, then stop next to the television.

src: walk out of bedroom turn walk right of bathroom just inside bedroom
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn left. Walk to the right of the bathroom and stop just inside the bedroom.

src: turn right through door turn hallway turn again in through door right of bathroom
tgt: Turn right and go through the door. Turn left down the hallway, turn left again, and go in through the door to the right of the bathroom.

src: exit room through door turn first left then quick right turn into bedroom wait by door
tgt: Exit the room through the door and turn left.  Take the first left, then a quick right turn into the bedroom.  Wait by door.

src: bottom of stairs turn along orange wall past stone statue through doorway turn at top of steps
tgt: Go to the bottom of the stairs and turn left. Walk along the orange wall, past the stone statue, and go through the doorway. Turn left and stop at the top of the steps leading down.

src: stairs left around dining table exit through door on left stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs, and take a left. Go around the dining table and exit through the door on the left. Go down the three stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: downstairs u turn straight then wait near double white doors
tgt: Go downstairs. U turn left. Go straight and then turn left. Wait near the double white doors.

src: turn house left bedroom on left wait in between beds
tgt: Turn around and enter the house. Take a left. Enter the bedroom on the left. Wait in between the two beds.

src: enter building through double glass doors on left turn down hallway bedroom wait between benches
tgt: Enter the building through the double glass doors on the left. Turn left and walk down the hallway to the bedroom. Wait between the benches.

src: inside house through glass double doors left left into archway just right of black chair near base of beds in middle of room stop
tgt: Go inside the house through the glass double doors, make a left, make another left and go into the archway that is just to the right of the black chair, go near the base of the beds in the middle of the room and stop.

src: turn right first set of stairs right stop on first landing
tgt: Turn right and go down the first set of stairs to the right stop on the first landing.

src: cross hallway towards stairway flight of stairs wait on landing
tgt: Cross the hallway towards the stairway. Go down one flight of stairs and wait on the landing.

src: past gym equipment halfway stairs
tgt: Go past gym equipment. Stop halfway down stairs.

src: turn then head straight until middle arch grand piano then
tgt: Turn left then head straight until you pass the middle arch and get to the grand piano then stop.

src: walk through first archway on left straight ahead until room with grand piano next grand piano in front of table chairs
tgt: Walk through the first archway on your left.  Walk straight ahead until you reach a room with a grand piano.  Stop next to the grand piano in front of the table and chairs.

src: exit alcove walk past dining area wait in library next piano
tgt: Exit the alcove and walk past the dining area. Wait in the library next to the piano.

src: walk through room past exercise equipment walk out through open door into hallway down tiled hall past closed doors through arched entry into next hall with mirror on wall walk through open door opposite mirror large room with fireplace in center
tgt: Walk through the room past the exercise equipment. Walk out through the open door into the hallway. Walk down the tiled hall past the closed doors. Walk through the arched entry and into the next hall with a mirror on the wall. Walk through the open door opposite the mirror that leads to a large room with a fireplace in the center.

src: walk down hallway turn into open doorway
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway. Turn left into the open doorway.

src: exit door right past mirror in open doorway
tgt: Exit the door. Turn right. Go past mirror. Stop in open doorway.

src: white room with buttons on left side turn in hallway walk straight until circle floor decoration on left step on circle then
tgt: Leave the white room with the buttons on the left side and turn left in the hallway.  Walk straight until you see a circle floor decoration on the left.  Step on the circle and then stop.

src: walk out of elevator hard left out of doorway left wait in front of door
tgt: Walk out of the elevator and take a hard left, walk out of the doorway and take a left. Wait in front of the door.

src: move forwards out of elevator turn exit through door just ahead turn on rug in front of door
tgt: Move forwards out of the elevator. Turn left and exit through the door. just ahead. Turn left and stop on the rug in front of the door.

src: straight then toward round table after round table straight door on left wait there
tgt: Go straight then walk toward the round table. After you pass the round table continue straight and go out the door on the left. Wait there.

src: turn door way across room other side windows on other side turn right before door exit
tgt: Turn left and exit out the door. Walk all the way across the room to the other side. When you reach the windows on the other side, turn left and stop right before you reach the door to exit.

src: through door on right window straight forward through far left hall once hall
tgt: Go through the door on the right facing the window. Walk straight forward and go through the far left hall. Stop once you enter the hall.

src: walk past bottom of stairs right through open door walk into room with couch walk past piano walk through open french door wait on outdoor rug
tgt: Walk past bottom of stairs. Make right through open door. Walk into room with couch. Walk past piano. Walk through open french door. Wait on outdoor rug.

src: walk past stairs out door right into living room turn behind couch walk past piano right outside just outside doors
tgt: Walk past the stairs and out the door. Turn right and walk into the living room. Turn left and walk behind the couch. Walk past the piano and turn right. Walk outside. Stop just outside the doors.

src: walk towards place with white tiles then hard right into living room slight left into room with piano then slightly right towards outside doors outside wait at outside patio
tgt: Walk towards place with white tiles then make a hard right into the living room. Turn a slight left into a room with a piano, then head slightly right towards the outside doors. Go outside and wait at the outside patio.

src: walk along patio area past potted plants along exterior wall of home into front door down hall through open door next hallway with small side table with lamp on top
tgt: Walk along the patio area past the potted plants. Continue along the exterior wall of the home into the front door. Walk down the hall and through the open door to the next hallway with a small side table with lamp on top.

src: down walkway into building hallway in doorway
tgt: Walk down the walkway into the building. Cross the hallway and stop in the doorway.

src: enter cabin by blue dots
tgt: Enter the cabin by following the blue dots.

src: walkway through screen door inside console table with lamp on
tgt: Go down the walkway and through the screen door. Go inside, and stop facing the console table with the lamp on it.

src: walk past painting right toward red painting through doorway left of by chair
tgt: Walk past the painting and turn right. Walk toward the red painting and through the doorway to the left of it. Stop by the chair.

src: end of bed immediate right past bathroom exit bedroom through open doorway walk straight until large red painting at turn o clock through doorway on left of painting through there destination
tgt: Facing the end of the bed, take an immediate right, walk past the bathroom and exit the bedroom through the open doorway. Walk straight until you see a large red painting. At the painting make a turn towards 11 o clock and go through the doorway on the left of the painting. Through there, you will reach your destination.

src: straight hallway right hallway stairs then into room on far left wait at entrance
tgt: Go straight down the hallway. Turn right and continue down the hallway. Pass the stairs and then go into the room on the far left. Wait at the entrance.

src: turn kitchen turn at kitchen until right before yellow couch by picture on right
tgt: Turn left and to towards the kitchen, turn left at the kitchen and go until you are right before the yellow couch by the picture on your right.

src: dining room through door kitchen turn straight room past refrigerator area area in front of fireplace
tgt: Leave the dining room through the closest door and enter the kitchen.  Turn left and walk straight down the room past the refrigerator, dining area, and sitting area.  Stop in front of the fireplace.

src: forward into kitchen left through kitchen next fireplace in living room
tgt: Walk forward into the kitchen and take a left. Walk through the kitchen. Stop next to the fireplace in the living room.

src: onto large rug across other side of room toward archway through arched hallway into room with seating

tgt: Go down the stairs and stop in front of the painting to the right.

tgt: Walk down the walkway and wait at the top of the steps.

Then turn ninety degrees to the right after entering the room. Move forward past two large circular tables to your left and a display case on your right while walking to the stairs leading downwards. Walk past the stairs with the stairs on your left and stop at the vaulted hallway on your right.

Move across the carpet with the grey chair just to your left and then stop at the doorway to the hallway with five pictures on the wall.

tgt: Walk past the screen in the hallway and enter the room with the beauty chair. Turn to the right and stop in the doorway on the right. This enters into a room with two long benches and a glass case.

src: exit bathroom down hallway with lockers on left exit room right hard right in doorway
tgt: Exit bathroom. Walk down the hallway with the lockers on the left. Exit room and turn right. Make another hard right and stop in the doorway.

src: walk past bedroom door right hallway past ceiling rafter wait at open door on left
tgt: Walk past bedroom door. Make right down hallway. Walk past ceiling rafter. Wait at open door on left.

src: exit room right across room hallway wait in middle of hallway between door entrances
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Keep walking across the room and hallway and wait in middle of the hallway between two door entrances.

src: walk through door out of attic bedroom right down small corridor living room with glass coffee table.walk past coffee table down long corridor settee left before corridor wait in corridor at first doors with open doors on left right
tgt: Walk through the door and out of the attic bedroom. Turn right and walk down the small corridor to a living room with a glass coffee table.Walk past the coffee table and down the long corridor which has a settee to the left before entering the corridor. Wait in the corridor at the first doors you come to, with open doors on both the left and the right.

src: exit kitchen opening on left head until large glass doors right wait by fireplace on right
tgt: Exit the kitchen using the opening on the left. Head straight until you get to large glass doors. Turn right and wait by the fireplace on the right.

src: walk around table out of kitchen walk through hall into living room into fireplace stop
tgt: Walk around the table and out of the kitchen. Walk through the hall and into the living room. Go into the fireplace and stop.

src: straight stove hall room right stop next black brick wall
tgt: Go straight passed the stove and follow the hall to dining room, turn right and stop next to the black brick wall.

src: toward then behind desks with glass wall on right past book case toward long table in between tables near post
tgt: Go toward and then behind the desks with the glass wall on the right.  Go past the book case and toward the long table.  Stop in between the two tables and near the post.

tgt: When you are at the top of the stairs go straight back to the table with the computer and black office chair. Once you are at the table walk around the back of the chair, then walk straight back until you get to the wooden table that is in front of a projection screen. Now walk to the wooden chair in front of the screen and wait.

src: walk from stairs work space directly ahead conference room bookcase on right wait by wooden tables
tgt: Walk from the stairs to the work space directly ahead. Pass the conference room and the bookcase on the right. Wait by the wooden tables.

src: exit bathroom right outside wait just outside door left
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Walk outside. Wait just outside the door and to the left.

src: after bathroom through arched opening on extreme right forward past fireplace on right through doors ahead after building couple of steps left wait
tgt: After exiting the bathroom, go through the arched opening on your extreme right. Go forward past the fireplace on your right, through the doors straight ahead. After exiting the building, take a couple of steps to the left and wait.

src: walk towards giant leather couch fireplace on way glass door outside house wait here
tgt: Walk towards the giant leather couch.  Pass the fireplace on your way to the glass door leading outside. Exit the house.  Wait here.

src: exit area staircase turn through door chairs toward way wait by first window
tgt: Exit living area, pass the staircase and turn left and exit through the door. Pass the chairs toward walk way. Wait by first window encountered.

tgt: Walk past the double doors and veer left. Walk through the door to the left and outside. Walk to the right of the patio furniture and stop by the railing on the walkway.

src: walk through large double doors cross left through double doors right on balcony
tgt: Walk through the large double doors, cross to the left and go through those double doors. Continue to the right and stop on the balcony.

src: down stairs wait on red rug
tgt: Walk down the stairs and wait on the red rug.

src: turn steps as on red rug
tgt: Turn left to steps leading down. Go down steps and continue following them down as they spiral left. Stop on red rug.

src: stairs on mat at bottom on tile floor
tgt: Go down all the stairs and stop on the mat at the bottom on the tile floor.

src: turn slightly right forward straight into doorway in front of with rug once right in doorway of room
tgt: Turn slightly right and walk forward straight into the doorway in front of you with a rug, Once you enter, turn right and stop in the doorway of the room.

src: forward inside toward curtain then right into doorway in doorway
tgt: Walk down forward and go inside. walk toward the curtain and then turn right into the doorway. Stop in the doorway.

src: straight walkway through archway right into archway on right
tgt: Go straight down the walkway through the archway, take a right into the archway on the right and stop.

src: into room right then at stairs next left
tgt: Go into the room and turn right. Then turn left at the stairs and take your next left.

src: walk into room with hardwood floor as forward past steps turn room between dining room elevator wait here
tgt: Walk into the room with hardwood floor.  Keep left as you move forward,past the steps.  Turn left, and enter the room between the dining room and elevator.  Wait here.

tgt: Enter the house and walk past the stairs and turn left.  Enter the mini kitchen and stand near the glass cookie jar.

src: through glass doors turn into double glass doors on left wait there
tgt: Go through the glass sliding doors. Turn left and go into the double glass doors on the left. Wait there.

src: enter glass doors turn through double doors near lounge chairs there
tgt: Enter glass doors. Turn left and enter through double doors near lounge chairs. Stop there.

src: walk through glass doorway doorway on left
tgt: Walk left out through the glass doorway and go to the doorway on the left.

src: exit bedroom turn bedroom on right
tgt: exit bedroom, turn left, enter bedroom on right.

src: thorough door through hallway right bedroom on right enter bedroom in front of desk
tgt: Go thorough door, through the hallway, turn right, to the furthest bedroom on the right. Enter, bedroom and stop in front of the desk.

src: door hard left.turn right into bedroom
tgt: Go out the door, turn hard left.turn right and go into bedroom.

src: head into room exit into hallway right wait inside bedroom through first door on left
tgt: Head into the sitting room and exit into the hallway. Turn right and wait inside the bedroom through the first door on the left.

src: forward into room then into hallway then right forward first door on left then step through bedroom doorway wait
tgt: Walk forward into the sitting room. Then turn left and walk into the hallway. Then turn right and walk forward to the first door on the left. Then step through the bedroom doorway and wait.

src: exit room door in middle then door on left right into door on left across green brown cloth artwork on right wall wait there near fireplace
tgt: Exit the room using the door in the middle then turn left and go out the door on the left. Turn right and go into the door on the left that is straight across the green and brown cloth artwork on the right wall. Wait there near the fireplace.

tgt: Walk out of the room and go down the stairs. Stop in the middle of the landing on the stairs next to the flowers.

src: walk through doorway directly in front of right down stairs landing
tgt: Walk through the doorway directly in front of you and turn to the right.  Walk down the stairs.  Stop when you get to the landing.

src: exit through double doors first half of stairs right on landing just in front of flowers
tgt: Exit through the double doors and go down the first half of stairs located to your right. Wait on the landing just in front of the flowers.

tgt: Make a left out of the doorway and walk behind the table and chairs, with the table on your right. Then walk around the sitting area in front of you to the doorway on the right. Make a right turn and walk toward the doorway at the end. Wait there.

tgt: After you leave the pantry take a left into the dinning room and walk to the sitting area at the end of the dinning room. Now make a right in the sitting area and in the doorway to the hall. Next make a left in the hallway and waitin the doorway of the room with the stairs.

src: laundry room right onto balcony through door across hall once off rug
tgt: Leave the laundry room and go right. Go onto the balcony through the door across the hall. Stop once you are off the rug.

src: turn right down hallway wood doors ahead once outside in area
tgt: Turn right and walk down the hallway. Go out both wood doors straight ahead and stop once you are outside in the sitting area.

src: walk down hallway house doors ahead in porch
tgt: Walk straight down the hallway. Exit the house using the two doors straight ahead and wait in the porch.

src: turn around straight at hallway
tgt: turn around and walk straight. Stop at the hallway.

src: walk forward in kitchen past sink on right straight past stove out of kitchen once out of kitchen in hallway stop just beyond doorway
tgt: Walk forward in the kitchen past the sink on your right Keep walking straight past the stove and out of the kitchen. Once out of the kitchen in the hallway stop just beyond the doorway.

src: turn right until stove on left sink on right though kitchen doorway next cabinets forward until in middle of hallway by doors
tgt: TURN RIGHT UNTIL THE STOVE IS ON THE LEFT AND A SINK IS ON THE RIGHT, WALK THOUGH THE KITCHEN TO GET TO A DOORWAY NEXT TO SOME CABINETS, WALK FORWARD UNTIL YOU ARE IN THE MIDDLE OF THE HALLWAY SURROUNDED BY DOORS.

src: walk from stairs across room table stop
tgt: Walk from stairs across room to pool table and stop.

src: corner of fireplace right head towards closet left of pool table wait in front of
tgt: Go to the corner of the fireplace and turn right. Head towards the closet to the left of the pool table and wait in front of it.

src: turn right at bottom of stairs walk across room fireplace on left as then right towards billiards table in front of wooden door with horizontal slats by billiards table
tgt: Turn right at the bottom of the stairs and walk across the room.  The fireplace will be on your left as you pass.  Then, turn right and walk towards the billiards table.  Stop in front of the wooden door with horizontal slats that is by the billiards table.

src: turn right down hallway till right past fireplace walk towards chairs then right stand by first open door wait there
tgt: Turn to the right and walk down the hallway.  Walk till you can turn to the right and walk past the fireplace.  Walk towards the chairs.  Then turn to the right and go stand by the first open door.  Wait there.

src: walk out of bedroom turn down hallway right past fireplace walk right of glass case turn in doorway
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn left. Walk down the hallway and turn right. Walk past the fireplace and walk to the right of the glass case. Turn left and stop in the doorway.

src: turn left straight right past stairs fireplace straight wait in doorway of room right of hutch
tgt: Turn around and take a left. Walk straight. Take a right and walk past the stairs and the fireplace. Keep walking straight and wait in the doorway of the room to the right of the hutch.

src: walk across kitchen slight right towards hallway.enter hallway slight left hallway study at desk
tgt: walk across the kitchen and make a slight right towards the hallway.enter the hallway and make a slight left follow the hallway and enter the study. Stop at the desk.

src: exit kitchen through arched doorway down hallway slight right door slight right office wait by desk
tgt: Exit the kitchen through the arched doorway, walk down the hallway to the slight right, walk to the door, turn slight right to enter the office, wait by the desk.

src: walk behind couch exit room office right
tgt: walk behind couch, exit room to right, enter office to right.

src: exit room right by doorway bathroom
tgt: Exit the room and take a right by the doorway. Enter the bathroom.

src: door right at hall into kitchen right turn at first door on right bathroom
tgt: Go to the door and turn right at the hall and into the kitchen. Keep going to the right and turn at the first door on the right which is a bathroom.

src: past bed exit room then into next room right wait by bathroom sink
tgt: Go past the bed and exit the room then go into the next room to the right and wait by the bathroom sink.

src: walk between tables towards doorway then left once through doors couple of steps then right there
tgt: Walk between the tables.  And go towards the doorway.  Then turn to the left once you're through the doors.  Walk a couple of steps and then stop. Wait right there.

src: move past massage tables out door left just outside doorway
tgt: Move past the massage tables and out the door to the left. Stop just outside the doorway.

src: walk across room right on other side of door
tgt: Walk across the room, and stop right on the other side of the door.

src: turn right down hall at end of hall wait near exit sign
tgt: Turn right and walk down the hall. Stop at the end of the hall and wait near the exit sign.

src: turn right across hall wait in middle of first intersection with exit sign in front
tgt: Turn right and walk across the hall. Wait in the middle of the first intersection with an EXIT sign in front.

src: walk into hallway right walk end of hallway stand under exit sign
tgt: Walk into the hallway and turn right.  Walk to the end of the hallway and stand under the exit sign.

src: exit massage room straight into next doorway then
tgt: Exit the massage room, go straight into the next doorway and then stop.

src: exit room walk into doorway across from next tall green plant in doorway
tgt: Exit the room and walk into the doorway straight across from it, next to the tall green plant. Stop in the doorway.

src: through doorway then across hall stop
tgt: Go through the doorway and then go across the hall and stop.

tgt: With the entrance to the kitchen on your left, move forward down the hallway. then climb the stairs on your right. At the top of the first flight of stairs, go into the room on your left.

src: walk then right stairs on right left into room on left wait near desk
tgt: Walk straight then turn right and go up the stairs on the right. Turn left and go into the room on the left. Wait near the desk.

tgt: Walk down hall, turn right at the stairs and go up them. On top of stairs turn left into the study. Wait at desk.

src: straight hallway turn stairs wait there
tgt: Go straight down the hallway. Turn left and go down the stairs. Wait there.

src: walk through hall stairs on left bottom turn
tgt: Walk through the hall and go to the stairs on the left. When you get to the bottom, turn left and stop.

src: glass floor stairs in dining room wait near banister
tgt: Follow the glass floor to head down the stairs, stop in the dining room and wait near the banister.

src: walk through entryway stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Walk through the entryway and left up the stairs that curve left. Stop at the top of the stairs.

tgt: Walk forward towards the staircases and go up the staircase on the left. Once you have finished climbing up the first set of stairs there will be a short landing area. Wait there do not continue upstairs or go back downstairs on the set of stairs in front of you.

tgt: Turn around and go past the bar and then turn slightly right, past the brown chair.  Continue down the hall.  When you get the bedroom, you stop right before walking into it.

tgt: Exit the living room. Turn right. Walk into the bedroom and wait by the table.

src: hall with sailboat art left turn after doorway in bathroom doorway next sink
tgt: Continue down the hall with the sailboat art to your left. Turn left after the doorway. Stop in the bathroom doorway, next to the sink.

tgt: Turn left and go past the stairs on your right then turn right and go past the bench on your right. Enter the room on your right and wait by the white couch.

tgt: With the water fountain directly behind you, enter the room ahead and turn ninety degrees to the left and walk past the wooden staircase on your right. Turn right underneath the staircase and walk down the hallway leading to the exit. Just before reaching the exit, turn right into the room with the sign "Bridal Room" next to the entrance. Go to the right after you enter the room and wait in front to the two chairs that will be on your right.

tgt: Go out of the room then turn left and go out to the hallway then turn left and wait at the laundry entrance.

tgt: Exit the office, turn right, then turn right again. Stop in the doorway.

src: stairs in bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairs and stop in the bathroom.

tgt: Walk up the stairs and into the room that is almost straight in front of you. Enter the room and wait.

tgt: Leave the room and take a right. Once on the stone ground take a left, and go straight. take a left into the dining room. Walk forward and stop in the doorway to the living room.

tgt: Exit bedroom and walk down hallway. When you have and opening to your left in front of a wooden door, turn left toward the potted plants. Follow this pathway until you can turn left just before the white chair, into the library. Walk past the sink on the right side of the table and wait at the entryway of the living room.

src: walk over pool
tgt: Walk over to the pool.

src: turn beside pool next potted plants
tgt: Turn left and wait beside the pool and next to the potted plants.
