tgt: Walk forward with the pool on your left. Stop half way down the pool next to the middle planter.

tgt: Walk down the steps and turn right. Walk forward past the guitar. Walk into the second door to the left. Stop just inside the door.

tgt: Walk down the stairs and take a right. Walk forward and enter the foyer through the second door on the left. Stop inside the doorway next to the door.

tgt: Walk straight and then turn right at the couch. Walk straight past the guitar and then walk into the middle doorway. Wait in the entryway.

tgt: Turn left and walk past the bar. Walk outside and stop just outside the doorway.

src: room left straight room at end of hall once past doors
tgt: Leave the room and take a left. Walk straight and leave the room at the end of the hall. Stop once you are past the doors.

tgt: Turn left and go past the bar and out the large double doors. Wait outside.

tgt: Walk towards the white door on the left and turn left into the kitchen. Walk straight past the  white chairs and past the dining room. Wait at the doorway to the foyer.

tgt: Cross the entryway and go into the kitchen. Walk to the far end of the kitchen and wait near the stairs.

tgt: Leave the laundry room and enter the kitchen. Walk through the kitchen heading to the foyer. Stop once you enter the foyer with the round whit table.

tgt: Exit the room on the door to your left then head straight until you get to a large room with three lounge chairs. Wait near the table and basket in that room.

tgt: Walk straight and go out the wood door to your left. Once out, keep walking straight across the room. Once you reach the wall in front of you, turn left and stop in the doorway to the room with 2 large chairs.

tgt: Exit medical building to main lobby and into room with loungers. Stop at desk.

tgt: Exit the bathroom. Walk straight until you see two silver vases straight ahead then turn left. Wait near the white door with the glass decoration. Wait there.

tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and through the entryway. Turn left at the end table and stop in the doorway.

tgt: Walk along the path with the guardrail to your right. At the end of the hall, stop in the doorway of the bedroom on the right.

tgt: face the railing,turn left and walk down the hall, pass a closet on your right and stand in the doorway to a bedroom on your right.

tgt: Walk down the hallway, past the stairway banister. Walk past the double closet doors, and then wait in the threshold of the open door on the right.

tgt: Exit bedroom and take a right.  Walk to the end of the hallway and into the other bedroom.

tgt: Walk into the hallway and turn right.  Keep going right until you get to the end of the hallway and enter a bedroom.  Stop after stepping into the bathroom.

tgt: Exit the bedroom. Turn right.Go down the hallway until you get to a room. Wait near the bed.

tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn left and go straight until you get the chandelier on top of your head.

src: right into hall left just paintings on left
tgt: Turn right into the hall and take a left. Stop just passed the paintings on the left.

src: straight left first right near right side chair
tgt: go straight and take left and turn first right near right side chair.

tgt: Move into the hallway with the tall house plant to your left. Move forward and pass the two doors to your left. Turn 45 degrees to the left and pass the grey couch to your left. Move toward the steps and turn left. Ascend two steps and then stop.

tgt: Walk along the hallway keeping to your left. Walk up the first few steps of the stairs to your left. Wait there.

tgt: Stand so the patio is behind you and walk past the dining table and screen after that.  When you reach the front door, turn left going into the kitchen.  Stop in the doorway to the kitchen.

tgt: Go passed the glass table to the right, go through the way and step into the archway to the left of the small glass of table and stop.

tgt: walk past the two white couches, make a left turn and stop near the door to the left.

tgt: walk past the plant, over the rug, down the stairs. Go into bedroom and make a sharp left into closet.

tgt: Turn to the right and walk past the Indian rug. Go down the stairs and make a very sharp left into the closet.

tgt: Walk across the carpet past the plant. Walk down the stairs into the bedroom and make a sharp turn left. Walk into the closet and stop.

src: exit door turn past mirror first door on right wait by kitchen counter
tgt: Exit the door and turn left.   Walk past mirror, and enter the first door on your right.  Wait by kitchen counter.

src: turn slightly right towards wall turn across hallway past mirror on floor right wait by kitchen counter in kitchen area
tgt: Turn slightly right and walk towards the wall. Turn left and walk across the hallway past the mirror on the floor. Turn right and wait by the kitchen counter in the kitchen area.

src: walk forward then forward again then at kitchen area
tgt: walk forward then turn left, walk forward again then turn left at the kitchen area.

src: stairs on left at top of stairs right sraight towards other stairs in front of spiral staircase
tgt: Go up the stairs on the left. At the top of the stairs turn right and go sraight towards the other stairs. Stop in front of the spiral staircase.

src: stairwell then straight at base of next stairwell
tgt: Go up the stairwell then go straight and stop at the base of the next stairwell.

src: up stairs right up stairs under spiral staircase
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn right. Walk up the stairs and stop under the spiral staircase.

src: down hallway. at bottom of stairs turn right into dining room stop
tgt: Walk down the hallway., at the bottom of the stairs turn right, walk into the dining room and stop.

src: walk down hall past large urns right after large plant dining room
tgt: Walk straight down this hall, past the two large urns and right after the large plant you will see the dining room.

src: hard left hallway at end of hallway turn right into dining room
tgt: turn hard left and walk down hallway. at the end of the hallway turn right and go into the dining room.

src: walk way down stairs next at second bottom step of stairs
tgt: Walk all the way down the stairs next to you.  Wait at the second to bottom step of the stairs.

src: way down stairway in front of monitor small table open door
tgt: Go all the way down the stairway and stop in front of a monitor, facing a small table and an open door.

src: stairs down next part of stairs level straight ahead at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and down the next part of the stairs to the lower level. Go straight ahead and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: straight turn table couch into large room right into exercise room stop in doorway on left
tgt: Go straight and turn left passed the table. Go passed the couch and into the large room. Turn right into the exercise room and stop in the doorway on the left.

src: walk past kitchen on right through dining room walk past curved sofa on left right into home gym wait in threshold of open double doors exterior
tgt: Walk past kitchen on the right. Walk through the dining room. Walk past the curved sofa on the left. Make a right into the home gym. Wait in the threshold of the open double doors to the exterior.

src: walk through doorway in front of left ninety degrees once through doorway walk past table on right twenty degrees right walk through large doorway in front of straight through doorway past large couch on left once past couch right until chair in corner doorway right through doorway exercise machine doorway left through open doorway
tgt: Walk straight through the doorway that is in front of you.  Turn left ninety degrees once you are through the doorway.  Walk straight past the table that is on your right.  Turn twenty degrees to your right and walk through the large doorway in front of you.  Walk straight through the doorway and past the large couch that is on your left.  Once you are past the couch, turn right until you are facing a chair in the corner.  You will see a doorway to your right.  Walk through the doorway.  You will see an exercise machine and another doorway to your left.  Walk through the open doorway.

src: turn near glass office
tgt: Turn around and stop near the glass office.

src: down corridor till corner next fire extinguisher wait
tgt: Walk down the corridor till you reach the corner. Stop there next to the fire extinguisher and wait.

src: about face at end of corridor
tgt: About face and stop at the end of the corridor.

src: turn around past stairs through doorway right into other room ahead there
tgt: Turn around and walk past the stairs and through the doorway. Take a right and go into the other room that is straight ahead and wait there.

src: forward with elevators on left through door on right third door on left in room stop just past door
tgt: Walk forward with the elevators on your left. Go through the door on your right and enter the third door on the left. In the room stop just past the door.

src: walk around counter past statue stairwell forward woven chair area through open doorway ahead walk through hallway past wall art into open doorway near small hanging ceiling lamp
tgt: Walk around the counter past the statue and stairwell. Continue forward passed the woven chair area through the open doorway ahead. Walk through the hallway past the wall art and into the open doorway near the small hanging ceiling lamp.

src: walk forward painting of light bulbs once first hallway left before again
tgt: Walk forward pass the painting of the light bulbs. Once you pass them, turn down the first hallway to your left and stop before you can turn again.

src: down hall past chairs turn under exit sign few feet past door on right
tgt: Walk down the hall past the chairs and turn left under the exit sign. Stop a few feet past the door on the right.

src: down hall at exit sign in middle of hall
tgt: Walk down the hall to and turn left at the exit sign. Stop in the middle of the hall.

src: walk out of sauna into massage room walk around massage beds through door at far left turn through first door on left wait near sinks
tgt: Walk out of the sauna into the massage room. Walk around the two massage beds and go through the door at the far left. Turn left and walk through the first door on the left. Wait near the sinks.

src: walk out of sauna walk past glass display out of sauna door walk past triptych left at pendant lighting wait at planter half-wall
tgt: Walk out of sauna. Walk past glass display shelving. Make left out of sauna door. Walk past framed triptych. Make left at pendant lighting. Wait at planter half-wall.

src: walk out of sauna exit massage room in massage room left second left bathroom at corner of parttion before sink
tgt: Walk out of the sauna and exit the massage room. In the massage room take a left. take the second left and enter the bathroom. Stop at the corner of the parttion before you reach the sink.

src: exit building through entryway on patio just outside front door
tgt: Exit the building through entryway. Stop on patio just outside the front door.

src: at bottom of stairs face left of marble table turn outside as soon as onto pavement outside
tgt: at the bottom of the stairs face left, walk to the left of the marble table and turn left to walk outside. Stop as soon as you make it onto the pavement outside.

src: turn toward round table between large benches out glass/wood door then
tgt: Turn left and walk toward the round table. Go between the two large benches and out the glass/wood door then stop.

src: enter door right wall right again at bathroom entrance door
tgt: Enter the door and turn right passing the wall. Turn right again, and stop at the bathroom entrance door.

src: turn through doorway right towards wall turn bathroom
tgt: Turn left, walk through the doorway, turn right, walk towards the wall, turn left, and enter the bathroom.

src: into room right then right again into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Go into the room, turn right and then turn right again and go into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: walk around bed forward at foot of bed with patio on right enter bathroom through door on right in bathroom across from shower
tgt: Walk around the bed go forward at the foot of the bed. With the patio on your right enter the bathroom through the door on the right. Stop in the bathroom across from the shower.

src: left after bed walk into bathroom on right wait in bathroom
tgt: Take a left after the bed and walk into the bathroom on the right. Wait in the bathroom.

src: walk into bedroom turn past bed into bathroom in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and turn left. Walk past the bed into the bathroom. Stop in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: walk on stairs at window
tgt: Walk straight to stairs and go down them. Stop on stairs at window.

src: walk forward turn stairs down stairs at stairs window
tgt: Walk forward and turn left towards the stairs. Walk down the stairs, and stop at the stairs where the window is.

src: walk forward stairs on right side down stairs wait on bottom step by hand statue
tgt: Walk forward to the stairs on the right side. Walk down the stairs. Wait on the bottom step by the hand statue.

src: turn in front of statue.head spiral staircase head half-way down stairs after landing on stair next wall outlet
tgt: Turn left in front of the statue.Head down the spiral staircase. Head half-way down the stairs after the landing. Stop on the stair next to the wall outlet.

src: downstairs level down next stairs about halfway down
tgt: Go downstairs one level. Start down the next stairs and stop about halfway down.

src: turn then stairs then around down stairs on step
tgt: Turn left then go down the stairs and then go around and continue going down the stairs. Stop on the 11th step.

src: down hallway past restrooms elevators small lobby with telephone
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the restrooms and some elevators.  Stop when you pass a small lobby with a telephone.

src: hallway until gold trash in front of middle elevator
tgt: Follow the hallway until you see a gold colored trash can. Wait in front of the middle elevator.

src: straight across hall until elevators in front of middle elevator
tgt: Go straight across the hall until you get to the elevators and stop in front of the middle elevator.

src: exit closet then bathroom via door right ninety degrees right then pass through doorway ahead of
tgt: Exit the closet and then exit the bathroom via the door to your right. Turn ninety degrees to the right and then pass through the doorway ahead of you.

src: exit closet right door right forward towards bookcase with bear cabinet stuff bear on right wait here
tgt: Exit the closet and go out the right door. Turn right and walk forward towards bookcase with the bear. Stop when you see the cabinet and the stuff bear on the right and wait here.

src: turn right bathroom right then right again into hallway next door wait there
tgt: Turn right to exit the bathroom. Turn right and then right again to go into the hallway next door. Wait there.

src: walk forward down hall onto section of floor from wood here
tgt: Walk forward, down The hall. Step onto the section of the floor which goes from wood to tile. Stop here.

src: walk past fireplace past long white table on left straight middle of long room stop after wooden floor onto tile almost under last chandelier
tgt: Walk straight past the fireplace and past the long white table on the left.  Keep walking straight down the middle of this long room and stop after stepping off the wooden floor and onto the tile, almost under the last chandelier.

src: hallway passed fireplace hallway white banquet table wood floor into tile
tgt: Walk down hallway passed fireplace. Continue down hallway passed white banquet table. Stop where the wood floor turns into tile.

src: walk towards large bookshelf right into first doorway before bookshelf down hallway sculpture in front of sculpture
tgt: Walk towards the large bookshelf.  Turn right into the first doorway before the bookshelf.  Walk down the hallway to the sculpture and stop in front of the sculpture.

src: straight until leather chair right through doorway towards end of hall then wooden glass doorway left then wait
tgt: Go straight until you get to the leather chair.  Turn right.  Go through a doorway, towards the end of the hall.  Then there will be a wooden and glass doorway, that's where you need to turn left and then wait.

src: walk forward degrees left hall just right of bookcase through second doorway on left with double doors in doorway
tgt: Walk forward, turn 90 degrees to the left, go down the hall just to the right of the bookcase.  Go through the second doorway on the left (with the double doors) and stop in the doorway.

src: turn right down hallway turn wait near round table
tgt: Turn right and down the hallway. Turn left and wait near the round table .

src: turn wood green door right of fire extinguisher forward until rope on other side of rope next rug
tgt: Turn around and exit out the wood and green door to the right of the fire extinguisher. Walk forward until you reach the rope. Stop on the other side of the rope when you reach the next rug.

src: turn door right of fire extinguisher forward next room walk over small table behind first stool
tgt: Turn around and exit the door to the right of the fire extinguisher. Walk forward and enter the next room. Walk over to the small table and stop behind the first stool you reach.

src: away from bookshelf next room walk through toward staircase up stairs about steps up
tgt: Walk away from the bookshelf. Enter the next room and walk through it, toward the staircase. Start up the stairs and stop about two steps up.

src: straight table straight into other room straight couch into other room stair second step
tgt: Go straight and pass the table and go straight into the other room. Go straight and pass the couch and go into the other room and go up the stair to the second step.

src: dining room through entryway through living room wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Leave the dining room, go through the entryway, walk through the living room, and wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: closet painting print with heads light switch
tgt: Go to the closet. Go to the painting. Go to the print with six heads. Go to the light switch.

src: walk forward bed right outside room down hallway past end of landing stop
tgt: walk forward, pastt the bed, take a right to go outside the room and down the hallway.  Move past the end of the landing and stop.

src: walk forward past bed right into hallway outside of room down corridor stop in front of closet across from painting
tgt: Walk forward past the bed  and take a right into the hallway outside of the room and walk down the corridor an stop in front of the closet across from the painting.

src: head until closet wait inside
tgt: Head straight until you get to the closet and wait inside.

src: walk past bathtub then into walk in closet then in middle of room
tgt: walk past the bathtub then go into the walk in closet then stand in the middle of the room.

src: walk straight across room group of sinks on left walk in closet wait
tgt: Walk straight across the room, passing the group of sinks on your left. Enter the walk in closet and wait.

src: walk past red purple furniture in living room area glass table on left turn up small staircase into kitchen area wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk past the red and purple furniture in the living room area and the glass table on your left.  Turn left and walk up the small staircase into the kitchen area and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: turn right past table stairs next sink
tgt: Turn right and walk past the table. Go up the stairs and wait next to the sink.

src: walk straight toward red purple couches steps on left wait near sink of kitchen
tgt: Walk straight toward the red and purple couches. Pass them and go up the steps on the left. Wait near the sink of the kitchen.

src: exit locker room second into massage room wait there in between massage tables
tgt: Exit the locker room and take your second left into the massage room. Wait there in between the two massage tables.

src: turn out door once out past chair door on left once room
tgt: Turn left and walk out the door. Once out, walk past the chair and enter the 2nd door on the left. Stop once you enter the room.

src: bathroom left massage room through door left of stationary bike stand between beds at foot of bed
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and take a left. Enter the massage room through the door to the left of the stationary bike. Stand between the two beds at the foot of the bed.

src: walk past couch oven front door out door on entrance mat outside
tgt: Walk past the couch and the oven to the front door. Walk out the door and stop on the entrance mat outside.

src: onto balcony on top of place mat
tgt: Go out onto the balcony and stop on top of the place mat.

src: walk forward few steps doorway
tgt: walk forward and stop a few steps out the doorway.

src: walk forward down hallway into bedroom turn once bedroom in closet
tgt: Walk forward down the hallway and into the bedroom. Turn left once you enter the bedroom and stop in the closet.

src: straight until into bedroom turn into closet wait there
tgt: Go straight until you go into the bedroom. Turn left and go into the closet. Wait there.

src: down hall past pictures paintings of ocean scenes walk into bedroom ahead at end of hall into closet area near entrance of room
tgt: Walk down the hall past the pictures and paintings of ocean scenes. Walk into the  bedroom straight ahead at the end of the hall. Turn into the closet area near the entrance of the room.

src: walk through living room past kitchen second step on stairs
tgt: Walk through the living room past the kitchen to the second step on the stairs.

src: walk between couches walk bottom of stairs up stairs stop
tgt: Walk between the two couches. Walk to the bottom of the stairs.  Walk up two stairs and stop.

src: footstool on rug between tables on second stair
tgt: Go to the footstool. Go on the rug. Go between the tables. Go on the second stair.

src: exit room door on left then straight until stairs wait on third step
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the left and then go straight until you get to the stairs and wait on the third step.

src: walk toward desk with cushions in front of toward doorway right doorwaya nd walk toward stairs downstairs on third stair
tgt: Walk toward the desk with two cushions in front of it.  Turn left to walk toward the doorway.  Turn right to go out the doorwaya nd walk toward the stairs.  Go downstairs and stop on the third stair.

src: turn right towards desk turn bedroom door right exit bedroom stairs halfway stairs wait
tgt: Turn right, go towards the desk, turn left and go to the bedroom door. Turn right, exit bedroom, go to the stairs.  Go halfway down the stairs and wait.

src: turn into bedroom left again doorway on right glass doors of shower left at doorway toilet
tgt: Turn left, go into the bedroom, go left again, take the doorway on the right, pass the glass doors of the shower and to the left, stop at the doorway to the toilet.

src: exit closet walk across bedroom en suite bathroom in area outside door toilet
tgt: Exit the closet and walk across the bedroom. Enter the en suite bathroom and stop in the area outside the door to the toilet.

src: exit closet turn then around bedroom heading bathroom in corner enter through bathroom door in front of toilet
tgt: Exit the closet and turn left, then walk around the bedroom heading to the bathroom in the corner. Enter and go through the bathroom to the door in front of the toilet.

src: right staircase on left stairs turn left before outside
tgt: Go to the right and go down the staircase on the left. Continue down the stairs and turn to the left. Stop before going outside.

src: stairs at bottom of stairs degrees left feet away from open glass door
tgt: Go down the stairs.  At the bottom of the stairs, turn 90 degrees to the left and stop 5 feet away from the open sliding glass door.

src: turn right top of stairs down stairs right down stairs turn in front of glass doors
tgt: Turn right and walk to the top of the stairs. Walk down the stairs and turn right. Walk down the stairs and turn left. Stop in front of the glass doors.

src: walk past tub right left of pool table in doorway
tgt: Walk past the tub and to the right. Walk to the left of the pool table and stop in the doorway.

src: exit bedroom into game room across game room at dresser
tgt: Exit bedroom into game room, walk across game room to bedroom. Stop at dresser.

src: exit master bedroom walk past pool table couches wait by doorway left of lamp post
tgt: Exit the master bedroom and walk past the pool table and couches.  Wait by the doorway to the left of the lamp post.

src: walk ahead past blue chair out door once out of door right door ahead in center of room
tgt: Walk straight ahead past the blue chair and out the door. Once you are out of the door, turn right and enter the door straight ahead. Stop in the center of the room.

src: exit bedroom immediately right unfinished room stand in center double windows wait there
tgt: Exit the bedroom and immediately turn right. Enter the unfinished room and stand in the center facing the double windows. Wait there.

src: past bed chair right into doorway in middle of room
tgt: Go past bed and chair to doorway. Turn right into doorway. Stop in the middle of the room.

src: stairs left straight until set of stairs then right wait at top of stairs
tgt: Facing the stairs turn to the left and go straight until you get to another set of stairs. Then turn right and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk by bannister then right at top of stairs
tgt: walk by bannister then turn right, stop at top of stairs.

src: down hallway towards stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk down the hallway towards the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: down stairs forward down stairs toward door just before doorway
tgt: Walk down the stairs and walk forward. Walk down the stairs toward the door. Stop just before the doorway.

src: straight hallway stop before door ahead
tgt: Go straight down the hallway and stop before entering the door straight ahead.

src: walk forward at doorway
tgt: Walk forward, stop at the doorway.

src: walk into cathedral walk through footpath of single pew on right towards center of room up center of cathedral front of altar
tgt: Walk straight into the cathedral. Walk through the footpath of the single pew on your right, moving towards the center of the room.  Walk up the center of the cathedral and stop when you get to the front of the altar.

src: turn slight right over chair at next row of pews slight into center of main room right up stairs main alter cross
tgt: turn slight right and walk over chair, at next row of pews turn slight left into center of main room, turn right  and walk up 2 stairs, stop facing main alter and cross.

src: in center of main alter
tgt: Go and stand in the center of the main alter.

src: exit bedroom turn towards stairs wait in doorway theater
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn towards the stairs. Wait in the doorway to the theater.

src: exit bedroom right theater on left wait there
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right. Enter the theater on the left and wait there.

src: exit room door on left right then into room wait near entrance
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the left. Turn right and then turn left into the room. Wait near the entrance.

src: away from purple chairs into house slight left at red cabinet chairs on right in front of refrigerator
tgt: walk away from the purple chairs and into the house, take a slight left at the red cabinet, there will be two chairs on your right and stop in front of the refrigerator.

src: turn building through glass door walk counter sink into kitchen stop wait about meter half in front of refrigerator
tgt: Turn around and enter the building through the glass door. Walk passed the counter and sink and into the kitchen. Stop and wait about a meter and a half in front of the refrigerator.

src: walk past large cacti into house past triangular red clock into kitchen area
tgt: Walk past the large cacti and into the house and proceed past the triangular red clock into the kitchen area.

src: down stairs in spiral staircase at bottom of stairs straight forward past wooden art sculpture on right at end of blue rug
tgt: Walk down the remaining stairs in the spiral staircase.  At the bottom of the stairs, walk straight forward, past the wooden art sculpture on your right.  Stop when you are standing at the end of the blue rug.

src: stairs next level forward rug next dining table once on rug
tgt: Go down the stairs to the next level. Walk forward to the rug next to the dining table. Stop once you step on the rug.

src: stairs forward dinning room rug
tgt: Go down the stairs and walk forward to the dinning room rug.

src: exit bathroom right door next stairs next walk up small set of stairs turn straight into living room
tgt: Exit the bathroom, turn right, and enter the door next to the stairs. Next walk up a small set of stairs, and turn left.  Walk straight, and turn left into the living room.

src: walk out of bathroom right up steps turn down steps by fireplace
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right. Walk up the steps and turn left. Walk down the steps and stop by the fireplace.

src: through door right stairs into left doorway white couches stop
tgt: Go through the door, and turn right to go up the stairs. Turn into the left doorway and go left to the white couches and stop.

src: patio through door on right through bedroom into bathroom in front of toilet
tgt: Leave the patio through the door on the right. Walk through the bedroom, into the bathroom. Stop in front of the toilet.

src: inside house past bed into bathroom on left turn wait near toilet
tgt: Go inside the house. Walk past the bed and go into the bathroom on the left. Turn left and wait near the toilet.

src: inside through bedroom through doorway right of bed into bathroom step into toilet room doorway stop
tgt: Go inside, go through the bedroom and go through the doorway to the right of the bed, go into the bathroom and step into the toilet room doorway and stop.

src: down stairs then across floor then first set of stairs on other side
tgt: walk down the stairs and then across the floor.  Then proceed up the first set of stairs on the other side.

src: downstairs across lobby wait near bottom of second stairs
tgt: Go downstairs, across the lobby and wait near the bottom of the second stairs.

src: down stairs then across foyer stand on 2nd step wait there
tgt: Walk down the stairs, then across the foyer and stand on the 2nd step.  Wait there.

src: finish stairs walk straight until large room with white beige right steps then
tgt: Finish going down the stairs and walk straight until you get to a large room with white beige. Turn right and go down six steps then stop.

src: down stairs straight into next room right across room through door on left wait there
tgt: Walk down the stairs and keep going straight into the next room. Turn right and walk across the room. Go through the door on the left and wait there.

src: rest of stairs toward fireplace right at bottom of next set of steps right again steps wait on stairs in hallway
tgt: Go down the rest of the stairs and toward the fireplace. Turn right at the bottom of the next set of steps and turn right again and go down five steps and wait on the stairs that are in a hallway.

src: stairs stairs stairs light switches stairs
tgt: Go to the stairs. Go down three stairs. Go down five stairs. Go to the four light switches. Go down two stairs.

src: down stairs behind glass door turn steps on left
tgt: Walk down the stairs behind the glass door, turn left, and walk down two steps on the left.

src: turn stairs at bottom turn set of stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and go down the stairs. At the bottom turn left and go down another set of stairs. Stop at the bottom of these stairs.

src: turn slightly right staircase top of stairs past closed door on right immediately left again hallway around staircase arched passageway immediately right into short hallway stop bathroom straight ahead of bedroom with sofa left bedroom right here
tgt: Turn slightly right to walk up the staircase. When you get to the top of the stairs turn left to walk past the closed door on your right. You will have to immediately turn left again to follow the hallway around the staircase. Take the arched passageway that is immediately to your right to walk into a short hallway and stop. There should be a bathroom straight ahead of you, a bedroom with a sofa to the left and a smaller bedroom to the right. Stop here.

src: stairs onto landing at top of stairs left then right into first doorway into small hallway in middle of hallway outside of bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairs, and onto the landing. At the top of the stairs take a left, then a right into the first doorway into a small hallway. Stop in the middle of the hallway outside of the bathroom.

src: travel up stairs once at top turn through second door way wait
tgt: Travel up the stairs. Once at the top turn left and go through the second door way and wait.

src: pass meters ulity room into main area towards second door on left face into room wait
tgt: Pass the meters, exit the ulity room, into the main area, and go towards the second door on the left.  Face into this room and wait.

src: walk out of pump room main hall slight empty room left room right in window
tgt: walk out of the pump room to the main hall. Turn slight left to the empty room, turn more left and enter the room. Stop right when you get in it and face the window.

src: forward room turn second door from left by door
tgt: Go forward and exit the room, turn left and enter the second door from the left, stop by the door.

src: once in library right through door room with glasses now right area wait in doorway
tgt: Once you are in the library make a right and go through the door to the room with the glasses. Now make a right to leave the area and wait in the doorway.

src: turn so that open doorway walk towards open white doors through doors hall until open doorway on right ninety degrees until open doorway walk through open doorway in large room large table in front of
tgt: Turn around so that you are facing the open doorway.  Walk towards the two open white doors.  Walk through the doors.  Proceed down the hall until you reach an open doorway on your right.  Stop and turn ninety degrees until you are facing the open doorway.  Walk through the open doorway and stop.  You are in a large room, and there should be a large table in front of you.

src: away from piano through double doors with bookshelf on left right in doorway
tgt: walk away from piano through double doors with bookshelf on left, turn right and stop in doorway.

src: head in through office then left doorway seating area by chair
tgt: Head in and through the office, then use the left doorway to enter the seating area. Stop and wait by the nearest chair.

src: walk table chairs into next room stop
tgt: Walk left pas the table and chairs and into the next room and stop.

src: turn formal study past table turn room wait near t
tgt: Turn left and enter the formal study. Walk past the table, turn left and enter the room.  Wait near t he chair.

src: turn exit into room with large table once out left side into area door on far left once tun left walk through doorway once room with stairs
tgt: Turn around and exit into the room with the large table. Once out, walk to the left side into the sitting area and enter the door on the far left. Once you exit, tun left and walk through the doorway. Stop once you reach the room with the stairs.

src: head through dining room into door nearest fireplace then in landing wait near stairs
tgt: Head out through the dining room and into the door nearest the fireplace, then turn left. Stop in the landing and wait near the stairs.

src: turn across room hallway turn exit onto stairway landing wait there
tgt: Turn around, go left across the room, enter the hallway and turn left, exit onto the stairway landing and wait there.

src: exit patio from large sliding doors towards pool area at base of stairs right
tgt: Exit to the patio from the large sliding doors and continue going towards the pool area. Stop at the base of the stairs to the right.

src: exit home through sliding doors then through archway right walk stair on right there next railing
tgt: Exit the home through the sliding doors, then walk through the archway and turn right. Walk to the stair landing on the right and wait there next to the railing.

src: turn through large entryway couch through arches by stairs on right
tgt: Turn around and go through the large entryway. Go to the couch and continue through the arches. Stop by the stairs on the right.

src: walk along glass wall turn walk straight through door with exit sign above next first desk on right
tgt: Walk to exit along glass wall. Turn left and walk straight through door with exit sign above it. Stop next to first desk on right.

src: exit room door on right then exit sign straight into office wait near first desk
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the right then turn left. Pass the exit sign and continue straight to go into that office. Wait near the first desk.

src: walk between tables glass with glass on right wooden door on right turn under exit sign past double wooden doors into room with desks in doorway
tgt: Walk between the tables and the glass windows, with the glass windows on your right. Exit the wooden door on your right. Turn left, walking under the exit sign, past the double wooden doors, and into a room with two desks. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn around forward hallway way other end slight right hallway in hallway beside small refrigerator
tgt: Turn around and walk forward down the hallway all the way to the other end and make a slight right to keep following the hallway. Stop in the hallway beside the small refrigerator.

src: long hall past living room kitchen hall before room at end
tgt: Go down the long hall past the living room and kitchen. Continue down the hall and stop before you enter the room at the end.

src: straight hallway until small wine fridge on right there
tgt: Go straight down the hallway until you get to a small wine fridge on the right. Wait there.

src: stairs turn left far end of glass table chairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Go to the far end of the glass table and chairs.

src: down staircase right at bottom right again past table after dining table talk step right

tgt: With the couch on your right walk forward through the living room and through the door out onto the patio stopping just outside of the door.

src: turn outside
tgt: Turn left, walk outside.

tgt: Walk towards the computer and proceed to exit the room by the doorway.

src: turn right around table chairs through double doors walk right past current photo on wall in hallway before rug wait
tgt: Turn to the right and walk around the table and chairs.  go through the double doors.  Walk to the right and go past the "Current" photo on the wall.  You're in a hallway.  Stop before you get to the rug. Wait.

tgt: Go downstairs, go toward the big black table and turn right before the table and go into the white doorway to the left of the blue-green pot and stop.

tgt: Walk down the stairs and take a left. Walk down the hall and take a left into the living room. Stop next to the gray chaise lounger nest to the piano.

tgt: Turn to the left and go down the stairs.  When you get to the bottom of the stairs, turn left and walk down a hallway.  Turn to the left immediately and walk towards the grand piano.  And stop there, wait.

tgt: Walk down stairs, turn left at the bottom of the  stairs, go straight, turn left into the living room area, walk to wards the piano and stop beside the piano.

tgt: Head towards the two ivory tusks at the opposite side of the room, then exit the room through the narrow corridor to the left. Stop once you've exited the corridor and have entered the next room.

tgt: With your back faced towards the art easel, walk straight forward past the wooden box towards the two large white tusks. Directly to the left of those tusks is an open door to which you turn towards and your destination is just a few feet beyond that.

tgt: Go to the statue on a pedestal. Go through the corner passageway.

tgt: With the pictures on your left go straight down the hall into the bedroom and walk past the bed taking a right onto the patio and stopping in the doorway just outside on the patio.

src: doorway forward metre chair painting plastic chair water faucet
tgt: Go to the doorway. Go forward 1 metre. Go to the chair. Go to the painting. Go to the plastic chair. Go to the water faucet.

tgt: Turn left and go down the hall.  Go past the foot of the bed and veer left.  Go out of the door way and onto the terrace.  Stop when you finally get there and wait.

tgt: Go to the far end of the room and wait in the doorway to the dining room.

tgt: Walk past the fixtures and table and chairs. Turn right past the bathtub. Stop just inside the doorway.

tgt: Go straight ahead through the doorway, and then turn to the left.  Go through the doorway and into the office.  Stop just behind the desk chair.

tgt: go through door by chair, turn left, stop by chair.

Continue walking along the same wall into the first open door, which leads to a storage room with wooden shelves.

src: turn right wait in front of fire place on right
tgt: Turn right and wait in front of the fire place on the right.

Keeping the windows to your left, walk the length of the rooms until you enter a room with chairs around a round table with a horse statue on it.  Turn right into the area with the yellow walls and stop on the carpet in front of the bottles.

Before you enter the area with the long table turn right to move between the marble vase and the faucet display. You should be moving through an arched passageway towards a gilt framed mirror. In the hallway that is to the left of the gilt mirror there is a closed door. The door is at the beginning of the hallway and is on the right side of the hallway. Move to stand directly in front of this door and stop.

tgt: Enter house from garage, go up stairs to the slight right. At top of stairst turn slight right in hall enter bedroom. Stop in front of bed.

src: garage house stairs right bedroom on left of double doors in bedroom
tgt: Leave the garage and enter the house. Go up the stairs and take a right. Enter the bedroom on the left of the double doors. Stop in the bedroom.

src: exit bathroom walk towards stairs up on third stair
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk towards the stairs.  Walk up and stop on the third stair.

src: leave bathroom right straight down hall step on stairs stairwell
tgt: leave bathroom, turn right and walk straight down hall to stairs, turn left and take one step, stop on stairs facing up stairwell.

src: forward out of bathroom into hallway in hallway right past living room once past living room left at stairs stairs on third step from bottom
tgt: Walk forward out of the bathroom into the hallway. In the hallway take a right and walk past the living room. Once past the living room take a left at the stairs. Go up the stairs and stop on the third step from the bottom.

src: turn around right of pool onto sidewalk walk door on left stop
tgt: Turn around and walk to the right of the pool onto the sidewalk. Walk to the door on the left and stop.

src: face hot tub right past hot tub patch slightly on concrete walkway straight stop next last plan on left
tgt: face hot tub, turn right, walk past hot tub, follow patch slightly to left and straight, turn left on concrete walkway, continue straight and stop next to last plan on left.

src: walk along path beside hot tub.go between pillars in front of door inside
tgt: Walk along the path beside the hot tub.Go between 4 pillars, and stop in front of the door to the inside.

src: turn towards door out door right
tgt: Turn around and go towards the door. Walk out the door and look to your right and stop.

src: walk toward entranceway of room out of room into next
tgt: Walk toward the entranceway of the room.  Step out of the room and into the next.

src: office area wait
tgt: Leave the office area and wait.

src: steps on left turn stairs right right again near vanity table with fancy chair
tgt: Go up the three steps on the left. Turn left and go down the stairs. Turn right. Turn right again and wait near the vanity table with the fancy chair.

src: exit room by marble stairs then down carpeted stairs right at bottom of stairs down hallway right at first doorway on side wait just inside bathroom
tgt: Exit the room by walking up the marble stairs, then turn left and walk down the carpeted stairs. Turn right at the bottom of the stairs and walk down the hallway. Turn right at the first doorway on that side and wait just inside the bathroom.

src: up small set of granite stairs at top turn hard carpeted set of stairs hard right at bottom of stairs walk straight until room on right room wait by desk
tgt: Walk up small set of granite stairs.  At the top turn hard left to go down the carpeted set of stairs.  Turn hard right at bottom of stairs. Walk straight until you reach a room on the right. Enter the room, and wait by desk.

src: turn towards on right large hall turn towards short stairs short staircase stop at top between set of stairs
tgt: turn left and walk towards opening on the right. Enter large hall. turn left towards short stairs. Go up short staircase and stop at the top between another set of stairs.

src: walk through living room area chairs through open double doors into entry room with red carpet up stairwells
tgt: Walk through the living room area passed the chairs. Walk through the open double doors and into the entry room with red carpet. Walk up to the stairwells.

src: couch round table out door on right side of room up stairs left on landing between winding staircases
tgt: Follow the couch round the table and out the door on the right side of the room. Walk up the stairs to the left and hold on the landing between the winding staircases.

src: room with barber chain in feet into room with long table right feet end point of long table on left at end of long table turn open door with glass windows on top half with ventilation grate directly in front of door jam approximately feet entrance of open door just outside entrance into hallway open door with bed facing
tgt: leave the room with the barber chain in it and walk 5 feet into room with long table. turn right and walk 20 feet to the end point of the long table which should be on your left. at the end of the long table turn left to face an open door with glass windows on the top half and with a ventilation grate directly in front of door jam. Walk approximately 8 feet to the entrance of the open door and stop just outside the entrance to peer into a hallway which opens to another open door with a bed facing you.

src: turn around into dining room right left after table wait in doorway
tgt: Turn around and walk into the dining room. Take a right. Take a left after the table and wait in the doorway.

src: walk into dining room right past long table turn before round table walk open door glass panes in doorway
tgt: Walk into the dining room and turn right.  Walk past the long table and turn left before you reach the smaller round table.  Walk to the open door that has the four glass panes, and stand in the doorway.

src: walk out of bathroom head under arch doorway left as soon as through double doors at top of stairs
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom, head under the arch doorway. Take a left as soon as you can and walk through the double doors and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: exit hot tub room on left turn through double glass doors.stop in circular room with stairs
tgt: Exit hot tub room to archway on the left. Turn left and go through double glass doors.Stop in circular room with stairs leading down.

src: away from bathtub hallway turn at long white glass table walk through double glass doors stop
tgt: walk away from the bathtub, straight down the hallway and turn left at the long white glass table. Walk through the double glass doors and stop.

src: walk toward end of hall lockers sink seating area with stools turn hall just before area hall until just inside of first room on right with white tables black chairs
tgt: Walk toward the end of the hall where there are lockers, a sink, and a seating area with stools. Turn left down the hall just before reaching that area. Continue down this hall until it turns left. Stand just inside of the first room on the right, with 3 white tables having 4 black chairs each.

src: down hall turn by round pillar walk end of hall turn just before double doors by desk
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn left by the round pillar. Walk to the end of the hall and turn left just before the double doors and stop by the desk.

src: head corridor towards exit signs turn in front of break room hall step into conference left of exit sign
tgt: Head down the corridor towards the two exit signs. turn left in front of the break room and go down the hall and step into the conference to the left of the exit sign.

src: walk forward past zebra print on right right into opening after jaguar print past display on left into bedroom
tgt: Walk forward past the zebra print on your right and turn right into the opening after the jaguar print. Continue past the display on your left and turn left into the bedroom.

src: down hall right in hall straight bedroom on far left next door
tgt: Walk down the hall, and take a right. In the hall go straight and enter the bedroom on the far left. Stop next to the door.

src: turn right enter into bedroom on left wait there
tgt: Turn around and take a right. Enter into the bedroom on the left and wait there.

src: exit bathroom right bedroom stairs turn stairs wait in doorway living room
tgt: Exit the bathroom, turn right, exit the bedroom, go up the stairs, turn left, go up the stairs, wait in the doorway to the living room.

src: exit bathroom right small flight of stairs turn small set of stairs step into doorway wait
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Go up the small flight of stairs. Turn left and go up one more small set of stairs. Step into the doorway and wait.

src: turn out of bathroom through door right stairs then stairs right before into room there den/living room
tgt: Turn around, go out of the bathroom through the door, and turn right.  Go up the stairs.  Then turn left and go up some more stairs.  Right before you go into the room, you'll stop there.  This appears to be a den/living room.

src: exit bedroom head straight hallway second door on left in bathroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom and head straight down the hallway. Enter the second door on the left and stop in the bathroom.

src: turn bed hall left bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Turn around and go passed the bed and go down the hall. Turn to your left and enter the bathroom. Stop in front of the sink.

src: walk around right of bed straight through door turn in second door bathroom stop
tgt: Walk around the right of the bed, and go straight through the door. Turn left in the second door to the bathroom and stop.

src: away from fireplace around couches through doorway on right hallway doorway on right into bedroom past foot of bed through doorway on left bathroom stop
tgt: walk away from the fireplace, around the couches and through the doorway on the right. continue down the hallway, there will be a doorway on your right, walk into the bedroom, past the foot of the bed and through the doorway on the left, enter the bathroom and stop.

src: walk across living room way right into bedroom walk across bedroom enter bathroom in front of bathtub
tgt: Walk across living room to entry way, turn right into bedroom. Walk across bedroom and enter bathroom, stop in front of the bathtub.

src: walk past window seat through archway on right first bedroom on right wait in en suite bathroom
tgt: Walk past the window seat through the archway on the right. Enter the first bedroom on the right and wait in the en suite bathroom.

src: walk out of restroom through door walk towards foot of bed move left out of bedroom door down hallway first door on left right in first door on right inside bathroom
tgt: Walk out of the restroom through the door. Walk towards the foot of the bed. Move to the left and out of the bedroom door. Move down the hallway and take the first door on the left. Turn right in the first door on the right. Stop inside the bathroom.

src: walk from bathroom through bedroom into hall turn into bathroom on right at blue vase
tgt: Walk from bathroom through bedroom and into hall. Turn left and walk into bathroom on the right. Stop at blue vase.

src: exit bathroom bedroom.turn bedroom door on left turn right into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Exit the bathroom to the bedroom.Turn left and go out the bedroom using the door on the left. Turn left. Turn right into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: exit bedroom dining table wooden dining table in next room
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Go to the dining table Go to the wooden dining table in the next room.

src: exit bedroom turn then right just past kitchen counter in dining room wait near painting
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left, then turn right just past the kitchen counter. Stop in the dining room and wait near the painting.

src: exit room turn past bar with chairs/stools.turn right straight toward table chairs wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go past the bar with the chairs/stools.Turn right and go straight toward the table and chairs and wait there.

src: forward into large room turn past plywood cabinet walk past desks turn in front of hammock
tgt: walk forward into the large room. Turn left and walk past the plywood cabinet. Walk straight past the desks. Turn left and stop in front of the hammock.

src: walk end of hall turn left across room left turn left around red carpet with green chairs
tgt: Walk to the end of the hall and turn left. Keep walking across the room staying the the left and turn left and stay around a red carpet with green chairs.

src: walk towards table turn in front of table straight past desk turn near hammock
tgt: Walk towards the table, turn left in front of the table, go straight, walk past the desk, turn left and stop near the hammock.

src: face columns walk between columns right down hall walk thru breakfast nook between columns stop
tgt: Face the two columns.  Walk between the columns, turn right and walk down the hall.  Walk thru the breakfast nook, between the two columns and stop.

src: walk past grand piano walk past chairs table wait near couches
tgt: Walk straight past the grand piano. Walk past the chairs and table and wait near the couches.

src: down hallway on right of piano straight tv room behind couch with pillars behind
tgt: Walk down the hallway on the right of the piano. Go straight, and enter the TV room. Stop behind the couch with the pillars behind you.

src: door plant rocks pool treadmill
tgt: Go to the door. Go to the plant. Go to the rocks. Go to the pool. Go to the treadmill.

src: turn room hard right walk towards treadmills wait by first treadmill
tgt: Turn left and exit the room. Turn hard right and walk towards the treadmills. Wait by the first treadmill.

src: walk around bed exit through door on left right past pool wait by treadmill
tgt: Walk around the bed and exit through the door on the left. Turn right and walk past the pool. Wait by the treadmill.

src: walk on brick past back of couch through doorway onto hardwood right before rug
tgt: walk straight on the brick past the back of the couch, through the doorway onto hardwood, turn right and stop before the rug.

src: down living room living room sitting room through first right after on wood before on carpet in front of rug
tgt: Walk down the living room passing the living room. Enter the sitting room through the first right after you are on the wood. Stop before you are on the carpet in front of the rug.

src: doorway past lamps room with stairs right in room with blue couch stand at edge of rug
tgt: Go to the doorway past the two lamps. Enter the room with the stairs and turn right. Go in to the room with the blue couch and stand at the edge of the rug.

src: on balcony right into bedroom between bed couch turn right into bathroom toilet room there wait
tgt: on the balcony, turn right and go into the bedroom, walking between the bed and couch.  Turn to the right and walk into the bathroom.  Go to the toilet room and stand there and wait.

src: walk into bedroom from balcony walk across bedroom bathroom by first door on right doorways close doorway for bathroom in darker wall inside bathroom left in front of toilet
tgt: Walk into the bedroom from the balcony.  Walk across the bedroom.  Enter the bathroom by the first door on your right.  There are two doorways close to one another.  The doorway for the bathroom is in the darker painted wall.  Inside the bathroom, make a left and stop in front of the toilet.

src: check on bathroom in bedroom as soon as through door off porch
tgt: Go check on the bathroom that is in the bedroom as soon as you walk through the door off the porch.

src: stairs turn left kitchen table doorway into doorway on tight stop near couches
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Go passed the kitchen table and enter the doorway. Go into the doorway on the tight and stop near the couches.

src: down stairs into kitchen through door on left kitchen table into right entryway once carpet
tgt: Walk down the stairs and turn left into the kitchen. Go through the door on the left passed the kitchen table and go into the right entryway. Stop once you reach the carpet.

src: down stairs turn at first doorway through kitchen table through doorway into hallway right into living room stop
tgt: keep going down the stairs, turn left at the first doorway through the kitchen pass the table, through the doorway into the hallway, take a right into the living room and stop.

src: exit bedroom walk down hallway past first door on right until second door on right there
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Walk straight down the hallway past the first door on your right. Continue walking until you reach the second door on your right. Stop and wait there.

src: turn right through door through hallway through door frame in same direction then at door frame of bedroom
tgt: Turn right and walk through door, continue straight through hallway and through door frame, and continue in same direction, then stop at the door frame of bedroom.

src: down hallway passing by stairwell bathroom walk through open door at end of hallway
tgt: Walk down the hallway passing by the stairwell and bathroom. Walk through the open door at the end of the hallway.

src: walk from bedroom hallway through double doors next bed
tgt: Walk from bedroom to hallway, through double doors to outside. Stop next to bed.

src: exit room walk towards striped stool in hallway room left of stool walk foot of bed wait here
tgt: Exit the room and walk towards the striped stool in hallway.  Enter the room to the left of the stool.  Walk to foot of bed.  Wait here.

src: exit bedroom head outside wait on area rug at front of bed
tgt: Exit the bedroom and head outside.  Wait on the area rug at the front of the bed.

src: exit bathroom turn left through door ahead into room with quilts on display room through door on far left empty room there
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn left. Go through the door ahead and into the room with quilts on display. Exit the room through the door on the far left. Enter the empty room. Stop there.

src: exit bathroom door right of sink turn in hallway forward next room room left of large glass center piece wait here
tgt: Exit bathroom door to the right of the sink.   Turn left in the hallway, and walk forward to enter the next room.  Enter the room to the left of the large glass center piece.  Wait here.

src: bathroom left far left main room once in room
tgt: Leave the bathroom, and go left. Take the far left and enter the main room. Stop once you are in the this room.

src: walk past dining room bench turn chair right in front of other chair right up small flight of stairs under doorway straight ahead
tgt: walk past the dining room bench, turn left and pass the chair, and turn right to walk in front of the other chair, turn right and walk up the small flight of stairs and stop under the doorway straight ahead.

src: walk with pillows degrees first stairs wait in doorway room with chairs fireplace
tgt: Walk to couch with pillows. Turn 180 degrees and go up first stairs. Wait in doorway to room with chairs and fireplace.

src: exit alcove up first flight of stairs inside doorway room
tgt: Exit the alcove and walk up the first flight of stairs. Stop inside the doorway to the sitting room.

src: exit bathroom through door on right downstairs exit through doors left
tgt: exit bathroom, walk through door on right, go downstairs, exit through doors to left.

src: walk into bedroom area walk bed glass door into next room walk towards couches in room down set of stairs towards couches towards open door
tgt: Walk into the bedroom area. Walk passed the bed to the glass door into the next room. Walk towards the couches in the room and walk down the set of stairs. Continue walking towards the passed the couches towards the open door to outside.

src: right through doorway walk past red chair outside door wait before doorway
tgt: You will go to the right and through a doorway.  Walk past the red chair.  You will see an outside door.  Wait before you get to the doorway.

src: walk forward door enter inside house at door mat
tgt: Walk forward towards the door, and enter inside the house. Stop at the door mat.

src: turn so that steps behind straight through open door on doormat just outside interior door
tgt: Turn around so that the 4 steps are behind you and proceed straight through the open door. Stop on the doormat just outside the interior door.

src: turn through screen door left of stairs doorway on left stop
tgt: Turn around and go through the screen door to the left of the stairs. Go to the doorway on the left and stop.

src: along patio left of black pillars then through last second last pillar top of stairs ahead on white tile before staircase
tgt: Go along the patio to the left of the black pillars and then through the last and second to last pillar, go to the top of the stairs straight ahead and stop on the white tile before the staircase.

src: straight table chairs on right straight wait at top of stairs on left
tgt: Go straight and pass the table and chairs on the right. Walk straight and wait at the top of the stairs on the left.

src: stand so indoor area left straight patio past table chairs at top of stairs at end
tgt: Stand so the indoor area is to your left and walk straight down the patio, past the table and chairs.  Stop at the top of the stairs going down at the end.

src: bedroom walk through area into bedroom directly across from room in walk past bed tub in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and walk through the sitting area into the bedroom directly across from the room you start in.  Walk past the bed and the tub and stop in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: room walk through living room walk straight across bedroom on other side of room walk past bed bathroom on left in doorway bathroom
tgt: Leave the room and walk through the living room. Walk straight across to the bedroom on the other side of the room. Walk past the bed and enter the bathroom on the left. Stop in the doorway to the bathroom.

src: walk out of bedroom in front of couch walk past couch chair into next bedroom turn in front of bed walk past tub in doorway
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and in front of the couch. Walk past the couch and chair into the next bedroom. Turn left and walk in front of the bed. Walk past the tub and stop in the doorway.

src: walk forward past couch second door from left entry way in doorway entryway
tgt: Walk forward past the couch. Enter the second door from the left which is the entry way. Stop in the doorway to the entryway.

src: turn at painting right forward past guitar through hallway entrance in front of brown wooden door
tgt: Turn left and look at the painting. Turn right and move forward past the guitar and keep going through the hallway entrance to wait in front of the brown wooden door.

src: past stairs guitar into middle doorway stand in doorway empty room with door at other end
tgt: Go past the stairs, and a guitar and go into the middle doorway.  Stand in the doorway facing an empty room with a door at the other end.

src: stairs way wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go to the stairs and go all the way down. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: face stairway down wait at bottom of steps
tgt: Face the stairway and walk down.  Wait at bottom of steps.

src: bottom of staircase stop
tgt: Go to the bottom of the staircase and stop.

src: walk through hallway slight left directly by left into bathroom then
tgt: Walk through the hallway and turn a slight left followed directly by another left and into the bathroom then stop.

src: turn right towards chair in corner of hallway once chair turn end pictures tun once bathroom
tgt: Turn right and walk towards the chair in the corner of the hallway. Once you reach the chair, turn left and walk to the end where there are two pictures hanging. Tun left and stop once you enter the bathroom.

src: exit room walk straight until chair turn hallway until picture frames on wall turn into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Exit the room and walk straight until you get to a chair. Turn left and go down the hallway until you get to two picture frames on the wall. Turn left and go into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: turn hallway wait under exit sign
tgt: Turn left. go down the hallway and wait under the exit sign.

src: with office chair behind right down hallway once underneath exit sign
tgt: With the office chair behind you, turn right and walk down the hallway.  Stop once you are underneath the "exit" sign.

src: walk end of hallway stand end in middle of hallways
tgt: Walk to the end of the hallway. Stand and the end, in the middle of the two hallways.

src: down hallway with pictures on right right after through open door frame
tgt: Walk down the hallway, with the pictures on the right. Stop right after you pass through the open door frame.

src: walk past painting of einstein into corridor straight until bedroom door wait here
tgt: Walk straight past the painting of Einstein into the corridor.  Continue straight until you reach the bedroom door.  Wait here.

src: down hall just inside bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hall and stop just inside the bedroom.

src: exit room right right through first doorway wait near shelves
tgt: Exit the room and make a right, make a right through the first doorway and wait near the shelves.

src: laundry room right hall first right into bedroom at foot of bed
tgt: Leave the laundry room and take a right. Go down the hall and take the first right into a bedroom. Stop at the foot of the bed.

src: exit laundry room right past double window on left past covered cord into wall on right right opposite glass doors bedroom wait at built-in shelves
tgt: Exit the laundry room, and make a right. Walk past the double window on the left. Walk past the covered cord plugged into the wall on the right. Make a right opposite the sliding glass doors. Enter the bedroom, and wait at the built-in shelves.

src: slight right around purple chair then slight left other side of room -left of glass wall forwards toward red chair right at window wall outside straight hot tub stop
tgt: Go slight right around purple chair. then go slight left to the other side of the room -left of the glass wall go forwards toward the red chair. turn right at the window wall and go outside. Walk straight to the hot tub and stop.

src: enter bedroom with large glass wall walk past bed on left through doorway into hallway toward open glass doors on right out of building turn along pathway with glass wall on right wait by splash pool ahead with glass wall cactus right
tgt: Enter the bedroom with the large glass wall. Walk past the bed on the left and go through the doorway into a hallway. Walk toward the open glass doors on the right. Walk out of the building and turn left. Walk along the pathway with a glass wall on the right. Wait by the splash pool ahead, with the glass wall and a cactus to the right.

src: walk toward glass outside turn past bed walk through door straight outside through door on right in front of hot tub
tgt: Walk toward the glass windows looking outside. Turn left and walk past the bed. Walk through the door. Continue straight and go outside through the door on your right. Stop in front of the hot tub.

src: hallway t then at first hall then right into room with long tables black chairs
tgt: Walk down hallway to the T then turn left, and left at first opening hall and then turn right into room with long tables and black chairs.

src: walk forward then hallway once clear glass wall on right without black at top hallway forward first door right
tgt: Walk forward and then turn left to walk down the hallway. Once you reach the clear glass wall on your right without black at the top, turn left and enter the hallway. Walk forward and enter the first door to your right and stop.

src: exit door turn forward at very first visible corner forward right towards very first door conference room enter inside door there
tgt: Exit out the door, and turn left. Walk forward and turn left at the very first visible corner. Walk forward, and turn right towards the very first door leading to the conference room. Enter inside the door and stop there.

src: up stairs right pass door right
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Take a right pass the door. Take another right.

src: up stairs right wait in doorway of area on right
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn right. Wait in the doorway of the living area on the right.

src: stairs then right then right there
tgt: Go up the stairs then turn right and then turn right and wait there.

src: turn approximately degrees toward right bedroom slightly left through hallway towards common area right under archway by area
tgt: Turn approximately 90 degrees toward the right. Exit the bedroom. Move slightly to the left. Walk through the hallway towards the common area. Turn right. Wait under the archway by the dining area.

src: walk past foot of bed on right bedroom through door in front of dogleg right ninety degree turn right so just left of circular rug in front of door outside
tgt: Walk past the foot of the bed on your right and exit the bedroom through the door in front of you. Take a dogleg to the right and continue walking. When you can take a ninety degree turn to the right, do so and stop just to the left of the circular rug in front of the door leading outside.

src: pass by television exit through doorway straight hallway past light switch on wall until path on right right forward until kitchen table on left near kitchen table
tgt: Pass by the television and exit through the doorway, continue straight down the hallway past the light switch on the wall until you reach a path on the right, turn right and move forward until you see a kitchen table on your left, stand near the kitchen table.

src: enter family room left turn in back of couch past grand piano exit building stop before rug in front of couches
tgt: Enter the family room and take a left turn in back of the couch. Go past the grand piano and exit the building. Stop before reaching the rug in front of the two couches.

src: turn left in piano room through open glass door until outside
tgt: Turn around and take a left in the piano room. Go through the open glass door until you are outside.

src: behind grey couch into archway then piano middle set of glass doors step outside then
tgt: Go behind the grey couch, turn left into the archway and then proceed passed the piano, go to the middle set of glass doors, take a step outside and then stop.

src: exit bathroom cross over second door on right near door
tgt: Exit the bathroom and cross over the to the second door on your right. Stand near the door.

src: bathroom into second door right of kitchen after empty room
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go into the second door to the right of the kitchen.  Stop after entering this empty room.

src: exit bathroom right into second door on right there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and go into the second door on the right. Wait there.

src: forward between tables left right left forward through of tables forward in front of set of chairs
tgt: Move forward between the two tables to the left and right. Turn left and move forward through all of the remaining tables. Continue going forward and stop in front of the set of seven chairs.

src: forward between pair of tables chairs turn walk between sets of tables chairs turn center of room with carpet wait next upholstered chairs
tgt: walk forward between one pair of tables and chairs. Turn left and walk between three sets of tables and chairs. Turn left  and move to the center of the room with the patterned carpet and wait next to the upholstered chairs.

src: step forward then straight exit room wait at opposite chairs
tgt: two step forward then left go straight exit room and wait at the opposite to chairs.

src: walk between stone walls right at bookcase walk across room between table ping pong table wait there
tgt: Walk between the stone walls and turn right at the bookcase. Walk across the room between the table and ping pong table and wait there.

src: office room right past ping pong table wait near desk with white garbage
tgt: Enter the office room and turn right. Walk past the ping pong table and wait near the desk with the white garbage can.

src: straight tables chairs past ping pong table wait by desk with brown chairs black chair
tgt: Go straight and pass the tables and chairs. Go past the ping pong table and wait by the desk with two brown chairs and one black chair.

src: walk past coat rack walk through closed door wait at fireplace
tgt: Walk past coat rack. Walk through closed door. Wait at fireplace.

src: walk out doorway around chair in front of fireplace in front of fireplace
tgt: Walk out the doorway. Move around the chair in front of the fireplace. Stop in front of the fireplace.

src: through door with glass oval toward fireplace in front of fireplace
tgt: Go through the door with the glass oval. Go toward the fireplace and stop in front of the fireplace.

src: left into library then sit on white chair immediate left
tgt: Take a left into the library, then sit on the white chair to the immediate left.

src: walk forward dining room table turn room wait at chair by door
tgt: Walk forward to the dining room table. Turn left and enter the room. Wait at the chair by the door.

src: past table turn on second door right by light blue couch
tgt: Go past the table and turn left on the second door. Wait right by the light blue couch.

src: room doors right
tgt: leave the room and go two doors to the right.

src: bedroom right in hallway forward bedroom through second door on right in doorway bedroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right in the hallway. Walk forward and enter the bedroom through the second door on the right. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: exit bathroom right into bedroom straight into hallway right straight at stairs bedroom doorway
tgt: exit bathroom, turn right into bedroom. Walk straight into hallway. turn right  and walk straight to stairs., stop at stairs and bedroom doorway.

src: stairs then left into room right next kitchen island
tgt: Go down the stairs and then go to your left, walk into the room and turn right. Stop next to the kitchen island.

src: stairs hall on left beside counter on right
tgt: Go down the stairs. Enter the hall on the left. Wait beside the counter on the right.

src: down stairs door on left right wait by end of counter top
tgt: Walk down the stairs, and enter the door on the left.  Turn right, and wait by the end of the counter top.

src: walk across room hallway past stairs wait in doorway kitchen
tgt: Walk across the room and hallway, past the stairs and wait in the doorway to the kitchen.

src: walk across living room behind couch walk towards straight into room stop before table kitchen
tgt: walk across living room behind couch walk slight let towards stairs, continue straight into dining room, stop before table and kitchen.

src: walk end of white couch slightly right pictures on wall near entrance way turn stone wall in front of set of stairs walk towards past stairs until opening dinning room table walk into room
