src: walk past stairs in front of set of windows on by area
tgt: Walk straight past the stairs and stop in front of the set of windows on the left by the sitting area.

src: forward out of dining room past table on left through living room in front of door parallel with table o left
tgt: Walk forward out of the dining room past the table on the left. Walk through the living room. Stop in front of the door, but parallel with the table o the left.

src: bedroom hall in front of bedroom next living room wait by chair
tgt: You need to leave the bedroom and go down the hall in front of the bedroom. Next, you need to stop when you get to the living room and wait by the chair.

src: tv door light switch paintings
tgt: Go to the TV. Go to the door. Go to the light switch. Go to the paintings.

src: exit room head straight until living room then wait by couches
tgt: Exit the room and head straight until you get to the living room. Then wait by the couches.

src: walk on carpet past bed double doors wait by wine rack
tgt: Walk on carpet, past the bed, go out double doors and wait by wine rack.

src: bed through door right of closet then right next door
tgt: Go passed the bed and through the door to the right of the closet and then stop right next to the door.

src: bedroom in front of left door of wine closet
tgt: Leave the bedroom. Stop in front of the left door of the wine closet.

src: exit room straight toward couch there
tgt: Exit the room and go straight toward the couch and stop there.

src: room walk couch in front of right side of couch
tgt: Leave the room and walk to the couch. Stop in front of the right side of the couch.

src: room walk into area between guitar couch
tgt: Leave the room and walk into the bigger area.  Stop between the guitar and the couch.

src: down first flight of stairs right steps stop
tgt: Walk down the first flight of stairs and turn right. Go down 2 steps and stop.

src: stairs at first landing right
tgt: Go down the stairs, at the first landing go to the right and stop.

src: stairs first landing right steps
tgt: Go down the stairs to the first landing. Turn right and go down three more steps.

src: turn right down hallway right past water cooler once at last doorway on right
tgt: Turn right and walk down the hallway to your right past the water cooler. Stop once you are at the last doorway on the right.

src: walk through archway through locker room past water cooler on left bathroom area wait there
tgt: Walk through the archway and go through the locker room. Go past the water cooler on your left and enter the bathroom area. Wait there.

src: walk past lockers on right past water cooler on left wait in threshold bathroom on right
tgt: Walk past the lockers on the right. Walk past the water cooler on the left. Wait in the threshold to the bathroom on the right.

src: straight toward fireplace then stairs on left then
tgt: Go straight toward the fireplace then turn left and pass the stairs on your left then stop.

src: walk past bridal room office toward stone fireplace toward exit stairs wait
tgt: Walk past the bridal room and office toward the stone fireplace, and turn toward the exit and the stairs, and wait.

src: left at fireplace wait next coat room
tgt: Take a left at the fireplace. Wait next to the coat room.

src: stairs then right wait in front of double doors in hallway
tgt: Go up the stairs then turn right. Wait in front of the double doors in the hallway.

src: stairs right in front of double doors closet
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a right. Stop in front of the double doors to the closet.

src: turn stairs then right near door
tgt: Turn around and go up the stairs. Then go right and stand near the door.

src: exit room walk straight across next room wait in front of bathroom
tgt: Exit the room and walk straight across the next room. Wait in front of the bathroom.

src: turn left room across next room door across once bathroom door
tgt: Turn to your left and exit the room. Go across the next room and enter the door straight across. Stop once you enter the bathroom door.

src: salon walk past table through door across stop in doorway
tgt: Leave the salon and walk past the table. Go through the door straight across. Stop in the doorway.

src: with pool behind into house right past chairs piano into room with shelves with books alcohol
tgt: With the pool behind you, go into the house. Take a right past the chairs and to the piano. Go into the room with all the shelves with books and alcohol.

src: pool house through living room library on left once in library
tgt: Leave the pool, and enter the house. Walk through the living room, and enter the library on the left. Stop once you are in the library.

src: enter through glass door straight wait behind piano next shelves
tgt: Enter through the glass door and continue straight. Wait behind the piano next to the shelves.

src: stairs straight into kitchen there
tgt: Go down stairs, walk straight into the kitchen and stop there.

src: down stairs into room ahead wait by cabinets
tgt: Walk down the stairs and straight into the room ahead. Wait by the cabinets.

src: downstairs through hall in kitchen
tgt: go downstairs, through hall, stop in kitchen.

src: straightly with upstairs.then enter in room
tgt: Go straightly with upstairs.Then enter in to wash room.

src: walk past leather chairs towards hardwood steps up steps down hallway towards bathroom walk into bathroom just past sink
tgt: Walk past two leather chairs, towards three hardwood steps. Walk up the three steps and down the hallway towards the bathroom. Walk into the bathroom and stop just past the sink.

src: walk forward stairs into bathroom on right in front of sink
tgt: Walk forward and go up the three stairs. Go into the bathroom on the right and stop in front of the sink.

src: walk out of closet right through door on right down steps once down steps right down steps once at bottom of steps there
tgt: Walk out of the closet and turn right. Go through the door that will be on your right and walk down the steps. Once down the steps, turn right and walk down more steps. Once at the bottom of the steps, wait there.

src: exit storage room right hard right just after open grey door down stairs right on landing at built-in bench down stairs wait at landing at bottom of stairs
tgt: Exit the storage room, and make a right. Make a hard right just after the open grey door. Walk down stairs. Make right on the landing at the built-in bench. Walk down stairs. Wait at the landing at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk through door in front of once in turn right into large room right door down small set of steps at bottom right mirror on wall
tgt: Walk through the door in front of you. Once in turn right and walk into the large room. Turn right and enter the door and down the small set of steps. At the bottom, turn right and stop facing the mirror on the wall.

src: with green wall immediate left forward into hallway way end at end of hallway right bedroom
tgt: With the green painted wall to your immediate left, walk forward into the hallway all the way to the end. At the end of the hallway, turn right and enter the bedroom.

src: down long hallway towards square tapestry on wall right through open door sunset room few steps into room on carpet next bed white nightstand with clock radio on
tgt: Walk down the long hallway towards the square tapestry on the wall.  Turn right and walk through the open door that says "Sunset Room."  Take a few steps into the room and stop on the carpet that is next to the bed and the white nightstand with a clock radio on it.

src: down hallway away from door master suite through second doorway on right door sunset room stop next bed in sunset room
tgt: Walk down the hallway, heading away from the door labelled "Master Suite."  Go through the second doorway on your right.  The door will be labelled "Sunset Room."  Stop next to the bed in the Sunset Room.

src: stairs with slatted fence left forward until door on left
tgt: Go down the stairs with the slatted fence to your left and continue forward until you reach the door on your left.

src: stairs stop near first column
tgt: Go down the stairs and stop near the first column.

src: way down stairs stop
tgt: Go all the way down the stairs and stop.

src: walk past couch turn walk past counter in front of shelf
tgt: Walk past the couch and turn left. Walk left past the counter and stop in front of the shelf.

src: walk counter clockwise around couch on right side of fireplace in front of cabinet with crosses on
tgt: Walk counter clockwise around the couch and stop on the right side of the fireplace in front of a cabinet with crosses on it.

src: walk past sofa turn straight past sofa in front of living room shelf
tgt: Walk past the sofa and turn left. Walk straight past the sofa and stop in front of the living room shelf.

src: forward first door on right into door then right into second door on right forward diagonally in front of bed
tgt: Move forward to the first door on the right. Turn into the door, and then turn right into the second door on the right. Move forward diagonally to stand in front of the bed.

src: hallway with several paintings on right walk forward end of hallway right until hallway with in cabinet shelf area left open door right open door right so cabinet behind bedroom with green while bed into bedroom until foot of bed
tgt: FACING A HALLWAY WITH SEVERAL PAINTINGS ON THE RIGHT WALK FORWARD TO THE END OF THE HALLWAY, TURN RIGHT UNTIL YOU FACE ANOTHER HALLWAY WITH A  BUILT IN CABINET SHELF AREA TO THE LEFT AND AN OPEN DOOR TO THE RIGHT, WALK TO THE OPEN DOOR AND TURN RIGHT SO THE CABINET IS BEHIND YOU AND YOU ARE FACING A BEDROOM WITH A GREEN AND WHILE BED, WALK INTO THE BEDROOM UNTIL YOU REACH THE FOOT OF THE BED.

src: hallway right into hallway forward right at second door bedroom stop at foot of bed
tgt: Move down the hallway and turn right into another hallway. Move forward and turn right at the second door. Enter the bedroom and stop at the foot of the bed.

src: walk around exterior of home through tiled patio area towards backyard pool area walk between home pool along tiled patio open door home walk towards hot tub in corner of yard
tgt: Walk around the exterior of the home through the tiled patio area towards the backyard and pool area. Walk between the home and the pool along the tiled patio continue passed the open door to the home and walk towards the hot tub in the corner of the yard.

src: walk towards pool down length of on side closest building stop in front of half circle-shaped hot tub in front of circle cut outs in wall cactus on side large potted plant on other side
tgt: Walk towards the pool and walk down the length of it. on the side closest to the building.  Stop in front of the half circle-shaped hot tub in front of the two circle cut outs in the wall.  It has a cactus on one side and a large potted plant on the other side.

src: towards pool then pool right near hot tub
tgt: Go towards the pool, then passed the pool to the right, and stop near the hot tub.

src: turn next second black chair
tgt: Turn around and wait next to the second black chair.

src: workshop head black leather chair nextt chair red wicker chairs
tgt: Leave the workshop and head to the black leather chair. Stop nextt he chair and the red wicker chairs.
